PolicyTipsAge:
1. This is a casual online third-person tactical shooter, suitable for players aged 12 and older. Parental supervision is recommended for players under 18.
2. Set in a fantasy sci-fi world, this game is a work of fiction involving a series of main and side quests facilitated through conversations and interactions. Players assume the role of the Navigator, who guides the Strinovians in solving a global crisis and combating mysterious forces. The game features text-based and voice-based interaction systems, which comply with relevant laws and regulations.
3. Accounts will undergo real-name authentication. Verified minors will face the following restrictions:
- Gaming session time limits: Minors can only play from 8 PM to 9 PM on Fridays, Saturdays, Sundays, and public holidays.
- Payment restrictions: Players under 12 may not make purchases. Players aged 12-15 may spend up to CN¥50 per transaction, with a monthly limit of CN¥200. Players aged 16-17 may spend up to CN¥100 per transaction, with a monthly limit of CN¥400.
4. This game falls within the competitive arena shooting genre, which can help improve player reaction times and hand-eye coordination. Its scientific concepts, artwork, text, and actions are designed to enhance understanding of fundamental scientific principles.

4F3CFD964BDE4C1D43D53DA57D169B7F:
<Black22>1. Basic star acquisition rules will remain unchanged. The winners of a match will earn one star, losers will lose one star. String Energy Score will now also add stars.</>
<Black22>2. After each match, you will earn String Energy Score regardless of the outcome. String Energy Score = Game Points + Victory Streak Reward + Match Rating Reward + Strength Reward (where team average strength exceeds the division average). </>
<Black22>3. Star Protection Mechanic: Star Protection activates upon reaching a certain number of String Energy Score. When you have a Star Protection and lose a ranked match, a corresponding number of String Energy Score will be consumed and you won't lose a star. String Energy Score consumed by Star Protection will increase as your tier increases.</>
<Black22>4. String Energy Score Added Stars: When String Energy Score reaches the limit and you win a ranked match, some of your String Energy Score will be consumed and you will gain an extra star. The number of String Energy Score consumed will be equal to your current tier's Star Protection points.</>
<Black22>5. Match Rating Rewards: 1st place (5 points), 2nd place (4 points), 3rd place (4 points), 4th place (3 points), 5th place (3 points).</>
<Black22>6. Victory Streak Rewards: 1 win (3 points), 2 wins (8 points), 3 wins (13 points), 4 wins (18 points), 5 or more wins (23 points).</>
E00E59F046E870AB1D30DA83D70FD4F7: <Black22>The ranked mode is the most challenging mode of Strinova. Every season, players who dare to take the challenge will receive epic rewards. You have to reach Lv. 5 and own at least 5 heroes to play the ranked mode. Keep leveling up and unlocking heroes, and you can start your legendary journey.</>
1EADFF374C01182D0FC177B91446D5F1: <Black22>In ranked mode, you earn a star for each victory and lose a star for each defeat by default. After your star count is full, earning another star increases your division or rank. When you have no stars left, losing another star demotes you to the next division or rank.</>
7C625C414E3DAEFCDB768AA88331CBA7: <Black22>During each season, once you reach a certain rank, you can obtain the corresponding rewards. For details on rewards and their corresponding rank, please visit the Season Rewards page.</>
521DAE3C4098E173811A319B83BAEE77:
<Black22>Players are assigned to one of several ranked divisions, broadly indicative of a player's skill level.</>
<Black22>Division lowest to highest are: Substance, Molecule, Atom, Quark, Origin Stringification, Superstring, Strinova.</> <Black22>The Substance to the Superstring divisions are further subdivided into grades, each accompanied by a number of stars. See here for further details in the Rank Map.</>
B269A49A462DA8FC329F0ABA2D70CE3C:
<Black22>When a player reaches Strinova rank, their maximum star limit will be increased to 9,999. The system performs a check every hour, and if a player has not played any ranked matches during the previous 7 days, they will lose 1 star.</>
<Black22>The server updates the rankings of all players every hour. The top players in the rank of Strinova will be listed on the leaderboard. This information will be sent to all the players on the server.</>
1D45CF5E49018AA8F72DE38993BD6B34:
<Black22>Season Duration: Each season lasts for approximately three months.</>
<Black22>Your rank and division reset after the end of each season. After the previous season ends, everyone has a chance to start over. Your starting position in the new season will be determined by your highest rank from the previous season.</>

<Rank-Title>1. </>When you have enough String Energy Score, upon suffering a loss, a portion of your String Energy Score will be deducted to offset losing a star.
<Rank-Title>2. </>When your String Energy Score has reached the maximum limit, winning another ranked match will consume some String Energy Score to grant you an additional star.
<Rank-Title>3. </>The maximum String Energy Score limits differ for each rank, and the total String Energy Score deducted for losses or consumed for wins varies.
<Rank-Title>Bonus Scores:</>
        <Rank-Title>1. No AFK: </>3 points.
        <Rank-Title>2. Match Score Rankings: </>Earn different amounts of String Energy Score based on your score ranking within your time. <Rank-Red>First place: </>24 points. <Rank-Red>Second place: </>18 points. <Rank-Red>Third place: </>13 points. <Rank-Red>Fourth place: </>9 points. <Rank-Red>Fifth place: </>6 points.
        <Rank-Title>3. Win Streaks: </><Rank-Red>One consecutive win: </>3 points. <Rank-Red>Two consecutive wins: </>8 points. <Rank-Red>Three consecutive wins: </>13 points. <Rank-Red>Four consecutive wins: </>18 points. <Rank-Red>Five or more consecutive wins: </>23 points.
        <Rank-Title>4. Skill Compensation: </>10 points. Awarded when your rank is lower than the average rank of the enemy team by a certain degree, regardless of the outcome.
        <Rank-Title>5. Effort Compensation: </>50 points. Awarded to outstanding players in case of defeat or a draw.
2128FE554069B0F3A7F55EB9BB8722F7:
<Rank-Title>1. </>When you reach the Supernova rank, your ranked matches become point-based. At the end of every ranked game, you will either gain or lose Supernova points based on the results of the match and your performance.
<Rank-Title>2. </>When you are promoted to Supernova from Nova, your string energy score will be converted to Supernova score at a <Rank-Red>20:1</> ratio.
<Rank-Title>3. </>When your Supernova score is 0, your first loss triggers rank protection. If you suffer another loss afterward, you will be demoted to Nova I.
<Rank-Title>4. </>After achieving the Supernova rank, if you do not play ranked matches for <Rank-Red>7 consecutive days</>, you will lose 30 Supernova points, down to a minimum of 0.
<Rank-Title>5. </>After reaching Supernova score 200, if you are ranked in the top 500 on the leaderboard, you will be promoted to Singularity. However, if you drop out of the top 500, you will be demoted back to Supernova.
<Rank-Title>6. </>Players in the Supernova and Singularity ranks may only queue solo or as a duo.
4F67D88745917ED06C833AAF52B628F7:
<Rank-Title>Participation Rules:</> When you reach <Rank-Red>Lv. 5</>, you can start playing ranked matches.

<Rank-Title>Season Duration:</> Each ranked season lasts for approximately two months. At the beginning of each season, you need to play placement matches again to determine your starting rank.

<Rank-Title>Ranks:</> There are a total of nine ranks, each with different divisions and string energy point limits. 

<Rank-Title>Promotion and Demotion:</> When you reach the maximum number of stars in each division, one more victory will promote you, granting you one star (some exceptional Navigators may skip one additional division upon promotion).

After losing all your stars in a division, one more loss will trigger a demotion of divisions or ranks.

<Rank-Title>Rank Protection:</> Players in the Iron or Bronze rank will not lose any stars after losses. Players in the Gold rank will not be demoted after losing all stars in a division.
8136FED340C7D2939F2315AEFBE4C198: <White14>It seems Michele stumbled on an old classified file on 【Unexplained Incidents】 that the Sistine had been trying their best to keep hidden.</></br></br><White14>The higher the level of authority required, the more overwhelming the urge to read something without permission.</></br><White14>The files revealed a shocking story on the fatal retirement of the previous P.U.S Captain, the many ambushes of The Scissors terrorists, and the civilians whose reputations may have been tarnished thereunder...</></br><White14>A succession of names thought to provide at least part of an answer turn out only to be part of a much bigger unofficial smokescreen associated with a mysterious photo.</></br><White14>The truth is far stranger than any of those supposedly in the know have realized, a fact noted with some amusement by the multidimensional entity responsible.</>

[Event Background]
One day, you receive an anonymous urgent message from the leader of an exploration team. The frequent communication disruptions caused by the Reverstring Storm indicate that the sender must be located in the True Wilderness.
The mysterious sender requests your assistance in locating team members in the True Wilderness and helping her collect energy crystals. Although her true intentions are unknown, as a navigator, it is imperative to intervene and save lives.
[Event Duration]
August 3, 2023, 6:00 AM to August 31, 2023, 5:59 AM
[Event Rules]
1. During the event, complete quests to obtain energy points and recharge the Pyramid Device.
2. When the energy of the Pyramid Device reaches a certain level, you will receive rewards and have a chance to obtain a clue.
3. When the Pyramid Device is fully charged, you can summon the new Superstring [Meredith].
4. After summoning and unlocking [Meredith], your remaining energy points can be exchanged for items.
5. Daily quests refresh at 6:00 AM

ActivityCNYFireStory.6_StoryContext: While you watched the fireworks with Maddelena, she felt bittersweet at the fleeting scenery. You comfort her that the purpose of art is to capture beauty in eternity.
ActivityCNYFireStory.4_StoryContext: You join Lawine on the observation deck to watch the fireworks celebrations. The grand display brought out some homesickness in Lawine, making her feel small and lonely. No matter - you're willing to be a safe harbor for drifters.
ActivityCNYFireStory.2_StoryContext: The brave Michele and her partner, the Navigator, embark on an adventure together - a hidden stage that our heroes can't get enough of!
ActivityCNYFireStory.3_StoryContext: Busy with her work, Audrey has been unable to help out with the preparations. To make sure she felt included and to reward her for all her hard work, you decided to join her in the fireworks celebrations.
ActivityCNYFireStory.5_StoryContext: After your busy week helping with the celebration preparations, Kokona invites you to watch the fireworks together. The mighty sea bunny captain uses her makeshift telescope to “see into the future” - for both you and Strinova, the future is sure to get better and better!
ActivityCNYFireStory.1_StoryContext: The celebrations are approaching, and work in the Astral Sanctuary is finally coming to an end. You go to watch the fireworks together, enjoy the beautiful display side by side, and understand each other's feelings without needing to say a word.

ActivityConcertLevel.1_LevelRoleContent: “Took you long enough to get here, my savior! Good thing at least you're reliable. I'll be waiting for you in the practice room. Come over soon!”
ActivityConcertLevel.2_LevelRoleContent: “What to do... such an important task left to me... I can't handle it...!”
ActivityConcertLevel.4_LevelRoleContent: “Performing is an idol's specialty! Hehe... Don't worry, Navigator, I won't let you down!”
ActivityConcertLevel.3_LevelRoleContent: “Piano? Don't worry. Just be natural and enjoy the music!”
ActivityConcertLevel.5_LevelRoleContent: “Music brings peace to the mind. I have no objection to your invitation, Navigator. I'll be there.”

ActivityConcertStory.5_Content:
“Navigator! Wait, no... It's 'conductor' now... you're here! Let's get started!”
Kanami's face is full of enthusiasm. Gazing at the practice room mirror, she's long imagined seeing this side of herself, displaying a musical prowess that none could match.
But when she finally saw who she wanted to see, it was in the lounge at night, body covered in a conductor's coat.
“Huh? Did I mess something up? Kanami just wanted to give the Navigator a surprise... After all, Lawine and the other said as much, and even gave me such beautiful clothes...”
Kanami lowers her head, a flurry of emotions on her red face.
Surprise, self-blame, bashfulness...
“A-Are you surprised? I...”
Her face becomes redder, and she fumbles over herself even more.
“I-I'll definitely become your favorite idol!”
The girl speaks while covering her face with a sheet of music. The conductor in front of her gives a simple nod and starts turning to leave.
Feelings were conveyed, albeit with a misunderstanding.
But even so... this still counts as being bold and achieving one's goal... doesn't it?
ActivityConcertStory.6_Content:
“It's you. No need to worry. I'm not the most experienced in classical music, but I'm familiar with music theory.”
When the sunset comes, the lone shadow in the practice room finally comes to a stop.
“Not good enough again... No, I guess it can count as a success. What do you think, Navigator?”
The lone figure keeps their distance, holding their saxophone.
“...I wouldn't feel very comfortable being so close, but if you feel it will help you conduct, I won't voice any complaints.”
Lawine speaks calmly, maintaining a mysterious profile in the sunset.
A calming and nostalgic étude is played once more.
One can't help but be confident that the performance will be one that lingers in the memory.
ActivityConcertStory.3_Content:
“Bai Mo suddenly dumped this task on me. I'm really a little... uh... unconfident.”
In the practice room, Maddelena looks at me with a violin in her hand. Through her glasses, I can see a lost look on her pale and youthful face.
“I really... uhm... what if my sister sees? Eh...? Just let you guide me? Treat it as a paintbrush...?”
Instead of replying, I simply raise my baton and start conducting with the score. Maddelena makes a lot of harsh and pained sounds, and it takes till dark for us to get the atmosphere right.
“Can you feel it, Navigator? In this way, even someone ordinary like me can keep up with someone like Bai Mo...!”
She's got it the wrong way around. The ordinary timbre is the most important part of any performance. Without the violin's thread, the entire performance may as well be empty talk.
Maddelena's shy smile gives off the airs of a reserved calmness that is hers alone. With it, one can't help but be intoxicated by the sound of the music...
ActivityConcertStory.4_Content:
Outside the practice room, I hear the sound of piano movements slowly flowing out from a crack in the door.
Even after I open the door, the girl remains focused. Her light, slender fingers dance along the black and white keys, continuing until they strike the last note on a black.
“Music is fascinating. It's so different from medicine and anything else I've dabbled in. It's so easy to get drawn in without even noticing.”
As she speaks, she lifts the little hat on her head and shoots me a playful wink.
“Want to try piano four hands? You won't be able to conduct properly without giving it a go.”
Before I can react, Kokona pulls me to her side.
“Don't worry, just follow my lead.”
Our melody steadily blooms into a cheerful dance of keys.
Kokona might be right. If you spend all your time on the podium, you lose sight of the full picture.
“I'm looking forward to the performance. If we could continue playing together in the future... I think I'd like that.”
There's a hint of caring expectation in her smile...
ActivityConcertStory.7_Content:
Standing on the podium and looking into the packed crowd, you feel surprisingly at ease.
You know that each and every member of your band has great faith in you.
The next step is to just raise your baton and kick off a grand performance. With the music of the new year, the band will bid the past farewell and welcome blessings anew.
This serves as both an invitation and a hope for joyful news.
We wish you happiness, all of you who love Strinova.
ActivityConcertStory.2_Content:
When I arrived at the practice room, I found Bai Mo already perched in a chair, hard at work on his études, glancing at me through the corner of his eye.
“What do you think, friend? A good pitch, is it not?”
I must admit that Bai Mo is quite the accomplished musician. Knowing his unreliable nature, it's hard to imagine he could be as elegant and gentle as he is now.
“Come and conduct. Let's have a proper practice performance.”
I raise my baton and extend an invitation for him to begin.
“Alright! Check this out!”
The tuba becomes spirited, moving in lockstep with the conductor's baton and leading the rhythm - most fitting for Bai Mo, indeed.
“Capital, my friend! But now is not the time to trade compliments. There is still much work to be done.”
The corners of his mouth are raised in expectation. It seems that he has all the faith in the world that I'll make this a success.
ActivityConcertStory.7_Title: Finale: Thank You for a Successful Performance
ActivityConcertStory.1_Content:
At the start of the new year, a special invitation from Urbino was handed to you.
This message comes from Bai Mo, head of the Urbino Business Alliance. Having been inspired to celebrate the New Year with music, Bai Mo has called for talented musicians from far and wide to participate in the event.
Yet Bai Mo has greatly underestimated the opinions of these talented individuals, and their rift I fear is so great as to have destroyed any promise of this great performance. It is for this reason I especially wanted to pass this letter to you...
“There's no time, my friend. Only you can help me now! Only you can put these weirdos... Ahem, I mean, only you can get everyone on the same page to make this performance a success. I'm counting on you!”
                                               - Bai Mo

ActivityStrangeThiefStory.22_ContentAside:
The Origin
       During a routine operation of The Scissors, Ming learns crucial information: The “top secret item” previously stolen by The Scissors is to be auctioned at [Kidd Hall of Laurel Hall]. The starting bid of the item is extremely high. It is also guarded closely due to its high security level. The organization can neither afford to outbid everyone nor can it seize it before the auction.
       “Take back what is rightfully yours.” - this is one of The Scissors' mottos. Led by Lawine, Operation Black Cat, a plan to retrieve the item, is initiated.

       The Plan
       The team scouts Laurel Hall, the target location. Composed of [Philharmonia Hall] and [Kidd Hall] side by side, Laurel Hall is one of the most famous music venues of Urbino.
Intel suggested that the auction will take place at [Kidd Hall]. On the same day, the idol Kanami has been invited to perform at [Philharmonia Hall] next door. The auction and the concert are scheduled to start and end at the same time.
       Ming makes two significant discoveries during the reconnaissance mission:
1. [Kidd Hall] and [Philharmonia Hall] used to be connected by a passage, likely abandoned during renovation. The passage has now been sealed, leaving behind only a gap too narrow for ordinary folks. However, it should be a piece of cake for a Superstring.
2.       The staff of [Kidd Hall] have marked the locations of the auction items prior to the event.
       As the team discusses their operation, Kanami comes up with a plan to add a segment of <Outline_14>{aside1}</> magic show at the end of her concert. Ming and Lawine will act as performers. <Outline_14>{aside2}</>. The details of the plan are as follows:
       1. Ming plays a temporary performer, Lady M, hiding inside the compartment of the magic black box.
       2. Lawine plays a temporary performer, Lady L. She is to take the stage with Kanami and enter the magic box.
       3. Ming and Lawine switch places inside the box. As Ming steps out of the box, Lawine is to enter the secret passage, follow it all the way to the spot under the final auction item in [Kidd Hall], and secure the item once the opportunity arises. After the performance ends, Lawine is to find an opportunity and make her exit.
       4. <Outline_14>{aside3}</>, the audience will be unable to realize that the performer coming out for a curtain call is, in fact, Ming rather than Lawine. Kanami will lead the audience to believe that Lawine has completed a “<Outline_14>{aside4}</>” inside the compressing black box.
       5. Thus, Operation Black Cat will have given the audience a brilliant performance, providing a cast-iron alibi for every performer at the same time. No one will suspect The Scissors next door for the theft of the auction item.
       After the discussion, everyone begins to make separate preparations. Soon, it is the day of the operation.

       The Operation
       On the day of the operation, the magic show goes as planned. Kanami, Ming, and Lawine coordinate perfectly as a team. Having switched places with Ming inside the box, Lawine successfully infiltrates Kidd Hall. She is one step away from the final auction item.
At the same time, Bai Mo enters Kidd Hall in a ridiculous costume. The sole light source shines on the special guest, drawing everyone's attention. Seizing the opportunity, Lawine picks the lock and steals the final auction item, leaving behind a work of her own.
       Bai Mo takes the stage to lift up the cover of the auction item only to reveal a self-portrait of Mr. Black Cat, the same character he is dressed up as.

       <Outline_14>{aside5}</>
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.23_ContentAside:
- Multiple clue cards mention surveillance footage. Who installed the cameras?
     - “Me, the mastermind, of course. I knew exactly where everyone was.”

- Did you really forget about the time? How did you manage to show up at the exact moment Lawine entered Kidd Hall?
     - “Why do you think I had cameras installed, Navigator? As a competent member of the Phantom Thieves, I adjusted my time of arrival based on the situation to ensure the item would be unveiled on time.”

- Why did you plan a bomb? I don't get it.
     - “Because I wanted something fun! Besides, I had to blow up the surveillance devices and the secret passage. I wasn't going to tell everyone that Kanami and the gang stole the final auction item.”

- Had I failed to solve the puzzle in time, would you still have detonated the bomb?
     - “While I had other methods to take out the cameras without the risk of injuries, Navigator, I knew what you were capable of. A simple puzzle was a piece of cake for you.”

- Does that mean you gave Ming the details of the auction item?
     - “Not bad. Did you notice my call? Besides that, I was also the person responsible for the secret passage. I'd wanted them to have the item for a while. It was more fun than purchasing it and giving it to them.”

- What about the codes on the clue cards? According to your plan, Lawine and the others wouldn't have known about you.
     - “You figured that out as well, Navigator? Well, I thought it would be cool, that's all. You know me. I'm an indispensable member of the Phantom Thieves. The family has to stay together.”

- Was the self-portrait of Mr. Black Cat a part of your plan as well?
     - “How dare you... No, certainly not. I could never have expected it! They've ruined my reputation...”

- What exactly was the final auction item?
     - “I can't tell you. Why don't you ask The Scissors? Hahahaha!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.5_ContentMono: “Mr. Black Cat is awesome! Let's head out and see if there's anything requiring Mr. Black Cat's attention!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.10_ContentMono: “The auction at [Kidd Hall]starts tonight? Of course! I totally forgot about it! I have to be there! Let's go!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.11_ContentMono: “Now, my partner, Lady L, will enter the magic black box. Don't blink, lest you miss it!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.1_ContentMono:
“The bomb planted at the venue will detonate in 10 minutes. They're still there, Navigator. You don't have much time to solve the puzzle.”
“Beep... Beep... Beep...”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.15_ContentMono: “You got this, Kanami! You'll get it back!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.20_ContentMono:
“The final auction item was seized from PUS with a top secret security level. Guard it closely.”
“Certainly, Mr. Bai.”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.21_ContentMono: “Well done, Navigator. As a reward, I have notified them of the detonation time. They have plenty of time to leave.”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.16_ContentMono: “That was close. It's all up to her now!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.8_ContentMono:
“You're adding a magic show to your concert? What do you plan to achieve...
...Oh, that's a brilliant idea! Hahaha. Nice one, Kanami!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.13_ContentMono:
“Intel suggests that the final item at the [Kidd Hall] auction is the top secret item we're after.”
“The one that was stolen? Humph, we'll get it back!”
ActivityStrangeThiefStory.14_ContentMono:
“It's been too long. I'm running out of patience. Alright, let's see what's inside...
...Uh, what is this thing?!”

ApartmentBirthdaySeasonComments.1_Desc: So... your birthday's in spring? It's a perfect season for an outing together in such warm weather.
ApartmentBirthdaySeasonComments.2_Desc: On summer nights, the stars twinkle endlessly. Maybe we could watch them together sometime.
ApartmentBirthdaySeasonComments.4_Desc: When it's time to celebrate your birthday, we can also have a snowball fight together~

ApartmentMapCfg.1001_Desc: Strinova Guide at your service. Please do not try gliding after drinking sparkling water.
ApartmentMapCfg.124_Desc: Kokona briefly worked at P.U.S' training unit, but she prefers frontline work.
ApartmentMapCfg.128_Desc: Lawine had her personnel file redacted when she left P.U.S. No one even knows her true name...
ApartmentMapCfg.146_Desc: Urbino has invested a lot of resources in Astral Sanctuary of Celestia.
ApartmentMapCfg.105_Desc: Grove Bank is an important asset of the Grove Family and Audrey's pride.
ApartmentMapCfg.101_Desc: As the organization that governs Strinova World, Painting Utopia Security demands strict discipline, and all its members live in assigned dormitories.
ApartmentMapCfg.131_Desc: Whenever she is asked about her address, Yvette quickly gives the location of the PUS lounge before nervously clutching the hem of her clothes...
ApartmentMapCfg.107_Desc: Maddelena has always believed in the saying that designers are either in the process of creation or the process of inspiration!

ApartmentMapLoadingTips.15_Tips: “This is the song of my soul, the gift I would like to offer the world♪” - Kanami
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.54_Tips: Yvette has a mysterious past... Perhaps she is waiting for someone she can open up to.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.52_Tips: Yvette prefers cold beverages and desserts, but she has never fallen ill because of them.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.57_Tips: Yvette offers to make Fay all kinds of clothes, but Fay refuses every time. Yet, Yvette does not intend to give up.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.16_Tips: Yvette is familiar with all sorts of creatures and helps them survive in this world.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.22_Tips: As the head of Astral Sanctuary, she is respected by all healthcare workers, yet she remains humble and kind.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.14_Tips: Every day, Nobunaga wakes up in agony due to the betrayal of his kin.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.20_Tips: A physician cannot cure themself. Celestia treats patients, but she also needs a doctor to look after her.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.19_Tips: She has spent countless nights observing and waiting. Will the stars ever respond to her?
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.42_Tips: If you are unsure about what takeout to order, try asking Kokona. She is sure to have special recommendations.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.12_Tips: In the dead of night, Reiichi always seems to be kind and gentle.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.55_Tips: At work, Yvette is always calm and rational, seemingly unaffected by anything... Possibly?
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.34_Tips: As a capitalist, Audrey is not mature enough, still possessing the weakness that is kindness.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.30_Tips: Audrey likes to talk about family.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.32_Tips: Audrey's firepower and her keen mind are her most powerful weapons.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.5_Tips: Audrey once suffered from collapse syndrome, but she still managed to piece herself back together with the help of her diary and the kindness of others.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.29_Tips: Audrey's crown is the heirloom and symbol of her family. Its shiny, tough surface encases a soft, pure core, serving as the definition of family.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.31_Tips: Able to analyze various situations rationally and face changes calmly without fail, she still blushes every time she receives a compliment.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.21_Tips: The stars she lights up become the path forward for those who come after.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.49_Tips: If you, too, are in pursuit of artistic surprises and wonders in life, don't forget to contact designer Maddelena Leary.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.10_Tips: Chase your dream if you still have one, for all dreams can be realized right here!
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.46_Tips: To Maddelena, her art consultant is also her best model.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.44_Tips: Kokona's strong drive and proactiveness come from her innate curiosity, always open to trying unusual dishes.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.45_Tips: Kokona excels at taking care of others emotionally, but she rarely allows herself to be cared for.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.41_Tips: Kokona's room is full of piles of unlabeled, miscellaneous items. Watch your step when you visit her.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.7_Tips: Kokona claims the secret to staying energized is smiling a lot.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.37_Tips: It is obvious that Lawine and the impulsive Ming are complementary to one another. On the battlefield, they are able to inspire the fighting spirit of their teammates.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.39_Tips: Clenching the Pulse Blade, showing its sharp edge in the dark of the night, Lawine tells herself to bid farewell to the past.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.6_Tips: Lawine is an outstanding budo practitioner, thanks to her childhood experiences.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.38_Tips: Formerly one of the best investigators of P.U.S, Lawine had a bright future.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.36_Tips: Lawine likes drinking tea, especially green tea.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.35_Tips: Lawine is meticulous and diligent, two contributing factors to her becoming an executor of The Scissors.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.40_Tips: Lawine hones her body and mind through budō, dispelling her confusion.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.50_Tips: Legend has it that the tiny Maddelena can be seen gathering materials for her art all around the world.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.48_Tips: When people hear the name, Ms. Leary, they usually think of Maddelena's older sister, an artist.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.24_Tips: On countless nights, Michele lies in bed wide awake, contemplating the meaning of justice.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.9_Tips: The fire in Ming's eyes has never been extinguished. As a child, she protected the weak with her fists. Nowadays, she points her gun at oppressors.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.11_Tips: Celestia still gets upset when dealing with disobedient patients.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.1_Tips: Celestia still gets upset when dealing with disobedient patients.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.3_Tips: Celestia likes drinking coffee in hopes that its rich aroma will dispel her internal conflict.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.17_Tips: Celestia changes her coffee mix a little every day, to the point where she has lost count of how many versions there have been.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.27_Tips: Michele's father left her Mighty Meow as a companion, who is always there to support and care for Michele.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.25_Tips: Michele's father is her best role model and the kind of person she strives to be.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.47_Tips: Maddelena has always believed in the saying that designers are either in the process of creation or the process of inspiration!
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.8_Tips: Maddelena's view of the world is simple: create beautiful art that allows everyone to experience this brand-new world.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.51_Tips: The majority of Maddelena's designs arise from accidents and troubles.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.13_Tips: Bai Mo has a spray can gifted to him by his best friend. He uses it to leave behind his mark of memories and liberty in the True Wilderness.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.28_Tips: Michele doesn't enjoy solo missions, always hoping someone would accompany her on her adventures.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.4_Tips: Michele is a passionate gamer and the holder of multiple video game world records.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.23_Tips: Michele's favorite animals are cats, although she has yet to keep one as a pet.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.26_Tips: Michele often emerges victorious by breaking rules, but she has to write letters of apology as a disciplinary procedure for it.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.56_Tips: Her colleagues often ask to borrow Fay. A people pleaser, Yvette agrees most of the time. But she always feels uneasy whenever Fay is away.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.18_Tips: Although her encounter with you was merely accidental, Celestia cherishes it as an inevitability all the same.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.43_Tips: Although Kokona enjoys bustling places, she excels at solo operations in combat.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.2_Tips: Superstrings are individuals who are battle-hardened, constantly evolving, and possess special abilities.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.53_Tips: In crowds, Yvette goes into stealth to avoid potential social interactions. This tactic seems to be quite effective.
ApartmentMapLoadingTips.33_Tips: Behind the heavy firepower are trustworthy teammates and a belief that must be protected at all costs.

AVGEvent.1012_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_TextPa: Constructs and commanders, your brave choices will give us the spark we need to rekindle this dark night.

AVGEvent_Activity.104214646_TextContext: I really enjoyed spending tonight with you. I couldn't have asked for a better Spring Blessing gift. I hope you'll find my gift to your liking, too.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212420_TextContext: Let's watch some real fireworks together!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212821_TextContext: No need. Lawine is fine the way she is.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210522_TextContext: You want to take me somewhere else?
AVGEvent_Activity.104210137_TextContext: Don't the fireworks look prettier after going through the effort of climbing those stairs?
AVGEvent_Activity.104214604_TextContext: But... will you also be busy with the celebration preparations today?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212820_TextContext: But I wonder... would it be too conspicuous to go out with you like this? Maybe I need to put on a disguise...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210149_TextContext: Still, I'm satisfied for now. No matter how beautiful the journey may be, heroes need to keep moving forward.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210749_TextContext: Just capture it in your memory.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210133_TextContext: D-Don't laugh! It's normal to want to grab at shiny things...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210711_TextContext: The goal of the inspiration collection team? To make a splash at the fireworks celebrations!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210144_TextContext: To ensure that people can attend the fireworks celebrations next year and the year after that, and so that everyone can feel the joy we did...
AVGEvent_Activity.104212845_TextContext: I was worried that I wouldn't have the chance to give it to you... that we wouldn't be seeing much of each other during this season.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214633_TextContext: There will be many more opportunities in the days to come.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210145_TextContext: I'll continue to work hard in the future!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210155_TextContext: After that, let's continue our journey!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210710_TextContext: Our numbers may be few... but we make up for it in talent!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210516_TextContext: W-What are you saying? What expression...?!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210721_TextContext: What?? You're the one judging me?!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210125_TextContext: You didn't have to do that.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210538_TextContext: This has been a complicated and difficult year for the both of us... are the words “worked hard” really enough to describe it?
AVGEvent_Activity.104214625_TextContext: They say that fireworks are like shooting stars...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210146_TextContext: Partner, I'm trusting you to keep me honest!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212829_TextContext: But nothing beats the feeling of seeing it with my own eyes.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210724_TextContext: but I'm really looking forward to seeing what you come up with.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212836_TextContext: These are all facts that I've long accepted.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210743_TextContext: But... why do I feel this inexplicable sadness after seeing something so majestic...?
AVGEvent_Activity.104210718_TextContext: Is that so? Seems like I've got a good eye! Which part are you helping out with?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212847_TextContext: Why don't you open the gift once you're home? If you like what I picked out, just leave me a note.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210535_TextContext: You always manage to exceed my expectations. Thank you once again.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210510_TextContext: Are you actually interested in the celebration, or perhaps you just enjoy the feeling of helping out...?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212806_TextContext: You've come. How are you doing these days?
AVGEvent_Activity.104210515_TextContext: Glad to hear that it's settled, then.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210747_TextContext: You're right. Maybe that's why art was born - to capture moments of beauty in eternity.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212411_TextContext: In that case, I'll find you when the time comes. Don't be late!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210713_TextContext: A beam of light shoots high above, scattering fireworks all across the sky. What follows is a lively chorus: bangs, crackles, and booms. It should be a night to remember!
AVGEvent_Activity.104214613_TextContext: I've gone down the checklist. There aren't any pending patients or appointments. We're all set here.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212414_TextContext: Ready to go! I'm a bit nervous... but excited, too!
AVGEvent_Activity.104214603_TextContext: Senior, that was the last patient. We don't have any more appointments today. We can clock out early!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210106_TextContext: Lo, this valiant adventurer hath traversed the treacherous depths and perilous heights to lay claim to a boon, which she now seeks to bestow upon her comrades in arms!
AVGEvent_Activity.104214632_TextContext: It's only the celebrations for today.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214636_TextContext: As long as you're by my side...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210530_TextContext: May I open my eyes now?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212429_TextContext: Don't underestimate this telescope. It's good for more than fireworks. It can show you many other things, too.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210124_TextContext: I heard there was a huge traffic jam near the venue, so I wanted to make sure we could pass the time...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210148_TextContext: I really wish there was more...
AVGEvent_Activity.104212440_TextContext: Maybe this is what it means for something to be “good in your eyes.”
AVGEvent_Activity.104212403_TextContext: I hear you’ve been helping with the celebrations after work at the Astral Sanctuary. How are you feeling? Overwhelmed?
AVGEvent_Activity.104210720_TextContext: Um... Actually, I was supposed to help review the fireworks.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212418_TextContext: I mean... getting hit by a flashbang thrown around by some kid while out patrolling doesn't count...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210725_TextContext: Wah... Alright, then! The winds are back in my sails! I won't let you down!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212835_TextContext: Heh... I was thinking... compared with this vast expanse, how small I am; compared with these bright fireworks, how dim I am...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210714_TextContext: And humble old me got invited to help design the fireworks!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210760_TextContext: Eh? No need for a reward.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212430_TextContext: Oh? You've piqued my curiosity. What else did you see?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212809_TextContext: Ah, I didn't come here for that.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210547_TextContext: Ah? Did we take that long? It felt like we could have stayed a little more...
AVGEvent_Activity.104212843_TextContext: Mm... Since you're here, I might as well hand over your Spring Blessing gift.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214606_TextContext: Mhm. It's a shame we're in charge of different things. I was looking forward to working together...
AVGEvent_Activity.104214634_TextContext: Oh! Even when there aren't any celebrations, could we come by every now and then to watch the stars together?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212446_TextContext: Shh! Don't ruin the magic. In any case, let's do this again next year!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212402_TextContext: Heyo, Navigator! You seem lively today!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212435_TextContext: Hehe! We protect this world together, after all.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214645_TextContext: Remember to check your mailbox when you get home.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210550_TextContext: The housekeeper will be by with a gift... I hope we can also enjoy a night like this next time.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210539_TextContext: We are doing what we have to do - meeting our responsibilities.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210546_TextContext: It must be because we stayed longer than everyone else...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210715_TextContext: That's why I set up this inspiration collection team. I'll be the captain, and you'll be my second-in-command. Let's set sail and collect the inspiration we need to create the best fireworks display ever!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210119_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: The atmosphere brimming with anticipation, the day of the fireworks celebration soon arrived.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210520_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: The atmosphere brimming with anticipation, the day of the fireworks celebration soon arrived.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210727_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: The atmosphere brimming with anticipation, the day of the fireworks celebration soon arrived.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212413_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: The atmosphere brimming with anticipation, the day of the fireworks celebration soon arrived.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212818_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: The atmosphere brimming with anticipation, the day of the fireworks celebration soon arrived.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214612_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: The atmosphere brimming with anticipation, the day of the fireworks celebration soon arrived.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210518_TextContext: I'll be looking forward to seeing it for myself.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210524_TextContext: The extra time we spend on the road won't be wasted.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210117_TextContext: Great! I knew you'd say yes, partner!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210514_TextContext: I wouldn't miss the expression on your face for anything in the world.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214611_TextContext: Great. In that case, I'll make sure to give the preparations my all!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212433_TextContext: An accurate prediction. I believe you!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210139_TextContext: I guess you have a point.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210523_TextContext: Alright. As long as we really can see something special...
AVGEvent_Activity.104214642_TextContext: Alright. Try not to stay up yourself.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212848_TextContext: Alright. I'll make sure to cherish it.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212419_TextContext: Please look forward to it, then.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210512_TextContext: If you happen to be free... perhaps we can enjoy the fireworks together...
AVGEvent_Activity.104212839_TextContext: Even if we can't set sail together, I hope to be your safe harbor.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210154_TextContext: Oh, right! Don't forget about my gift - fate's boon!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210134_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: Though everyone was reluctant to leave, once the fireworks display ended, the night sky slowly became silent once more.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210533_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: Though everyone was reluctant to leave, once the fireworks display ended, the night sky slowly became silent once more.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210741_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: Though everyone was reluctant to leave, once the fireworks display ended, the night sky slowly became silent once more.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212426_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: Though everyone was reluctant to leave, once the fireworks display ended, the night sky slowly became silent once more.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212831_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: Though everyone was reluctant to leave, once the fireworks display ended, the night sky slowly became silent once more.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214629_ExtendPerformanceList_Index0_T: Though everyone was reluctant to leave, once the fireworks display ended, the night sky slowly became silent once more.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210521_TextContext: All ready? Then let's go. The driver's already downstairs.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210120_TextContext: I brought plenty of water and snacks!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210728_TextContext: Navigator! Just in time. I was just trying to find you! We agreed to watch the fireworks together, and I thought you had forgotten...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210740_TextContext: Navigator, I'm at a loss for words... If only time could stop right now, right here.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212410_TextContext: I'd be happy to accompany you any time, Kokona.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210729_TextContext: How could I forget? The road was just a little crowded.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210549_TextContext: In any case... Thank you, Navigator. I really enjoyed myself.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210110_TextContext: I feel like I've heard this line before...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210111_TextContext: I feel a sense of déjà vu...
AVGEvent_Activity.104214608_TextContext: I feel like we haven't been able to spend much time together lately.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210114_TextContext: I'm getting excited just thinking about it! Please, please! Just say yes, partner!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210113_TextContext: What I mean is... I want to invite you to the fireworks celebration! I'm told that there's going to be all kinds of delicious food and fun activities. We'll even be able to watch the fireworks up close...
AVGEvent_Activity.104212838_TextContext: If you're ever lonely, I'll be here for you.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212445_TextContext: Thanks for the gift, Lady Luck!
AVGEvent_Activity.611001505_TextContext: Now, I can't help but look forward to what tomorrow will bring. Mmm... with this biscuit, I feel like my mood's improved, too!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212436_TextContext: We'll build a better future. I'm sure of it.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210517_TextContext: I've gotten a little curious... Just what kind of an occasion is a fireworks celebration?
AVGEvent_Activity.104210733_TextContext: While I was searching for inspiration, I found an incredible viewpoint. I just know you'll love it too!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212819_TextContext: I'm all set and ready to go.
AVGEvent_Activity.611001503_TextContext: It's been a long time since I've celebrated such a meaningful day with a friend.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210126_TextContext: I'll take you on a shortcut!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212834_TextContext: I’m curious. What were you thinking at the time?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212812_TextContext: I wanted to invite you to watch the fireworks celebrations with me.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212814_TextContext: I understand why you felt the need to invite me. But don't worry, there's no need to take pity-
AVGEvent_Activity.104212810_TextContext: I'm here to extend you an invitation.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212830_TextContext: I like this feeling much better.
AVGEvent_Activity.611001504_TextContext: There was a time when I had completely lost hope for the future, but things are different now.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210730_TextContext: If only I could stringify and glide over...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210748_TextContext: But through what medium? A photo? A painting? Or...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210717_TextContext: I was also invited to help with the preparations.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214635_TextContext: Actually... we don't have to watch the stars or anything else at all...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210150_TextContext: We should count ourselves lucky to enjoy the blessings of fate.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210112_TextContext: And so, I wanted to give one of my tickets to a friend...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210540_TextContext: That's why everything we've gone through... it's all unavoidable “hard work.”
AVGEvent_Activity.104210122_TextContext: I've got the folding chairs, consoles, and a bunch of manga, too!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210751_TextContext: Keep your head up. If you fixate on the past, you'll miss the present.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214641_TextContext: It's getting late. You should get some sleep. I'll see you tomorrow at the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Activity.611001501_TextContext: The stars are out and shining - what a perfect time to enjoy some tea and biscuits.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210762_TextContext: Just make sure you're on my team for next year!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212817_TextContext: I see... okay. I will remember this appointment and wait for the day of the celebration.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210153_TextContext: Have I? I suppose it's all thanks to a special partner.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214605_TextContext: That's right. You're helping out too, aren't you, Celestia?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212815_TextContext: I wanted to invite you as a friend.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210744_TextContext: Am I unsatisfied? I couldn't help but wish that the night sky would freeze, like a canvas.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210712_TextContext: I'm sure you've heard, Navigator. To celebrate this Spring Blessing, they're holding a huge fireworks display!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210105_TextContext: My friend and mentor, the brave Michele has finally summoned you!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210534_TextContext: Even though I was the one who asked you out, you were the one who surprised me in the end.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212807_TextContext: I saw you out and about a few times over the last week, but you always seemed busy, so I didn't want to intrude.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214631_TextContext: I'm a bit sad that it's ending this way...
AVGEvent_Activity.611001506_TextContext: If the opportunity arises next year, I hope we can enjoy a peaceful celebration together once more.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210509_TextContext: Sure enough, as I suspected, you're not just taking part; you're enjoying it.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210506_TextContext: Grove Enterprises has been doing its year-end inventory, so I've been too busy to help with the preparations. That said, the topic keeps coming up, so I was curious about your thoughts...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210732_TextContext: Some of the people here have been in the queue since noon...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210761_TextContext: Your expectations helped me come up with a work of art I was truly satisfied with. You played a huge role in my success!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212417_TextContext: That's because I've never seen fireworks before.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212808_TextContext: The Spring Blessing is an important celebration for Strinovians. Rest assured, The Scissors will not attempt to disrupt the event. We'll also help maintain safety if need be.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210731_TextContext: No biggie. We won't have to fight over the good seats.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214630_TextContext: Now that the fireworks are over, will the celebrations also come to a close?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212427_TextContext: But seeing them with my eyes isn't enough. I need my special telescope!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212844_TextContext: I thought it suited you well when I saw it through the window.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212439_TextContext: Watching this celebration feels as good as clearing out an entire street's worth of food stalls.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214618_TextContext: I've been looking forward to watching the fireworks with you for a while now...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210716_TextContext: The fireworks celebration does sound familiar...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210140_TextContext: The moment I saw the sky, I felt the climbing was worth it, after all!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210107_TextContext: Wait a moment. Let me find a translator...
AVGEvent_Activity.104214607_TextContext: Once we're done with the preparations, there's going to be a huge fireworks display. Why don't we watch it together?
AVGEvent_Activity.104210548_TextContext: It's fine. If we stayed any longer, leaving would have felt even more unbearable.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210141_TextContext: Michele, you're calmer than I expected.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210109_TextContext: Investigator Michele completed all the tasks as quickly as possible, winning two tickets to the front row of the fireworks celebration!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210135_TextContext: So we were headed to the rooftop...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210541_TextContext: And we made it to the end, didn't we? Now, we can stand under the night sky and enjoy these beautiful fireworks together. That's the reward for my “hard work.”
AVGEvent_Activity.104214610_TextContext: Of course, I'll watch it with you!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210723_TextContext: I might not be able to help you find inspiration,
AVGEvent_Activity.104210757_TextContext: These memories are precious. It was the first time we watched the fireworks together, after all. That said... I still wanted to give you a keepsake.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212407_TextContext: I'm sure there will be many more, but I figured the first one should be enjoyed with my closest partner.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210136_TextContext: If it wasn't for you, I would have just stringified and glided right up...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210511_TextContext: On that subject, Grove Enterprises helped sponsor the fireworks celebration. As is tradition, they always reserve a few front-row tickets for sponsors.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214627_TextContext: Eh... When did you discover my secret?!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210108_TextContext: Oi oi oi! Don't go! I'll talk normally! Hasn't the search team been busy with celebration preparations?
AVGEvent_Activity.104210142_TextContext: Eh? Is that so? I absolutely, unequivocally, don't want you to think that this means I don't like fireworks!
AVGEvent_Activity.104214640_TextContext: Thanks for taking me home, Senpai.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212832_TextContext: Thank you, Navigator. If you didn't invite me here, I would have only been able to enjoy this view from a distance.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214619_TextContext: Let's go. We need to find a good spot!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210735_TextContext: It's time to watch the fireworks!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212846_TextContext: Fortunately... now I have no regrets.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212432_TextContext: For both you and this world, the future is sure to get better and better!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210758_TextContext: I made it while searching for inspiration. It's yours now!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210545_TextContext: That was faster than I expected. It turned out to be a pretty peaceful walk.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212425_TextContext: These real fireworks... they're so amazing... so beautiful!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210138_TextContext: It's the reward for hard work!
AVGEvent_Activity.104214637_TextContext: For me, that's as good as any celebration.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212828_TextContext: This scene... I’ve seen it many times in my dreams...
AVGEvent_Activity.104210707_TextContext: Alright then. The inspiration collection team has been assembled!
AVGEvent_Activity.611001502_TextContext: The rich aroma of pastry and the fragrant smell of fillings are the perfect accompaniment to these celebrations, don't you agree?
AVGEvent_Activity.104212837_TextContext: They don't scare me. In fact, they push me forward. It's just... a little lonely.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210508_TextContext: I'm a key part of the preparation efforts!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212833_TextContext: I would never have been in the state of mind that I am right now.
AVGEvent_Activity.104214628_TextContext: This star will continue to stay by your side in the days to come.
AVGEvent_Activity.104212406_TextContext: Great! In that case, I can ask you to accompany me to the fireworks celebrations without feeling guilty!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210722_TextContext: Doesn't that mean... you can't help me with the inspiration...? That would be cheating... The team is going to have to disband...!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210118_TextContext: I'll draw up our battle plan when I have some free time over the next few days. On the day of the fireworks celebration - be there or be square!
AVGEvent_Activity.104214626_TextContext: If that's the case, Celestia, you're like a shooting star that landed right next to me.
AVGEvent_Activity.104210127_TextContext: A hidden path? That's more like it, partner! Just lead the way!
AVGEvent_Activity.104212442_TextContext: Congratulations, by the way. Since you were the first to watch the fireworks with me, I have a feeling you'll be getting a mysterious gift. A sign of good luck!
AVGEvent_Activity.104210543_TextContext: (As I stood beside Audrey under the night sky, contentment and warmth filled the atmosphere.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104212849_TextContext: (As I bid farewell to Lawine, I felt her tender gaze on me. The feeling remained long after I returned home.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210753_TextContext: (Maddelena and I continued to gaze at the night sky in silence until the last of the fireworks fell.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210504_TextContext: (And so, once I got off work, I made my way to Audrey's home.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210103_TextContext: (Unfortunately, being busy with celebration preparations, I missed them all.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210755_TextContext: (Once the fireworks celebration ended, I escorted Maddelena back to her dormitory.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104212802_TextContext: (During the hustle and bustle of preparing for the celebrations, I suddenly remembered that it had been a while since I last saw Lawine.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210502_TextContext: (During the busy celebration preparations, I suddenly received a text from Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104212803_TextContext: (She once mentioned a custom of welcoming the new year in her hometown; it sounded fairly similar to the Spring Blessing...)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210519_TextContext: (And just like that, I promised to go watch the fireworks with Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104212428_TextContext: (I hold back a chuckle as Kokona fumbles around to make a “telescope” out of her fingers.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104212841_TextContext: (Lawine shifted her gaze toward the night sky, but this time, she had a smile in her eyes.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210702_TextContext: (I got a text from Maddelena asking me to visit her when I had the time.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210703_TextContext: (The Astral Sanctuary's been unusually quiet, and with the celebrations approaching, we're able to clock out earlier than usual.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210102_TextContext: (One day, I suddenly got a barrage of messages from Michele: phone calls, texts, and even in-game DMs...)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210756_TextContext: (Just as I was about to say goodbye, my companion handed me something with a hint of bashfulness.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104214602_TextContext: (It's been a busy afternoon, but we finally managed to clear the last patient.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210503_TextContext: (There was a lot of pretext, but the gist of the conversation was simple enough - “can you pay me a visit?”)
AVGEvent_Activity.104212804_TextContext: (I'd better find a chance to visit her.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210704_TextContext: (Alright. I guess I should pay Maddelena a visit.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104214638_TextContext: (I gave Celestia my solemn promise and made a silent vow to spend more time with her in the future.)
AVGEvent_Activity.104210104_TextContext: (Once I had some free time, I went to check out the cat café.)

AVGEvent_Audrey.105204031_TextContext: “Lady Audrey's arguments were very convincing, and she provided unique insights into the coffee market. We cannot miss out on this potential partnership.”
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102010_TextContext: ...But since it was your first offense, just don't let it happen again.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202047_TextContext: ...But please, just give me a little of your feedback.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204045_TextContext: ...Would you like to try it on? Only if you want to, of course.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102003_TextContext: ...Hmpf! About time. You're five minutes late!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202033_TextContext: ...Mm. I will remember your kindness. The Groves always pay their debts.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201027_TextContext: Hmm... that could work! Ahem. We can quench our thirst while continuing to survey the public.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101038_TextContext: ...I didn't expect it to be this simple. This kind of communication skill isn't in my negotiation manual.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201050_TextContext: I... I would never make such a misjudgment!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203015_TextContext: ...I don't really want that to happen.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204015_TextContext: ...And so, I haven't deviated from my original goal. There weren't any alternate motives behind my involvement with this café.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201042_TextContext: Nowadays, we're just humble proprietors of this café... I still have a lot of customers to take care of, please excuse me!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201058_TextContext: Sigh... I can't win when it comes to you! According to our contract, I cannot refuse the sincere invitation of my ally without a proper reason...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202055_TextContext: ...T-truly? My standards are very strict. The quality barely passes the mark, but...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202041_TextContext: ...How do we judge how sincere something is? Just how in the world are you supposed to make that kind of chocolate? Sure enough... I should just give up.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204013_TextContext: ...Now is not the time to run around and hand out gifts. Our priority now should be to secure the café's financing.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203030_TextContext: ...Listen carefully, now. This is a common negotiation tactic known as “the two unicorns.” One of us plays the white unicorn, representing emotion, while the other plays the black unicorn, representing logic.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203006_TextContext: ...Isn't that a matter of course? It's just a few pieces of chocolate...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201032_TextContext: ...I just said I don't drink coffee!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201047_TextContext: “The Many Discourses” is my secret weapon. It's helped me close countless favorable deals, and I've never doubted its effectiveness.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102033_TextContext: It's been a long time since I've played the violin... From my old home to Strinova, how many years has this instrument accompanied me?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202046_TextContext: I'm not taking responsibility if it tastes bad!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201011_TextContext: You can't make friends like that!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102039_TextContext: Keep moving forward, beyond the forest, other than the desert...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201007_TextContext: That's right. True friendship guarantees a far stronger base of support than anything you can buy with money.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203062_TextContext: You're right. The uniform taste of mass-produced coffee is a mark against its competitiveness. The automated production process can't produce the rich aroma that we expect from good coffee.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204021_TextContext: Long time no see! I just got a response from the Committee...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203008_TextContext: Welcome! What would you two like today?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204003_TextContext: Why haven't we received a response yet?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102028_TextContext: Let me be clear. I-I just want to practice my violin...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203011_TextContext: They've taken most of our customers. We've only been getting a handful of regulars with a taste for artisanal coffee over the past few weeks.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203022_TextContext: What the Committee is looking for is simple - “new ideas and artisanal craft.”
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204119_TextContext: Since he invited us here, I guess the shopkeeper must have gotten some news from the Committee, right?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204053_TextContext: B-But I've enjoyed getting along with you during our time together. So, thank you...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203013_TextContext: But for some reason, the idea of not being able to enjoy this “sincere” coffee bothers me...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203060_TextContext: The market is clear - artisanal coffee is on the way out! Compared to coffee made through automated production methods, it loses out in volume and price!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102037_TextContext: But at least for now... Ally, would you mind listening to me play a song?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101019_TextContext: Y-You could be a friend of the Groves...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202058_TextContext: Why are you so hung up on quality?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203018_TextContext: You too? ...Indeed, we discovered this coffee together.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101025_TextContext: You didn't sound like a friend...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201005_TextContext: All you need to do is help me negotiate. Did I tell you that I've mastered every technique written in “The Many Discourses” and have a 100% closing rate?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101012_TextContext: You want me as your business partner?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201006_TextContext: Are you trying to make friends through negotiation?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101017_TextContext: I find your attitude... somewhat unexpected. The Grove family is reputable and respected in both the business and finance sectors. I don't see a single reason why you would say no.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203028_TextContext: That's a good attitude. Confidence is the key to a successful negotiation.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201009_TextContext: Your understanding is a bit off...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102030_TextContext: You must be a great violinist!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201045_TextContext: Let's try a skill other than negotiation!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201064_TextContext: My judgment tells me that this coffee is unmatched by most teas on the market! I didn't expect to find such an incredible hand-brewed drink in this small shop.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101034_TextContext: I would like to reiterate that the friendship I desire is one that's long-lasting and stable. You will be my most valuable ally. Your wishes and demands will also be respected to the greatest extent possible as reflected in the contract.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203048_TextContext: I'd recommend you start by sampling Café Reminiscence's signature drink - coffee cherry wine.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202003_TextContext: I wonder where I'm going wrong. I've never made a mistake in the business world...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202029_TextContext: Making chocolates was never part of our contract, so you can stop anytime. This is my battle at the end of the day...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201043_TextContext: Another failed negotiation... I-I don't believe it!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202022_TextContext: I-It's just a few pieces of chocolate. Hardly anything I can't handle!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101018_TextContext: Darn it. I have never failed a business negotiation... Are you sure you don't want to reconsider? I'm hoping that...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204024_TextContext: Uh... how should I put this? I really didn't expect...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204008_TextContext: We came here to make friends...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203052_TextContext: When did we stop serving coffee? How long has it been since the family got together for a tea party?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204051_TextContext: Saying that all of a sudden...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203010_TextContext: It's a long story... The cat café nearby, Paw Pledge, came out with a new type of coffee. The production process is fully automated, so they can pump out coffee at low prices.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201012_TextContext: Hmpf! What did I just say? I've never lost a negotiation!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101020_TextContext: Business cooperation is not in my area of expertise.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203046_TextContext: The choice between investments and investors has always been a two-way street. In a roundabout way, you two and my partner over here are also competing.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203019_TextContext: Um... don't misunderstand. What I mean is... discovering this great coffee was an important outcome of our alliance!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204018_TextContext: Ah! A message from the shopkeeper.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102056_TextContext: Ah! There was one more thing that I have to say! Please listen carefully. I'm not going to repeat myself...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202051_TextContext: Hey, I don't want to think about these chocolates anymo...!!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203077_TextContext: Mm. It was a gift from my parents when I was young.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202008_TextContext: The Grove family has an old tradition. Every time the family meets, we exchange handmade chocolates with each other to convey our feelings.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201008_TextContext: The way I see it, making friends and negotiating are the same thing. In essence, both are a struggle to earn someone's respect.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102048_TextContext: At some point, wearing the unicorn medal, you've become like family to me.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203053_TextContext: As time marched on, technological advances and automated production have gradually pushed out artisanal craft. Our family went through much, too.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101011_TextContext: Based on our previous cooperation, I am interested in establishing a long-term partnership with you. Together, we will be unstoppable!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202030_TextContext: Adding a new cook to the kitchen requires further coordination, so efficiency may be damaged... But, rather than doing things myself, f-from a subjective point of view...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102000_PrologueTitle: Music as Warm as the Sunset
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101007_TextContext: With the election fast approaching, the Grove family shall become the leader of the business world for the next decade.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102047_TextContext: Our contract is made. I do hope that we can remain allies for a long time to come, but...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204033_TextContext: Thank you so much for your interest. However, after much thought, we have decided to partner with the Investment Committee.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101006_TextContext: If one were to compare the entire business world to a giant cruise ship, the leader would be the person steering the ship and determining its course.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203016_TextContext: Such exquisite artisanship and ingenuity shouldn't be allowed to die.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102009_TextContext: Punctuality is an important aspect of one's character and reflects their professionalism and standards.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203024_TextContext: Given such ambiguous standards, I might not be able to convince them...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203023_TextContext: The Committee makes the final judgment on which stores meet their standards. Strong market potential is a must, but the store also needs to have the ability to move people.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201041_TextContext: Miss, I think you have the wrong person. For us, “Grove” is just a name we were born with. We broke away from the family a long time ago.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201066_TextContext: Today has been largely unsuccessful, but this find may turn things around!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204138_TextContext: Even though we no longer think of ourselves as Groves, please accept this gift.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204010_TextContext: I'm sure that helping such an incredible café obtain financing will improve my reputation among the common man.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201039_TextContext: Nice to meet you. Perhaps you didn't recognize me, so allow me to introduce myself. I'm Audrey Grove.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203009_TextContext: Shopkeeper, did you just open? You seem to have far fewer customers than usual.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101010_TextContext: Become a friend of the Grove family, Navigator!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102018_TextContext: And of course, we can't have a tea party without tea...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204044_TextContext: In the future, we plan to refine and improve our current offerings. If you're willing, we would love to invite you two to be our official tasters. Of course, all your drinks will be free of charge.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102006_TextContext: Well... at least you seem sincerely sorry. What's important is that you're willing to correct your mistakes.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204037_TextContext: I'm happy for you. We need to celebrate!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204030_TextContext: Don't say that. If it wasn't for you, the Investment Committee would not have approved the grant.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102057_TextContext: May our friendship be noble and everlasting, no matter the world and no matter how many years may pass.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204011_TextContext: T-That was my plan from the start!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203017_TextContext: I don't want to see that either.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102034_TextContext: After all the conflict and strife in my family, I now shoulder the heavy burden of restoring the Grove legacy. My weekends are full of busy and trivial matters that cannot be avoided.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201025_TextContext: We can canvass for votes inside!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203054_TextContext: But through it all, one of our names has carried on the art of handground coffee. I assure you, the cup of coffee placed in front of you today... it carries the taste of our memories.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201015_TextContext: Just watch. The results will prove my skills!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204002_TextContext: The “two unicorns” show we put on seemed promising in theory, and the reactions we got were also in line with expectations.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102035_TextContext: I haven't been able to take out this violin in ages, and I really wonder if I'll have any opportunities in the future...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101013_TextContext: The relationship I would like to establish is more than just business...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202007_TextContext: I want to establish new “friendships” with the common man, but just how am I supposed to express this feeling? Being direct doesn't seem very effective.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101021_TextContext: That's... That's not what I meant! I said, “friend.”
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101004_TextContext: I'm going to tell you something you're probably already aware of.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203050_TextContext: There's a reason I recommended this drink - regretful memories.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101002_TextContext: Audrey Grove, current head of the Grove Corporation. A pleasure to meet you.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101014_TextContext: I'm a navigator, not a businessperson...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202006_TextContext: I've been reviewing our field research. You suggested we try some alternate negotiation strategies, so I'm brainstorming new ideas...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201040_TextContext: I'm setting up to run as the next Leader of the Urbino Alliance. I need the support of each and every member of the family. Rest assured, I will do my utmost to protect everyone's interests.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201004_TextContext: I am eager to gain their trust and build friendships like the one that we have.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202040_TextContext: What I'm feeling? How should I put it...? Nervous. Worried.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203035_TextContext: My guests have arrived. Excuse me, are you two the representatives sent by the Investment Committee?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101032_TextContext: I was quite sincere with you!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203058_TextContext: What I look for in coffee is quality.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204052_TextContext: I recognize your judgment and reactiveness, ally, but that doesn't mean I don't see room for improvement. I have very exacting standards for my allies!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102017_TextContext: From what I recall... there should be at least three layers of snacks on the dining tray. They should be eaten from light to heavy, from sweet to savory.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203067_TextContext: That's why they need our help!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101009_TextContext: What does all this have to do with me?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203014_TextContext: Will there no longer be a place for artisanal coffee?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203065_TextContext: Artisanal coffee has a more complex taste and a deeper texture, and it fully extracts the flavor of coffee beans. With its unique nature and high quality, it's got high user stickiness and has attracted a loyal base of customers.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102023_TextContext: I-It's not a special invitation or anything. I just felt like going out for a walk...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201030_TextContext: I'm sorry, but this cafe only has coffee drinks. I can offer you black coffee, cappuccino, latte, and cold brews. Our signature drink, coffee cherry wine, is a best-seller.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204029_TextContext: I'm sorry that we couldn't be of help...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201014_TextContext: Rest assured. I'm an excellent negotiator! What's more, I still remember what you taught me last time - “just spit it out.”
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202009_TextContext: Gifts can help express thoughts that can't be in words.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102055_TextContext: I didn't realize how much time had passed...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201010_TextContext: Is that so? What am I missing?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202002_TextContext: Perhaps it's my phrasing, my tone of voice, or maybe my body language... Could it be that I still haven't fully understood “The Many Discourses?”
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203068_TextContext: Indeed. They urgently need outside help to get the word out and keep their craft alive.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203036_TextContext: That's right, Lady Audrey. Following your recommendation, we've been instructed to take a closer look at the operations of Café Reminiscence.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202011_TextContext: That's right. I've already started making preparations. My preference has always been doing things cleanly and decisively, so please provide me with some feedback on the quality once I finish making the chocolates.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203051_TextContext: Coffee used to be a fixture of Grove tea parties. Back then, the family was united and free of petty grudges.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201029_TextContext: Do you have any black tea? I don't have a habit of drinking coffee.
