AVGEvent_Audrey.105101023_TextContext: Is this concept so difficult to understand... I would like you to be my navigator; for us to establish...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203021_TextContext: The Grove Investment Committee recently launched a new initiative to discover and invest in local stores with competitive potential.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201034_TextContext: Grove Winery? The wine produced there is for the family's use. We've never sold bottles to anyone else...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202017_TextContext: To make cherry wine chocolate, we need 300 grams of dark chocolate, 15 grams of butter, and 35 grams of cream. The key ingredient is a bottle of cherry wine from Grove Winery, but how much should we use?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201028_TextContext: Welcome! What can I get you two?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101005_TextContext: Urbino leader elections take place once a decade. This is a significant event in all of Urbino.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201038_TextContext: I didn't expect a Grove to visit my humble store...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102021_TextContext: No tea party is complete without music...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204049_TextContext: The unicorn represents the Grove family. Medals adorned with its pattern represent recognition and honor.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101035_TextContext: Now, would you consider... being my friend?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202010_TextContext: Are you saying that our new strategy is making chocolates?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203059_TextContext: In such a competitive market, nothing is more important than the quality of the product.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102022_TextContext: Ally, there's somewhere you must accompany me!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203025_TextContext: Ally, we need to join forces!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102015_TextContext: My ally, over the course of our partnership, we've had many cups of coffee together just like this.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201024_TextContext: Ally, we've yet to make any progress in our field research. Taking a break before seeing any results will only delay things further.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102046_TextContext: Ally, I've only ever played this song for my family...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201054_TextContext: Ally, I've told you many times already. I don't like coffee. These kinds of instant beverages all taste the same - rough and bitter. I really don't...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201002_TextContext: Ally, our next course of action is to carry out some field research in this neighborhood.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203003_TextContext: Ally, this batch is my latest attempt. The taste and shape are an improvement on last time... this one should do it, right?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201055_TextContext: You'll love it. Just trust me!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201019_TextContext: Just where did I go wrong?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202043_TextContext: Wait a moment! Didn't I just say that we were putting the plan on hold...? This chocolate is no good, I'm sure of it!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203027_TextContext: It's finally my time to shine!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202025_TextContext: Come on, work with your ally!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204014_TextContext: When it comes to improving my reputation, saving this café and then getting the word out through an ad campaign would surely be a better use of our time, wouldn't it?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203064_TextContext: The delicate taste of artisanal blends can make up for their shortcomings in other areas!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101008_TextContext: And I happen to be the most promising candidate in the upcoming election!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101039_TextContext: You're truly a worthy ally of mine, having easily accomplished such a feat. I must not underestimate you.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203012_TextContext: Automated production is the way of the future, indeed.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201044_TextContext: Maybe we should try a different strategy?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202059_TextContext: How should I put it... I guess it's the influence of that shopkeeper.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203044_TextContext: Please allow me to make the introductions. This investor, like you two, has come here to do some field research. They're also... an important friend of mine.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203041_TextContext: Please allow me to make the introductions. Like you two, this investor has come here to do some field research. They're also an important partner of mine.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201031_TextContext: Two cups of coffee cherry wine, please.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101001_TextContext: Excuse me, are you the Navigator? We worked together during the Grove Bank Incident. Do you remember?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203033_TextContext: Excuse me. Is this Café Reminiscence?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101027_TextContext: Isn't that how cooperation is supposed to be?!
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102053_TextContext: This song is dedicated to you, my ally.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204042_TextContext: Honoring those who have helped us with a medal is a tradition from our forefathers.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203074_TextContext: T-This time... why didn't you take the initiative?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204043_TextContext: We will remember your kindness. Thank you for everything you've done for us.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204050_TextContext: This honor belongs to us alone.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201033_TextContext: Miss, this coffee cherry wine was brewed with cherry wine from the Grove Winery. It's sweet with a tang of acidity, and the smooth texture does an excellent job of balancing out the natural bitterness of coffee. Even if you don't care for coffee, I highly recommend you try it.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102058_TextContext: This is my sincere contract with you, my ally.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201003_TextContext: To stand a chance at winning the election, I need to learn what people really think of me. Polling data will only get me so far.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202037_TextContext: This is our last recipe for wine-filled chocolate. If we fail again...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201063_TextContext: This coffee... The slightly sour top note complements the cherry fragrance, the nutty middle note feels natural and unpretentious, and the wine and caramel blend together in a perfect union...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202061_TextContext: Fragile and precious... perhaps this is the secret behind the Grove unicorn's success.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102016_TextContext: I'm reminded of my family's old tea parties. We'd pick out a spacious room with plenty of light and spend the entire afternoon chatting.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105101033_TextContext: Here is a contract. I hope you don't mind. It's a family tradition; we have always valued contracts and commitments.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203066_TextContext: This craft has been passed down through generations - both innovative and timeless. In my research, I've found that Café Reminiscence is a business that pursues quality with the spirit of ingenuity. But despite this, they are facing unprecedented difficulties in running their business...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201067_TextContext: Uhm, about... changing my communication strategy or something... give me some more time - I'll think about it.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102054_TextContext: Have I managed to clearly convey the ending to the fairytale... and all that exists between us?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203056_TextContext: So... ally, why did you want to invest in Café Reminiscence?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102032_TextContext: Of course! Every child of the Grove is required to take music lessons. Without an interest in art, one's life will lack refinement.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202028_TextContext: In that case, could you help me with those dark chocolates? They need to be melted right after you chop them.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203061_TextContext: Mass-produced coffee all tastes the same.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203045_TextContext: In addition to identifying investment opportunities, I'm also searching for solid business partners.
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201018_TextContext: I can't believe it. This was the worst day of negotiations I've had in my life...
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203026_TextContext: What do you need of me?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203001_TextContext: (Sitting at a table in Café Reminiscence.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204020_TextContext: (Sitting at a table in Café Reminiscence.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102025_TextContext: (Handbag in her hand, Audrey took me to a park at the intersection of the nearby block.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102043_TextContext: (As the sun set, I found my thoughts drifting with the golden light, back to the girl before me.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203047_TextContext: (There was a sudden glimmer in the representatives' eyes. They seemed to be wondering why the head of the Grove family and her partner were so interested in a little store like this.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203072_TextContext: (Once the representatives bid farewell, a tired Audrey sat down beside me. As a show of thanks, the shopkeeper told us everything was on house.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203049_TextContext: (Two cups of coffee cherry wine were quickly served, but the representatives, accustomed to the smoother taste of black tea, remained unconvinced. According to our plan, Audrey would play the role of the “white unicorn” and speak first.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204054_TextContext: (Audrey remained silent after that. The medals, one black and one white, shone calmy on our chests.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102059_TextContext: (Afterwards, Audrey and I spend a long time taking a walk through the park.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202045_TextContext: (It may not match the greatest chocolates in the world, but in both texture and taste, you immediately feel the chef’s dedication.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102044_TextContext: (The barriers to the girl's heart were slowly breaking away; her rhythm carried the sun's warmth.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202034_TextContext: (She got things twisted again, but at least she's started opening up.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102050_TextContext: (And yet, the hard shell that once protected her had faded away.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204001_TextContext: (It had been a few days since I was last at Café Reminiscence. The shopkeeper has asked us to meet them in front of the café, but it seems closed right now.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202044_TextContext: (The cold and sugary shell dissolves in the mouth, spreading the faint aroma of cherry wine across the tip of the tongue, while the tang of sweet and sour cherry perfectly complemented the richness of the dark chocolate.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102002_TextContext: (The anxious girl seems to have been waiting for a long time, but no matter her expectations, it's not in her character to express anything directly.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204041_TextContext: (As the medal reflected in Audrey's green eyes, her face betrayed a child-like expression, if only for a moment.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201021_TextContext: (After a morning of hard work, we made our way to the entrance of a café.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202042_TextContext: (I pop one of the chocolates into my mouth.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102042_TextContext: (In that place, a new and warm world awaits.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202049_TextContext: (I pop another piece of the chocolates in Audrey's mouth.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202001_TextContext: (Still worried about improving her popularity, Audrey has summoned me to her dorm once more.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202039_TextContext: (Audrey removed the chilled chocolates from the fridge. Some were shaped like a four-leaf clover, while others resembled a flower. Though their taste was still a mystery, the effort that went into them was clear to see.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203063_TextContext: (Audrey passes a copy of her market research to everyone at the table.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203002_TextContext: (Audrey opens a delicate, elegant metal box filled with fragrant chocolates.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203020_TextContext: (Audrey took out her phone and seemed to be messaging someone.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201060_TextContext: (Audrey takes a sip with great caution.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203078_TextContext: (After filling the cup with coffee, she picked the cup up and gestured to me with the same hand.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203055_TextContext: (Audrey picked up a finely crafted bone china coffee cup, filled it with coffee cherry wine, and toasted the representatives.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202018_TextContext: (Audrey was too focused on the piles of ingredients to pay me much mind.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203031_TextContext: (Audrey drew closer to me than usual and lowered her voice.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203075_TextContext: (Audrey gazed silently at the coffee cup she had pulled out during her speech. Did she want to drink from that one?)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102038_TextContext: (Her voice was gentle and solemn, and as soon as she finished speaking, pure chords embraced the reverberation of the violin's strings and danced across the air.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102027_TextContext: (Audrey bends down to open her bag and produce a violin.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204004_TextContext: (Audrey's thoughts were still fully on getting Café Reminiscence the funding it needs. But originally, the reason we came here was to...)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202014_TextContext: (On her desk stood stacks of chocolate recipe books, listing over ten different cooking methods, along with various shapes and styles. It's clear that she's put a lot of effort into getting the chocolates just right.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203057_TextContext: (Audrey turned her gaze to me, signaling that it was time for the “black unicorn” to speak.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202015_TextContext: (I wonder what the feelings behind these chocolates are? Looking at all the books laid out, I felt a gentle warmth in my heart. All of a sudden, I started looking forward to how they would turn out.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102020_TextContext: (Her green eyes had lit up, accentuating a bright smile.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204055_TextContext: (As she stares at her newly acquired medal, Audrey’s face resembles that of a child who has just opened a present.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203069_TextContext: (Once the dialogue ends, the two representatives whisper among themselves, then turn to us with a tentative expression.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204035_TextContext: (Whispering) Hey, aren't you playing your role a bit too seriously?
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102049_TextContext: (The uncertainty in the girl's voice blended into the sound of her violin, almost as if she had never spoken the words at all.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204016_TextContext: (Despite Audrey's attempt to explain herself, I could easily glimpse the truth from the panicked expression in her eyes...)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203070_TextContext: (They seemed extremely anxious, but they gave no clear answer. All they asked was that Audrey negotiate with the shopkeeper and leave some time for a follow-up inspection.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203007_TextContext: (Despite Audrey's calm voice, her dainty hands were covered with ingredients. She must have gone through many attempts before settling on this batch.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202057_TextContext: (Though her tone was a little forced, the smile on her face spoke volumes. Audrey had poured all her warm emotions into these chocolates.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203038_TextContext: (The elderly gentleman looked towards me and pushed up his glasses.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204032_TextContext: (The shopkeeper takes out a document, reads it out with some discomfort, then shifts his attention to me.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204025_TextContext: (The shopkeeper looked at us with a pained expression.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105203034_TextContext: (Two customers, a young woman, and an older man, entered the store, both dressed in business attire. The man was particularly well-pruned and wore a unicorn medal on his chest.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204039_TextContext: (The shopkeeper took out two unicorn badges, one black and one white, each overflowing with the pride and purity of the storied family.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102045_TextContext: (As the two of us enjoyed the open square, it felt as if the unicorn was seeking a companion.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202019_TextContext: (She obviously plans to make more than one type of chocolate, but this is way too much work for one person.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102026_TextContext: (The park was as peaceful as one would expect for this lazy afternoon. Only the sound of gentle sprinklers broke the silence.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201051_TextContext: (Audrey and I reach an uncomfortable deadlock. Audrey casts her eyes downward as the coffee cherry wine’s lasting aroma drifts up toward us. She still seems reluctant to give it a try.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202036_TextContext: (We stayed in the kitchen the entire day. If there was even the slightest problem, Audrey would throw out the batch and move on to something else. By the time we were done, there were only a few recipes left.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102001_TextContext: (Inside Audrey's dorm on a warm and sunny day.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102052_TextContext: (Once the performance ended, the night quickly fell.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201017_TextContext: (But her attempts at “making friends” proved less than successful. Even when she was still in the middle of her loquacious introductions, the passers-by would quickly excuse themselves after hearing Audrey's name.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102014_TextContext: (I'm unable to read the glimmer in her eyes. It could have something to do with that musical score mentioned earlier, or perhaps it's the answer to one of the unicorn's stories...)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201056_TextContext: (I hand Audrey the cup of coffee.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202012_TextContext: (Things still don't feel quite right, but in any case, the stubborn Audrey being willing to change her mind is definitely a step in the right direction.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202048_TextContext: (Though there's a hint of awkwardness on the surface, Audrey's eyes flash with a hidden expectation.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105202035_TextContext: (Once the hot melted chocolate is poured into the mold, the rich liquid is transformed into various shapes and sizes with the help of some special tools and a little ingenuity.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201001_TextContext: (While I was out, Audrey asked me to help survey her popularity amongst the people of Strinova.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102011_TextContext: (While she was talking, Audrey placed an oversized handbag down behind her. I wonder what could be inside...)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105204017_TextContext: (It was clear that sentimentality was what truly drove her to save the café.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102051_TextContext: (The lonely unicorn disappeared. What remained was the girl, her eyebrows furrowed as she continued to play.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105201016_TextContext: (And so the inspired negotiator applied their unique insights to try and make friends with one stranger after another.)
AVGEvent_Audrey.105102040_TextContext: (As Audrey hummed, the last unicorn from the fairy tale galloped in the direction of the flying notes.)

AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202097_TextContext: The thirty-second mark was just a basic passing grade.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204119_TextContext: “Bunny Mark got more than one parent. Next time, don't you dare try to scrap him without a single word!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204102_TextContext: “...A few days ago, someone going by the title of “Navigator” came to me with a badly damaged bot.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204106_TextContext: “Whether it comes to worrying about an exam or deciding to become an investigator all on your own... you worry about it alone, never discuss it with anyone, and make the decision all by yourself!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204110_TextContext: “But, even if you want to be a hero, why don't you tell us when you were struggling?”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204108_TextContext: “You're just 'Kokona', a little brat who likes to show off!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204114_TextContext: “When I repaired the bot, it became clear to me... you never realized the importance of all its combat logs!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204103_TextContext: “Seeing all the marks from field use and maintenance... It made me realize how hard you must have been working. But you're just trying to go it alone again!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204117_TextContext: “The design data of each module has been stored in this projector. We've done the assembly - you just need to finish up the fine-tuning.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204098_TextContext: “Haha... We all have much to say, but allow me to speak for everyone for now.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204113_TextContext: “Hmpf! There's still so many things I want to say, but this will have to suffice for now.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204122_TextContext: “And don't forget, we've all left you a message! Don't forget to listen to them when you're home!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204111_TextContext: “Even if it's not us, you have many trustworthy companions by your side, right?”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204096_TextContext: “Kokona, you may have graduated, but you're still just a kid.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204104_TextContext: “Kokona, did you forget why I dragged you kicking and screaming into this club?”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204115_TextContext: “I'm working at the AI Institute now. This is exactly the kind of data we need to train our new models.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204107_TextContext: “I couldn't stand it! What do you think you are? A genius? A hero? That's not it...”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204118_TextContext: “This new Sea Bunny drone - 'Bunny Mark' is now yours! In all the battles you've been through together, you've given him a soul.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204116_TextContext: “I've installed a new intelligent core in your bot, while Elise and your mentor have improved the design of the basic framework.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204105_TextContext: “Even though you were always smiling and seemed to get along with everyone... I could tell you were hiding so many things in your heart.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204121_TextContext: “Bunny Mark”... is this your new name?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102009_TextContext: “Bunny Mark” still needs some finishing touches.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201057_TextContext: ...Eating this, it feels like I've seen the Milky Way.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202038_TextContext: ...I hope that means we lived up to everyone's expectations.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202035_TextContext: So much time has passed in the blink of an eye. Even this place has transformed from an abandoned construction site to the beautiful greenway we see now.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202022_TextContext: We would come up with strange gadgets without any clear purpose and talk about the new food stalls that opened up near the school.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202114_TextContext: If collapse syndrome gets me one day... this little Sea Bunny is proof of my existence.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201011_TextContext: Actually... Maybe I should say that it's even more home than home?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203085_TextContext: No can do. I still have work at the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203037_TextContext: Sorry. I was exhausted from work...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204024_TextContext: Why don't we go for a walk?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202107_TextContext: In fact, with better equipment, I'll be able to help even more people!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204057_TextContext: Why don't we go in and take a look?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204064_TextContext: Something's off... Navigator, are you hiding something from me?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201027_TextContext: Believe me when I say that I've sampled food from hundreds, if not thousands, of food stalls.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203069_TextContext: Not for one person, but for many people. For generations, even. These many memories intertwined into “culture”, which they dedicated their lives to preserving.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102010_TextContext: Don't worry. It's just a few technical details!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201025_TextContext: To tell you the truth, I've been invited here as a guest judge.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202032_TextContext: I wonder how Erica and the gang are doing...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202007_TextContext: That said... sigh... I guess we won't be able to play survival games here anymore.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201083_TextContext: But... Hey! Wouldn't it be better with a little bit of protein?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203076_TextContext: Don't worry! The Kokona, as you know her, has returned!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202016_TextContext: But at the time, it was still a barren plot of land.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101021_TextContext: But I must say, the expression on your face reminds me of Celestia when she left P.U.S.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203033_TextContext: But... uh... what are you doing?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202099_TextContext: But, no matter how I feel, I guess this is it...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203059_TextContext: But recently, I feel as if I can finally understand their choice.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203038_TextContext: But... this place is a total mess... heheh... let's clean up together.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101039_TextContext: So... how exactly are we supposed to verify the efficacy of the treatment?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203063_TextContext: No, I really mean it. Thank you so much for being there when I needed it the most.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203071_TextContext: Sometimes, in order to move forward, we need to leave something behind... But at the same time, we also need to remember the past.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202049_TextContext: What's more, wounded combatants tend to be hiding behind cover or otherwise concealed.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201075_TextContext: What customers? I made this special for you, little Kokona.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204066_TextContext: There have been way too many coincidences today.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201014_TextContext: Today's mission is an important one. We can't be careless!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202039_TextContext: You seem to be in a strange mood today.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202102_TextContext: That's why we came here, to confirm my suspicion.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102045_TextContext: Let's learn and grow together! There are many, many people who need our help!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201044_TextContext: The food is unpretentious yet delicious. The best skewers in town!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204097_TextContext: Elise, Ling, Jack, Luna... and my mentor?! Why would everyone...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201115_TextContext: But I have faith that you'll make the right choice. We're good partners, after all!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101031_TextContext: Receiving treatment as a test subject... wouldn't that be a violation of P.U.S regulations?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101004_TextContext: You made an appointment at the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101009_TextContext: Are you aware that... Painting Utopia Security places strict controls on technological research?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201090_TextContext: Look - I'm a sniper, aren't I?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204054_TextContext: Look - there's a corner of the door frame missing. No one's bothered to patch it up.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101011_TextContext: You're right. P.U.S regulations don't strictly apply to you.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202112_TextContext: Protecting precious memories is your job, isn't it?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101007_TextContext: Keeping silent? Hmm... You're a careful one.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101040_TextContext: Let's start by having a chat.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204067_TextContext: First, you invite me to my school's open day...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202100_TextContext: I knew it was going to be this way... He's simply too outdated. No matter how much I try to tweak him, he's fallen behind the newer models and can't keep up with the demands of high-intensity combat.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201000_PrologueTitle: Let's go! Set sail for the taste-testing!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201010_TextContext: Don't worry. Everyone here is super friendly. It always feels like home.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201077_TextContext: You shouldn't stuff yourself with skewers, fried chicken, and soda every day. You need to eat some vegetables to stay healthy.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204070_TextContext: Don't tell me you went through all that just to surprise me when I open the door?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102051_TextContext: Don't tell me you forgot! We were supposed to test out my healing drones!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203045_TextContext: I didn't expect Kokona to like this kinda thing...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202061_TextContext: That took... 31.37 seconds. Not good enough. Let me adjust the parameters, and we'll try again. I won't lose twice!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201093_TextContext: It's only out and about here that I can clearly see the expression on everyone's faces.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203073_TextContext: Knowing this is enough to give me the courage to keep on fighting.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101018_TextContext: Whoa... You must have a strong heart if you're willing to say such an embarrassing line.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201072_TextContext: Just like the name suggests, it's an ordinary vegetable salad. I honestly can't come up with a single adjective besides “ordinary.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204112_TextContext: Guh... I don't know what to say...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203046_TextContext: Mm? Don't misunderstand! Even I don't have such strange tastes!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201127_TextContext: Eh? A surprising choice... but this way, I'm sure the store is gonna get much more lively!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204006_TextContext: Whooa! I haven't been back in ages - Open Day is still as lively as ever!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202047_TextContext: It's nothing complicated. All we need to do is play hide and seek!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201005_TextContext: Things haven't been so lively in a while!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201132_TextContext: Sigh... Making decisions can be hard at times, but you were so decisive! I wish I could be so cool... You've gotta teach me!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201049_TextContext: Mhmm! It's good to be confident, but don't underestimate the creativity of your young and hungry competitors!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201067_TextContext: Hum... It might be better if you don't know.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201048_TextContext: Hmpf! My stall's food speaks for itself!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204023_TextContext: Sigh... Navigator, what are we gonna do? We can't celebrate without the guest of honor...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204039_TextContext: Eh...? (sniff) That familiar smell... It's the fried noodle stall at Canteen No. 2!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201055_TextContext: Mm... Hmm! Nn... how should I put this...?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203029_TextContext: Mm? N-Navigator? What are you doing here...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204052_TextContext: Eh? Room? Let me take a look...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203083_TextContext: Ah... look at the time! Tidying up is such a pain.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203051_TextContext: Guh! You're making fun of me! I shouldn't have said anything!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204053_TextContext: Ah! Wasn't this our club room?!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102008_TextContext: Uhm. You should be able to find a seat over there...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201101_TextContext: Ah! Don't tell Michele about anything I just said. I don't want her to feel like I'm losing focus.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201114_TextContext: Mhmm... To be honest, I'm having a hard time with this final decision.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201053_TextContext: Hmm... An eye-catching name and rainbow-like color... this dish is full of personality.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202111_TextContext: Mhm... I've made up my mind.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201119_TextContext: Mmm. Good choice, Navigator! Skewers and soda are the ultimate form of street food!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202006_TextContext: Mmm... it's become a good place for a picnic.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204123_TextContext: Mhm! Everyone... I'm sorry for worrying you.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201081_TextContext: Mmm... The ingredients themselves are super fresh, and since the seasonings are kept to a minimum, nothing overpowers the natural flavors.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203053_TextContext: Hehe... Looking at all this stuff makes me feel like a kid again.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204020_TextContext: Hehe... I already know where we're going to celebrate. Just follow me!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204010_TextContext: Hehe... what are friends for? I know how hard you guys have been working.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201099_TextContext: Heheh... How strange. It feels like whenever we're together, I end up babbling on about a lot of things.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201089_TextContext: Hehe... you got me. That's why you're the Navigator!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201047_TextContext: Hehe! Thanks, but that won't earn you any extra points!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202069_TextContext: Heyo! I win this time. Try a little harder on the next one!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203031_TextContext: Oh, right... Today is the check-up.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201028_TextContext: When it comes to food stalls, “Kokona's approval” is better than any five-star review.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202025_TextContext: We'd dig around the abandoned construction sites to search for useful components or good camping spots.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203049_TextContext: But, when I was young, there weren't any “normal” girls' toys in the house, so I did end up playing house with it...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203067_TextContext: When I handed my bot over to you, I felt as if I suddenly understood how my parents felt.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204068_TextContext: Then, when I asked for a day off, my usually strict captain approved my request without so much as a word.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202048_TextContext: Healing bots often have to perform search and rescue operations in complex combat environments, usually with limited intervention from their handlers.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201092_TextContext: From such a distance, even busy crowds turn into blurred, moving dots.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101020_TextContext: Sticking to your ideals... that's easier said than done.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102049_TextContext: If it weren't for you, “Bunny Mark” wouldn't be able to live this way.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202004_TextContext: It's been a while since I've been here. Things sure have changed...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201050_TextContext: Alright, Navigator. Time for the next one.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202073_TextContext: Ready for round ten? Starting the countdown!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204036_TextContext: Alright, let's not waste our free time talking about work!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102025_TextContext: I think I know where the problem is. Just need the welding gun...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202017_TextContext: I think there was some kind of dispute over development rights with Urbino... In any case, the plot was abandoned. As time passed, it gradually transformed into an urban forest scattered with building materials.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203058_TextContext: I'd be lying if I told you I never felt lonely back then.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201074_TextContext: Ma'am, this kind of salad won't attract many customers. Shouldn't you add some ham or bacon or tuna? Something to spice things up!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202094_TextContext: The truth is, I invited you here to give this child their retirement exam.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201009_TextContext: If you're scared, you can hold my hand.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203032_TextContext: Sorry! Seems like I dozed off...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202034_TextContext: Oh, right! Fun fact - the bot you always see by my side was first tested here with the help of my mentor and the club.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101003_TextContext: Oh, right. Do you know why I called you here?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204131_TextContext: I'll make up for the celebration party next time!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201066_TextContext: Hey! What is this dish made up of? What's this red thing? ...And what's that blue one over there?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203056_TextContext: My childhood... Back then, I basically grew up all by myself.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203068_TextContext: Just as that bot contains my precious memories, I'm sure this doll was the same for others.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202045_TextContext: It'll be just like my mentor's old project assessments.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201046_TextContext: I knew you'd say that! Here, take this. I've already chilled it for you!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203072_TextContext: Even if it's not me, it could be someone else...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101016_TextContext: Are you guys really ready to travel on this winding path?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101014_TextContext: It’s true that Painting Utopia Security has a lot of red tape and rules to follow, but no one values the security and stability of Strinova more than we do.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201105_TextContext: I'm ready to get back out there! We still have a lot of food to try!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202105_TextContext: What? Don't give me that face!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204128_TextContext: Sorry, Navigator! But I'll have to bid you farewell for today!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203084_TextContext: Sorry for all the trouble today, Navigator. Give me a sec to change my clothes. Let's find a restaurant and have a bite to eat.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204087_TextContext: Navigator, I don't get what you're saying...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201112_TextContext: Navigator, I leave the last piece of “Kokona's approval” to you.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202109_TextContext: Navigator, could you please take this child under your care?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202014_TextContext: Thank you for accompanying me here, Navigator.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202037_TextContext: Even that little Sea Bunny of mine has accompanied me into many battles and helped save countless lives.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101013_TextContext: I'm sorry. I can't speak for my superiors.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201088_TextContext: You didn't come here just for the food, did you, Kokona?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204051_TextContext: Kokona, what's that room over there?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204062_TextContext: What's the matter? Don't want to?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201013_TextContext: In any case, just stay close!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201045_TextContext: Just the right amount of heat and sprinkled with their special spice mix... this would go perfectly with a nice can of ice-cold soda!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203034_TextContext: I was trying to help out.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204008_TextContext: I remember making up my mind to become an investigator after watching a P.U.S presentation right here.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201096_TextContext: Whenever I feel drained of motivation, I head out into the streets, order some skewers, and chat with the people here. This is what gives me the energy to keep going.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201078_TextContext: I-I know! I do eat vegetables! It's just today...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202096_TextContext: I needed the results to be objective, so I couldn't tell you that much.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101006_TextContext: I don't quite understand what you mean...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204085_TextContext: It's not like I want things to be this way, but...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101015_TextContext: I'm also a student of medicine. I know from experience that treating collapse syndrome is a long and arduous journey.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101010_TextContext: We aren't part of Painting Utopia Security.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202018_TextContext: For us, it was a place we used to adventure and test new gadgets.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204038_TextContext: As seniors, we can't let down our juniors like that.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201102_TextContext: Your secret is safe with me.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101028_TextContext: I just wanted to see what kind of people Celestia was working with for myself... But it seems like I was worried for nothing.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101019_TextContext: I just want to do the right thing.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202028_TextContext: Most of the club were robotics students.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203091_TextContext: Want me to throw them away?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204083_TextContext: I want to thank you for your kindness, but didn't I already tell you? In order to move forward, we need to leave something behind.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102013_TextContext: I'll have to take him apart and see what's going on inside the integration module.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204031_TextContext: Let me think... If you're not putting out fires, then you're no different from any other office worker, right?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203057_TextContext: My parents were both scholars. They spent most of the year traveling to preserve the heritage of the old world.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101017_TextContext: I believe in the ideals of the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203074_TextContext: You're worried about me, aren't you?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204130_TextContext: I need to start working on “Bunny Mark” ASAP to get him battle-ready!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102014_TextContext: I need a screwdriver... Navigator, do you see one?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102050_TextContext: So... my good partner, you'll see this through to the end, won't you?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204009_TextContext: That's why we need your help.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202051_TextContext: You hide while I count down to ten. As long as you manage to stay hidden from the bot for thirty seconds, you'll be the winner.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201029_TextContext: That's why the organizer invited me on as a guest judge.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204014_TextContext: So just this once, leave everything to me!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202113_TextContext: That's why I'm leaving this “memory” to you.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202093_TextContext: Apologies, Navigator. I didn't tell you the whole truth.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201076_TextContext: I don't care about any competition, but I have to take this chance to lecture you...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204028_TextContext: Is work as an investigator keeping you busy?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202106_TextContext: Don't worry. Since I've lost my little Sea Bunny, P.U.S will equip me with a more advanced healing drone. I'll still be able to help people on the battlefield!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202101_TextContext: Tools that can't meet their test targets will just be burdens on the battlefield.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101030_TextContext: In that case... I volunteer as a test subject! I can help you verify the efficacy of your treatment!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204025_TextContext: In that case, let me be your guide! I'll take you to the ten points of interest here at the Wright Institute of Technology!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201031_TextContext: Copy that? Then, let's get started!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203066_TextContext: Well, it's true that you might not feel like you've done anything special.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101026_TextContext: Of course! What's wrong with worrying about your friends?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102003_TextContext: Navigator, is that you? Come in!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203041_TextContext: Is that so? Oh right... what's with that box? Did that come from here?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203105_TextContext: Please help me contact the Wright Institute of Technology.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201069_TextContext: It's a shame we didn't find out how that dish was made.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202041_TextContext: Am I? Maybe you're just imagining things.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202030_TextContext: Every now and then, one of us would get a bright idea, and we'd all work together to try and make it work.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204032_TextContext: It's your regular nine to five with the occasional overtime, usually going out for a late-night snack with my fellow investigators after work...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202042_TextContext: This is a rare opportunity! Since we're already here, why don't you help me test my bot?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201042_TextContext: You've gotta start out with the classics! And when it comes to food stalls, nothing is more classic than skewers!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202036_TextContext: This world is in constant flux.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203097_TextContext: Sure enough, Kokona wasn't being entirely honest...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101012_TextContext: What does Painting Utopia Security want?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204109_TextContext: Uhm... Do you have to take it that far?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204058_TextContext: Um, can we? I'm no longer a student here...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204044_TextContext: Really? What a sec! How did you know what I was gonna say?!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203086_TextContext: What a pity... next time, then!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101002_TextContext: Allow me to introduce myself! P.U.S investigator Kokona, at your service!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201060_TextContext: Let me explain it like this!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204084_TextContext: There's nothing that we need to leave behind.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202024_TextContext: That's right. There's nothing the club loved more than going on adventures.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101024_TextContext: That's right. Celestia is one of my best friends!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202044_TextContext: Mhm! We’ll need to simulate an actual combat environment to evaluate its effectiveness.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201118_TextContext: The Sea, Land, and Air Platter
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203070_TextContext: Retiring an old bot and abandoning the old world for this new one... In a way, these two things are the same.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201091_TextContext: Snipers are always far above, looking at people through the eye of a scope.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204069_TextContext: And now, you've taken me to my old club room.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201068_TextContext: Creativity and ambience are great ways to score points, but you'll need more than just an eye-catching wish to keep customers in the long term.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204011_TextContext: Everyone will pay attention with an alumnus and field medic at your side!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101044_TextContext: Let's work hard together. Until the day collapse syndrome is cured once and for all!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101022_TextContext: Looking at you, I feel as if I understand Celestia's motives a bit better.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101005_TextContext: Looks like you know what you're doing.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101029_TextContext: You're also more interesting than the rumors let on.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202090_TextContext: Looks like that was the limit.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204037_TextContext: Look around at all these college students, full of hope for their future. Hearing us talk like this is gonna shatter their dreams!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202031_TextContext: How strange... To me, it started off as a club of misfits that I was dragged into joining. But now that I reflect on those days, they've become precious memories.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201087_TextContext: Amazing... This is how the city should be.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102012_TextContext: Strange... the operating data doesn't match the projections at all.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204007_TextContext: I didn't expect that you guys would be participating. What a great opportunity!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101042_TextContext: Is that it?? I was mentally preparing myself for human experimentation...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102048_TextContext: Wait a moment! Navigator, why are you acting so detached? I was just talking about you!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204071_TextContext: Be honest and tell me what you guys have been hiding. I won't open this door if you don't.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204013_TextContext: Treatment aside... there's a lot you've helped me with.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201097_TextContext: Moreover, I know every blind spot, shortcut, stall owner, and customer here by heart. No matter what happens in these streets, I'll be invincible.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201030_TextContext: So our task is to try out each and every stall, rate the food, and give out these coveted signs marking “Kokona's approval!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201094_TextContext: It's these smiles that an investigator pledges to protect.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203048_TextContext: These dolls were objects of worship in ancient times. This one is just a replica, of course.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101043_TextContext: Chatting... that sounds nice. In that case, make sure you visit often!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204065_TextContext: You might have forgotten, but I'm a deputy captain!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202005_TextContext: It's a bit different from my expectations, but I'm not complaining too much.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202029_TextContext: We all had different majors, but there were times when our specialties would overlap.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201017_TextContext: Even if The Scissors don't seem like the sort to attack civilians, I suppose we should be keeping an eye on their movements.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201082_TextContext: Even if you can't call it a delicacy, this vegetable salad is full of heart.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204012_TextContext: Even if crystal purification is the only way to truly cure collapse syndrome, your treatment has bought precious time for many people.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201095_TextContext: To be honest... this job is a tiring one.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202021_TextContext: Well, we were called a club, but we didn't really have any activities. It was just a place for a bunch of college kids without much else to do to get together and have fun.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202119_TextContext: Let's go, Navigator. It's been a long day. I'll treat you to a snack before we head home!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204000_PrologueTitle: The Door of the Past Leads to the Future
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203042_TextContext: And this one on the ground... Ah! This is...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204086_TextContext: He isn't just your past alone.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203044_TextContext: This... was a gift from my parents. No wonder I couldn't find it.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203047_TextContext: This box is filled with gifts from my parents - souvenirs from the old world.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201073_TextContext: You'd be able to guess how this one tastes without even putting it in your mouth...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204060_TextContext: Well, when you put it like that...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203060_TextContext: This is also thanks to you, Navigator.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202098_TextContext: This child was born with the help of many people, and he carried all their expectations. That's why... I didn't want to give up on him so easily.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201043_TextContext: This barbecue stall is a mainstay of the area, and I happen to be a regular. Mmm... The same taste as always!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202015_TextContext: This riverbank is full of memories for me.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201019_TextContext: Indeed... Ordinary citizens won't be able to stringify themselves to avoid danger.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202050_TextContext: So, finding the wounded faster than the enemy is critical to mission success!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202026_TextContext: The complex environment was perfect for our experiments.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201123_TextContext: A bold choice with good vision! People are definitely gonna be looking forward to their next dish now!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204033_TextContext: So that time you passed out...
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201054_TextContext: But flavor is king. Let's give it a try!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201079_TextContext: I won't accept that. You're the judge, aren't you? Finish the salad!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101037_TextContext: Great! From now on, we'll be partners!
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203094_TextContext: Yeah, please do. You might as well get rid of them.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124101008_TextContext: In that case, let me just get to the point. You're aware that the Astral Sanctuary is testing out a new treatment for collapse syndrome, aren't you?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204035_TextContext: That was a special situation... Not like I'm a workaholic.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204034_TextContext: Were you burning the midnight oil on something of your own?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201016_TextContext: Could there be a terrorist plot?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201110_TextContext: (Some storeowners became elated, while others deflated. Kokona tried her best to comfort everyone who didn't get a sign, and everyone promised to do even better next time.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102026_TextContext: (I think I put it in the utility room the last time I helped clean Kokona's room.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201061_TextContext: (Without warning, Kokona shoves a spoonful of the bibimbap into my mouth.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203101_TextContext: (I can't let her keep going on like this. Something has to be done.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202076_TextContext: (But no matter where I hide, the drone almost always finds me before the thirty-second mark.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204027_TextContext: (But I can't let her take the lead today. I need to find a way to open.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202053_TextContext: (Then again, since we're talking about testing her bot, maybe I should take this seriously...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203088_TextContext: (But, there's still one thing on my mind...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203095_TextContext: (I say goodbye to Kokona, carry a garbage bag filled with paper out the door, then return to the Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102029_TextContext: (An unspoken understanding gradually formed between us.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204004_TextContext: (To promote its consciousness restoration treatment and another “secret reason,” the Astral Sanctuary is also taking part.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201058_TextContext: (The Milky Way? What's that got to do with food?)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204088_TextContext: (With Kokona's confused gaze following me around the room, I take out a portable projector and place it next to the bot.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201023_TextContext: (Squinting closely, I can see a sign with a chibi avatar of Kokona giving a thumbs up.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202057_TextContext: (I carefully scan the surrounding area for a good hiding place).
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202059_TextContext: (The bot flies around, but I eventually hear the faint hum of the bot hovering somewhere nearby.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202078_TextContext: (I've come to understand why Kokona's companions trust her so much in battle.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102004_TextContext: (The week after our opening, I pay a visit to Kokona's dorm.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202066_TextContext: (That thick tree trunk might do. I'll just curl up and try to stay behind the cover.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202058_TextContext: (I dive into the bushes. It's cramped inside, and the branches dig into my skin.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202063_TextContext: (It's just a game. No need to take things too seriously.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203025_TextContext: (As soon as I lift the box, a cloud of dust enters my nostrils.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203027_TextContext: (The noise seems to have woken Kokona up.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102030_TextContext: (By the end, Kokona didn't even need to speak up anymore - the right tool always was placed next to her when she needed it.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203102_TextContext: (Calming the worry building in my heart, I gradually come up with the makings of a plan...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202120_TextContext: (I follow Kokona as she turns to leave, with nothing else to say.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202071_TextContext: (Well... if she's game, so am I.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202052_TextContext: (Sounds like an ordinary game of hide-and-seek. I can't help but feel that Kokona's just messing around.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204016_TextContext: (Kokona and I head to the event and meet up with Celestia.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201106_TextContext: (Kokona and I worked hard to complete the second part of our taste-testing.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201133_TextContext: (Kokona and I spend the rest of the night keeping things orderly. We wait until everyone leaves before we return home.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201040_TextContext: (Kokona and I are trying out the “Sea, Land, and Air Platter.”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201070_TextContext: (Kokona and I are now trying a “Vegetable Salad.”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201051_TextContext: (Kokona and I are now trying the “Spacetime Bibimbap.”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203079_TextContext: (Kokona and I finish organizing the remaining clutter.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203052_TextContext: (Kokona and I work together to organize all the items in the boxes, covering the entire table.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201086_TextContext: (Kokona and I sit beside each other by the side of the street, gazing at the teeming crowd.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102022_TextContext: (After looking far and wide, I find that it's fallen under the workbench.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203080_TextContext: (By the time we were done, the sun had already set.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204018_TextContext: (With Kokona's help, the event was a great success.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102047_TextContext: (Now that the bot saga is over, it's time for me to return to the Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203022_TextContext: (In the corner of the room stands an old, dusty cardboard box that seems like it hasn't been opened for a long time.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202089_TextContext: (The Sea Bunny drone lay lifeless on the ground, sparks flashing from its body.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203001_TextContext: (I arrive at Kokona's dorm at the agreed-upon time for a routine medical examination.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204050_TextContext: (At the end of a corridor stands a door that hasn't been opened in a long time.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201003_TextContext: (As soon as I arrived at our meeting place, I saw her jumping and gesturing wildly from within the crowd.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202092_TextContext: (The unpowered drone twitches its ears, resembling an injured rabbit.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201063_TextContext: (Surprisingly, what seemed to be a hodgepodge of complex flavors delicately balanced each other out without being overwhelming.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204127_TextContext: (I had never seen her smile so brightly.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102005_TextContext: (As expected, the place was a total mess.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204135_TextContext: (Let's see... that fried noodle stall should serve as the perfect venue.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204021_TextContext: (Celestia politely declines by saying she needs to attend some medical seminars.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203096_TextContext: (I pour the bag of crumpled-up paper onto the table and start opening a few up.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201120_TextContext: (We place the sign on the barbecue stall.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201128_TextContext: (We place the sign on the salad stall.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201124_TextContext: (We place the sign on the bibimbap stall.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202116_TextContext: (I carefully accept the Sea Bunny drone.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202067_TextContext: (Just need to watch the bot's movements and stay in its blind spot.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203099_TextContext: (All these scraps of paper contain blueprints for an improved version of the Sea Bunny drone.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201111_TextContext: (Soon enough, Kokona had gone down to her last sign.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102015_TextContext: (Kokona keeps her eyes fixated on “Bunny Mark” as she scratches her head in thought, the other hand feeling around the messy table.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201022_TextContext: (Kokona takes out a few acrylic sheets from her pocket.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201109_TextContext: (Kokona carefully recalls the taste of each dish she sampled, then allocates signs to all the stores that performed well with a serious expression.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202117_TextContext: (Kokona stretches her waist as if she had just let go of a heavy burden.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202091_TextContext: (Kokona turns off the bot's power and carefully picks it up.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204061_TextContext: (Kokona places a hand on the handle, but stops right after.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204132_TextContext: (Kokona darts away with “Bunny Mark” in her hands.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203043_TextContext: (Kokona picks the doll up from the ground.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102011_TextContext: (Kokona's workbench is covered with components and tools. As for Kokona herself, she's been busy disassembling, inspecting, and reassembling her new bot, module by module.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203087_TextContext: (Looks like Kokona has recovered from her bad mood. I should be happy for her.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204026_TextContext: (Kokona is the same as always, full of energy and brimming with ideas.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204056_TextContext: (Kokona can't contain her inner excitement, her eyes sparkling.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202077_TextContext: (Kokona is very strict about this time limit, tweaking the bot whenever it exceeds the limit even slightly.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201116_TextContext: (I suddenly felt the expectant gaze of many onlookers following me around.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202087_TextContext: (Feeling that something is wrong, I leave my hiding place.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204076_TextContext: (As if aided by Kokona's friends behind me, my strength flows through Kokona's body and pushes the door in front of us open.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204078_TextContext: (Traces of the unique personalities that once spent their time here can be found scattered throughout.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203010_TextContext: (The room is overrun by cardboard boxes stacked higher than anyone can see, with mechanical components and tools covering most of the available space.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203026_TextContext: (As my hand shakes, an item falls out of the box. Through my blurred vision, I make out what seems to be a human doll.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203015_TextContext: (The desk lamp is still on... another all-nighter?)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204089_TextContext: (I turn on the power, and the machine buzzes, projecting a translucent holographic image in the air.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202065_TextContext: (I glance around, looking for a comfortable hiding place.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201080_TextContext: (Without a better excuse, Kokona finishes the salad as instructed.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203002_TextContext: (When I ring the doorbell, no one responds.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202075_TextContext: (In line with previous experience, I look for blind spots by the trees hidden from the bot's line of view.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201002_TextContext: (Kokona invited me to participate in a taste-testing.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102040_TextContext: (Equipped with a smart core, the control program continues to optimize itself at rapid speeds, gradually stabilizing the flight pattern of “Bunny Mark.”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203004_TextContext: (I knock on the door, only to find it slightly ajar.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102041_TextContext: (The newborn drone "Bunny Mark" seems to be curiously exploring the world all on its own.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102031_TextContext: (Time continues to pass in relative silence.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202001_TextContext: (After finishing my shift at the Astral Sanctuary, I accepted Kokona’s invitation to hang out, though we were to meet somewhere other than a food stall for once.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203008_TextContext: (Everyone's been a little worried for Kokona as of late.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204133_TextContext: (With how fast she's going, I'm a little worried she's going to trip over.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204017_TextContext: (Kokona, with her extensive experience as a field medic, adds a variety of reliable arguments to Celestia's speech.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204075_TextContext: (No words are needed right now. I just give Kokona a gentle push on the back.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203012_TextContext: (Every time I enter Kokona's dorm, I feel as if I've been transported to a warehouse.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201004_TextContext: (I didn't expect there to be so many people.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201032_TextContext: (I never expected the diligent Kokona to have this side to her.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202003_TextContext: (I didn't expect there to be such a place so close to downtown.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202002_TextContext: (The greenway built around the artificial river provides a refreshing refuge of nature away from the hustle and bustle of the city.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202060_TextContext: (The bush kept me hidden for a while, but the bot found me in the end.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203007_TextContext: (After hesitating for a bit, I open the door.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201064_TextContext: (It really does live up to the name of “Spacetime Bibimbap.”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201036_TextContext: (Today is turning out to be more exciting than expected.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201039_TextContext: (Today is turning out to be more arduous than expected...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102052_TextContext: (Looks like the story of Kokona and “Bunny Mark” has just begun.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203050_TextContext: (When the image of a young Kokona playing house with a doll came to mind, I couldn't help but chuckle.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102037_TextContext: (The lights outside the window seemed to shine with Kokona's smile.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102032_TextContext: (The daylight waned, the sun softly melting into the horizon, stretching the shadows into evening's embrace.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204124_TextContext: (Standing outside the room, I cannot make out Kokona's expression clearly, but I see her shoulders twitching.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201033_TextContext: (Wait a moment... did she just say “each and every stall?”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201108_TextContext: (It's finally time for the scoring session.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201130_TextContext: (After a busy day, the taste testing comes to a satisfying end.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204134_TextContext: (I send a message to Celestia. We're going to have to celebrate a job well done.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201084_TextContext: (We continue browsing for a bit, but with our stomachs close to bursting, we decide to stop and rest.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204079_TextContext: (On the room's table lies a strange-looking bot with rabbit ears, carrying marks from a repair job.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203013_TextContext: (I find Kokona sprawled out in the middle of the mess.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204048_TextContext: (I have to resist the allure of the fried noodle stand and slowly guide Kokona back to the subject.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203009_TextContext: (Even if she never said it outright, Kokona seems a little down ever since she gave up her bot.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203023_TextContext: (Though I'm a little curious, I feel it would be wrong of me to pry further. I'll just move it a bit and clean the nearby dust.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202070_TextContext: (Even though it was supposed to just be a test, Kokona seems pretty competitive about the whole thing.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102016_TextContext: (Isn't a toolbox filled with an entire set of screwdrivers right there?)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203100_TextContext: (Proofs, calculations, and corrections... one page after another.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204072_TextContext: (Should I be surprised? Looks like she was on to us from the start. But now that we've come this far, I won't leave her a choice.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203098_TextContext: (She talks about leaving things behind, but the truth is, she still can't let go.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102039_TextContext: (Under Kokona's command, “Bunny Mark” takes flight, swaying from side to side.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201062_TextContext: (The taste was mild at first, but as the ingredients melted in my mouth, an indescribable explosion of flavors danced across the tip of my tongue like the Big Bang.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203017_TextContext: (Might as well help her tidy up.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202085_TextContext: (The thirty-second mark passes, but the bot is nowhere to be found.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201015_TextContext: (As a P.U.S investigator, Kokona is probably here on a critical mission...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202068_TextContext: (Ah! Too slow... the bot found me.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204126_TextContext: (A minute, maybe two, passes. Kokona takes a deep breath and turns to the door.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203014_TextContext: (Her breathing is steady. Looks like she just fell asleep.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203089_TextContext: (In a corner of the room that remains uncleaned lies a trash can filled with crumpled-up pieces of paper.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204003_TextContext: (The Institute has opened its doors to the general public and is holding a variety of academic exchanges.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204077_TextContext: (Before us lies a makeshift activity room.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203005_TextContext: (Does that mean I can go in?)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204002_TextContext: (The Wright Institute of Technology is holding an Open Day.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124202079_TextContext: (This round will probably end like the others.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201117_TextContext: (One should follow their heart and make a careful decision...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124204049_TextContext: (We find ourselves at the corner of one of the campus buildings. There aren't any activities scheduled here for today, so there's basically no foot traffic around.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102042_TextContext: (I can't help but feel a resemblance with the girl standing in front of me.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124201134_TextContext: (At that time, I did not grasp the meaning behind Kokona's last words.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124203020_TextContext: (Components, tools, schematics... most of the stuff here seems related to robotics.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102020_TextContext: (Kokona takes the screwdriver without much comment, then immediately turns her attention back to her work.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.124102007_TextContext: (Following Kokona's voice, I make my way behind the mountain of cardboard boxes.)

AVGEvent_Lawine.128201041_TextContext: April 15 (crossed out), April 16... Area 89 (crossed out), Area 88... bombs successfully played at the demolition site.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201043_TextContext: April 16, Area 88 demolition, poor fortune: I was lost all morning. Turns out the objective wasn't in the video store? I bought one of Kanami's new records to try and turn things around.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201044_TextContext: May 3, Windy Town assault, poor fortune: Why do frag grenades look so similar to healing mines? At least I have Kanami's record to keep me company. Hoping for my luck to change soon.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201046_TextContext: June 16, Port Euler demolition, good fortune: The demolition mission and fan meetup happened to be right next to each other! Finally, some good luck... I didn't even get lost once!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201045_TextContext: June 1, rescue mission, unclear fortune: I got lost again, so I went to Kanami's concert. Believe in that light, chase that light, and keep believing that things will turn around one day!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201047_TextContext: ...This is the good luck my idol brings to me! (The last few words seem to be sparkling with gold dust.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101072_TextContext: “Nosy and doesn't play by the rules,” “full of hidden strength,” and “one who has the power to deal with collapse syndrome all on their own.”
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101012_TextContext: ...Though, I admit, most of it is purely rumor.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101009_TextContext: ...So the storied Navigator has heard of me. I should be honored.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202016_TextContext: ...Did you come here just for this?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204086_TextContext: ...I once made a pact with someone.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203069_TextContext: ...Longing for the sun yet unable to gaze at it. Is that why she's dressed this way?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202051_TextContext: ...The Astral Sanctuary? Isn't that the place that treats patients with collapse syndrome?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101065_TextContext: ...This hobby or that, does it matter?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202079_TextContext: ...The wound was treated very well. You have my thanks. I didn't expect you to be so good at first aid.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102006_TextContext: ...Thank you, Navigator. I'll make sure to follow your instructions.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201033_TextContext: This work is too much for one person.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202015_TextContext: It's just a flesh wound. No big deal.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204026_TextContext: The greatest characteristics of the dagger are its sharp edge and its ability to be hidden.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101006_TextContext: No need to worry, I'm not armed. We're here to parley.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102042_TextContext: You're not the only disciple here.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203072_TextContext: Is she ok? You said she was an ER patient, so it must be serious, right? Go on, then. Take her to the hospital!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202028_TextContext: Still, they did end up getting in a few...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204023_TextContext: As a beginner, you have to be prepared for monotonous training.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202024_TextContext: Indeed. They planned to use me to get rid of the guards, then turn on me while I was weak to take the crystals all for themselves.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102044_TextContext: That won't do. I was the one who invited you, so allow me to serve the tea...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202084_TextContext: For the sake of The Scissors, I have to do my best. A sharp blade that remains sheathed is of no use to anyone.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203080_TextContext: Don't apologize. Thanks to you, I've finally gotten rid of the investigators.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202018_TextContext: I took a small risk in performing my duties, that's all.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201061_TextContext: I was careless and neglected this part of our work. Sure enough, if the leader doesn't set an example, their subordinates won't know what to do.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102057_TextContext: Perhaps it's just a coincidence, but... those orchids I planted have finally bloomed.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202020_TextContext: So, I followed our source to the transport site to verify the truth of the report.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102046_TextContext: We've become mentors and friends to one another, and that's precisely why...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102000_PrologueTitle: A Mentor as Well as a Friend
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204122_TextContext: I confess: I had other intentions when I asked to meet you. I have sparred with a lot of people in an attempt to calm my mind but to little avail.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202088_TextContext: Thank you very much for your help today. If it wasn't for you, this mission might have been delayed.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202089_TextContext: Today's meeting was rushed, and I could not host you properly. The next time we see each other, let's enjoy a cup of hot tea.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102028_TextContext: I asked you here today so that we could finish our ceremony from last time.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202023_TextContext: They were also after the crystals?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202026_TextContext: They best remember the feeling of my pulse blade on their skin.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201035_TextContext: One must inspire others by taking the initiative.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101074_TextContext: These rumors are just exaggerations, Lawine. Don't be led astray by gossip...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101076_TextContext: But, we wouldn't have asked you to be our “guest” if we didn't recognize your strength, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203086_TextContext: But in the end, she's exactly like them. A bunch of hypocrites.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202025_TextContext: But I wasn't going to let them win that easily!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203018_TextContext: Now, P.U.S is bringing down the hammer. They've got investigators combing this place for signs of our activity.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204119_TextContext: But I won't be helpless facing her again. That's for sure.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102037_TextContext: But, Navigator, please allow me this toast!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101023_TextContext: We won't treat a “guest” with inhospitality.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204077_TextContext: As a beginner, you were able to parry my attacks with ease... What kind of tactics did you utilize?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204017_TextContext: I would like to teach it to you as a token of my appreciation.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203048_TextContext: See the person in the photo? That's Lawine, the Executor of The Scissors.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201007_TextContext: I suppose you got the request to meet. I wanted to talk a bit about how you've been doing, just like last time.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202055_TextContext: Thank you for your kindness, but I can do it myself. I have more experience treating wounds.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202061_TextContext: Could you bring me the active iodine?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203042_TextContext: Are you saying... they can help me avoid the investigators?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203037_TextContext: Get out of here. Don't worry about me - I'll find a way to escape.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202011_TextContext: This thing? They're the spider plant seeds I ordered a few days ago.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102031_TextContext: It's a tradition of my family dōjō. When passing on one's legacy to a disciple, it is customary for the disciple to hold a ceremony as a show of respect and gratitude. We can do this through tea.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202034_TextContext: Let me take a look at the wound, just to be safe.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201053_TextContext: No need for that. I'll be revising these reports myself.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201055_TextContext: We made quite a few mistakes in our last battle. The team ended up in a sticky situation and suffered injuries as a result.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201066_TextContext: Swift as the wind and agile as thunder... this is the speed we need to defeat P.U.S.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201054_TextContext: A report is not meant to be a diary. Clearly, they've gotten lost in the weeds.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202033_TextContext: It's not much. The blood will clot soon enough.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101005_TextContext: Pleasure to meet you, Navigator. I'm Lawine.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203025_TextContext: Lawine... You're not getting away this time!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202019_TextContext: I got a report that the P.U.S was making a secret shipment of purified crystals.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201060_TextContext: This is not difficult work. As you can see, some people are just lazy.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203010_TextContext: It's you... but why are you dressed up like that?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203097_TextContext: You were going to pick up some goods, right? I'm happy to come with you if you don't mind.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202022_TextContext: They were trying to get you to take each other out!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101084_TextContext: Looks like the tea's grown a little cold. Let me heat it up for you.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101035_TextContext: Just a pot of fresh tea from my hometown.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202017_TextContext: With your skills, I didn't expect...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202014_TextContext: I heard you were injured. How are you holding up?
