AVGEvent_Lawine.128203053_TextContext: Uh... What's wrong with your friend? Why is she all covered up?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203077_TextContext: (cough) The hat has a pungent smell.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102035_TextContext: Only with this peace, can I truly face that person...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203078_TextContext: Oh, sorry about that. It must've been unpleasant.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204073_TextContext: Tsk, I got distracted in practice...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203026_TextContext: Tsk. Looks like they caught on to my scent.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201068_TextContext: Mmm... I should be able to go faster. There are more ways to save time than I expected.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204113_TextContext: How do I put this... Your tips probably helped.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201024_TextContext: Mm. It's not a big deal.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202065_TextContext: Hm. The wound is recovering nicely. As expected, there was only a small amount of bleeding.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204022_TextContext: Good. As long as you're interested.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202038_TextContext: I do, but it's mostly for minor injuries.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203020_TextContext: Yeah. I've been staying behind to make sure everyone gets out.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102016_TextContext: It's fine, I'll wait here. We should finish our last conversation in person.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204118_TextContext: Perhaps I do not yet know how to deal with things related to her...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201052_TextContext: Mm... what a wonderful collection of words. I'm taking my time to appreciate them carefully.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101075_TextContext: That's true. Seeing is believing - rumors are never quite reliable.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202078_TextContext: Looks like the bleeding has stopped.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201031_TextContext: A team surely works faster than a single person, but...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102036_TextContext: Arranging a tea ceremony today may have been a bit presumptuous...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204027_TextContext: Before attacking, a warrior does not reveal to the enemy the position of their dagger.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101022_TextContext: If you find something lacking, just say so.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101283_TextContext: It's been a while since you arrived. I'm sure you want to stretch your legs.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204028_TextContext: Enough talk. Let's practice with the real thing, beginning with how to hold the dagger.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204094_TextContext: She's become the way she is... because of my weakness. Because I couldn't stop P.U.S; because I could not prevent her from betraying us...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203049_TextContext: She is our most wanted fugitive. Evidence suggests that she is active in this area. If you see or hear anything about her, please inform me immediately.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102023_TextContext: Good to see you again, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201004_TextContext: If it's not urgent, come back later.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201028_TextContext: If we found them out any later, there would be even more work to do.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102056_TextContext: Mother often said that if you plant a seed with your heart's desire, you will sow a different fate.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203096_TextContext: Don't you have things to take care of?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201049_TextContext: Navigator, a few reports that need to be revised are missing. Have you seen them?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204133_TextContext: I have important things to tell you...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204029_TextContext: For a beginner like yourself, I recommend a forward grip. Like this...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204021_TextContext: Show interest in learning martial arts.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101040_TextContext: I respect your vigilance in the face of the unknown.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101053_TextContext: Indeed. It's a hobby of mine.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203091_TextContext: Yes, she was my partner back at P.U.S.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204124_TextContext: While I taught you martial arts, in a way, you have...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204117_TextContext: I hope you'll stop being affected by past events.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101017_TextContext: Not used to it, are you?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101059_TextContext: They'll be flowering a bit later.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101069_TextContext: You're not too different from the rumors, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102058_TextContext: Fate is a wonderful thing, Navigator... not to say that you aren't incredible in your own right.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204020_TextContext: Of course, I have high expectations of you.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204034_TextContext: I'll go easy on you. No one has to get hurt.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204088_TextContext: Although, I'm probably the only one who still remembers the pact.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101070_TextContext: I'd be curious to know what the rumors say about me.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101064_TextContext: Does it surprise you? Why the interest, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204083_TextContext: To be as still as water, as immovable as a mountain. You managed to achieve this as a mere beginner... I still have a long way to go...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204114_TextContext: Thinking of the special tactics you told me about, my body seemingly moved on its own, and the dagger felt incredibly light.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204127_TextContext: Go on, then. They need you.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203024_TextContext: This is where we lost her. Search the place, and don't let anyone suspicious escape.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102047_TextContext: We can sit here and enjoy this tea together!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203022_TextContext: I think I just heard “her” voice!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203016_TextContext: I just finished a combat operation.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101013_TextContext: I've heard that you're proficient at treating collapse syndrome and that you played a pivotal role in the Grove Bank Incident.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204011_TextContext: My family runs a dojo. We are accustomed to expressing our intentions and thoughts through martial arts. Therefore, I've prepared a gift in my own way.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201025_TextContext: I took part in many of these battles. Based on memory and record, I should be able to get through most of this soon enough.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102054_TextContext: I once believed that constant and silent struggle was my ultimate calling.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204084_TextContext: I have trained far from enough... I still lack strength.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204116_TextContext: The Lawine I know is a formidable opponent.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201062_TextContext: I learned this lesson when I was a P.U.S squad leader.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201051_TextContext: That's why they need to be revised. We can't take our battlefield operations so lightly.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101014_TextContext: That's why you've been invited here as a “guest.”
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204096_TextContext: I must keep fighting and honing my skills, for this is the only way.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202082_TextContext: When performing your missions... do you really have to take things so far?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201030_TextContext: Wouldn't it be easier to share this work amongst several people?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202087_TextContext: Apologies, Navigator. I have to go.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204126_TextContext: Excuse me, Navigator. It's an urgent assembly order. A group of gangsters is targeting the shelter in Preton...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204074_TextContext: Apologies. I failed to take seriously the training session I initiated.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101044_TextContext: If you're worried about scalding your mouth, let it rest for a while. Though it's best to drink the tea while it's hot.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101007_TextContext: Lawine... You're the executor of The Scissors, aren't you?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201013_TextContext: Are executors responsible for so much paperwork?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202037_TextContext: Do you have a medkit around?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204085_TextContext: What's the drive behind your determination to become stronger?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204036_TextContext: Please go easy on me, Lawine.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102043_TextContext: Please allow me to toast you, too.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101083_TextContext: This pass will give you limited access to our territory, within reason, of course.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203087_TextContext: If they were refugees from Preton, she would have left them all alone, pretending to be unaware.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204033_TextContext: Not bad. Let's see if you can put it into practice.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204008_TextContext: Relax. This is a safe place. The owner is a friend.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204035_TextContext: Bring it on. I'm feeling great.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202032_TextContext: I'm fine. The wound is just bleeding a little.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204076_TextContext: I lost, Navigator... You have bested me.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201050_TextContext: You mean these “rejected” reports? I'm getting a headache just reading them.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204078_TextContext: The best of them all - psychological tactics!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102034_TextContext: Your guidance and inspiration has cleared away some of the fog and calmed my chaotic blade.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203073_TextContext: There are no traces of the suspect! Let's go. We need to search other areas!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102026_TextContext: You're just in time. It takes a while to brew the tea, anyway.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204123_TextContext: You're different from all of them. Now more than ever, I'm convinced that you are indeed as extraordinary as the rumors say.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204115_TextContext: That was fun, Navigator. It's been a while since I've felt this way.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201042_TextContext: The sea breeze at Port Euler is wonderful. Definitely the best place to carry out a mission! Let’s go there on our next one, Captain Lawine!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202021_TextContext: The report of the secret shipment was true, but once I got rid of the P.U.S guards, the source turned on me.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101025_TextContext: Just in time. The tea's ready.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101066_TextContext: As you said, we're just chatting.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101018_TextContext: You walk in P.U.S and Urbino circles. I'm not surprised that you've grown used to superficial comforts.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101021_TextContext: You walk in P.U.S and Urbino circles. I'm not surprised that you've grown used to superficial comforts.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202066_TextContext: I didn't expect you to be so familiar with first aid. Your assistance was a great help.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101004_TextContext: I didn't expect for us to meet like this...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101063_TextContext: I just didn't expect you to have such a hobby.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204092_TextContext: I did not expect to see her again. She really didn't remember anything from the past.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203084_TextContext: Good-hearted... I used to think so as well. How could there be such a kind fool?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204047_TextContext: Suddenly sit down, upright as a clock
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203093_TextContext: But now... she's become a completely different person.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201026_TextContext: The troublesome part comes in correcting mistakes, especially for operations that I didn't take part in. I'll have to go through all the records carefully.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204041_TextContext: Suddenly stand up, straight as a pine
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202012_TextContext: Once the pots and soil arrive, I'll plant some of them.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203054_TextContext: Wait. You're telling me you're a doctor from Astral Sanctuary, and she's an ER patient?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202036_TextContext: It should be time to change the dressing, anyway.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204087_TextContext: We promised each other that we'd become stronger together and protect the people tormented by collapse syndrome.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204095_TextContext: I'm very aware of my own weakness and hesitation, and I despise myself for it...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101045_TextContext: The heat of the water unlocks the flavor of the tea leaves, resulting in the best taste and aroma.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102053_TextContext: We've been drinking tea together since the day we met, but this feeling is entirely different.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102033_TextContext: Though I'm the one who's teaching your martial arts, in terms of spirit, you're as immovable as a mountain. Here, I'm the disciple.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201019_TextContext: To be clear, it's necessities only.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201056_TextContext: As long as we carefully consider our tactics and learn from our mistakes, this kind of thing won't happen again.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202049_TextContext: Let me help. I'm also a doctor at the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203055_TextContext: Tell a story about a doctor and patient desperately trying to save another
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203062_TextContext: Tell an inspirational story of a photophobic patient wanting to feel the sunlight
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203083_TextContext: That investigator seemed to be quite good-hearted.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201017_TextContext: But back to you... I'm requisitioning a new batch of supplies. If there's anything you need, just mark it down on this sheet.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203013_TextContext: It's a long story. Follow me.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204010_TextContext: So... Thanks for helping me last time.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204128_TextContext: Please be careful and don't get hurt.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102007_TextContext: Don't forget to make an appointment for the follow-up.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201027_TextContext: The person who was responsible for this work hid their injury from the rest of us and tried to push on...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201015_TextContext: The person responsible for recording our battlefield operations was injured in battle. It's going to take some time for them to fully recover.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203021_TextContext: Before the investigators arrive, I should probably make my...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204015_TextContext: Growing up, I learned swordsmanship under my father, who passed to me this style of dagger technique.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201016_TextContext: Someone needs to do it, so it might as well be me.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101079_TextContext: Would you like some more? Seems like it's to your liking.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204100_TextContext: Please don't hold back this time!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204018_TextContext: Does that mean I can become a hero as well?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204019_TextContext: If you've got what it takes, yes.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204079_TextContext: This is a martial arts technique called “responding to endless changes with constancy.”
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201032_TextContext: This is my responsibility as a captain. I should lead by example.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201036_TextContext: I'm sorry I can't host you like usual... but make sure you fill out the requisition sheet.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203017_TextContext: This one was a great success. We managed to intercept a number of high-purity crystals.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101015_TextContext: How do you find it here?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101058_TextContext: The ones with broad oval-shaped leaves and large buds are moth orchids, while those that still need some time to bloom are spring orchids.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201023_TextContext: So much work... can one person really handle it all?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101026_TextContext: There's a cup for you, too. This is how I was raised to host people.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101067_TextContext: (This face-to-face has given me a better idea of the kind of person Lawine is.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102055_TextContext: But after meeting you, this feeling seems to have slowly faded away...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203088_TextContext: Is she a friend of yours?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204090_TextContext: We ran into her last time. Do you remember?
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203019_TextContext: How dangerous! You should return to base as soon as possible.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203092_TextContext: She was unknown for her unexpected warm-heartedness... A bit like you, now that I think about it.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202035_TextContext: That's too much of a hassle. This way is fine.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203031_TextContext: You two over there! Submit yourself to the Sentinel Bureau's inspection!
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201063_TextContext: The rest of this will take around an hour to complete. Once I'm done, I'll take you to the warehouse to pick up your supplies.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203079_TextContext: (Realizing that I bought the hat on sale, I feel guilty.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204108_TextContext: (Lawine manages to defeat me with a single move.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204056_TextContext: (For a moment, Lawine is lost in thought.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102060_TextContext: (We drink from the cup of fragrant tea, its comforting aroma lingering in our throats.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202072_TextContext: (The bandage falls to the wayside, revealing a deep gash. It must have been a desperate battle.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102020_TextContext: (The breeze blows past me, taking days of fatigue away with it.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201057_TextContext: (In the span of just a few minutes, Lawine manages to revise the battle reports into something more useful.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101032_TextContext: (What an incredible cup of tea, I must say!)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101046_TextContext: (Drawn in by the aroma coming from the cup, I lift it to my lips and take a tentative sip.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204290_TextContext: (As we look at one another, her eyes become dim and confused.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202062_TextContext: (Keeping some distance from Lawine, I hand her the requested item.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202075_TextContext: (We have never been so close before. Lawine remains silent, uncomfortable with the distance.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102040_TextContext: (Though I'm happy that Lawine has put aside some of her troubles, I can't help but feel a bit bashful at her hospitality.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204032_TextContext: (Afterward, Lawine teaches me a few basic dagger techniques.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201074_TextContext: (Afterwards, holding the filled-in requisition sheet, I accompany Lawine to the warehouse.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201029_TextContext: (I can understand what happened, but I still don't understand why Lawine must take on everything herself.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203003_TextContext: (This hat and pair of sunglasses are my disguise. I got them at a sale, but they've proven useful for keeping the sun at bay.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204137_TextContext: (The streets are quiet, just like Lawine. who has finally found inner peace.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102002_TextContext: (I received an invitation from Lawine today, but when I glance at my work schedule, I can't help but let out a sigh of despair.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201039_TextContext: (Looks like this executor has a different style.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204038_TextContext: (But in the blink of an eye...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204057_TextContext: (But then, she launches another round of attack.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202071_TextContext: (I grab some activated iodine and use it to separate the adhesive bandage from her wound.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203002_TextContext: (I used my pass to leave the base, but not before being warned to keep my identity hidden from the outside world.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102013_TextContext: (I check and double-check to make sure all the work for the day is really done.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201001_TextContext: (Having agreed to meet again, I use my pass to make my way to Lawine's dorm.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101081_TextContext: (As I reach to take the cup from her, she hands me a pass embossed with the mark of The Scissors.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202054_TextContext: (Just as I was about to step forward, Lawine stoped me.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102059_TextContext: (In almost perfect sync, we look at each other with a smile of clear understanding.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204014_TextContext: (Despite showing signs of wear, the blade gleams as a result of proper maintenance.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204061_TextContext: (I barely manage to dodge Lawine's attack, maintaining my balance.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204059_TextContext: (The dagger moves as a swift flash of lightning in her hand.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204040_TextContext: (Her dagger is closing in on me!)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201012_TextContext: (Paperwork never really comes to mind when I think about Lawine.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203030_TextContext: (Lawine's feet seemed to be locked in place.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204064_TextContext: (Adjusting her stance, Lawine restricts my range of movement, trapping me where I stand.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203071_TextContext: (Lawine can't help but cough, possibly as a result of being all covered up.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201022_TextContext: (As I bemoan my situation, I see Lawine returning to the mountain of paperwork.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203058_TextContext: (Afterward, in order to save the patient, the doctor bets everything on her, willing to give it her all...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203065_TextContext: (It's only natural for living beings to long for sunlight. But for her, it's terrifyingly beautiful.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102027_TextContext: (Lawine sits at the front of the table with a smile on her face, a beautiful aroma rising from the pot next to her.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102015_TextContext: (I text Lawine. She responds that she’s still at the teahouse.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204135_TextContext: (By the time I realize what Lawine just said, she has also disappeared into the night.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101001_TextContext: (Having received some “special care” from The Scissors, I end up at their base.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202092_TextContext: (I can only watch as she disappears silently into the night.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204003_TextContext: (Outside the courtyard, I hear the faint sound of bamboo swaying in the wind.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201011_TextContext: (The familiar scent of fresh tea was nowhere to be found. Instead, I found a desk buried under piles of files.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202004_TextContext: (I wait a moment by the door.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101037_TextContext: (As the fragrance of the tea fills the room, we both relax our guard.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101048_TextContext: (As the fragrance of the tea fills the room, we both relax our guard.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203001_TextContext: (The console and game cartridges I ordered from Hermes have finally arrived.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101002_TextContext: (When I arrive, Lawine asks that we meet at her residence.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201073_TextContext: (I must have drifted off... When Lawine came into view again, she was organizing the final document into a folder, her movements smooth, as if sheathing her blade.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203023_TextContext: (A party of investigators enters the area, following behind a young captain.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202043_TextContext: (Lawine removes the rubbing alcohol and a fresh bandage.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203095_TextContext: (Looking down in silence for a couple of seconds, she seems to have remembered something.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202081_TextContext: (During that mission... it's as if she had no regard for her own life at all.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204284_TextContext: (Lower her head, she mutters that phrase as if to remind and punish herself.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101027_TextContext: (Lawine carefully pours the tea into two miniature cups decorated in oriental print.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204046_TextContext: (She instinctively steps back, as if expecting me to unleash a powerful move.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204105_TextContext: (Her gaze becomes as sharp as a knife, just like when we first met.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102050_TextContext: (Her eyes, previously clouded with hesitation and doubt, now shine as clear as the bamboo in her dōjō courtyard or the fragrant tea in our cups.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204052_TextContext: (She quickly sheathes her dagger, carefully observing the situation.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102009_TextContext: (I get ready to call the next patient.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201018_TextContext: (Excited, I start making a mental note of the supplies I need.
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101028_TextContext: (Still unsure about Lawine's intentions, I mull over the safety of accepting the tea.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101039_TextContext: (I hesitate to touch the tea in front of me.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202090_TextContext: (I try to convince Lawine to rest until the wound heals, but she doesn't look back.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204063_TextContext: (I try to get behind her, but she sees through my intention.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202031_TextContext: (Like drops of ink, her blood has pooled into a patch on her bandage.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203099_TextContext: (In our unique disguises, we manage to pick up the goods. Although she's still not used to her disguise, Lawine is in surprisingly good spirits.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202064_TextContext: (With much effort, Lawine eventually manages to dress her wound.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101031_TextContext: (Despite her cold demeanor, it's clear that Lawine put a lot of effort into this brew.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202002_TextContext: (I look left and right, but don't see Lawine.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203046_TextContext: (I'm curious about her expression under the hat and sunglasses.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202048_TextContext: (Clearly... it's not that easy to treat a wound by yourself.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202077_TextContext: (I finish dressing her wound in no time.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202001_TextContext: (Having learned about Lawine's injury, I rush to her dorm to see her.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204136_TextContext: (Thinking of our future meeting, I walk under the moonlight.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102021_TextContext: (I mentally prepare myself and step into the teahouse.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102017_TextContext: (I get the feeling that I can't miss this meeting.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203011_TextContext: (I unexpectedly ran into Lawine in full combat attire, busy scanning our surroundings with great vigilance.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202091_TextContext: (She treats herself with the same coldness she directs at her enemies.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102061_TextContext: (Words don't seem to be needed. The gentle breeze and swaying bamboo bear witness.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204097_TextContext: (Perhaps troubled by her inner turmoil, Lawine does not know what the future holds for her.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203029_TextContext: (I've never seen this expression on Lawine's face before. She looked sorrowful, stunned, lost in a haze.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101061_TextContext: (She's not just an executor... she also knows how to grow flowers and make great tea.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203094_TextContext: (Not wanting to discuss her former friend, Lawine changes the subject.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204013_TextContext: (Lawine produces a wooden dagger from seemingly nowhere.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203076_TextContext: (Lawine double-checks to make sure all the investigators are gone before removing her disguise. She takes me to another hiding spot.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202006_TextContext: (Lawine appears by the door dressed in her old plain white clothes.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201067_TextContext: (Lawine lowers her head to the papers in front of her.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101060_TextContext: (As she introduces all her flowers, I can't help but see Lawine as an ordinary girl.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204075_TextContext: (Lawine struggles to strike again. However, just like when she faced the investigator, she becomes flustered all of a sudden.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202013_TextContext: (Lawine places the package down, revealing the bandage hidden by her sleeve.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204089_TextContext: (Lawine lifts up her head, revealing a wry smile.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203082_TextContext: (Lawine looks in the direction the girl had left.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101043_TextContext: (Lawine takes a sip from her cup.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101055_TextContext: (Lawine looks over the plants out of the corner of her eye.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102045_TextContext: (Lawine furrows her brows as we reach an awkward impasse.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201071_TextContext: (With sparks coming out of her eyes, Lawine's gaze was as firm as a warrior drawing their weapon.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102049_TextContext: (Lawine thinks for a moment before raising her cup again.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101008_TextContext: (Lawine remains silent as her blue eyes look me up and down.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202030_TextContext: (Lawine suddenly puts a hand over her injured arm.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202056_TextContext: (Lawine continues trying to untie the bandage, but it seems to have gotten stuck on the wound.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201037_TextContext: (Lawine continues to devote herself to the paperwork.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204121_TextContext: (Lawine closes her eyes, feeling the gentle breeze, her hair swaying with the bamboo in the courtyard.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203085_TextContext: (Mentioning the investigator, Lawine sounds slightly sad.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101036_TextContext: (When she speaks the word “hometown,” a little warmth flows to Lawine's icy demeanor.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203032_TextContext: (The investigators had found us. Their footsteps were approaching...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201038_TextContext: (Several battle reports marked “rejected” fall out of the pile of documents.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204054_TextContext: (No one dares to make a move, resulting in a lasting stalemate.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203066_TextContext: (Time and time again, she embraces the sun like a moth to a flame, suffering the scorching heat.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204099_TextContext: (Disagreeing with the conclusion of her self-assessment, I ask to spar with Lawine again.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204384_TextContext: (Her desire to become powerful no matter the cost... I am curious about the reason behind it.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203005_TextContext: (The streets are as calm and peaceful as I remember. I've missed the feeling of being out like this.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102041_TextContext: (Especially with all the help she's given me in the past...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201021_TextContext: (Not a single console or game cartridge in sight. Such a shame...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204002_TextContext: (Under the gentle evening breeze, I arrive at the teahouse where I had agreed to meet Lawine.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204009_TextContext: (Breathing a sigh of relief, I notice that Lawine looks worried, seemingly out of place in the serene teahouse.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203258_TextContext: (A desperate doctor, overlooked by everyone, meets an equally demoralized patient, tormented by illness...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203100_TextContext: (On the way back to the base, Lawine and I agree to meet again for the fourth time.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203067_TextContext: (The desperate struggle of a fragile life touches everyone present.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102032_TextContext: (Lawine picks up a teacup as she speaks.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204025_TextContext: (As she speaks, she unsheathes another sharp dagger with a bright red tip.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204005_TextContext: (As I step into the teahouse, I realize that Lawine has been waiting for me for quite some time.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102014_TextContext: (Looks right... I can finally get off work!)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101050_TextContext: (I notice the myriad flowerpots on Lawine's table, along with many books related to horticulture.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202063_TextContext: (Lawine applies the medicine, then tears off the gauze in a smooth motion, revealing a deep wound beneath.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201020_TextContext: (The sheet only spares the luxury of common food items, medicine, and personal hygiene products.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203039_TextContext: (Scratching my head, I feel the beret I bought on sale. I've got an idea!)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101030_TextContext: (The steaming tea is hot in my mouth, but its unique fragrance lingers on the tip of my tongue... incredible.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203098_TextContext: (Concerned about our identities being exposed, I suggest we split the hat and sunglasses between us.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202010_TextContext: (I notice that she's holding a package.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202047_TextContext: (Lawine holds back her pain as she struggles to untie the blood-stained bandage.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101003_TextContext: (Lawine looks so different outside of her combat attire. Adorned in plain white, she gives off an air of simplicity and elegance.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204237_TextContext: (After a brief exchange, Lawine swings her dagger.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202073_TextContext: (Looking over, I confirm that there's no pus, only a little blood.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203306_TextContext: (I hear sudden, hurried footsteps approaching from behind...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204044_TextContext: (My sudden move puts Lawine on high alert.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102011_TextContext: (I wait and wait... but hear no response.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204065_TextContext: (I wait for Lawine to make her next move...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201072_TextContext: (The mountain of papers disappears, as if cut through by an invisible blade.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204276_TextContext: (In the end, she gives up, with great reluctance in her speech.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203040_TextContext: (I put a pair of sunglasses and a hat on Lawine.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203051_TextContext: (I shrug my shoulders, indicating that I don't know anything about this person.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101077_TextContext: (I gradually empty my cup as we continue chatting.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203075_TextContext: (The investigators in their blue and white uniforms leave us.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202058_TextContext: (Lawine shoots me a look out of the corner of her eye. This must be her way of asking for help...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203043_TextContext: (Filled with disbelief, Lawine lets me put the disguise on her.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204007_TextContext: (Although dressed in her combat suit, Lawine does not appear to be on alert.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204098_TextContext: (I have seen firsthand Lawine's down-to-earth attitude as a leader and her decisive, swift actions as an executor.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202027_TextContext: (Lawine's glare was as sharp as a blade)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128101024_TextContext: (As we speak, steam starts escaping from the kettle on Lawine's table.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128201002_TextContext: (I give the door a few cautious knocks.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204102_TextContext: (She seems slightly confused at the beginning, but as our eyes lock...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203044_TextContext: (The oversized sunglasses cover half of Lawine's face while the large hat hides her long azure hair.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203015_TextContext: (I follow Lawine into a secluded corner.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204031_TextContext: (Following Lawine's instruction, I change the way I hold the dagger, no longer looking like a common thug...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203406_TextContext: (I turn around and see a familiar person.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102003_TextContext: (We've admitted so many patients as of late that everyone's on constant overtime, but I don't want to disappoint Lawine by not showing up...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202069_TextContext: (I push forward to untie Lawine's bandage on my own.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203047_TextContext: (Standing close to Lawine, I can hear her breathing as she can hear mine. Both of us are equally nervous.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204107_TextContext: (No longer confused, she swings her dagger with great precision, as if dancing in the wind.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128204069_TextContext: (She spins her dagger before sheathing it as if she's lost the will to attack.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128202042_TextContext: (It's fully stocked with a variety of common medical supplies, along with a bunch of rubbing alcohol and bandages.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102012_TextContext: (Eh...? I check the patient list to make sure... that was the last one!)
AVGEvent_Lawine.128203059_TextContext: (Hearing a bizarre and twisted story about the pair, the investigators present are all moved to tears.)

AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101005_TextContext: ...Hi, are you here to pre-order the Surprises series of designs?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204057_TextContext: He documented and shared the Story of Harvest IV online.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101051_TextContext: Feel free to join me on my next adventure. We just may encounter something magical.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202086_TextContext: If you don't mind, let us help!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101032_TextContext: Do you not believe me? It's true! I was there during the 9th Street Explosion, and I even made the news headlines!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203021_TextContext: Excuse me, Navigator. Looks like I'm needed elsewhere.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202053_TextContext: Shall we go pick some berries? It may help with the creation of my next project.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201048_TextContext: I have to admit that I sometimes have trouble understanding my fellow artists.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102015_TextContext: Don't be nervous. It's not a formal occasion. I'm just inviting you to come over and have dinner with my parents and me...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201032_TextContext: No way! Few have ever been to that place...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201047_TextContext: No, I can't keep making stuff up... I'm feeling dizzy...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202063_TextContext: But you've arrived at an unfortunate time.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201062_TextContext: It would seem that she will soon be bringing yet another trophy home.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102056_TextContext: However, in order to make a unique pizza, one needs novel and interesting condiments...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204053_TextContext: No, this is important. The name of a painting is its very soul!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102023_TextContext: To showcase the Story of Harvest IV and to welcome you, we have prepared a lot of delicious dishes.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201020_TextContext: The Fun and Wonders exhibition is the perfect place to gather inspiration!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202015_TextContext: After several revisions and iterations, the latest version naturally retains the names of its predecessors.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101033_TextContext: By a stroke of luck amidst an unfortunate situation, I left the scene before the bomb went off because the breakfast I wanted was sold out.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204073_TextContext: Perhaps I could offer some advice?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204008_TextContext: The main piece of the exhibition hasn't been revealed, no?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202064_TextContext: It has been a rainy fall. Several of our sweet tea strawberry and coffee grape fields have been flooded...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203104_TextContext: The colors extracted from the berries are beautiful.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204064_TextContext: And he'd offer me a “life-changing opportunity.”
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201067_TextContext: Any designer worth their salt would be. This is a significant exhibition slash competition in the industry...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201006_TextContext: As if scrutinizing and contemplating the difficulties humanity is destined to face.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201030_TextContext: It depicts the legendary True Wilderness!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204061_TextContext: But I'm not sure if being famous is positive for me...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204076_TextContext: But this time, I would like to make my own decision!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101027_TextContext: But, yes, I'm serious about this, Navigator! I sent you a sincere invitation...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204070_TextContext: However, by accepting his offer, I would have to give up everything I have now.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204044_TextContext: As compensation, I'll bake a spicy strawberry pizza for you!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201034_TextContext: It's called Komos under the Starlight. It depicts an Area 88 evening when the stars are the brightest in the year. The dark building is Komos Tower, the tallest structure in Area 88.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201070_TextContext: You don't want to wait another three years, do you?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204065_TextContext: Are you going to accept the offer?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101028_TextContext: You seem to have underestimated one of your talents!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204037_TextContext: Did you trigger the fire alarm again?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102051_TextContext: Have you gotten over with what your sister said?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102018_TextContext: Why aren't you saying anything... Is that a no?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101036_TextContext: Are you saying that... the anonymous hero is actually...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203011_TextContext: Your relaxed yet confident demeanor... It's as if you've just walked right out of a Michelangelo painting!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204047_TextContext: Your room is exactly like last time...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204054_TextContext: How the hell do you even remember that name?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204056_TextContext: Do you remember the traveling photographer?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203073_TextContext: Do you remember why we came here in the first place?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201016_TextContext: Your expression and posture were quite evocative, and I couldn't resist... Heh-heh!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201061_TextContext: I should have known that something as unique and incomprehensible had to be the work of my sister!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204082_TextContext: My family will host an art seminar in a couple of weeks.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101023_TextContext: In the interest of safety, please remember to tidy up your room in the future.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204063_TextContext: The offer is about the same as what I make in several months... He also said, if I was willing, I could visit him in Neutroville...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204062_TextContext: I've just had a call from a wealthy businessman from Neutroville. He told me he really appreciated my work and wanted to purchase it.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101049_TextContext: Don't be so surprised. Only by observing and feeling this beautiful world can one inadvertently generate creative inspiration.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203046_TextContext: Forget about them. Take shelter now!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204059_TextContext: So, that's what you meant by “famous.”
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201015_TextContext: It's you, Navigator... What was I doing? I was recording my latest inspiration.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204068_TextContext: It must be cool to work as a top designer in a metropolis, right?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202035_TextContext: Materials... Yes, that is what we'll do.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201081_TextContext: By the way... we still have a couple of exhibition halls to visit, right?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202089_TextContext: Also, I'm happy to do manual labor such as moving items!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201010_TextContext: It's such a pity that the muscles are too relaxed to highlight pain and twitching...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203075_TextContext: But what does this have anything to do with helping everyone?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101034_TextContext: I heard that an investigator worked with two good Samaritans to solve the case...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101026_TextContext: Why did I choose you? I should have asked you to be my medical consultant instead? We could discuss that in the future...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102017_TextContext: I know you're pretty busy. That's why I picked your day off and confirmed your schedule with Miss Celestia.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204042_TextContext: Uh, I don't think I'm that lucky...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201013_TextContext: Ah! Where did you come from?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204028_TextContext: What? You want a picture of me?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201023_TextContext: Wow. Would you look at the composition, palette, and mood... It's absolutely flawless!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201005_TextContext: Wow. The perfect angle of looking down and those deep eyes that seem to see through everything...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203100_TextContext: Hah-hah. You're looking just like a clown!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202062_TextContext: That's right! Our berries are known for their unique taste. Eating them feels just like drinking milk tea.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202073_TextContext: Hah, storms don't quench our enthusiasm!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101048_TextContext: Hah, the answer is simple... Going out together!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101020_TextContext: Hah, I stepped on my unfinished draft from yesterday. I was wondering where it went...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102043_TextContext: It's the truth. I had Mom give me some special training. I'm sure it's delicious!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202066_TextContext: I'm afraid that this year's bonfire celebration is going to attract far fewer tourists than in previous years.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202055_TextContext: Hmm, something's not right. The berry bushes should have borne fruit by now...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102045_TextContext: So, how is it? I've finally made a pizza that is both beautiful and delicious!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102052_TextContext: Well... Using food as a metaphor... in the world of art, most people would rather become a plate of noble white truffle.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203085_TextContext: Mm-hmm. We can't miss out on such fine materials!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102059_TextContext: I'm counting on you, then, consultant!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204085_TextContext: Heh... You'll see when the time comes!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201077_TextContext: Alright, since you say so, consultant...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101030_TextContext: Heh, yes, we're quite alike in that regard.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202044_TextContext: I'll leave the consulting to you, then!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102022_TextContext: Hah... Got it! Then you definitely can't miss tonight's dinner!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202014_TextContext: Because it is the third iteration of the Story of Harvest!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203016_TextContext: Thanks to everyone's hard work, tonight's Early Spring, Midsummer, Golden Fall, and Warm Winter - The Night of Berry Harvest Exhibition will surely attract many visitors!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202065_TextContext: Here in the Old Earth Scenic Area, we don't have artificially controllable weather systems. Our way of life means we're destined to be at the mercy of the weather...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204079_TextContext: Before I make a final decision...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203065_TextContext: Destroyed before revealing its full potential... I do not accept such an ending...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102024_TextContext: The address is... here. Call me when you arrive, and I'll come down to get you!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203027_TextContext: Just a few clouds, that's all. Get back to work. We still have a lot to do.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101024_TextContext: Thanks for the reminder... I didn't think a messy room could result in safety hazards.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203044_TextContext: Everyone, take shelter from the rain!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203054_TextContext: Now is no time to mourn, everyone. Let's count the number of berries we've lost.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204022_TextContext: Can we find everyone's berries in the painting?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203026_TextContext: What's with the weather? Wasn't today forecast to be sunny?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202007_TextContext: That's strange; I don't see my work on the list of winners.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102055_TextContext: Her boring, adult statements don't get to me anymore. It's whatever.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202032_TextContext: I wish I could get back to a good mood... I'm in no state to create art.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201009_TextContext: Suffering and contemplation would be a great theme for a fine piece.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201079_TextContext: Shall we consider this competition our first design project together, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203077_TextContext: Are they not fine materials for creation?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204051_TextContext: It's called Sweet and Dreamy, Liberty and Longing, and Colorful Berries under the Fluffy Clouds: Protecting the Most Beautiful Story of Harvest of Strinova with the Paintbrush IV!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204011_TextContext: R-Right... Everyone, the next piece is the focus of this exhibition!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202078_TextContext: By the way, please try these.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202036_TextContext: For a designer, the only thing as important as creating art is gathering materials...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202071_TextContext: It's like if I were to spend a long time painting a piece, only for the competition to be canceled or coffee to be spilled on the canvas...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202077_TextContext: If you'll excuse me, I still have to help organize the party...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202031_TextContext: I'm just slightly at loss, like it's hard to breathe... Ugh... I hate this feeling...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202045_TextContext: And I'll leave it to you to lead the way!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204036_TextContext: N-Navigator, a terrible thing has happened!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203006_TextContext: We need more berries for Warm Winter, Navigator. Could you fetch some for me?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204083_TextContext: As my art consultant and co-designer of the Story of Harvest, Navigator, you must not miss it!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203039_TextContext: You've just created a magnificent piece of art, Navigator!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102042_TextContext: Look, Navigator, I designed this pizza. I made sure that the colors matched the composition while also considering its taste and texture...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102039_TextContext: What are you still standing there, Navigator? Have a seat.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203093_TextContext: S-Stop laughing, Navigator... It's normal for an artist's face to be covered in “paint”!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101044_TextContext: What separates me from all the other artists in the world, Navigator, is my ability to discover and design unique art amidst troubles and accidents.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201024_TextContext: Look at this, Navigator. Can you guess what this painting depicts?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202005_TextContext: According to the latest notice, Navigator, the results will be announced online. Let's check the website...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201042_TextContext: O-Of course, I do. This is my home ground...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202046_TextContext: You got it! I know the place like the back of my hand.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101047_TextContext: What exactly does an art consultant do?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201087_TextContext: T-Take that away! Pineapple pizzas could never bring me inspiration. They are a desecration of pizzas!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204031_TextContext: Go on, then. After all, you're the star of the exhibition!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201043_TextContext: Look at the strong contrast of the two colors and the highly symmetrical composition, each occupying half of the canvas...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201044_TextContext: Surely, the artist wishes to convey... such strong emotions, right?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202070_TextContext: I understand the struggle of seeing your hard work go to waste...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202076_TextContext: We will showcase the town's best berries and try to boost this year's sales for one last time!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203058_TextContext: Our fruit is usually sold to other towns. Soaked berries are not suitable for long-distance transport as they spoil quickly.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102058_TextContext: I'll fulfill my duties as your consultant.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201054_TextContext: Let's find out who the artist is...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202037_TextContext: I happen to know a nice place. I've been there a couple of times for sketching and painting en plein air.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102038_TextContext: The navigator and I have resolved a great number of crises and incidents, creating remarkable artistic achievements in the process.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202088_TextContext: I have experience in planning exhibitions and arranging artwork at Cloudscape Gallery. I could bring some creativity and surprises to the bonfire celebration.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204019_TextContext: Has it got something of mine as well?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202008_TextContext: I've scrolled from the first page to the last...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201075_TextContext: I look forward to seeing your work.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101040_TextContext: I find your trait of frequently being involved in troubles quite valuable!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203080_TextContext: How could I have missed that... I can make art with the unsellable berries!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102050_TextContext: I guess this is my way of creating - drawing inspiration from ordinary objects!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203033_TextContext: I'm going to count from three... Three!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204027_TextContext: (I'm a traveling photographer. I find your work quite creative! May I take a photo of you?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202087_TextContext: I am a designer from Cloudscape Gallery. This is my art consultant.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102049_TextContext: Many of my works, just like this painting, were born in the mountains, fields, and ordinary moments of life.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203057_TextContext: I know you meant well, but I'm afraid that we can't do that, Maddelena.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102054_TextContext: I know, I know. If my sister heard that, she'd probably call me a “naive kid full of impractical thoughts”...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202034_TextContext: You once told me that if a designer isn't creating, she's on her way to gather materials...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204030_TextContext: What should I do, Navigator? I'm not used to this kind of situation.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201050_TextContext: I prefer that kind of art.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101045_TextContext: If you team up with me, we'll surely discover all sorts of fun and interesting things!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202017_TextContext: I can't find it. I can't find it...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203055_TextContext: I'm sorry, guys... Can you not salvage the berries to be sold?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202061_TextContext: I hear it's sweet, like milk tea.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201058_TextContext: Is that a relative of yours?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204020_TextContext: Yes! In the bottom left corner. The small, red one that looks like it's watered with milk tea. That's your sweet tea strawberry.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202075_TextContext: If you're free, try to make it to the bonfire celebration in a few days!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201083_TextContext: Food can sometimes bring unexpected inspiration.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202091_TextContext: With you professionals helping us, I'm sure the party will go smoothly.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202019_TextContext: I thought I could win this time...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204016_TextContext: Look, Ms. Julia! The thing in the middle, black with a hint of purple, like latte art, is the coffee grape you grow.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101013_TextContext: Eh? It's you, Navigator. Had I known you were coming, I would've tidied up...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201076_TextContext: It's a fine chance to put the materials you've gathered today to work.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202043_TextContext: Sure. I'm your consultant, after all.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101035_TextContext: Well, one of the good Samaritans happens to be...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101031_TextContext: Like running into explosions or finding feral bulls while gathering materials...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204078_TextContext: I can't always rely on you, Navigator. I have to be as reliable as you every now and then!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101022_TextContext: I'm fine. Falling is inevitable in life, right?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204023_TextContext: That's right. I've painted them all!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202052_TextContext: Berries are the local specialty. During my previous visits, some berry fields were open to tourists.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201045_TextContext: And... besides the composition, palette, symbolism, and... Uh. I mean...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102037_TextContext: Mom, Dad, this is the navigator I told you about. My amazing art consultant!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102016_TextContext: I told my parents about your deeds, they're eager to meet you!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204006_TextContext: Especially the eyes. They're as bright as my grapes!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201065_TextContext: Are you also interested in the competition, Maddelena?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203018_TextContext: How should we arrange the exhibits for Golden Fall, Miss Maddelena? Could you come over and have a look?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203070_TextContext: This is not the time to give up, Maddelena.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204021_TextContext: Martina and Luca, I've also painted your raspberries!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203081_TextContext: I can recreate them in another form!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204043_TextContext: It's hard to explain it over the phone. Could you come over, please?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203052_TextContext: Gone to waste. Everything has gone to waste! We're not going to sell a single berry now!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101039_TextContext: You are exactly the kind of legendary consultant I need! One that's capable of causing accidents and surviving perils!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101037_TextContext: Good on you, Navigator. Other than the Grove Bank Incident, you've also taken care of the 9th Street Explosion case... Wait, you helped fend off the feral bulls in Windy Town too?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203020_TextContext: One second. I’ll be right over!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204058_TextContext: The Hand of da Vinci, the famous art show, reposted it, and it went on to be reported by mainstream media!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201068_TextContext: And it only takes place once every three years!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102053_TextContext: As for me... I'd probably just want to be a warm, affordable pizza.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204069_TextContext: I could meet outstanding fellow designers and see with my own eyes first-class designs. Perhaps then, I'll have a better chance of outdoing my sister...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201053_TextContext: Colors... could be discarded? Are artists of suprematism this liberated in their way of thinking?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201049_TextContext: Art should be understandable and appreciable. It should be able to bring joy to critics as well as common folks...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101041_TextContext: As much as I hate to admit it...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204071_TextContext: It's really difficult to make a decision, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203053_TextContext: If only I could have saved a few more berries...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203067_TextContext: If only I could do something to help... If only I could find a way to restore the berries...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203059_TextContext: Merchants are not willing to take that risk. Several who had planned to purchase berries during the celebration had already left.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201033_TextContext: It's time to reveal the answer: This is my classmate's work, and a candidate for this year's Aspiring Artist Award.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201040_TextContext: So... Have you any idea what this painting is about?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102046_TextContext: By the way, I've been thinking about what happened last time...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203015_TextContext: By the way, the bonfire celebration is tonight. I can't wait!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101025_TextContext: By the way, Navigator, have you made a decision on becoming my art consultant?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201082_TextContext: I said I'd take you to see the Waterfall of Joy and the Coffee Fountain, didn't I?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202050_TextContext: By the way, it's almost time for the bonfire celebration of the Fall Harvest Festival.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201017_TextContext: Please don't be offended. As a designer, if I'm not creating, I'm on the way to gathering materials...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203012_TextContext: Please stay still. Let me capture this moment!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204048_TextContext: Please ignore the details... Take a look at this, Navigator. It's the Strinovan Popularity Rankings!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203031_TextContext: Thank you for your patience, everyone. The bonfire celebration is about to start!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204000_PrologueTitle: The Change, the Unknown, and the Crossroads
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203014_TextContext: Thanks, Navigator. I've got one more piece of useful material now.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101046_TextContext: If we're lucky, we may even make names for ourselves in the art world!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101038_TextContext: A-And... You were present at every chaotic and troublesome incident I experienced!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204017_TextContext: I-Is this really our grape? It's much prettier in the painting!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201057_TextContext: The artist is also a Leary.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204055_TextContext: It's a simple name... in my opinion.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202060_TextContext: I've heard that name before... They're one of Berrytown's signature berries, right?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203105_TextContext: I must make good use of such precious and rare materials...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201018_TextContext: This is exactly why we're here today.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204025_TextContext: Excuse me, miss, is this your work?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203095_TextContext: It's like the juice has got springs. It's hard to control it. Give it a try if you don't believe me!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203064_TextContext: Everyone put their hearts and souls to it. We all worked very hard to complete this work of art...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202012_TextContext: Is this the name of your piece?!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204050_TextContext: The editor was so careless... They got the name wrong.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204005_TextContext: The Navigator Holding a Basket of Berries depicts such a vivid picture...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102048_TextContext: The Story of Harvest IV is a testament to our friendship... I wish for you to keep it, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204007_TextContext: This piece was actually inspired by my consultant and Michelangelo...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204060_TextContext: The attention this painting has brought should be able to help the townspeople sell more berries!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204081_TextContext: I want to show this painting to my parents!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202081_TextContext: These are our home-grown sweet tea strawberries. I managed to save them before the storm. Have fun in our little town!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204067_TextContext: This is the first time in my life I've been offered such an opportunity...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201073_TextContext: A chance to compete with my sister...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203010_TextContext: What inspiration have you got now?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101000_PrologueTitle: The Artist in Pursuit of Accidents
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102014_TextContext: So... About the Leary family art seminar I told you about that last...
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101043_TextContext: Don't get me wrong. All I'm saying is that you and I would get along well.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202040_TextContext: The place is called Berrytown. It's located in the Old Earth Scenic Area east of Strian, not far from the Astral Sanctuary branch.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202072_TextContext: That would be a huge blow to an artist! More heartbreaking than losing in a competition!
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202057_TextContext: Hiya... Are you here to pick sweet tea strawberries?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202038_TextContext: That place is an endless supply of creative materials.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202051_TextContext: The townspeople must be busy harvesting the berries and preparing for the celebration.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101006_TextContext: The door's open. Please come in... Sorry, I can't come to the door right now.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101029_TextContext: Are you referring to some kind of hidden talent?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203063_TextContext: Is this the end of the bonfire celebration?
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202025_TextContext: (“You're like a fledgling, hiding in the comfort of your nest!”)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204049_TextContext: (“Shock! A stunning painting made with berries - Sweet and Dreamy: Story of Harvest IV!”)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202026_TextContext: (“You don't have what it takes to be an artist!”)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201052_TextContext: (“That is, to discard all unnecessary colors. To hell with pointless arguments!”)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202058_TextContext: (A man in a straw hat walks over from the berry field.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201038_TextContext: (Before me is a legendary painting called Whitest White, Blackest Black. There is nothing on the half-white and half-black canvas.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203040_TextContext: (Standing next to me, Maddelena is deeply fascinated by the bonfire.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201078_TextContext: (A golden hue flashes over her lens.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203108_TextContext: (Not wanting to disturb Maddelena, I quietly leave her room.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201007_TextContext: (Not far from where I stand, a girl in a beret observes me with interest as if reviewing her own work.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203028_TextContext: (As evening approaches, preparations have finally been completed.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102008_TextContext: (Trying to alleviate my hunger, I plan to chug it.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202023_TextContext: (Why can I not even win once against my sister?)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102063_TextContext: (Afterward, I have more slices of the pizza she made for me, looking at our Story of Harvest IV...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201084_TextContext: (Afterward, Maddelena and I visit the creative dining area, enjoying the Waterfall of Joy and the Coffee Fountain as planned.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203091_TextContext: (Perhaps accidentally set to maximum power, the juicer bounces up and down, spraying juice all over Maddelena!)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202093_TextContext: (We help the man organize the bonfire celebration.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101002_TextContext: (I visit her at the address on her name card.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203030_TextContext: (The crowd gathers around the bonfire about to be lit, waiting for the start of the town's grandest celebration.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202002_TextContext: (The closing ceremony of Fun and Wonders takes place today when the results of the submissions are announced.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203066_TextContext: (There are tears in her eyes as if it has just rained.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102002_TextContext: (I am working overtime at Astral Sanctuary sorting medical reports on my day off...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204046_TextContext: (The anxious Maddelena gets up behind a messy pile of drafts, giving me a sense of déjà vu.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204015_TextContext: (But what separates the painting from reality is the colorful berries on the green fields shimmering with a new light bestowed upon by the girl.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201085_TextContext: (But as I ask Maddelena to try the pineapple durian pizza...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202095_TextContext: (As a reward, the man gives us a basket full of berries.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101001_TextContext: (A painter has invited me to become her consultant, helping her find artistic inspiration.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203083_TextContext: (Maddelena finally brightens up as if standing under a warm ray of sunshine.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203032_TextContext: (I happen to draw a lot to light the bonfire. With everyone's eyes on me, I walk toward the pile of wood holding a torch.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202022_TextContext: (The last impromptu creation contest of Windy Town. The alumni design competition the year before. And this one. I've lost to my sister every single time...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203029_TextContext: (The overcast sky does not dampen the enthusiasm of the participants.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203019_TextContext: (On the other side, a woman eagerly calls for Maddelena.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102027_TextContext: (However, the thought of having dinner with her parents... makes me slightly nervous.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101003_TextContext: (Her name card reads: Maddelena Leary, designer in sename cardh of fun and surprises.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201035_TextContext: (After listening to her enthusiastic introduction, I move to the next painting.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201004_TextContext: (Maddelena mentioned that the exhibition would feature designs such as the Waterfall of Joy and the Coffee Fountain...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201022_TextContext: (Maddelena and I enter the Impressionism and Abstract Art exhibition hall, surrounded by colorful, styled paintings.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204034_TextContext: (Back at Astral Sanctuary, I finish up my work before my vacation...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203103_TextContext: (In laughter, we try to tame the juice that has gone wild, extracting the colorful juice of various berries.
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102025_TextContext: (In laughter, Maddelena hangs up the phone.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204087_TextContext: (Deep in thought, she contemplates the future of her career and life.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202024_TextContext: (Must I remain dim under the brilliance of my sister's?)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102030_TextContext: (At the entrance of the residential complex, I see from afar a girl in bright clothes and a ponytail waving at me with a silly smile.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203048_TextContext: (Amidst the panicked crowd and the pouring rain, the bonfire celebration comes to an abrupt end.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204033_TextContext: (Amidst laughter, shutter clicks, and the endless fields, our journey to Berrytown comes to an end.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203089_TextContext: (At the guesthouse, Maddelena starts creating with a juicer she has obtained from who knows where.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202074_TextContext: (Admitting the tense atmosphere, the man laughs heartily.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202094_TextContext: (Under the blazing sun, we walk back and forth between the damp fields and the mud, sweat soaking our clothes.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102061_TextContext: (The candlelight illuminates a warm orange hue on her blushing cheek and fluff, cute homewear.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201051_TextContext: (A flattering comment is written underneath the painting: “Artists have always debated over palette. The artist of this piece, however, offers a perfect solution...”)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203024_TextContext: (With the start of the bonfire celebration around the corner, everyone is working tirelessly to make the final arrangements.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203109_TextContext: (Filled with colors and inspiration, a beautiful night passes...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203069_TextContext: (In sadness and silence, I look at the scattered berries...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203043_TextContext: (As if the sky has been split open, torrential rain pours down on us, striking the bonfire celebration like a sharp knife.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201080_TextContext: (Her amber eyes sparkle, just like the sunlight outside.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201008_TextContext: (She mutters to herself while casually sketching something with the pen in her hand.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102047_TextContext: (She leans over and whispers to me as if sharing a secret between the two of us.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201064_TextContext: (She stares at the painting for a little while, her eyes fainty revealing a sense of longing and anticipation.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203086_TextContext: (Holding my hand, she runs to the townspeople with excitement.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203003_TextContext: (She helps plan a separate berry exhibition area, dividing it into four themes based on the colors and flavors of the fruit: Early Spring, Midsummer, Golden Fall, and Warm Winter.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201086_TextContext: (Her expression fills with shock and anger as if someone has placed wriggling worms on her plate.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202011_TextContext: (She has entered the following names: Sweet and Dreamy, Liberty and Longing, and Colorful Berries under the Fluffy Clouds: The Most Beautiful Story of Harvest of Strinova III!)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102033_TextContext: (She welcomes me with joy, as if greeting her own family...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204032_TextContext: (I shove the shy Maddelena back in front of the camera and the smiling crowd.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203107_TextContext: (Stroke after stroke, she starts painting the wonderful world in her mind on the white canvas.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203041_TextContext: (Suddenly, as if the thick clouds have also been lit, a flash of lightning tears through the sky.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203112_TextContext: (I see a smile on her colorful face as if she has finally reclaimed the lost colors.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102007_TextContext: (Though the manufacturer still kept subtle amounts of strange ingredients, such as tuna...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102040_TextContext: (Already seated, Maddelena points to me the seat next to her)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203051_TextContext: (The celebration was ravaged by the storm. Judging from the expressions of the villagers cleaning up, the storm never ended.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202004_TextContext: (As the exhibition comes to an end, the exhibits are gradually removed from Cloudscape Gallery. The place seems extra desolate today.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203025_TextContext: (Think clouds begin to accumulate in the azure sky.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202016_TextContext: (I am curious about the full names of the Story of Harvest I and the Story of Harvest II...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102064_TextContext: (The warmth in my heart lingers for a long time.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101008_TextContext: (I can't help but cough... There is a pungent smell of paint in the air.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204080_TextContext: (Maddelena's eyes widen as if she has suddenly thought of something.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201037_TextContext: (Suddenly, I feel dizzy, as if everything had gone dark.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203042_TextContext: (The impatient clouds have finally started a celebration of their own.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203087_TextContext: (We purchase a batch of unsellable berries from the townspeople.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102035_TextContext: (As the door is opened, the aroma of the food wafts over.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203007_TextContext: (I pick up a basket of berries.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201039_TextContext: (I hear this piece is the favorite of the Fun and Wonders jury.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203002_TextContext: (Over the next couple of days, Maddelena and I help the townspeople prepare for the bonfire celebration.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202039_TextContext: (As Maddelena talks about this place, her amber eyes slightly light up.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204077_TextContext: (The once indecisive girl stands confidently, her eyes sparkling with determination.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202018_TextContext: (Maddelena sighs as she puts her phone down.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202049_TextContext: (The crowded town is filled with a lively, festive atmosphere that can be felt all the way from the fields in the suburbs.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102006_TextContext: (Starlight Coffee has been upgraded to version .36.9.87.66, greatly improving its taste and flavor.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202083_TextContext: (As the man turns around and leaves, Maddelena blinks at me.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202056_TextContext: (Looking at the fruitless berry brushes, Maddelena frowns.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202068_TextContext: (Looking at the frustrated man, Maddelena starts to seem sad again.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203056_TextContext: (Looking at the berries soaked in puddles or scattered over the ground, Maddelena cautiously asks.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204003_TextContext: (Maddelena has invited the townspeople to attend a small, temporary outdoor exhibition.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203060_TextContext: (The townspeople get back to cleaning. The atmosphere remains somber.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201003_TextContext: (I arrive at the place Maddelena and I agreed to meet to visit a creative designed exhibition called Fun and Wonders.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101012_TextContext: (A drowsy girl slowly gets up from behind the desk with smudges of paint on her petite face.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203099_TextContext: (The juice inside is traveling in a parabolic path toward me...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102044_TextContext: (As she speaks, Maddelena cuts me a small, steaming slice of pizza.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201019_TextContext: (As she speaks, Maddelena takes out two tickets.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203110_TextContext: (The next morning, I visit Maddelena in her room, checking on her creation...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203038_TextContext: (As the torch gets close, the stacked woodpile slowly lights up as if a bright star has finally awoken from the darkness.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202009_TextContext: (The anxious Maddelena laboriously types a long string of characters on her phone...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204086_TextContext: (With a sly smile, the girl falls silent.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204012_TextContext: (Maddelena takes out a painting from her backpack, carefully placing it on the only empty easel.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202096_TextContext: (Maddelena shows our reward to me as if holding a trophy, her smile finally returning.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202021_TextContext: (Maddelena hangs her head in utter dejection, her eyes brimming with sadness as if she were a fledgling that has just broken her wings.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203106_TextContext: (Taking out her paintbrush and palette, Maddelena starts mixing the colors.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202054_TextContext: (Carrying a small fruit basket she brought, Maddelena walks toward a berry field.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203068_TextContext: (Maddelena hangs her head in frustration, the light in her eyes dimming for the first time.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201072_TextContext: (Maddelena lifts up her head, having realized the importance.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203092_TextContext: (Maddelena's face is instantly splattered like a palette.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203078_TextContext: (Maddelena's eyes brighten as if she has just come to a realization.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201056_TextContext: (Maddelena's eyes widen, as if she has been electrocuted.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203009_TextContext: (Her eyes widened, Maddelena pulls out her sketchbook from her backpack.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204004_TextContext: (A few easels are set up at the exhibition, mainly displaying records of her inspiration from Berrytown.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204014_TextContext: (The scenery depicted in the painting is no different from that of Berrytown's...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201026_TextContext: (On a blue-purple canvas, there is a huge black structure reflecting a swirling galaxy.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107101009_TextContext: (There are drafts scattered all over the floor, but I cannot seem to find the host...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204002_TextContext: (Outside Berrytown, after the bonfire celebration of the Fall Harvest Festival.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204010_TextContext: (I gently remind Maddelena, who is a bit carried away with pride.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203004_TextContext: (On the day of the bonfire celebration, I see Maddelena running back and forth between every area.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202047_TextContext: (After a few hours, Maddelena and I arrive at Berrytown.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201011_TextContext: (A slight flaw in the otherwise perfect material causes her to sigh.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203023_TextContext: (I continue to help organize the celebration.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203050_TextContext: (The next day, Maddelena and I return to the bonfire celebration site.)
