AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202079_TextContext: (The man takes out a few large plump strawberries from his basket.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102036_TextContext: (Although the dishes are ordinary home-cooked food, the bright candlelight and the hosts' smiles convey the unique warmth of this family.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202003_TextContext: (Maddelena has asked me to meet with her and wait for the announcement.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201059_TextContext: (Having heard my question, Maddelena slowly comes to her senses, as if she has just had an out-of-body experience.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203022_TextContext: (The hopeful Maddelena runs over to the other area as she finishes speaking.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102060_TextContext: (As she finishes speaking, Maddelena glances at her parents, who are trying to hold their laughter, and shyly falls silent.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202067_TextContext: (The man sighs multiple times as he speaks.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202010_TextContext: (I get closer to take a look...)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102005_TextContext: (I get up for a cup of coffee.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107201021_TextContext: (I follow the excited Maddelena into the museum.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107102034_TextContext: (Following Maddelena as she prances up the stairs, I keep worrying that she may fall.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202082_TextContext: (The strawberries shine like gems under the golden sun.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203017_TextContext: (Only Maddelena could come up with such a unique name.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204026_TextContext: (The man with a camera keeps taking photos of the lively exhibition.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203049_TextContext: (The rain lasts for the entire night.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107204013_TextContext: (Painted with colors of berries, the piece overflows with the girl's whimsy.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203047_TextContext: (Barely lit up, the fire is extinguished by the rain in an instant.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203111_TextContext: (Through the door left ajar, I see the artist sleeping soundly next to a painting.)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107202027_TextContext: (Is... Is my sister right about me?)
AVGEvent_Maddelena.107203098_TextContext: (Operating at high speed, the juice spins as if it's dancing on its own.)

AVGEvent_Michel.101204019_TextContext: ...Stop staring at me. There's nothing on my face... Fine. I'll tell you the truth!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202050_TextContext: ...Moreover, if I were to keep acting recklessly and breaking the rules, I might end up being fired...
AVGEvent_Michel.101204015_TextContext: ...Uh, I can't hide it from you, can I...
AVGEvent_Michel.101202012_TextContext: ...Okay, okay. I can't hide anything from you.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202024_TextContext: I suffered a lot of consequences the last time I had to work with you! You repeatedly ignored rules, acted rashly, and tarnished the image of investigators. You should have been suspended long ago!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202015_TextContext: Unsurprisingly, my superiors punished me with dozens of pages of written apologies... But this time, they told me that if I were to continue breaking the rules...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102028_TextContext: Through video games, I learned to think like a gamer without realizing it, even applying the traits to my work... As a result, it made me different, subjecting me to ostracism from colleagues and criticisms from superiors.
AVGEvent_Michel.101204035_TextContext: Whoever it is, bring it on!
AVGEvent_Michel.51101002_TextContext: No. I must get it together...
AVGEvent_Michel.101203061_TextContext: Don't panic. Get to the exit!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201036_TextContext: Fret not, for we have another chance! You're doing well for a beginner, partner!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202055_TextContext: Before I do that, we have to bid a proper farewell to the past. Would you like to play one more round mano a mano, partner?
AVGEvent_Michel.101202004_TextContext: Worries, be gone! O' might breeze of the sea, help me forget the pain of writing letters of apology!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203050_TextContext: I'm also the super gamer Michele!
AVGEvent_Michel.51101011_TextContext: You're here to hang out with me, right. I'm sorry, partner...
AVGEvent_Michel.101204012_TextContext: That must be why I invited you here...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102026_TextContext: Just like Mighty Meow, he'd protect me, wielding his giant sword. And I, like the shield-holding Pawtector, would safely hide behind him.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202035_TextContext: Even though he is now a wounded man, he'll always be a hero to me!
AVGEvent_Michel.101102003_TextContext: Are you interested in unlocking the secret map of Elmond on this fine day, partner?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201019_TextContext: What are you looking at, partner?
AVGEvent_Michel.101202040_TextContext: Did you know, partner, that putting on the badge as an investigator was my proudest moment in life...
AVGEvent_Michel.101202002_TextContext: Partner, did you know that when you're feeling gloomy, you can come to the back and let the sea breeze carry all your troubles away?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201030_TextContext: In this game, partner, you and I will control Mighty Meow, the dragon-slaying swordsman, and Pawtector, the girl with a giant shield, respectively. Our objective is to defeat all of the monsters invading the Kingdom of Light.
AVGEvent_Michel.101201037_TextContext: Watch out, partner. The dragon is casting poisonous mist. Roll and get away from the area in front of you!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204021_TextContext: Honestly, partner, you have a great knack in reading between the lines and understanding people's feelings, almost as good as a professional investigator.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102034_TextContext: These cats have taken a liking to you, partner! They see you as one of their own now!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201057_TextContext: Besides exciting adventure games, partner, I also know a lot of interesting things. I'll show you around the next time we meet.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102040_TextContext: However, I can't manage that on my own...
AVGEvent_Michel.101204023_TextContext: However, I dismantled the prop shield without prior authorization and failed to strictly follow the lock-down order, which constitutes a serious breach of discipline, potentially leading to unforeseen crisis.
AVGEvent_Michel.101101011_TextContext: But that's the person I am. I aspire to be a gamer-style investigator!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202047_TextContext: What's wrong with being a gamer?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201042_TextContext: As a super gamer, I'm not going to give up that easily!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203090_TextContext: As an investigator, you have to be mindful of your appearance.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202005_TextContext: Did you break the rules again?
AVGEvent_Michel.101204041_TextContext: After all, you're my coolest gaming buddy!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202027_TextContext: You're with her? Being partners with such a reckless fool will only get you in trouble!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201021_TextContext: You have the limited Sword of Light!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201023_TextContext: You know the sword? Are you also a...
AVGEvent_Michel.101203078_TextContext: I'm just glad you weren't hurt.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102018_TextContext: You've noticed, too? They're named after the two protagonists of No. 1's Superheroes of Justice. In fact, my father, the hero of the Sentinel Bureau, is the one most closely connected to the game.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102031_TextContext: Do you have an answer now?
AVGEvent_Michel.51101012_TextContext: I mean, look at the mountain of written apologies next to me. I'm afraid that I'm not going to...
AVGEvent_Michel.101203015_TextContext: Don't try to distract me! I won't fall for it!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202013_TextContext: So... during my last mission, I broke the rules and took a shortcut to ambush the enemy.
AVGEvent_Michel.101101002_TextContext: Let me introduce myself again. My name is Michele. My hobbies are cats and video games...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102047_TextContext: It's settled, then! The protagonists for the next Superheroes of Justice installment shall be the amazing navigator and the incredible investigator!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203003_TextContext: Are you ready... for the final showdown?
AVGEvent_Michel.101203052_TextContext: What other investigators can't think of, I can... Got it!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203022_TextContext: 30 Caprivi Street... Wait a second. That's...
AVGEvent_Michel.101202008_TextContext: Impressive, partner! Can you read my mind?
AVGEvent_Michel.101101020_TextContext: I was slightly worried that you might not be into video games...
AVGEvent_Michel.101201035_TextContext: Damn it! It interrupted our cast!
AVGEvent_Michel.101102027_TextContext: When he unfortunately contracted collapse syndrome, I lost my only gaming buddy...
AVGEvent_Michel.101201007_TextContext: You're here, partner! I've been waiting for you!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204003_TextContext: Right, why did I ask you to come... Please remind me. I've been rather forgetful as of late.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203039_TextContext: Investigator Michele calling HQ. There are civilians trapped at the site. Please advise! Over.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203035_TextContext: Come in, HQ. This is Investigator Michele, ID 44061. I've arrived at the erosion flow location. Please advise! Over.
AVGEvent_Michel.51101001_TextContext: Ah, I'm so tired. I can fall asleep any second now...
AVGEvent_Michel.101201052_TextContext: Your mindset is just like that of mine!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203179_TextContext: Looks like our match has to be postponed.
AVGEvent_Michel.101204022_TextContext: So... Since the erosion flow incident, my superiors partially recognized my effort, saying that it was commendable of me to prioritize the safety of the public and carry out the evacuation.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102046_TextContext: I would like to amend my wish: I wish for both of us to be models for the sequel...
AVGEvent_Michel.51101010_TextContext: Ha-ha. You're my partner, all right. Thanks to you, I'm half-awake now.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202036_TextContext: Ha-ha! You would call a cripple a hero?
AVGEvent_Michel.101202006_TextContext: Come on. Let's not talk about that here...
AVGEvent_Michel.101201054_TextContext: Wait a second. Have I finally found a like-minded friend?
AVGEvent_Michel.101102045_TextContext: Heh-heh... You know me too well.
AVGEvent_Michel.101201048_TextContext: Heh-heh... This is my gamer's mindset - choosing the shortest path and finding the quickest solution. Not everyone understands me...
AVGEvent_Michel.101201047_TextContext: I'm exhausted. We've finally beat the game...
AVGEvent_Michel.101101006_TextContext: You don't know, do you? That must be what it means to hide one's light under a bushel.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203006_TextContext: Humph. Looks like my chance of winning is pretty high!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204033_TextContext: Hmm... You're right, partner. It must be the courier! And definitely not my superiors!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204010_TextContext: Hmm... That's right. The latest installment of Superheroes of Justice will be released today! I pre-ordered the disc at Hermes Mall last week.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203082_TextContext: Oh. The other investigators have arrived. I have to brief them!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204009_TextContext: Yes, that's it! I remember now!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203020_TextContext: Come on! Now of all times...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102032_TextContext: Yes, I have an answer of my own... One which I'll only share with you.
AVGEvent_Michel.101101004_TextContext: Heh, you would never guess it in a hundred years, but that person is actually...
AVGEvent_Michel.101203073_TextContext: In hindsight, that was a bit scary.
AVGEvent_Michel.101201010_TextContext: It's the result of my reasonable energy management. By properly combining work and rest, I'm always full of energy!
AVGEvent_Michel.101102010_TextContext: So, this is my secret base!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201028_TextContext: When I was 12, dad gave me a model of Mighty Meow's weapon on my birthday... Time flies. That was a long time ago.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102020_TextContext: My father worked on the frontline for years before coming to Strinova. He was invited to join Painting Utopia Security as a hero.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102025_TextContext: Before I found out about that, I only saw him as my gaming buddy... He was always busy when I was a child, but he'd play games with me and my robo battlecats whenever he was free...
AVGEvent_Michel.101202046_TextContext: I'm going to be sad to lose my gaming buddy...
AVGEvent_Michel.101101022_TextContext: It's been a while since I played videos with other people at home. Do you think an adventure involving both an investigator and a navigator would be particularly interesting?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201008_TextContext: I don't think I've ever seen you tired, Michele!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201040_TextContext: I'm sorry, partner. I shouldn't have started with my ultimate as soon as the battle started... My bad.
AVGEvent_Michel.101204048_TextContext: Let's enjoy these cute cat paw cookies as we play the game!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202023_TextContext: Don't you address me as your junior!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202043_TextContext: My dad, who is also an investigator... He was wounded during the Port Euler operation, leaving me to uphold what the badge represents.
AVGEvent_Michel.101201033_TextContext: Now! Use the Sword and Shield as One ultimate combo!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201046_TextContext: Nice one, partner. We've done it!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203028_TextContext: Its disposal is normally regulated and managed. Pause the match! I have to...
AVGEvent_Michel.101101012_TextContext: In our rare free time, Navigator, are you interested in a challenge between gamers?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201049_TextContext: That's exactly what a gamer would do!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203044_TextContext: What should we do? What about the players trapped inside? I can't do anything... Must I watch as they...
AVGEvent_Michel.101203012_TextContext: The arcade is just up ahead! The final battle of the super gamer is about to start!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204024_TextContext: In any case, my merits balance out my demerits, and I still have to write dozens of pages of written apologies... It seems like I can never get away from them!
AVGEvent_Michel.51101005_TextContext: I've been here all this time.
AVGEvent_Michel.101201013_TextContext: I don't need one! I'm not tired at all!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204030_TextContext: They didn't hear me complain about them, did they? What do I do? What do I do? They're going to scold me again...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102030_TextContext: I was confused: Should I be a cool gamer or a disciplined investigator?
AVGEvent_Michel.101102036_TextContext: I've realized that being both a gamer and an investigator is not contradictory. Both of them are my unique traits.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202045_TextContext: I'm going to set aside my gamer's mindset for now and be a well-disciplined investigator.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202049_TextContext: I would like to follow the rules like everyone else. This would reduce the number of rumors about my dad and myself, thus preventing dad's name from being tarnished.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102021_TextContext: I only found out about this by accident while reading game guides. Turns out, the story of the game was adapted from my father's heroic deeds! The dragon-slaying Mighty Meow was based on him!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203056_TextContext: I'm coming in! Hang in there!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202009_TextContext: I know you're looking out for me... It's nothing, really. I'm used to being scolded.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202041_TextContext: I could finally put on the investigator's uniform and valiantly step onto the battlefield just like my hero.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202052_TextContext: With all that said, I am serious about this decision!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202044_TextContext: I've given it some thought. I'm going to make an important decision...
AVGEvent_Michel.101204025_TextContext: When will my superiors become more open-minded? I heard they were planning to visit me today to talk about it... Why must it be today of all days? I just want to play the new game in peace!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203071_TextContext: Sorry. You must have been worried.
AVGEvent_Michel.51101020_TextContext: I'm taking you to a mysterious event...
AVGEvent_Michel.101203058_TextContext: Investigator Michele coming to your rescue!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203040_TextContext: Investigator, fulfill your duty and lock down the site. Prevent the spread of the erosion flow and await further instructions! Over.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203036_TextContext: Investigator Michele, lock-down and secure the site immediately. Await backup with erosive substance collection equipment. Over.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202030_TextContext: The Sentinel Bureau has started disciplinary action against her father as a result of his incompetence in handling the Port Euler case, resulting in the department losing a significant amount of personnel. His superiors have decided to suspend him from frontline work.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102037_TextContext: I don't want to give up on either of them. I am the unique super gamer investigator!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204016_TextContext: Are you hiding something from me?
AVGEvent_Michel.101204005_TextContext: Really? But today is not my birthday...
AVGEvent_Michel.101203027_TextContext: It's extremely dangerous! Erosion substances are a type of harmful liquid produced during stringification! Contact with it is lethal!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204008_TextContext: The new game will be released today!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204439_TextContext: Your gamer's mindset has saved everyone!
AVGEvent_Michel.101101013_TextContext: We have Paper Detective, a candidate for Best Story of the Year, and Superheroes of Justice, a classic action game that continues childhood memories. Which one would you like to play?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201039_TextContext: It's too late. We have both died from the poison... We've lost all the equipment and items we collected along the way...
AVGEvent_Michel.101204011_TextContext: Based on the latest update, it should be delivered today. Let's play it together once it arrives.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202021_TextContext: Eh? I've met him before. He's a newly promoted investigator from the second squad, my junior from the academy. Back then, he and I were assigned to the same combat drill team.
AVGEvent_Michel.51101004_TextContext: Eh? Partner, when did you get here? Can you teleport?
AVGEvent_Michel.101102004_TextContext: Since neither of us is on the clock right now, let's forget about work!
AVGEvent_Michel.101101016_TextContext: They also gave out cartridges for the game. Let's experience what it feels like to be the great detective!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201034_TextContext: The dragon's running out of HP. We're about to win!
AVGEvent_Michel.101102042_TextContext: After all, a protagonist needs companions, right, my best gaming buddy?
AVGEvent_Michel.101203074_TextContext: After all, our duel has yet to start!
AVGEvent_Michel.51101019_TextContext: No time to explain. Come with me.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203077_TextContext: The arcade will probably be closed for a while.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202000_PrologueTitle: To Be a Gamer or Ordinary
AVGEvent_Michel.101101010_TextContext: An investigator slash gamer. Does it seem slightly out of place?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201000_PrologueTitle: A Day in the Life of a Gamer
AVGEvent_Michel.101102035_TextContext: I am no longer alone because I've met you, Navigator, my new gaming buddy!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201031_TextContext: So far, so good. These monsters are weak.
AVGEvent_Michel.51101018_TextContext: Judging from your expression, I feel like you're going to do something astonishing or announce important news...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102015_TextContext: They remind me of my own - Mighty Meow and Pawtector!
AVGEvent_Michel.51101007_TextContext: R-Really? I totally didn't notice you...
AVGEvent_Michel.101202014_TextContext: Just when I thought I had them, I walked right into a trap and lost my target. My gamer's mindset doesn't work every time...
AVGEvent_Michel.51101022_TextContext: Wait a moment, partner. Let me put down the pen and paper... W-Where are you taking me?
AVGEvent_Michel.101204049_TextContext: Thanks for your patience. A brand-new adventure featuring the navigator and the investigator is about to start!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202033_TextContext: Dad is not like that! He was transferred from field duty because of the injuries he sustained trying to protect his partner. It had nothing to do with his handling of the case!
AVGEvent_Michel.101101019_TextContext: It's time to find out how well we work together as a team. Show me what you've got, Navigator!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203025_TextContext: An erosion flow? Is it serious?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201032_TextContext: Up ahead is the boss of the first level, one nine-headed venomous dragon lurking underground. Be careful, partner!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203075_TextContext: It would be a shame for me to perish now, wouldn't it?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201055_TextContext: If only my superiors from the Sentinel Bureau were as understanding as you... Would save me from a ton of written apologies...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102006_TextContext: That's what I'm going for! You'll know when we get there!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203021_TextContext: Alert! An erosion flow has occurred at 30 Caprivi Street, Area 2, Elmond East. Requesting all nearby officers to respond immediately!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203016_TextContext: Let's get started. This is going to be the battle to end all battles!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201014_TextContext: By the way, check out the cartridge! I had to queue all night to get it.
AVGEvent_Michel.101102038_TextContext: This is embarrassing... But I would like to be a hero a game is based on, just like my father.
AVGEvent_Michel.101101003_TextContext: Speaking of games, if you regularly visit The No.1 Gaming Forum, you must have heard of the famous moderator, Super Pawtector. She frequently updates game guides and shares gaming news...
AVGEvent_Michel.51101016_TextContext: Now that I think about it, you've been acting all mysterious...
AVGEvent_Michel.101204040_TextContext: Please have faith in yourself, Investigator Michele.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202048_TextContext: Thank you, partner... At least one person cares about the gamer Michele.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203000_PrologueTitle: The Way of the Super Gamer
AVGEvent_Michel.101201029_TextContext: Enough about the past... Let's get started. I can't wait!
AVGEvent_Michel.101101018_TextContext: This series was already popular back on Old Earth. It is a co-op role-playing game.
AVGEvent_Michel.101101008_TextContext: How did you tell? You do have a keen eye.
AVGEvent_Michel.101201026_TextContext: What a coincidence! I wanted to play Superheroes of Justice with you today!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202029_TextContext: Her father was the hero of the Sentinel Bureau and well-known all across Elmond. But you're aware of the incident, right?
AVGEvent_Michel.101204639_TextContext: This is literally the first time someone has thanked me for my gamer's mindset... Turns out I'm awesome!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203007_TextContext: If we do this, you'll have no more regrets... right?
AVGEvent_Michel.101202031_TextContext: Such a reckless and incompetent man is no hero!
AVGEvent_Michel.101202011_TextContext: I don't think it's as simple as that this time...
AVGEvent_Michel.101101015_TextContext: This is a new text adventure game with a thrilling plot and plenty of suspense based on the TV series of the same name. Even the senior officers at the Sentinel Bureau are recommending it.
AVGEvent_Michel.101201027_TextContext: I used to play this game with my dad all the time. My favorite character is Mighty Meow, the young dragon slayer!
AVGEvent_Michel.101102011_TextContext: This is the only cat café in Elmond in collaboration with the No. 1 series. This is the go-to place for fan meetups!
AVGEvent_Michel.101203094_TextContext: Until next time, then. I'll contact you!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201015_TextContext: I know you're on the clock, but would you like to try it?
AVGEvent_Michel.101101009_TextContext: Let's get to know each other a bit better, shall we? I work as an investigator, but when I'm not on the job, I am Michele, the gamer. My ID is Super Pawtector.
AVGEvent_Michel.101101021_TextContext: From now on, you'll be my gaming buddy! Here is your controller. Give it a try. You can adjust the sensitivity and shortcut buttons if necessary.
AVGEvent_Michel.101204007_TextContext: Darn it... Let's try to remember.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202042_TextContext: Who is this hero you speak of?
AVGEvent_Michel.101202020_TextContext: (A P.U.S investigator on patrol walks over angrily, looking at us with disdain.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204013_TextContext: (The usually energetic, cat-like girl sounds exhausted, avoiding eye contact with me, giving me a feeling of déjà vu.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203018_TextContext: (A rapid alarm sounds from Michele's portable communication device.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102002_TextContext: (Without any prior work appointments, Michele mysteriously asks to meet.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201142_TextContext: (As if struck by a heavy blow, the disheartened girl hangs her head.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101202001_TextContext: (At Grand Beach on my day off.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201242_TextContext: (But after just a second, her blue eyes are filled with a fighting spirit.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203069_TextContext: (But now, she glows like a triumphant warrior.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102009_TextContext: (Holding my hand, the playful girl takes us to a cozy café where several cats are lounging.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204038_TextContext: (The letters read, “To the Cat Investigator, this is a commemorative trophy for players who have pre-ordered the game. It is our pleasure to bestow this honor upon you, whose courage and perseverance is akin to that of the heroes in the game.”
AVGEvent_Michel.101204339_TextContext: (Many names are signed at the bottom of the letter, followed by a note: “Included are the Mighty Meow Arcade co-branded cat paw cookies. If you like the cookies, please pre-order them as well.”)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201043_TextContext: (Replaying the first level, Michele and I are better coordinated.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203057_TextContext: (Rushing into the arcade, Michele stringifies the shield to block the gushing erosion flow as if she were a shimmer of hope in the darkness.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102013_TextContext: (Several playful cats come to us uninvited, frolicking around Michele.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204101_TextContext: (On another day off, Michele invites to visit her at the familiar Apartment One.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204045_TextContext: (On the other side, I have inserted the disc into the console and picked up the controller ready to start, but Michele is slow to join, staring blankly at her precious trophies.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201017_TextContext: (As I reach for the game console, I notice a familiar item on the coffee table next to the couch.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203067_TextContext: (As the crowd eagerly waits for her to come out, Michele emerges from the smoke, her face covered by ash, but underneath the grime, her smile shines through, bright as ever.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102049_TextContext: (Surrounded by cats, Michele and I stay at the café until late in the evening.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101202039_TextContext: (The disheartened girl produces a shiny badge bearing the P.U.S insignia with a sword of justice running through it, as if the bravery and determination of past P.U.S investigators were encapsulated within.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203049_TextContext: (She lifts her head and locks eyes with me, her blue eyes clear as ever.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101202037_TextContext: (The man does not dial down his sarcastic tone by a bit. Suddenly, someone calls out for him in the distance, and the man cheerfully runs off.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102008_TextContext: (Whispering) You're the only person I've ever brought to this place. Please keep it a secret!
AVGEvent_Michel.101204043_TextContext: (Whispering) Can I become a hero like my dad... That way, his will would not fade away...
AVGEvent_Michel.101102041_TextContext: (Smiling with joy, the girl looks at me with utmost seriousness.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204026_TextContext: (As the girl frets, sudden, hurried knocks are heard from the door.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101202010_TextContext: (The girl who is usually as playful as a kitty seems to have lost all her energy. Deliberately avoiding eye contact with me, she appears unwilling to share her feelings with me.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201002_TextContext: (As invited, I go to Apartment One of P.U.S in Elmond, where Michele lives. As I open the door, I witness the following scene...)
AVGEvent_Michel.101202028_TextContext: (My wrath is indescribable, but Michele grabs my hands, holding me back, seemingly indifferent to the situation. Is she used to such rumors and slander?)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204001_TextContext: (Through the door, I can hear Michele humming the theme song of Superheroes of Justice. Despite the lively and spirited melody, her voice sounds rather disheartened.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203060_TextContext: (The petite girl holds the shield against the gushing blue-purple erosion flow, as if she were a warrior facing off a flame-spitting dragon.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102001_TextContext: (A few days later, the commercial hub. The weather is clear.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204034_TextContext: (Sigh of relief) Phew. Let me catch my breath... Alright, I've plucked up courage to open the door!
AVGEvent_Michel.101201001_TextContext: (One day, Investigator Michele schedules a briefing session with me as soon as she returns from the field.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102033_TextContext: (As we speak, the fluffy fur babies shuffle closely between us, meowing for petting and hugging.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203089_TextContext: (I wipe the dust off Michele's face with a tissue.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203004_TextContext: (Michele is excited as well as if this were a regular round of a video game. But try as she might, she cannot hide the reluctance and sadness in her tone.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101202038_TextContext: (Michele and I sit on the beach, both of us silent, listening only to the sound of the waves.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204044_TextContext: (Muttering to herself, Michele places the trophy next to the sword and shield models. The three items act as her achievement trophies, shining brightly under the sunlight.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204037_TextContext: (Holding her breath, Michele carefully opens the package, which contains a game trophy filled with cat paw cookies and a letter of appreciation.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203053_TextContext: (Michele vanishes in front of my eyes, rushing to the arcade.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201044_TextContext: (Michele lures the dragon to a hidden trap while I seize the opportunity to cast our ultimate combo: Sword and Shield as One!)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203001_TextContext: (The commercial hub, on the day we agreed to meet.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203062_TextContext: (Though still terrified, the people trapped inside start moving with Michele's encouragement. As they start to pour out of the arcade, Michele is nowhere to be seen.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203063_TextContext: (The blue-purple erosion flow has swallowed the heroine. Just as everyone starts to lose hope, thinking they would never see that light again...)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203043_TextContext: (The blue-purple liquid keeps spilling out. Standing outside the arcade, we can still feel the severity of the situation, worsening by the minute.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203059_TextContext: (Standing outside the arcade entrance, I do not have a clear view of the situation inside, but Michele's brave voice is crystal clear.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201006_TextContext: (Both robo battlecats seem exhausted, slumping next to the charging station, sound asleep. The girl shows no sign of fatigue as if all her energy has been replenished as soon as she returns to the pure world of video games.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201016_TextContext: (I can't say no to the enthusiastic super gamer whose eyes twinkle like little stars.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102050_TextContext: (After an entire day, Michele does not seem tired at all.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101102014_TextContext: (All the cats seem to know her well. With cats all over her, the girl drops her act of slyness and mystery.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203051_TextContext: (Her cute eyes fill with a fighting spirit, sparkling with determination.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201018_TextContext: (It is a shining model of a giant sword. Finely crafted, it resembles the Sword of Light used by Mighty Meow, the protagonist of Superheroes of Justice.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203068_TextContext: (Her cute clothing seems to have been damaged, making her look somewhat disheveled.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101202053_TextContext: (Under the golden sun, against the backdrop of the surging waves, her blue eyes sparkle with determination.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101203055_TextContext: (With a series of clacks, she dismantles and holds the shield prop by the door.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101201045_TextContext: (In an instant, a dazzling golden light emits between the sword and shield, tearing the mighty dragon in half.)
AVGEvent_Michel.101204036_TextContext: (Having plucked her courage, the girl flings the door open to find not only the disc of the latest Superheroes of Justice game, but also a mysterious package without the sender's details.)

AVGEvent_Season2.231104074_TextContext: Anderson from Team 103... I've seen your name on our records.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104076_TextContext: Forty-three days... this record still hasn't been surpassed.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107155_TextContext: How about the best seafood buffet in all of Area 88?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104138_TextContext: ...Can you hear me? This is the Neutroville Control Center of the P.U.S Bureau of Investigation!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105107_TextContext: ...There's a stringified being gliding in the sky!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101006_TextContext: “...After a week of destruction, the storm is finally showing signs of slowing down.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231101086_TextContext: “Urbino announces that energy reserves are critical. Civilian energy use has been limited, and prices have risen significantly.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231106012_TextContext: “Abel” has confirmed it. There's no need to keep asking.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104060_TextContext: “The Great Awakening...” How dramatic. Are you a member of The Scissors, or are you just taking their orders?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101009_TextContext: “As of now, The Scissors have not yet claimed responsibility for the serial bombings.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231101008_TextContext: “Explosions and skirmishes have continued to plague affected areas, placing great pressure on security and medical services.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231101007_TextContext: “Thanks to an advance warning from Painting Utopia Security, local emergency services rapidly evacuated civilians before the worst hit the city.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231101010_TextContext: “Speaking about the relocation of those affected by the disaster, a spokesman for Grove Enterprises...”
AVGEvent_Season2.231104197_TextContext: “Citizens are advised to stay clear of the identified locations...”
AVGEvent_Season2.231103163_TextContext: ...Looks like Neutroville won't be very peaceful today.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103059_TextContext: ...So that's how it is. Just what are The Scissors planning?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102112_TextContext: Even the Bureau of Investigation is having difficulties. What makes two doctors think they can crack the case?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106020_TextContext: Just a bracelet from the old days.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102678_TextContext: Once the three-year term is up, the Grove unicorn will be restored to its place as alliance leader.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106030_TextContext: Three layers of superstring locks. We're lucky you didn't try to mess with it.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103047_TextContext: They destroyed the Komos Tower and stole many critical purified crystals. I saw it with my own two eyes...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104063_TextContext: Painting Utopia Security will be buried under its own arrogance, and from its ruins, a new dawn shall rise.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105089_TextContext: Kokona, there's more of them coming this way!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102676_TextContext: Apologies. I lost my temper, but everything I said was true.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105116_TextContext: Damn it! That's where we keep the vault!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103086_TextContext: Navigator, there's trouble! The suspect blended into the crowd - I've lost him!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103085_TextContext: I got this! Don't let the operative get away!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103017_TextContext: I wonder if she's mad at me...
AVGEvent_Season2.231103104_TextContext: It's no good. I won't be able to fight back with just Polaris alone.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103131_TextContext: Don't rush in all by yourself!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107074_TextContext: But... It looks like you've already helped us corner her.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106021_TextContext: But... It's being held inside a case. Is there some way we can open it?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105118_TextContext: But isn't this going a little far to rob a bank...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106005_TextContext: Such a commotion out there... Tch. What a pain.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106116_TextContext: But we're already at our limit now...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106032_TextContext: It's still P.U.S tech at the end of the day. Not particularly difficult to break.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101064_TextContext: I'm not sure why, but... none of the patients seem to like it.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104039_TextContext: But, from my experience, this kind of directionless search won't produce much results.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102080_TextContext: But, as you can see, our alliance leader is a strange man who can never be reached.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103160_TextContext: But the situation has changed. That's why I came here to find you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101039_TextContext: I didn't want to waste your concern, so I decided to stay there for a while...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101053_TextContext: What follows is the real challenge...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104023_TextContext: But, since the Astral Sanctuary is doing security consulting for Grove Enterprises, Celestia and the Navigator also have the right to know...
AVGEvent_Season2.231105125_TextContext: But the question remains: how are we going to escape this mob?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107052_TextContext: No... this is where I shine!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101072_TextContext: Ehm... That's not what I meant...
AVGEvent_Season2.231105038_TextContext: No... That shot came from further away.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107140_TextContext: No, it's fine... Most people who make use of our vaults are just regular customers. I'm not very familiar with these numerals...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101056_TextContext: No. This isn't the time to think about such things.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107125_TextContext: Not The Scissors, but a different enemy...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106110_TextContext: Come closer, you two. I'm nearly at my limit...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106115_TextContext: For when we turn things around.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104036_TextContext: We've cauterized the main thoroughfare between Neutroville and Elmond to prevent things from getting completely out of control.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107141_TextContext: I'll do some research. Until then, it's best that the Navigator holds on to the bracelet.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104183_TextContext: The dedicated Urbino line? Connect them through!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101088_TextContext: Is Urbino going to leave these people to die?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107020_TextContext: In other words... you won't repeat my past mistakes.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105120_TextContext: So what you're saying is, they've got their eyes on something worth going through all this trouble for...
AVGEvent_Season2.231103129_TextContext: He must be the main culprit! You! Don't even think about getting away!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104018_TextContext: You don't need to put it like that... Celestia helped me a lot, too!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104025_TextContext: What? How could there be so many?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104106_TextContext: We've recovered similar keys from previous targets, and now we know their purpose.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104037_TextContext: From now on, there's no way in and no way out. Neutroville is under quarantine.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103045_TextContext: If we look at the bombings, they've all happened at different times and places. The perpetrator isn't a lone wolf, but an organized group.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102040_TextContext: The receptionist only told me that Mr. Bai had said that a young lady would come looking for him today.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105027_TextContext: They have their duty, and I must perform mine, too.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107177_TextContext: They responded quickly. Once The Scissors showed up, things were resolved soon enough.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104042_TextContext: He was sent out on a secret mission, the kind that even I'm kept in the dark about. And not a moment too late, either.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103012_TextContext: To choose this teahouse as a meeting place, could it be that the investigator is...?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102138_TextContext: The future of the victims and the glory of the unicorn... they're both in your hands.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102027_TextContext: But you are not prey. Your scent is different... it's pure, complex, strange...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106130_TextContext: But detonating this mine is the best option I can think of right now.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102116_TextContext: But as an independent institution, the Astral Sanctuary can interfere with the Grove's affairs... have I got that right?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102123_TextContext: But no one in this world cares more about eliminating disease than me!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101106_TextContext: But... If Mr. Bai can speak for the Astral Sanctuary, then he must have some kind of voice in Urbino.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101060_TextContext: As a show of thanks... would you like to enjoy a cup of Starlight Coffee with me? If you don't mind, of course.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103070_TextContext: The battle plan is simple. Once we see The Scissors' operatives, we'll sneak up on them and make our move!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101082_TextContext: Didn't you say that we still had room to overdraft?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101068_TextContext: You've been working hard. Get some rest for now.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107098_TextContext: Don't think you can get away that easy!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104165_TextContext: You've been staring at the screen all this time. Have you seen something?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106154_TextContext: Do you really think you can defeat me with a toy?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102022_TextContext: Are you two... here for that guy?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102056_TextContext: You don't recognize me? Haven't you read the Urbino Employee Handbook?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102137_TextContext: You may act as my plenipotentiary representative when dealing with P.U.S investigators.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105077_TextContext: What are you guys doing here...?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107143_TextContext: You are my most trusted partners, so I trust there will be no problem.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106073_TextContext: Listen up, you impostors! This is Captain Ming of The Scissors!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104062_TextContext: You'll see soon enough. The destruction of Komos Tower is an omen.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104081_TextContext: When you're on the front lines “protecting the city,” all they're thinking about is how to protect their own interests.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102094_TextContext: You seem like you're in a rush.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103044_TextContext: Why are you so sure it's The Scissors?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102108_TextContext: If you understand the impact of the bombings, then shouldn't you be focused on treating its victims?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107067_TextContext: You're Executor No. 3 of The Scissors... Lawine!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104077_TextContext: You are clearly a talented man. Why don't you use your skills to protect the city?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103139_TextContext: Your arms are sticking out from there!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104170_TextContext: What you're saying is... the enemy is hiding another target amongst all the noise...?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104091_TextContext: Your actions will result in many people getting hurt... or saved. The choice is yours.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102098_TextContext: It's not Urbino that has you in a rush.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106085_TextContext: Do you have any idea how much trouble you've caused Grove Enterprises?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106011_TextContext: Are you sure that it's hidden here?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106003_TextContext: Are you sure we went through the right door?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106026_TextContext: Do I look like “Cain” to you? That stuff is for kids.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103035_TextContext: You know Kokona? She was my instructor during training, and now she's deputy captain!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103078_TextContext: What did you say?! Follow him!!! Wait, no, defuse the bomb!!!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104071_TextContext: What did you say?! Team 103 wasn't a piece of cake...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101110_TextContext: What are you doing standing there?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106100_TextContext: Save your ammo. I'll go create an opportunity...
AVGEvent_Season2.231105079_TextContext: Our duty is to protect your safety.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107128_TextContext: We keep a lot of things in our vaults. There's no way I can remember them all.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106082_TextContext: Believe what you want. Just leave this place to us. You can rest for now.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105024_TextContext: Hopefully, there's some good news from the Bureau of Investigation that will help calm public opinion and buy us some time.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104136_TextContext: Great job, Michele! Open the emergency channel. I need to make a public announcement!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107104_TextContext: We'll worry about it later. We don't have the strength to chase them, anyway.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105083_TextContext: We need to get out of here.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103066_TextContext: Let's tackle the case at hand first.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102113_TextContext: The two of us can't do it alone.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104998_TextContext: Regarding this matter, I am also... sorry. We were the ones who failed.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101103_TextContext: Ehm... To be honest, I don't know much about him. We've never met.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101038_TextContext: To be honest... I was already awake when you covered me with the blanket.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106107_TextContext: Actually, I was planning to leave one round for myself.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107112_TextContext: I'm going to throw up if you keep shaking me, Michele.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107117_TextContext: What was that anchor link I just felt from you...?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106125_TextContext: I just checked the P.U.S database.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103077_TextContext: I just saw someone in the queue place one at the cashier's desk and slip away...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102052_TextContext: Nice to meet you. Are you two his... representatives?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105011_TextContext: Don't think I'll go easy on you just because you're hiding among the ignorant!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106137_TextContext: Don't worry about that. I have to do my part to help.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103065_TextContext: Don't jump to conclusions so quickly.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106022_TextContext: Don't rush. Let me take a look.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102008_TextContext: I'm coming up with a plan.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107182_TextContext: Don't blame me, Audrey... You should have learned not to go beyond your station.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103071_TextContext: Worry not. I've made a mental note of what all their primary operatives look like. Even if it's Ming or Lawine, I won't be afraid!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101031_TextContext: Don't worry, I'll take care of it.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104059_TextContext: Don't waste your time. The “Great Awakening” is about to begin. The Scissors will bring a new dawn to this world.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101069_TextContext: It's no rush. We need you in tip-top shape.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103138_TextContext: Stop hiding, Scissor! I can see you!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105009_TextContext: Not a step back! They're hoarding all our emergency supplies!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101065_TextContext: Navigator... you won't hate it, will you?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103132_TextContext: Navigator... Michele's already rushed in! We need to follow her!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101058_TextContext: Navigator, thank you for accompanying me and helping so many patients.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102006_TextContext: Navigator? Don't tell me you dragged me to the Urbino HQ without a plan...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104034_TextContext: Do The Scissors intend to start an all-out war?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106080_TextContext: You're a Scissor! Weren't you the ones who planned this attack?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102114_TextContext: We'll need the power of the unicorn for that.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102072_TextContext: I see... So you two are also looking for that guy...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102115_TextContext: So that's your plan. Though alliance regulations prevent me from interfering with the business of the Astral Sanctuary...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104013_TextContext: Oh, that...? I knew you were busy, so I felt like I shouldn't bother you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101114_TextContext: Let's go meet this Mr. Bai!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105132_TextContext: Go! I'll clear a way for you!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102066_TextContext: The bombings in Area 88 are just an example. If we don't get this situation under control, things are just going to get worse.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106017_TextContext: Old buzzkill... going on missions with you is so boring.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107100_TextContext: Remember this point. The Scissors would never harm civilians.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106089_TextContext: As long as you don't try anything suspicious...
AVGEvent_Season2.231103054_TextContext: As long as you share what you know with us, of course.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101097_TextContext: As long as there's a chance, our responsibility as doctors is to try and make a miracle happen.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101044_TextContext: I can't let you shoulder this alone.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105092_TextContext: Damn it... If this continues, we're done for!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103110_TextContext: Where are we going to get that kind of weapon?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107150_TextContext: But, Kokona... what about my written apologies?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104130_TextContext: But... we didn't come here for protection!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102063_TextContext: But, the board's absurd energy rationing has completely disrupted our relief plans.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104174_TextContext: It has to be! Navigator, you discovered the blind spot!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101093_TextContext: Since we're a subsidiary, can't they offer us a discount?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102057_TextContext: Listen carefully. My name is Audrey... Audrey Grove. Please don't forget it.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103154_TextContext: Yahoooo! Long time no see, Celestia. How are you doing? You seem like you haven't been getting enough sleep.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103006_TextContext: Uh... here, right? The Greenview Teahouse?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104094_TextContext: Tell me, just who could instigate such a decorated P.U.S investigator to go against their duty?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105073_TextContext: Whoaaa! There's so many of them!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107152_TextContext: Hahaha... Kokona really hasn't changed at all.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105094_TextContext: Haha! We've caught those P.U.S investigators in our trap, too.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107070_TextContext: Hmpf! So you do recognize me!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103026_TextContext: Hum... Who would have thought that investigator Michele would encounter such a challenge on her first solo mission?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104082_TextContext: You superstring beings are at least worth something to them, but people like me are just pawns that can be readily replaced.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102681_TextContext: Eh? What do you mean? Aren't you his...?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101112_TextContext: Eh? Navigator? When did you call for a car? Wait a moment... where are we going?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106014_TextContext: When are we going to stop talking in riddles?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105026_TextContext: Ahem... It's nothing. I just met some interesting people, that's all.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103040_TextContext: Ahem... Alright. Allow me to give you a proper introduction.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103033_TextContext: Whoa! Kokona really has an eye for good food! You two should try some as well.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104143_TextContext: Ha... We can finally take a breather.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104008_TextContext: Hahaha! It really has been a while, hasn't it?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104068_TextContext: Ehehe... No, but it looks like I hit the mark. Tell me, which team were you on?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104148_TextContext: Oi, you two. You can continue this conversation later.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105124_TextContext: Oh dear... Celestia's really angry now. Our enemy better watch out...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104070_TextContext: Pfft! It's fine if you don't tell me. I know several people who've left P.U.S. Compared to them, you're nothing special.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107151_TextContext: Oh, let's not talk about such boring things! That guy isn't back anyway, so it's not like anyone's going to read it.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105075_TextContext: Saving a permanent director of Urbino is gonna earn me so much cred! I wonder how many written apologies this will save me...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106063_TextContext: In that case, let's have some fun.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103029_TextContext: Oh! Just the two I was looking for.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104198_TextContext: Oh? Looks like the Bureau of Investigation moves quickly...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101057_TextContext: I have to do my best to protect them all.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103122_TextContext: Hehehe! Taste the power of Mighty Meow, evil Scissors!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104112_TextContext: Hmpf! It's not like I play games for nothing!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102061_TextContext: Hmpf. That's enough chatter. Let's get to the point.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103055_TextContext: Well... Since you're Kokona's friends, I guess it should be fine...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101070_TextContext: Hmm... You're right! I'll get some rest first.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102034_TextContext: Eh? Navigator, who was that you were talking to?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105142_TextContext: Ah... The “last resort” has been used... What now, “Audrey?”
AVGEvent_Season2.231106086_TextContext: Ahhhh, that's enough, that's enough. I have no idea what you're talking about.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102059_TextContext: Ah! Are you the Lady Audrey who appeared in the latest episode of “30 Minutes?” One of the permanent directors of the Urbino Business Alliance?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103128_TextContext: Ah! That was the one who planted the bomb! He ran into the back alley!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107145_TextContext: Hey, are you guys done talking?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103050_TextContext: Oh, whoops! There was a gag order on this... I wasn't supposed to say anything!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105090_TextContext: Tch... Always using other people to do their dirty work. How detestable!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105066_TextContext: Tch... I'll need to use the “last resort.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231103127_TextContext: Tsk. Useless fools... The “Great Awakening” is at hand... I can't allow myself to be captured here!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106183_TextContext: Tch! Take this! Get away from them!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107171_TextContext: Tch! Okay, okay, you're the boss.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106081_TextContext: Tsk! The Scissors would never use ordinary people as shields!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106066_TextContext: Tsk! These fools... there's no end to them.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105088_TextContext: Oi! Don't let them get away!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103099_TextContext: Oi! I'm no match for them on my own! Stop hiding and help me!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103015_TextContext: Mmm... One of my friends in P.U.S.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102044_TextContext: Well... In any case, I got this guest pass.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102039_TextContext: Mmm... I'm not sure if this counts.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103036_TextContext: Ah. Seems like she still has a tooth for street food.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101099_TextContext: You're right! So long as there's a glimmer of hope, I'll never give up on my patients!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104145_TextContext: It was all thanks to Michele and Kokona... I'm sorry that we couldn't be of help.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104086_TextContext: Navigator, do you see it too?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103068_TextContext: Yes, I understand. That's why I asked for us to meet here.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107176_TextContext: Aye. As you instructed, I broadcast the situation at Grove Bank to the Bureau of Investigation through the Urbino line.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102096_TextContext: Mm? Navigator... is there something else?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101030_TextContext: Shh... let her rest for a while.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103126_TextContext: Hehe! Who are you praising? Me, or Mighty Meow?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101062_TextContext: Hehe. It's my own special brew!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107023_TextContext: You will come to understand everything soon enough.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104087_TextContext: Deep down, you still identify with the title of “investigator,” and you're proud of the work you've done.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105008_TextContext: Reinforcements will be here shortly. Just hold strong!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102111_TextContext: “Treat the disease...” you want to involve yourself in the investigation?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104093_TextContext: Even in a place like the True Wilderness, you stuck by your team and led them back home.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103072_TextContext: Until then, we can just pretend to be ordinary diners and chow down on these rice rolls!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104999_TextContext: After that, I decided to join The Scissors and got a bomb and key from that woman named Rafa...
AVGEvent_Season2.231105110_TextContext: Creating diversions with bombings and riots... It's the same tactic.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106004_TextContext: The distraction outside should last for a while. Continue with the recovery operation.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103159_TextContext: If it wasn't for you, we wouldn't have been able to prevent the 9th Street bombing.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106025_TextContext: Just a few minutes. If you're bored, go burn some time on the air guitar or something.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106099_TextContext: Mighty Meow's at his limit, too... If we continue on like this...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102058_TextContext: Audrey Grove... The name seems familiar.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107180_TextContext: Audrey Grove is quite impressive. They have value as prey.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105078_TextContext: Lady Audrey, did you forget? I'm your personally appointed security consultant!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105115_TextContext: Lady Audrey, which floor did the explosion come from?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107127_TextContext: Lady Audrey, do you know anything about that bracelet?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105109_TextContext: What are they trying to do?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104097_TextContext: She sought me out and told me that The Scissors would bring about a great change.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105114_TextContext: Her ultimate goal was to... enter Grove Bank?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104019_TextContext: Okay, okay. There's plenty of time to reminisce later.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106035_TextContext: You can complain later. Let's recover the “staff.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231106010_TextContext: Okay, fine. Let's just use The Scissors' methods to solve this problem, then.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105059_TextContext: Who else wants to come forward?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103097_TextContext: That was close... Navigator, are you okay?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103158_TextContext: Think nothing of it - we're a team. I should be the one thanking you!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104027_TextContext: That means that all of Neutroville is at risk.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106050_TextContext: Do you think I should surrender?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106052_TextContext: If you're willing, I think that would be best for everyone.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102043_TextContext: But if he did, that's incredible.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102104_TextContext: If things don't change, the Groves are in for a world of hurt.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107169_TextContext: If I could see you now, I would slap you twice.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102124_TextContext: If we can reduce the amount of fighting, then the patients are sure to follow...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104052_TextContext: Could I trouble you to sit in with me during the interrogation?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107018_TextContext: It is the morning star, the eye, and the “staff” you will need to cross this “sea.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231105007_TextContext: Security team, maintain the defense! Don't allow them to get any closer!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103051_TextContext: My career as an investigator is over...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101090_TextContext: I can understand implementing controls, but if things go on, the Astral Sanctuary and its patients...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104024_TextContext: The bombing you prevented in 9th Street was already the fifth one today.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102031_TextContext: By the way... if that guy doesn't want to reveal himself, even I won't be able to catch on to his scent.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102084_TextContext: Well, since you're here, it would be a shame if you didn't take a tour of our HQ.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104017_TextContext: Oh, right. I haven't formally introduced you two yet... Navigator, Kokona was one of my best friends at P.U.S, and the first to support my dream of opening the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102062_TextContext: Regarding the recovery efforts, the Grove family has opened up new supply chains, and we're making good progress with the relief supplies and relocation of refugees.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103076_TextContext: That's right! How did you know?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104021_TextContext: That's right, Kokona. Why were you in such a hurry to get back?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103105_TextContext: They've got the numbers and the positional advantage...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106075_TextContext: We will never let scum who prey on the innocent tarnish our name!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105063_TextContext: That's right! Don't worry, those rubber bullets can't hurt us!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105019_TextContext: Lady... the crowd out there is getting bigger and bigger.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105029_TextContext: Lady, forgive me, but... It's dangerous down there. You don't have to handle this yourself.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105042_TextContext: Lady, this looks like a planned attack.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107062_TextContext: Don't be so confident, you foolish girl...!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104135_TextContext: Unconfirmed explosion targets... there's 31 in total! I've uploaded all coordinates to the control center!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102075_TextContext: You especially, Ms. Celestia. From the way you speak and carry yourself, you must also come from a place of standing, am I right?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102097_TextContext: As you heard, Urbino has a lot of problems to deal with right now. I don't have the time...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102010_TextContext: Just like you said, we can't give up hope. Right?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105022_TextContext: We need the alliance leader's authority to open things up, but that guy...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101087_TextContext: Just while we were busy admitting patients...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106084_TextContext: Even if I believe you this time, Komos Tower was still your doing, wasn't it?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107134_TextContext: Just keep it there... give me your hand.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102081_TextContext: Even we permanent directors can't get a hold of him.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103123_TextContext: ...The enemy broke in the blink of an eye.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107041_TextContext: They knew?! The staff has fallen into their hands...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106028_TextContext: I'm nearly done. The glass cover took some time.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103125_TextContext: His cute appearance nearly fooled me.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104054_TextContext: I hope I can be of help.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105028_TextContext: Make the preparations. I shall personally meet with the rioters and explain the Grove family's position to them.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103067_TextContext: The Navigator is right. Our top priority right now should be to prevent further bombings.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107129_TextContext: Navigator, may I take a look?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102102_TextContext: Navigator, I don't know if you're trying to get my attention or my ire, but in either case, you've succeeded.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104051_TextContext: Navigator, I hear you also happen to be an expert in psychology.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103106_TextContext: Navigator, I'm going to stringify closer to them to nullify their range advantage.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106140_TextContext: Navigator, I'll leave the recovery to you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101113_TextContext: To the Urbino HQ, of course!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102012_TextContext: Sounds good. Why don't you go?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104064_TextContext: Such an abstract statement... who told you this?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102117_TextContext: That's an interesting perspective. But why should I trust you?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103153_TextContext: K-Kokona? What are you doing here?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104127_TextContext: Kokona...is there nothing we can do?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106043_TextContext: Take care of this, and be quick. Your evac is ready to go.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104146_TextContext: Don't say that! If it weren't for you, I might never have been able to uncover Anderson's identity and learn about the keys.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102023_TextContext: But what I heard was a bit different... has there been a mistake?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105037_TextContext: What's happening? I gave an explicit order prohibiting any gunfire!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101108_TextContext: Perhaps... No. I can't rely on her...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107115_TextContext: Anyway... we'll talk more once you've had a rest.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102130_TextContext: What I mean is, no matter what, the Astral Sanctuary will do its best to help the Groves crack the case!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106087_TextContext: In any case, I haven't fired on you today, so just don't fire on me, either.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106077_TextContext: Whatever! Open fire! Eliminate these impostors!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101052_TextContext: All the patients are taken care of, at least for now.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107116_TextContext: I want to know what exactly happened when you touched that bracelet.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104065_TextContext: You're trying to trick me into giving you information. Give it up, your P.U.S tricks won't work on me.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104992_TextContext: Think. What is the duty of an investigator?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104090_TextContext: Think about all the people who have been harmed by your bombings and all the doctors working day and night to keep them alive...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104066_TextContext: You must be very determined... or perhaps you're just familiar with our interrogation techniques, former investigator?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104089_TextContext: I don't care about your “Great Awakening,” but...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102079_TextContext: I also understand the trouble you're facing...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107072_TextContext: I came here to deal with the shameless scum who dared to act in our name.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102136_TextContext: In the name of Audrey Grove, I hire you, Miss Celestia, as a temporary security consultant for Grove Enterprises.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106038_TextContext: As an investigator, I order you to put your hands up!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105123_TextContext: We have to stop them and put an end to this farce!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102680_TextContext: We also want to know where he is.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106061_TextContext: We need to stop that guy! Navigator, you get back the stolen item!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106016_TextContext: We came here for the “staff.” Just keep your eye on our objective, Rafa.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106131_TextContext: I'll launch an attack. You two find a way to get her into a better range.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101100_TextContext: I've made up my mind. I'll talk to our angel investor... Mr. Bai.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104032_TextContext: Did I accidentally skip the last chapter?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107061_TextContext: I'd give up if I were you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105055_TextContext: I'll deal with their leaders. Hold the line here!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107162_TextContext: All I did was take on a mission.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102078_TextContext: I've heard about the research you're doing at the Astral Sanctuary. Your theories about treating and preventing collapse syndrome are novel, and I've heard you're making solid progress. You're carrying on Urbino's pioneering spirit.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102009_TextContext: I knew it... But, I guess it's fine.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102060_TextContext: This is so weird... I'm talking to someone who I've seen on TV.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102085_TextContext: I highly recommend the black tea and scones from the second-floor canteen.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106083_TextContext: How can I trust The Scissors?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104035_TextContext: I'm guessing the higher-ups are also considering this possibility as we speak.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102011_TextContext: Maybe if we ask the receptionist, they'll be able to tell us something about Mr. Bai?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107066_TextContext: That's my line! Who in the world are you people?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106045_TextContext: You've got to the count of three!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105117_TextContext: I see! So, after all this, it turns out the enemy is a master thief!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102133_TextContext: I understand. If you really can put an end to the bombings...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104131_TextContext: I understand how you feel, but that's exactly why I need you to remain calm.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103028_TextContext: I'm Celestia, and my companion here is the Astral Sanctuary's Navigator.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107148_TextContext: I've got an idea! Why don't we celebrate with a party?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101040_TextContext: I wanted to take care of Celestia...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107181_TextContext: What do I tell you? An interesting one, are they not?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106019_TextContext: I guess... this must be it? Doesn't look like anything special.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101105_TextContext: I don't even have his contact details.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101084_TextContext: Were my projections wrong? Wait, look at this! It's news from this morning...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102026_TextContext: My boss said that the target would come look for him here.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105043_TextContext: I know. Security team, head to the main entrance at once!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107046_TextContext: I'm right with you. Let's attack!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107190_TextContext: That place drifting along the sea of dimensions... we'll reach it one day.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106114_TextContext: I need to save some of my power.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103140_TextContext: If I were you, I'd make it easy for myself and confess. Surrender now, and I'll bring you a large serving of pork chops and fried rice in the interrogation room!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102064_TextContext: I demand that the Bai Group immediately exercise its power as alliance leader and put an end to the board's short-sighted behavior!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104079_TextContext: I've seen far too many unsophisticated investigators like you, all filled with lofty ideals.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106129_TextContext: I still have this thing. I hope Lady Audrey won't get too mad at me for damaging her building...
AVGEvent_Season2.231105060_TextContext: I, Audrey Grove, am willing to take you on!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102131_TextContext: And so... this request... please grant it to us, Lady Audrey!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107167_TextContext: So you put me through all that for nothing?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107159_TextContext: You're saying that the “staff” has fallen into the hands of the Navigator?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105080_TextContext: We rushed over here as soon as we got your call!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102032_TextContext: Best give up. You won't have any better luck.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104044_TextContext: That's why I ignored my orders and came directly to you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103063_TextContext: That's why, no matter what... I have to bring The Scissors to justice and stop their senseless destruction!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107135_TextContext: Everyone who deposits an item for safekeeping needs to register their information with us. Let me check the item number...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106136_TextContext: Sorry to drag you into so much trouble, Celestia.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104119_TextContext: Reporting in. The bomb in Area 11... went off. We were too late. Confirming the casualties.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104117_TextContext: Reporting in. Defused the bomb in Area 51. There was an exchange of fire with an unknown group. One of our operatives was injured.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104115_TextContext: Reporting in. Defused the bomb in Area 66 with no casualties.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102073_TextContext: Apologies. I should have realized earlier.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103080_TextContext: Michele, you defuse the bomb and handle the evacuation!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104102_TextContext: Rafa stored all the mission plans and bombing targets in an encrypted database. Each key unlocks the information for a single target.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103064_TextContext: Please aid me in this quest!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107091_TextContext: As you ordered, we've eliminated all the impostors.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107044_TextContext: Damage to private property. Add another crime to the list!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104022_TextContext: What I'm about to say hasn't been released to the public yet...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106058_TextContext: An investigator can never negotiate with a criminal.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104139_TextContext: The Bureau of Investigation has identified several possible bombing targets. Please listen carefully to this public broadcast!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106006_TextContext: We're just taking back what's ours, and yet we're acting like thieves.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104137_TextContext: Copy that! Line check complete. We're ready to broadcast!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104116_TextContext: Copy that. Stay alert and move to Area 67.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104118_TextContext: Copy that. Stand by. Medics are on the way.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104120_TextContext: Copy that. Organize the evacuation, then hand over to emergency services.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104109_TextContext: Don't worry, Kokona. Cracking a database is just like solving a puzzle - this is my specialty!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103102_TextContext: There's got too much firepower... they're trying to cover their retreat.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104128_TextContext: We can help treat the search team's injuries!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103155_TextContext: That person next to you must be the Navigator, then?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102125_TextContext: Then, no matter how hard the road is ahead, I'm willing to walk it!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105122_TextContext: I don't care what they're looking for. Nothing is worth the loss of so many innocent lives.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107010_TextContext: We meet again. I suppose your link must have been successful.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107154_TextContext: In that case, allow me, the host, to treat you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102003_TextContext: It's about time. Are you ready, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107022_TextContext: We don't have much time, Navigator. Please forgive me for not explaining further.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107121_TextContext: There's murder behind her smile. I'm a little scared to speak...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101073_TextContext: Got it... I'll make my preparations.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107087_TextContext: Ming, what's going on down there?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101092_TextContext: Urbino is an investor in the Astral Sanctuary, isn't it?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102106_TextContext: Many of the victims end up coming to the Astral Sanctuary for treatment.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101029_TextContext: Director Celestia, the patient in bed four...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102118_TextContext: Celestia, I leave this one to you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104096_TextContext: It was a hooded woman who went by the name of “Rafa.”
AVGEvent_Season2.231107166_TextContext: It could have been of use to us...
AVGEvent_Season2.231103157_TextContext: You must be the one who saved Michele.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107017_TextContext: It's something that I must return to you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104993_TextContext: Is a temporary sacrifice not still a sacrifice?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105104_TextContext: Riots and an explosion... Just what in the world is going on?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104075_TextContext: You led a team of five, survived the True Wilderness for forty-three days, and successfully recovered the intel left behind by the scouting team.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104181_TextContext: There are three likely targets: the Urbino Alliance HQ, the Hermes Plaza, and...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107165_TextContext: I merely thought that if we could get the “staff...”
AVGEvent_Season2.231104012_TextContext: I've been so busy with the Astral Sanctuary that I haven't contacted you at all...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107019_TextContext: With this, you will find your way and lead people to where they need to go.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104009_TextContext: Have you been eating good? Sleeping well? How are things at the Astral Sanctuary?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104038_TextContext: The Bureau of Investigation deployed all its reserves to search for bombs throughout the city.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104058_TextContext: Come on, speak. Who are you? Why are you involved in these bombings?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103005_TextContext: According to Lady Audrey, this should be the place.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103069_TextContext: Based on the locations of the previous bombings, we believe 9th Street will be the next target.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102134_TextContext: Then, the unicorn will become the Astral Sanctuary's staunchest ally.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102103_TextContext: Grove Bank is located in Area 88, right where the bombings are most frequent.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105119_TextContext: Our vaults serve every important organization and institution in Strinova. Any item they hold could be of immense value!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103043_TextContext: Has P.U.S already found some evidence?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102067_TextContext: Painting Utopia Security is dragging its feet and reluctant to commit more manpower... We have to fix this on our own!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105074_TextContext: P.U.S Search Team One, start the backup mission.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104125_TextContext: Calculating! Progress is 80%...83%... we're already using all our computing power. I can't go any faster!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107071_TextContext: Just as well! Today, you Scissors will pay for all your crimes - old and new!
AVGEvent_Season2.231105051_TextContext: Hostiles at the main entrance, twelve o'clock. Requesting backup!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101042_TextContext: What's important right now is that I take responsibility for my patients.
