AVGEvent_Season2.231102074_TextContext: You two have a unique air about you, different from the employees here.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102065_TextContext: Public dissatisfaction has triggered more violence, and the deterioration of public security is going to have long-term catastrophic effects.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104047_TextContext: Don't worry, it's not the first time. It's just a matter of writing a few reports afterward.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107122_TextContext: Looks like it's up to me.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106007_TextContext: We had no choice. “Abel” insisted we proceed this way.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101041_TextContext: But it turns out that Celestia was taking care of me instead.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104111_TextContext: I didn't expect Michele to have such a talent.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103037_TextContext: So my helper turns out to be a friend of Kokona... That's way too much of a coincidence... could this be a hidden side quest?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107073_TextContext: I don't have time to play house with you.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104179_TextContext: The most valuable targets not hit by the bombings are...
AVGEvent_Season2.231103113_TextContext: Of course! I'm here to back you up. Check this out!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104073_TextContext: Fine. I'm Anderson from Team 103. Are you satisfied yet?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104080_TextContext: Wake up already! Do you really think any of the higher-ups care if we live or die?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104172_TextContext: These bombings were just a distraction.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102077_TextContext: Thank you for all you've done for the bombing victims. This should not have been a responsibility for private institutions to bear.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104167_TextContext: Bombs have been planted in what “seems” to be all areas in the city.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107168_TextContext: Conjectures need to be put into practice. That's all we're doing.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104129_TextContext: Not now. It's too dangerous out there.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106108_TextContext: This isn't the time to joke around!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104099_TextContext: Thinking about it now, I have no idea what her true plans were. I don't even know if she was really affiliated with The Scissors.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104043_TextContext: We'll have to do this ourselves.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105021_TextContext: The public is angry at the board's decision to implement energy rationing. To make matters worse, a shipment of emergency supplies got stuck in our supply chain...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101104_TextContext: All his inspections and investments into the Astral Sanctuary were all done through intermediaries.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101094_TextContext: Urbino does offer preferential rates, but it's still just a drop in the bucket. We're in a huge hole.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102679_TextContext: Is the alliance leader you're speaking of this “Mr. Bai?”
AVGEvent_Season2.231105025_TextContext: From the look on your face, I suppose there's some good news?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106057_TextContext: Looks like negotiations have broken down.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106128_TextContext: No matter what, our first goal should be to make sure they don't get away.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104014_TextContext: So we were thinking the same way...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102053_TextContext: I suppose Mr. Bai isn't planning on making a personal appearance this time?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101096_TextContext: Seems like there's room for negotiation.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103030_TextContext: Look - I only just managed to snag the last three of their signature rice rolls!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107146_TextContext: It's been such an exhausting day...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102672_TextContext: Jeez... There are so many fires to put out, and yet...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104015_TextContext: That puts me at ease. Kokona is still the same as always.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105108_TextContext: You're right... It's too high up. I can't see them clearly from here.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101095_TextContext: Our priority has to be getting an injection of funding so we can weather this storm.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101055_TextContext: We can overdraft for now, but...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107014_TextContext: As suspected, you no longer remember who I am.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105050_TextContext: Make sure the wounded are okay and pull them into cover, quickly!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103061_TextContext: The destruction of Komos Tower and all the victims of the Reverstring Storm... it's all my responsibility.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101054_TextContext: We've already taken in more patients than we can handle.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101071_TextContext: But after this is all over, I'll make you the best cup of Starlight Coffee ever!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104101_TextContext: Wait a moment... What was that “key” you mentioned?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106113_TextContext: Wait, you should treat your own wounds, too.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103162_TextContext: Let's not speak here. Follow me back to HQ.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105023_TextContext: Forget it. Let's not think about him right now. It's just going to make me angry.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102030_TextContext: Never mind, you need to wait patiently for prey.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103062_TextContext: Miss Michele... it's not your fault.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103112_TextContext: Miss Michele! Did you defuse the bomb?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103075_TextContext: Miss Michele, that Type P-4 bomb you mentioned... was it composed of two inverted pyramids?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105072_TextContext: Investigator Michele has arrived at the scene!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106097_TextContext: Michele, how much ammo have you got left?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104107_TextContext: Michele, can we reverse engineer the code with the keys we have?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104176_TextContext: Michele, look through the areas not targeted in the bombings and find the most valuable targets!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103151_TextContext: Michele, your initiative is a strength, but don't forget to look around and think clearly.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104149_TextContext: Michele, come with me. We need to help defuse the remaining bombs.
AVGEvent_Season2.231107099_TextContext: Our objective has been achieved. There's no reason for me to stay here.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102122_TextContext: To be honest, fighting... is not my strength.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102029_TextContext: The boss said he'd give me a mission. Could he have been stringing me around?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102129_TextContext: And from a selfish perspective... If we put a stop to the bombings, we'll also reduce the pressure being placed on the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104103_TextContext: My key pointed me to the Greenview Teahouse on 9th Street.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104088_TextContext: This was your weakness. It was why we were able to get you to break through your defenses.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103046_TextContext: Terrorist organizations that dare carry out such brazen attacks in P.U.S and Urbino territory... who else could it be?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107021_TextContext: Can you say something that makes sense?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106034_TextContext: Is this worth all the attention from Urbino?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102109_TextContext: A good doctor treats the disease, not the symptom.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102082_TextContext: I really want to help, but the Astral Sanctuary belongs to the Bai Group. According to Urbino regulations, board members are forbidden from involving themselves in each other's business.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106127_TextContext: Though I'm curious why Urbino would hold such a thing...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106126_TextContext: There's information there, but I can't access it with my clearance!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107147_TextContext: Even though we have more questions than answers, let's just be happy about today's victory for now.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101059_TextContext: If it weren't for you, the Astral Sanctuary would have been overwhelmed for sure.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106156_TextContext: To pay attention to what's in front of you?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104040_TextContext: If Nobunaga were here, he would never have allowed this.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106024_TextContext: How long is this going to take?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107164_TextContext: Let the Navigator have it. The Revelator will know how to proceed.
AVGEvent_Season2.231106015_TextContext: Let me look... do all these crystals really not interest you?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107081_TextContext: It's time I take my leave. Adios, troublesome children!
AVGEvent_Season2.231101107_TextContext: How can we arrange a meeting with such a bigwig?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104100_TextContext: Damn it! What have I done...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104067_TextContext: Damn it... You've been on to me?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104175_TextContext: Inciting all these bombings and stretching the Bureau of Investigation across the city... Their real purpose is...
AVGEvent_Season2.231103039_TextContext: Let's get back to the main story.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104098_TextContext: To be honest, I didn't think The Scissors were bold or capable enough. But... the destruction of the Komos Tower made me realize for the first time that the order established by P.U.S could be broken.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105084_TextContext: You're right. Michele, deploy smoke grenades!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103016_TextContext: Now that I think about it, Area 88 was part of her district. But we haven't had much contact since I opened the Astral Sanctuary...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104011_TextContext: Eh? How could I be angry at Celestia?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104140_TextContext: Citizens are advised to stay clear of the identified locations! Nearby search teams have already been dispatched to identify and defuse the bombs!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102677_TextContext: Please convey the minutes of this meeting and the previous sentence to our “Dear Leader...”
AVGEvent_Season2.231103052_TextContext: Don't worry, we won't tell anyone. Right, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Season2.231107015_TextContext: Please take good care of it...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107119_TextContext: Will someone tell me what happened to my vault?!
AVGEvent_Season2.231102083_TextContext: Thank you anyway, Lady Audrey. We will figure something out.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104050_TextContext: Follow me. Let's see what our prisoner has to say.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105135_TextContext: When the flames go out! Quickly!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106141_TextContext: Time for the protagonist to show themself?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106031_TextContext: You'd have been lucky to be teleported to the True Wilderness. Chances are you would have been torn to pieces on the spot.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103027_TextContext: But to her great fortune, a kind-hearted civilian comes to her aid! Thank you... uhm?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104150_TextContext: And Celestia - now you can do what you wanted.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104061_TextContext: What do you plan to do next?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102068_TextContext: That's not all. There's also this, and this, and this...
AVGEvent_Season2.231102076_TextContext: Um... nothing like that. There's nothing special about my family background.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103120_TextContext: W-What the heck is this? Fall back!
AVGEvent_Season2.231107060_TextContext: Now we have the upper hand.
AVGEvent_Season2.231105111_TextContext: They're finally showing their true face!
AVGEvent_Season2.231104144_TextContext: Now that we've identified all the bombs and foiled The Scissors' plot, the city can rest easy.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101075_TextContext: Who could it be at this time of day?
AVGEvent_Season2.231104033_TextContext: Such a large scale... this isn't a mere attack...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107160_TextContext: I can't be blamed for this.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104026_TextContext: And those are just the ones we know about. The Bureau of Investigation highly suspects that far more have already been planted...
AVGEvent_Season2.231105095_TextContext: This is the moment I've been waiting for.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101077_TextContext: What are we going to do? If this goes on, the Astral Sanctuary will...
AVGEvent_Season2.231107131_TextContext: It belongs to Grove Bank to begin with.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103141_TextContext: Still nothing? This guy... he must be a professional.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103042_TextContext: Let's work hard to crack the Area 88 bombing case together! You have my word... I'll bring those dastardly Scissors to justice!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106070_TextContext: This time, there won't be any more reinforcements.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102673_TextContext: Disappearing at a time like this... how could such a person become the leader of Urbino?
AVGEvent_Season2.231101035_TextContext: Notify the duty nurse. Make sure the patient is comfortable, using sedatives if necessary, and...
AVGEvent_Season2.231106172_TextContext: With reverse hydrolysis, such high-purity crystals should be able to...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104048_TextContext: Then... Kokona, what should we do now?
AVGEvent_Season2.231105113_TextContext: They must be the culprit behind all these events!
AVGEvent_Season2.231106123_TextContext: Is that thing really so important?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102086_TextContext: I'll take my leave for now. If chance permits, I would love to visit the Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Season2.231102105_TextContext: What's your point? Is there some problem with me worrying about my family's affairs? How does this concern the Astral Sanctuary?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103111_TextContext: What a coincidence... there's one right here!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103056_TextContext: I'll give you the truth, then...
AVGEvent_Season2.231103023_TextContext: Oi! You, over there! Stop laughing and help me out!
AVGEvent_Season2.231103060_TextContext: It's all my fault. I didn't see their true intentions, only the bait they dangled in front of me.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104141_TextContext: I will now repeat the previous message...
AVGEvent_Season2.231101063_TextContext: I start with normal coffee beans, then I add a bunch of herbs that help calm and revitalize the mind...
AVGEvent_Season2.231104104_TextContext: That's all I know. Sorry, I can't help you further.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103109_TextContext: Not unless... we force a way through with heavy firepower and armor.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101089_TextContext: The bombings have forced Urbino to redirect Bablo energy from surrounding areas to maintain the city's spatial integrity.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101091_TextContext: Is there really nothing else we can do...?
AVGEvent_Season2.231103108_TextContext: Don't we have any other options?
AVGEvent_Season2.231102041_TextContext: Could it be that he guessed we would come?
AVGEvent_Season2.231106105_TextContext: By the way, I only have three rounds left.
AVGEvent_Season2.231104049_TextContext: First, we need to understand our enemy.
AVGEvent_Season2.231101028_TextContext: (...Just as I was musing, someone pushes the lounge door ajar.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103020_TextContext: (A female figure wearing an investigator's uniform and cat-ear headphones struggles to squeeze herself out from the wall.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102049_TextContext: (A well-dressed blonde beauty stands in front of us.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104196_TextContext: (A hooded woman observes the street below her with interest.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107085_TextContext: (As a bright silver helicopter rises into view, the enemy deftly takes advantage of the air current to glide into the cabin.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104156_TextContext: (A strange sense of unease lingers in my mind.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107118_TextContext: (The sound of rapid footsteps interrupts our thoughts.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105133_TextContext: (Audrey fires three grenades, igniting a raging flame at the point of impact.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103094_TextContext: (Right after, a muzzle flash appears from behind the cover, revealing a bullet fired in Celestia's direction.
AVGEvent_Season2.231103137_TextContext: (No way. He's not a superstring being, and he can't wall-stick... there's no way he could get away that quickly.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104004_TextContext: (There seem to be a lot of other patrol cars also rushing in this direction.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101049_TextContext: (It might be more accurate to say “sunrise...”)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106067_TextContext: (After splitting up from the rest of the party, Audrey stands her ground by a shattered wall.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104126_TextContext: (With the investigators busy at work, Celestia seems a little restless.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107133_TextContext: (I try to take the bracelet off to hand it to Audrey, but it's firmly attached to my wrist at the perfect size.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101016_TextContext: (Overwhelmed by the influx of patients from the explosion, the Astral Sanctuary has been operating at full capacity day and night.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102035_TextContext: (I look around, but the mysterious girl has vanished without a trace.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104003_TextContext: (We follow the patrol car holding the suspect back to the Bureau of Investigation HQ.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104132_TextContext: (The two remain silent for a while, neither willing to back down. They really are very similar in their stubbornness.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106148_TextContext: (A high-caliber sniper round pierces through the hail of bullets and flies toward the enemy.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106153_TextContext: (Mighty Meowblast unleashes a wave of fire, giving the enemy a taste of their own medicine.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106121_TextContext: (Bullets roar like a horrible typhoon, plowing directly into the load-bearing pillar the three are hiding behind.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107032_TextContext: (A zapping pain spreads throughout my body.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101003_TextContext: (Komos Tower crumbles in a violent explosion.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107005_TextContext: (The sound of waves crashing can be heard in the distance...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101020_TextContext: (Her body trembles slightly, and she lets out a light sniff. Guess the air conditioner might be a bit too strong.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106102_TextContext: (But the purple figure has already dodged into the next piece of cover.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106169_TextContext: (But despite it all, her face is steeled with the resolve to complete her mission.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102048_TextContext: (But what we found was not “Mr. Bai,” but “her.”)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107040_TextContext: (But without the superstring reaction caused by the bullet, the crystalline explosion has far less impact.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104122_TextContext: (Until the database is cracked, Kokona can only rely on her experience, intuition, and Anderson's assistance to identify possible targets.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106096_TextContext: (The container being used as cover makes constant creaking noises, like an animal's dying groan.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102128_TextContext: (Seems as if the idea of leaving anyone untreated had never even entered her mind.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107059_TextContext: (They're plastered over the wall like one of those old-world cartoons.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104157_TextContext: (I look again at the display with all the bombing targets.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107056_TextContext: (With a huge gust of wind, the Pummeler crashes against the enemy's chest with a firm thud.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101034_TextContext: (Despite just waking from her slumber, Celestia immediately returns to work mode and skillfully instructs the nurse on how to proceed.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103083_TextContext: (Bustling with activity just a few minutes ago, the Greenview Teahouse is now eerily silent, illuminated only by an active Type P-4 bomb blinking with a dazzling red light.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101066_TextContext: (What a weird-sounding coffee... can it even be considered coffee at this point?)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103096_TextContext: (Celestia stringifies just in time, the bullet missing her two-dimensional body by a hair.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101017_TextContext: (Even now, the consulting room outside the lounge is still teeming with people.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105087_TextContext: (The Grove security team originally stationed at the entrance also takes advantage of the situation to put down covering fire with their remaining ammo.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105039_TextContext: (Led by several instigators, a commotion starts breaking out in the crowd.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105015_TextContext: (Damn it... how many people do we need to knock out before this riot ends...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103135_TextContext: (All of a sudden, the suspect disappears from Michele's sight.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105093_TextContext: (At the same time, on the other side.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106167_TextContext: (Simultaneously hit by an explosion and rain of bullets, the enemy seems pinned to the wall.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103004_TextContext: (Celestia and I head to the meeting place we agreed on with the P.U.S investigator.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107058_TextContext: (The enemy stringifies to avoid the full brunt of the attack, but there's still enough force to send them flying.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105126_TextContext: (By the time we collect ourselves, we find that our position has already been surrounded.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105065_TextContext: (Having fought her way into the enemy's ranks alone, Audrey is quickly surrounded.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103092_TextContext: (As the panicked crowd disperses at the sound of the gunshot, we spot a tall figure deftly hiding behind cover.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104191_TextContext: (Everyone turns their attention back to Michele and waits for her unspoken answer.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107156_TextContext: (With the sounds of everyone's laughter, I wonder if the Neutroville bombings have finally come to an end...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105006_TextContext: (Before her stands a tide of thugs slamming against the blockade, her slender figure like a lone boat amidst the storm.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103103_TextContext: (During a brief lull in enemy fire, Celestia tries to counterattack, but is quickly suppressed once more.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107132_TextContext: (At some point in the battle, the bracelet somehow ended up on my wrist.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103121_TextContext: (Faced with Mighty Meow's terrifying firepower, the suspects panic and begin fleeing in all directions.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103093_TextContext: (The moment our eyes meet, the suspect realizes they've been found out.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106149_TextContext: (Forced to take evasive maneuvers, the enemy lets up their fire.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106189_TextContext: (A dark blue hue engulfs the battlefield.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102002_TextContext: (We stand in front of the lobby, clearly out of place given all the side-eye we're getting from the people coming and going.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101004_TextContext: (With Area 88's anchor point gone, a Reverstring Storm spews forth from the newly formed cracks of space and sweeps through most of the city block.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105010_TextContext: (Harsh and provocative words are mixed in with the shouting.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102069_TextContext: (Audrey throws more and more piles of documents onto the desk as she continues shouting.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105131_TextContext: (Audrey takes three grenades from her waist and switches her weapon to launcher mode.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105034_TextContext: (Audrey looks down from the observation deck to see several Molotov cocktails being thrown from the crowd, the flames burning at the entrance and into the sky.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105056_TextContext: (Like a proud unicorn rushing into a sea of thugs, Audrey carves a path through.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105012_TextContext: (Audrey fires her machine gun into the mob.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107136_TextContext: (Audrey twists and turns my arm, searching for the bracelet's item number.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103091_TextContext: (She takes out her weapon and fires a shot into the air.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102089_TextContext: (What little hope we held was instantly extinguished. Even though Celestia hasn't said anything, I can see the sense of loss in her eyes.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106093_TextContext: (If those guys were really The Scissors, then just who is our enemy?)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103116_TextContext: (Startled by the thrown object, the suspects unload their weapons onto Mighty Meow.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103118_TextContext: (Fully armed, Mighty Meow takes aim at the nearest suspect, instantly knocking him down with two dazzling superstring beams.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106171_TextContext: (An eerie silence washes over the battlefield.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106072_TextContext: (Intense gunfire rings out from all directions, then a flash of red fire appears in front of Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104005_TextContext: (After we transfer the suspect to the stationed guard...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101109_TextContext: (With Celestia deep in thought, a taxi stops outside the gate of the Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101027_TextContext: (Even if it's just for a while, I really hope that Celestia can get some proper rest.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107039_TextContext: (A huge explosion sounds, just like in my vision.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105100_TextContext: (A huge roar resounds through the sky.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107053_TextContext: (Michele casts aside her empty rifle, and the moment the enemy realizes something is wrong...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102674_TextContext: (After calming her breath, Audrey realizes that her behavior might have appeared rude.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107185_TextContext: (There's little light in this quiet place. Only the ouroboros-shaped bracelet reflects a natural shine in the darkness.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105005_TextContext: (A powerful wind blows against her golden hair, which shines as glorious as the morning light.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101050_TextContext: (When Celestia was taking her short nap, the clock had already struck twelve.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104160_TextContext: (They're far apart from one another and scattered across Neutroville in what seems to be a random manner.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101019_TextContext: (Her face illuminated by the weak glow of a computer screen, the white-haired girl let out a slight snore as she was nestled on the desk.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104154_TextContext: (Kokona drags Michele with her to finish up the operation.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104114_TextContext: (Kokona forces her way into the control center and nervously issues orders to all dispatched teams.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104108_TextContext: (Kokona shouts her suggestion through the two-way glass. Michele's voice comes crackling through the speaker in response.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105086_TextContext: (Kokona and Michele skillfully deploy smoke grenades to block the enemy's line of sight in key areas.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106177_TextContext: (Kokona turns her gaze to the Navigator's side.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106186_TextContext: (A flickering indigo light bursts from the cracking crystal structure.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105127_TextContext: (We'll be lucky to make it through them in one piece.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102051_TextContext: (Our arrival seems to have surprised her.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102046_TextContext: (We follow the receptionist's instructions to the meeting place.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103009_TextContext: (There's a line of people queued up to buy breakfast.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104121_TextContext: (More and more confirmed bombings flash red on the screen. There's already been 20, and the number is only increasing.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107080_TextContext: (The enemy strafes back and forth as they cover their retreat with gunfire.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106187_TextContext: (The enemy throws the cracking crystal at the bullet, causing a huge explosion.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104158_TextContext: (Dozens of flashing red spots with no clear pattern.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106150_TextContext: (Seizing on the opportunity, Michele rushes out of cover.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104180_TextContext: (With each passing minute, silence weighs heavily on the hearts of everyone in the control center. Only the click-clacking of keyboards echoes throughout the halls.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103008_TextContext: (It's 8:00 AM, just in time for the morning rush.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102021_TextContext: (Despite her conspicuous dress, I somehow didn't notice her at all until she started speaking.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107024_TextContext: (The stars that make up the figure grow unstable and gradually become covered in an ominous scarlet glow.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101081_TextContext: (It's an arrears warning from the Urbino Public Utilities Office.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101085_TextContext: (Celestia takes out her phone and quickly searches for reports on energy price spikes.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101074_TextContext: (Celestia's phone suddenly rings with a notification.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101067_TextContext: (Looks like it'll be hard to refuse Celestia directly. I'll have to...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102121_TextContext: (Celestia closes her eyes and takes a deep breath. When she opens them, they are wide and full of determination.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102037_TextContext: (Forget it for now. We should focus on the matter at hand.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105003_TextContext: (A rioting crowd carrying homemade weapons assaults the makeshift barrier at the front of the building, hurling shouts and expletives.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105134_TextContext: (The flames force the thugs back, cutting a path through the building.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103058_TextContext: (On several occasions throughout the story, I could feel Michele's body tremble in anger and frustration.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102087_TextContext: (As Audrey turns to leave, Celestia lowers her gaze once more.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105069_TextContext: (A shot from beyond the encirclement precisely knocks down an enemy approaching Audrey from behind.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106174_TextContext: (The enemy pries open a loose container and slips a bright crystal into their hands.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107048_TextContext: (Gunfire rings out once more, the remaining bullets making up a web of fire.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105041_TextContext: (Gunshots, explosions, curses, and shouts... a cacophony of chaotic noises meld into one another.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106095_TextContext: (Hails of fire rain down from both sides, sending a cascade of bullet casting to the floor.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105058_TextContext: (The machinegun sings a song across the battlefield, its sharp gaze sweeping over the enemies before it.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105046_TextContext: (The escalating violence at the entrance to Grove Bank has been going on for half an hour.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103101_TextContext: (The shots are poorly aimed, but the rain of fire pins the stringified Celestia behind cover.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102047_TextContext: (Using the signposts to guide us, we pass through the hustle and bustle, a symbol of Urbino's prosperity and influence.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106112_TextContext: (The purple light appears again, but far dimmer than before.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105057_TextContext: (The flames of Audrey's machine gun roar with unceasing passion as she stringifies to dodge enemies and continues her counterattack.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106162_TextContext: (The fire envelopes Michele and the enemy.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105141_TextContext: (Amidst the blazing flames, Audrey watches as the others make their way through, only letting out a breath when she sees them enter the building.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107084_TextContext: (A huge roar accompanies a massive air current, disrupting everyone's movements.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105036_TextContext: (Surprised by the sudden gunshot, the Grove security team looks at each other in confusion.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103117_TextContext: (To their shock, Mighty Meow seems virtually unscathed.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105014_TextContext: (But the crowd continues to move forward, pushing the hesitating thugs into the front.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104152_TextContext: (With all the targets identified, the Bureau of Investigation fully mobilizes to defuse the bombs and perform rescue operations.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106091_TextContext: (Another explosion sounds, sending debris from the building raining down on the battlefield.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105049_TextContext: (An explosion rages, almost sending the security team's defensive formation toppling over.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106122_TextContext: (The storm of bullets interjects in the conversation.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104188_TextContext: (The voice on the line was familiar... strong and proud...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104187_TextContext: (The call ends abruptly amid the noise of gunfire.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106068_TextContext: (Faced with the overwhelming firepower of her machine gun, the thugs dare not approach her, but...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102675_TextContext: (Audrey coughs twice in embarrassment, then rearranges her hair and resumes her elegant posture.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105053_TextContext: (Growing impatient, Audrey places a new ammo belt into her weapon, then quickly steps forward.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101015_TextContext: (Celestia, who was still slumped over her desk working just a moment ago, was now fast asleep.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104153_TextContext: (In a flash, the previously busy control center becomes empty.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102092_TextContext: (Looks like there isn't any other choice.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102014_TextContext: (As I watch Celestia move toward the desk, I feel a sense of relief.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103010_TextContext: (Groups of regulars are standing in the distance, chatting away with cups in their hand.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102088_TextContext: (It seems like Urbino has many moving parts, and this “Mr. Bai” isn't someone you can get an audience with easily.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104057_TextContext: (The suspect is handcuffed to the table. The height of the table and chairs seem designed to make the person sitting here as uncomfortable as possible.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107002_TextContext: (The explosion swallows everything around it, causing an intense buzzing in everyone's head.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103144_TextContext: (Bang! The piercing sound of a gunshot rings through the air.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104195_TextContext: (Some time ago, at an observation point with a vantage point over Grove Bank.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106165_TextContext: (Through the flames and smoke, two figures rush toward the enemy.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103081_TextContext: (The sudden crisis has caught us all off guard.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103018_TextContext: (Suddenly, a commotion breaks out in the crowd.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104056_TextContext: (This is my first time in the interrogation room. It's a bit hard to adapt to the depressing atmosphere.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103057_TextContext: (Michele gives us a complete account of the events that took place at Komos Tower on the day of its destruction.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103142_TextContext: (In the murky shadows beyond Michele's gaze, the cold steel of a pistol slithers forth, its presence as silent as the grave.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104178_TextContext: (Michele quickly searches through a list of possible targets.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103149_TextContext: (The tall suspect lay shackled on the pavement, his firearm discarded nearby. A telltale bullet scar etched upon its chamber betrays the precision of a well-aimed shot that sent it tumbling aside.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103150_TextContext: (Michele has a look of disbelief. Standing in front of us is an investigator carrying a massive sniper rifle completely out of proportion with her body.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103084_TextContext: (Michele skillfully takes out her defusal kit and begins cracking the detonation program.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103134_TextContext: (Michele pursues the tall suspect into the back alley of 9th Street.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106152_TextContext: (Michele quickly calls out her mechanical comrade.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103082_TextContext: (Michele rushes to evacuate the crowd gathered at the entrance to the teahouse.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102020_TextContext: (Her tight-fitting cycling jersey doesn't do much to hide her strong physique. Could she be an athlete?)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106168_TextContext: (Her purple cloak is heavily damaged, and numerous Bablo wounds have formed on her body.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107076_TextContext: (Purple liquid drips from the enemy's fingertips as they move toward the crystal cabinet behind them.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106164_TextContext: (A blue and violet light flickers amid the red flames.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106161_TextContext: (Bursting red flames and flashing shockwaves illuminate the damaged building once more.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102036_TextContext: (In the end, I wasn't able to discover the identity of that girl or her “boss...”)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107030_TextContext: (The image of something I had never seen before pops into my mind: the rapid friction between a sniper round and a cracking crystal...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107049_TextContext: (Despite being staggered, the enemy figure still deftly avoids the death being rained down upon them.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103090_TextContext: (Though confused at my instructions, Celestia chooses to trust my judgment.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107031_TextContext: (Two figures blown into the air... and the ruins of a battlefield.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106160_TextContext: (Kokona sends a grenade flying with all her strength.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107037_TextContext: (The crystal curves into the air, breaking apart more and more the further it travels...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106056_TextContext: (Before he can finish speaking, gunfire rings out, forcing the mysterious purple figure to evade.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103114_TextContext: (Michele produces a round cat-shaped bot and throws it toward the enemy position.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102091_TextContext: (At the end of the corridor, Audrey walks in quick strides, her figure about to disappear from sight.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231107025_TextContext: (Its form becomes more twisted and unnerving.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102016_TextContext: (It's not a bad start. At least we know Mr. Bai is a real person, and he really does have connections with Urbino.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231104159_TextContext: (The locations chosen were neither key facilities nor densely populated areas.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103007_TextContext: (This teahouse has a market-like feel, and it seems like it also serves snacks and breakfast.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102127_TextContext: (It's as if she was saying, “No matter how many more people are injured, I'll take on the burden of treating them all.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102015_TextContext: (I watch Celestia speak with the receptionist, and though I'm too far away to hear what they're saying, the receptionist's expression betrays that she's had the conversation about Mr. Bai many times before. She seems visibly pained.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103148_TextContext: (As we chase Michele into the alleyway, we're greeted with an unexpected sight.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231101002_TextContext: (That night, as a flash of light struck through the sky...)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105004_TextContext: (An elegant and proud lady stands at the forefront.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103021_TextContext: (She looks like a plump cat trying to get through a piece of railing.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106178_TextContext: (Ordinary but powerful fingertips make contact with the bracelet.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102090_TextContext: (We've already come this far... is there really no other way?!)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105013_TextContext: (The barrage of non-lethal rounds knocks down the lead rioters, making those ready to charge hesitate.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231105035_TextContext: (Subsequently, a shot is fired, silencing the crowd.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103119_TextContext: (Its first enemy dispatched, Mighty Meow turns to aim at the next suspect.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106101_TextContext: (A booming sound rings out as Kokona's bullet penetrates the shaky container.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231106185_TextContext: (As dark purple liquid flows into the crystal, its faint blue light starts to change.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103100_TextContext: (Shots ring out from four other places in the crowd.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231103011_TextContext: (The destruction of Komos Tower seems to just be one of many topics for them.)
AVGEvent_Season2.231102050_TextContext: (Her high ponytail drapes across both sides of her shoulders, giving her a refined and capable appearance. Her childish face held a stubborn look. It feels like she's not the kind to be easy to get along with.)

AVGEvent_Season3.240101023_TextContext: “But they successfully foiled the enemy's plans and protected the key assets of Urbino members at great cost.”
AVGEvent_Season3.240103080_TextContext: The Compound Eye. That's the name.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106024_TextContext: My name is Rafa. The organization is called New Bethlehem.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104088_TextContext: You're from Astral Sanctuary of Grove Enterprises, right? To what do I owe the pleasure?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101022_TextContext: “Grove Enterprises bore the brunt of these attacks from... ah... “unknown anti-Urbino forces...”
AVGEvent_Season3.240106118_TextContext: You're too troublesome in your current state.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102091_TextContext: The Steel Unicorn... It's quite something to have such an exaggerated nickname.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105043_TextContext: The Steel Unicorn has always been my ally.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108223_TextContext: ...“The protagonist awakens the sleeping princess, healing the curse with the power of miracles.”
AVGEvent_Season3.240103020_TextContext: ...It seems like forever ago when we last shared some peace and quiet together.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109077_TextContext: ...That concludes the incident report. Please accept my apologies for borrowing your agents.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101087_TextContext: If you don't mind... The mysterious dancer in front of you is no other than Mr. Bai Mo, president of the Bai Group and leader of the Urbino Business Alliance.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108051_TextContext: ...Even without the spider silk, I've seen through your tricks.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109070_TextContext: ...You're talking about the Navigator. Very well. I won't stop you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101047_TextContext: ...I am certain that the meeting time has been formally communicated to the Bai Group.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108005_TextContext: ...I've brought Audrey with me. Are you satisfied now?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108253_TextContext: ...How dare you refer to my masterpiece as a fake. What does that make you, then?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103108_TextContext: ...This is the first time I've heard this name.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108284_TextContext: It's all for The Great Awakening. Until then, please take care of the “staff” for us.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101155_TextContext: Your short-sightedness could destroy a brand-new, long-term value chain!
AVGEvent_Season3.240102075_TextContext: Bai Mo interrupted our last meeting. But they won't let it go. I'm sure of it.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104133_TextContext: Remember when I tested your arcade machine?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103114_TextContext: No... You are truly valuable to me...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104084_TextContext: Of course you are... L-Let them go!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106057_TextContext: It's fine if you don't. We've prepared another welcome gift for you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107079_TextContext: You shall not harm Lady Audrey!!!
AVGEvent_Season3.240105047_TextContext: If not, I could give you another one.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104070_TextContext: Sorry. We have been instructed that all members of Grove Enterprises must be investigated by Urbino Security.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101046_TextContext: Sorry, I must have overdid it. Weren't you all in the middle of a lively discussion?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106006_TextContext: I didn't have time to say hi last time. Sorry about that.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106015_TextContext: You're welcome. Your vault hadn't been cleaned for a while and smelled of mold. I was just helping you air it out.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106044_TextContext: Not only that... We'll even make you the leader of Urbino.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103066_TextContext: Can I not hang out with you if I'm not a patient, Miss Celestia?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106035_TextContext: No matter what evidence you want to leave behind or any information you want to leak, you'd end up being the one in trouble.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108088_TextContext: Do not stop. Do not despair, for there is a greater power between you and her...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108268_TextContext: Too many unwanted guests have shown up. I'm afraid that the show has to end here.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103088_TextContext: But... Before that, I need you to answer a few questions, Miss Celestia.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107153_TextContext: However, you must be at your limit, no?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101157_TextContext: However, if Astral Sanctuary carries on with its current management policy, our return will be disproportionate to our investment. Unless...
AVGEvent_Season3.240109058_TextContext: Nonetheless, now that we have ruled out Grove Enterprises...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102037_TextContext: You're actually the one who taught me to act this way, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109071_TextContext: However, instead of a resignation, let's treat it as a leave of absence.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101119_TextContext: Good choice. This one is uplifting but quite long. This may take a while.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104145_TextContext: Not bad, Navigator. This is valuable advice.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101145_TextContext: There is no need for words. I've learned everything from the navigator's dancing.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102046_TextContext: No, Celestia... I promise you that this will not affect our relationship. You and the Navigator will always be my friends.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102102_TextContext: No, this is a private address. There are few who know it...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101069_TextContext: No, I mean... Don't overthink it.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106119_TextContext: Rather than wasting my breath with you now, let's reset you to your factory settings first.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107022_TextContext: Rather than a unicorn, she's more like a wounded lioness.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101160_TextContext: In the interest of expanding and treating more patients, I'm sure you wouldn't mind giving up a tiny bit of profit, Miss Celestia, would you?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104034_TextContext: To avoid a repeat of what happened last time, the Bureau of Investigation offered to help Urbino maintain public order.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105054_TextContext: Why would New Bethlehem help an outsider take over as the leader of Urbino?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107101_TextContext: Why? Why can't I hit her?!
AVGEvent_Season3.240104033_TextContext: The widespread dissatisfaction toward Grove Enterprises has now turned to the Bai Group.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104105_TextContext: The next Urbino leadership election is about to start. Audrey's Grove Enterprises stands to be the Bai Group's biggest competitor.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101167_TextContext: Urbino does not force sales, nor do we engage in deception. All transactions are made on the basis of free will.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101146_TextContext: The choice of music perfectly reflects Astral Sanctuary's ideals...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107146_TextContext: Thanks to your stupidity, I now have a chance to tame this crazy wild horse.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105019_TextContext: Perhaps you've only seen what I want you to see.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105021_TextContext: Have you been deceiving others for so long that you've even fooled yourself?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102084_TextContext: Buying a failing clinic. You would never agree to something that makes as little financial sense as this, would you?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106078_TextContext: Don't you think it's time for you to get off your high horse?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109087_TextContext: Induced collapse syndrome... Is that really possible?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106060_TextContext: What are you talking about? What have you done?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104030_TextContext: Since this morning, there have been non-stop negative news reports about Bai Mo, the leader of Urbino.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102033_TextContext: This was a chance for me to vent my frustration. I feel much better already.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108125_TextContext: Shall we call it a day, shark girl?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103064_TextContext: We're done with patient appointments for the day.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102043_TextContext: From now on, Astral Sanctuary is an ally of Grove Enterprises.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105097_TextContext: You're under my command from now on.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102078_TextContext: He wouldn't really believe I'd agree to such a reckless proposal, would he?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106071_TextContext: It only takes him a single day to handle work that would take me a whole week. By doing only the strictly necessary tasks, he keeps the entire alliance running smoothly.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109024_TextContext: You always seemed troubled and spoke sternly... Oh. Don't get me wrong!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106092_TextContext: Spreading rumors is one thing, but I will not help you fabricate lies out of nothing!
AVGEvent_Season3.240108101_TextContext: Pass on our emotions, Astral Gate!
AVGEvent_Season3.240108256_TextContext: The fabled Compound Eye... Don't you forget - we've still got hostages...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107129_TextContext: But somehow, in that instant, I felt as if you were telling me where the enemy would attack...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101175_TextContext: Remember: the moment you walk out of this room, you can kiss our money goodbye.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108162_TextContext: But I am not Audrey Grove. I am not The Steel Unicorn...
AVGEvent_Season3.240109069_TextContext: But by staying with them, I can become stronger and meet more powerful opponents.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107200_TextContext: However... you will not get in my way again.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103143_TextContext: However... the Grove Bank Incident has reconnected the two.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102021_TextContext: But, Audrey... don't you forget that you're a permanent director of Urbino.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102085_TextContext: But why... Why do I instinctively want to do this?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102047_TextContext: In return, could you promise me something?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103024_TextContext: Come to think of it... There is a lot about you that I have yet to know.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103029_TextContext: However, as a fellow researcher, I'd never heard of you...
AVGEvent_Season3.240103086_TextContext: If I'm being honest, it's poorly written, glossing over many details.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107024_TextContext: But this is precisely what makes the hunt valuable.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103067_TextContext: You... What did you do to Nana?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108283_TextContext: Don't you know the answer already?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107191_TextContext: How did you defeat me? I mean, you seem pretty weak...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106037_TextContext: You don't want people to find out that you have been in contact with the organization, do you?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108028_TextContext: Why don't you struggle a bit for me?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108014_TextContext: What do you mean? Who else could there be?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104023_TextContext: Where the heck did you come from?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105085_TextContext: Are you... from the Bureau of Investigation?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106043_TextContext: Can you... really help Grove Enterprises survive the crisis?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103102_TextContext: The mastermind behind the Grove Bank Incident...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106064_TextContext: You're not going to blow up the Bai Group, are you?!
AVGEvent_Season3.240103121_TextContext: You were saying New Bethlehem's style was similar to something?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101004_TextContext: Have you heard? Are the rumors true?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105087_TextContext: What are you muttering about? Lay down your weapon!
AVGEvent_Season3.240107069_TextContext: You will take your leave now!
AVGEvent_Season3.240105071_TextContext: Keep wearing that mask of yours. One day, I will strip it piece by piece.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106048_TextContext: You've seen what New Bethlehem is capable of...
AVGEvent_Season3.240109021_TextContext: Your investment will earn its return.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106162_TextContext: Collapse syndrome will destroy your consciousness. You will be reincarnated at the New Bethlehem facility and start anew.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108244_TextContext: You're... quite good at encouraging others. However, that's a hard pass from me.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106080_TextContext: Do you truly believe that you can save Grove Enterprises via legitimate means?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108214_TextContext: Do you know who I am?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108239_TextContext: What are you talking about? Do you... know me?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109014_TextContext: Look at you. Joking and all that.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108024_TextContext: Are you a hunter as well?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107185_TextContext: Mercenary? I don't get it. Why did you save us?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105010_TextContext: An important member of New Bethlehem, according to intel.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103039_TextContext: Your secrets actually make you more charming!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101099_TextContext: Hold that thought... Miss Celestia, would you care to dance?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102072_TextContext: To add insult to injury, the decline in our credibility has also led to a loss of our savings.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103006_TextContext: Bye, Nana. Listen to your mom when you get home, okay?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101165_TextContext: Besides, I've provided nothing but the most reasonable solution given the current situation.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107128_TextContext: I thought... surely, I'd be hit...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101154_TextContext: Innovation and pioneering are Urbino's lifeblood. As its leader, you should be well aware of that!
AVGEvent_Season3.240109053_TextContext: Don't... Oh, you turned it off already...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106160_TextContext: Stop struggling. You're only making it worse for yourself.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108021_TextContext: Don't shoot next to me! You're going to make me deaf!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101139_TextContext: Don't beat yourself up. My record is hard to beat.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101117_TextContext: Don't be naive. A gentle song doesn't necessarily mean it's easy.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104009_TextContext: Shut up! Tell Bai Mo to come out!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101062_TextContext: Don't act as if I'm invisible.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108270_TextContext: Don't worry. I've got a more interesting idea in mind...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107142_TextContext: Relax. New Bethlehem will heal her...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106202_TextContext: Stop! Don't go! Help me out!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101050_TextContext: Oh, come on. I'm still the leader of Urbino, aren't I?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106180_TextContext: What are they talking about? It's late already...
AVGEvent_Season3.240100009_TextContext: What is going on with you, Audrey Grove?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106213_TextContext: What is going on with you, Audrey Grove?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102092_TextContext: What method did you use... What tricks did you have...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106163_TextContext: Perhaps then, we can resume our negotiation.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103056_TextContext: Navigator... do you think the people after the bracelet will come back?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103052_TextContext: Haven't you been trying to activate it to no avail?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103031_TextContext: What kind of research did you do back at P.U.S?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107209_TextContext: The Navigator is right... Your body cannot handle another fight as intense as the last one!
AVGEvent_Season3.240102052_TextContext: The Navigator is right! Your support has made it possible!
AVGEvent_Season3.240109029_TextContext: What did you do back then, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108044_TextContext: Is Miss Fuchsia going to be fine, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106053_TextContext: The Scissors dared not to do that.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105016_TextContext: I see... I'm getting to know you better.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102055_TextContext: Go on, then. There must be patients waiting for you back at Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108164_TextContext: After all, I'll just be replaced with another Audrey...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102103_TextContext: It's sent by an anonymous sender with an encoded address.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104032_TextContext: People are livid to find out that the leader is such an errant guy.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109025_TextContext: It's just that you seem more relaxed now. This, in turn, will benefit the treatment of collapse syndrome.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106072_TextContext: It's simply unfair to refer to him as “irresponsible”!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106084_TextContext: All you have to do is rub a little more salt into the wound... Shift the blame for the Grove Bank Incident to Bai Mo...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102020_TextContext: I have no reason to reject a fair deal. This will also enable Astral Sanctuary to generate value for me.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106049_TextContext: If we want to, we can even initiate a Reverstring Storm in Neutroville at a moment's notice.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101031_TextContext: So long as Grove Enterprises can take responsibility, calm public sentiment, and properly compensate Urbino's members for their losses, there's no reason to talk about revoking their board seat.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109030_TextContext: I would like to keep that secret.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105084_TextContext: Could you please come back to the station with us?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104082_TextContext: But Mr. Bai Rui instructed that...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107130_TextContext: Who is she? Why did she attack Lady Audrey?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104110_TextContext: If we stand back and do nothing, the mastermind behind all this is going to get exactly what they want.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107193_TextContext: Perhaps... I was just lucky? You're a formidable opponent, Miss Fuchsia...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107156_TextContext: Devour everything, the Flood of Lent.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104108_TextContext: I hope that answers your question. Go home now. There's nothing you can do to help.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101110_TextContext: Sounds a lot better than “mysterious dancer”.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101025_TextContext: It sounds like everyone here owes Grove Enterprises their thanks...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106023_TextContext: Tell me. You and the organization you work for - who are you people? What do you want?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109017_TextContext: Heh... This is not too bad.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109034_TextContext: Heh... Indeed, it's hard to explain...
AVGEvent_Season3.240103124_TextContext: Heh. You may have heard of this story.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103118_TextContext: Heh. Don't you worry. The Compound Eye does not need two players.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103008_TextContext: Don't be silly, Nana. You're free to hang out with me even if you're not sick.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103116_TextContext: If you like, we could meet in private...
AVGEvent_Season3.240109041_TextContext: Heh. In the end, we managed to figure out nothing. We may never know.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103073_TextContext: Very well. Allow me to introduce myself...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102032_TextContext: Phew... It's fine. I've been wanting to teach that guy a lesson for a while now.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109042_TextContext: That's nothing compared to saving a patient.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107006_TextContext: Ah... Get out of my way...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104147_TextContext: I don't follow. Was that a riddle, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102081_TextContext: Hmm... It's a complete deadlock. There's no way out.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106113_TextContext: Ha-ha... You've brought this upon yourself, Audrey Grove.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108193_TextContext: Ha-ha... What are you doing? Are we in a fairy tale play?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101097_TextContext: Ha-ha. I'll take that as a compliment.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104144_TextContext: Ha-ha-ha! Interesting! You have a valid point!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101084_TextContext: Ha-ha. Art indeed requires an audience!
AVGEvent_Season3.240102013_TextContext: Are you serious? This is going to make today's headlines.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109050_TextContext: You're here. I've been waiting for you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101063_TextContext: You... Navigator, you are yet another unpredictable person.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106022_TextContext: Humph. Don't be arrogant... I'll let you off this time.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101174_TextContext: You really don't like me, do you? Very well... Be that as it may.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106201_TextContext: By the way, should you fail again, the Revelator is going to be furious.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103034_TextContext: Oh! You don't have to tell me anything if you are bound by an NDA!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106075_TextContext: You're right about that. I absolutely detest his carefree attitude.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101052_TextContext: Topic? What are you talking about?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101005_TextContext: Eh? You mean the board asking Audrey to step down as permanent director?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106099_TextContext: Tsk... After all our efforts, it still ended up this way.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106193_TextContext: Hey! Julian! What the heck happened back there?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108269_TextContext: Hey! Are we retreating? What about the Revelator's plan?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101176_TextContext: Thanks for your kind words. Goodbye, Mr. Bai.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101006_TextContext: Shh... shh! Not so loud! Don't forget, that's the “Steel Unicorn” we're talking about...
AVGEvent_Season3.240103153_TextContext: Beep beep... Beep beep... Beep beep...
AVGEvent_Season3.240103151_TextContext: Beep beep... The number you have reached is not available.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103152_TextContext: Beep beep... The number you have reached is not available.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104041_TextContext: Don't worry about it. You don't have to tell me anything.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108181_TextContext: Because I made you a promise!
AVGEvent_Season3.240109062_TextContext: Stay off the radar for a while until the next mission.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106079_TextContext: Did you really not expect this would happen when you accepted our invitation?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103026_TextContext: Your résumé mentioned that you were an expert on collapse syndrome back at P.U.S...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102093_TextContext: How many different sides of you lie in the diary I have yet to finish reading?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107206_TextContext: We want the same thing. Until New Bethlehem is defeated, anyway.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103079_TextContext: There is an independent special intelligence unit within P.U.S...
AVGEvent_Season3.240103126_TextContext: In just three years, the heir built the most prosperous business empire of Neutroville, becoming one of the permanent directors of Urbino in the process.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108196_TextContext: In a fairy tale... The person who awakens the princess has to take responsibility.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106038_TextContext: You can speak freely. No signal gets through these walls.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104090_TextContext: Before I answer your question, could you please tell me what is going on?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103106_TextContext: The dangerous organization the Compound Eye has been tracking...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104007_TextContext: Listen to me, folks! Do not fight! Do not fight!
AVGEvent_Season3.240109013_TextContext: I thought we were all on a first-name basis?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103112_TextContext: Someone as talented as you leaving was a true loss for P.U.S.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103053_TextContext: How peculiar... Have I been wearing it all this time?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108216_TextContext: Weird. The symptoms of collapse syndrome are gone.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106073_TextContext: How peculiar. I thought you hated him.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107204_TextContext: Audrey Grove is my target. I won't allow anyone else to steal my prey.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103148_TextContext: Is Audrey Grove on the dark side or the light side...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108241_TextContext: Let me ask you again, Audrey Grove...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106007_TextContext: You won't blame me, Lady Audrey, would you?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104154_TextContext: Audrey went to Port Euler alone...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102031_TextContext: Lady Audrey... Please accept my apologies. I didn't mean to cause you any trouble.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104119_TextContext: No one has seen or heard from Lady Audrey since this morning.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102045_TextContext: Lady Audrey is now a majority stockholder of Astral Sanctuary. You'll have to mind your manners with her, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101059_TextContext: I know you're very busy, Lady Audrey. I'm sorry to have to drag you with us to meet with Mr. Bai.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101171_TextContext: Lady Audrey is right. I cannot entrust the hope of curing collapse syndrome patients to someone like you, Mr. Bai.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107140_TextContext: Lady Audrey! Put her down right now!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101020_TextContext: Lady Audrey, regarding what happened at Grove Bank...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107133_TextContext: She seemed like she was experiencing the symptoms of collapse syndrome! She needs immediate medical attention!
AVGEvent_Season3.240108113_TextContext: How is she capable of that?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101045_TextContext: Long time no see, Audrey. Oh, and all you guys, too!
AVGEvent_Season3.240103022_TextContext: Back when I just joined Astral Sanctuary, if I recall correctly.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102026_TextContext: Very well. If this small clinic is really that important to you...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102029_TextContext: Alright. I still have the graffiti challenge in Arton City to attend. Good day.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104151_TextContext: Very well. I'll give you a chance to bring Audrey back.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104106_TextContext: All the major families of Urbino are watching how this drama ends.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103111_TextContext: Had the Navigator not deduced their true objective from the explosions, we should have returned empty-handed once again.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101028_TextContext: If Grove Enterprises didn't vote against confirming Cherrus Tactical as Urbino's security contractor, none of this would have happened.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109016_TextContext: I wish you'd be here under different circumstances.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104114_TextContext: If you truly believe that Audrey is innocent.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101163_TextContext: If you give up the patent, Astral Sanctuary will become their puppet!
AVGEvent_Season3.240104121_TextContext: If she's not here, she might be in trouble!
AVGEvent_Season3.240105058_TextContext: What if New Bethlehem has found the cure for collapse syndrome, a way to regain lost memories?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105065_TextContext: So what if it is? And what if it's not?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101172_TextContext: I'm sorry, Mr. Bai, but I cannot accept your proposal.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108013_TextContext: By the way, Rafa, is she the only one you've brought back?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107132_TextContext: Right! Lady Audrey! Where is she?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104038_TextContext: By the way, what are you doing here? Don't you have work to do at Astral Sanctuary?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108031_TextContext: I can handle both of you just fine.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103120_TextContext: R-R-Right! Let's get back on track, Miss Flavia!
AVGEvent_Season3.240108245_TextContext: New Bethlehem forces unequal deals on people. You can never coexist with Urbino.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104078_TextContext: Please be careful! If the crowd sees you, we won't be able to stop all of them!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106040_TextContext: Cut to the chase. I haven't agreed to cooperate with you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104093_TextContext: As you've seen, I woke up to find my scandal all over Neutroville.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107208_TextContext: Do you really think you stand a chance in your current state?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101101_TextContext: That wasn't a metaphor. See the arcade machine over there?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104115_TextContext: Bring her to me. I'll ask her myself.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106014_TextContext: Are you the one who blew up my bank?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109020_TextContext: We'd fix you up either way.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101049_TextContext: The permanent directors are capable of advancing the agenda through voting in the absence of the Bai Group. You don't have to come here yourself.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105018_TextContext: Is it a bit too soon to come to a conclusion?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108029_TextContext: You've come all by yourself... Don't you think you've slightly underestimated us?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107081_TextContext: You split the bullet with a sword?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103141_TextContext: Collapse syndrome took away her memories and past relationships.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109026_TextContext: I can't hardly notice any traces of collapse syndrome.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104153_TextContext: As a matter of fact, I do.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104024_TextContext: You almost gave me a heart attack...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101029_TextContext: Perhaps the burden of the permanent director seat is too heavy a burden for you, Lady Audrey?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104155_TextContext: And met with a hooded woman there.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104141_TextContext: Are supposed to be enjoyed by all players.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103117_TextContext: N-Navigator... Excuse me. We do not accept poaching!
AVGEvent_Season3.240109044_TextContext: Navigator... since when did you and Audrey have so many secrets between you? I have no idea what you're talking about...
AVGEvent_Season3.240109061_TextContext: The Navigator is right. The game is more interesting with additional players.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103109_TextContext: Of course. Even within the Compound Eye, New Bethlehem is an urban legend.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102048_TextContext: Of course! What is it, Lady Audrey?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106029_TextContext: And neither have you. Could you turn off the audio recorder now?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109051_TextContext: It's too loud. May I turn off the speaker?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101129_TextContext: Quite the performer, aren't you? But isn't that a bit too ambitious for a beginner?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104083_TextContext: Am I no longer the leader?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104092_TextContext: I was hoping you'd be able to tell me.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104072_TextContext: What's wrong? Tell me what's going on!
AVGEvent_Season3.240108262_TextContext: Why do you keep getting yourself in trouble when I'm away?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105046_TextContext: Is this the answer you wanted to hear?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101008_TextContext: What are you worried about? Haven't you heard? They say she's fallen ill with collapse syndrome. She doesn't remember anything from the past.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108089_TextContext: The bond of longing transcends time and space...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108158_TextContext: Hasty for success. Trusting those who should not be trusted. Only to repeat the same mistakes.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109022_TextContext: I can't help but feel like... you seem different than before, Lady Audrey.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102076_TextContext: I'm afraid that they want to seize the opportunity and get rid of the troublesome Unicorn once and for all.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103065_TextContext: You don't look like you need medical attention. If there's nothing else...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101170_TextContext: I... I've made up my mind.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103089_TextContext: Understood... Please leave the investigators alone!
AVGEvent_Season3.240103145_TextContext: I... I believe in Lady Audrey.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107004_TextContext: I've always wanted to... fight you like this.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101156_TextContext: I don't deny it. This is why we invested in Astral Sanctuary in the first place.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109067_TextContext: I told you I'd prepare the best prey for you. Are you not satisfied?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107082_TextContext: I don't know who you are, but Lady Audrey is my close friend!
AVGEvent_Season3.240105014_TextContext: All I do is let people show their true selves, expressing their most sincere sensibilities...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107188_TextContext: And I shot at you. We're even.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102039_TextContext: Was I as awesome as you were just now?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103036_TextContext: I know there is more to P.U.S than meets the eye...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106069_TextContext: It was never my intention to take him down with such despicable methods!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106066_TextContext: All we've done is compiling every negative thing you've said to Bai Mo in Urbino into a collection.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105083_TextContext: We heard the sounds of fighting and came straight over.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103137_TextContext: The Audrey we know would never do something like this!
AVGEvent_Season3.240103081_TextContext: We are insects that exist to devour rotten flesh. The scalpel for P.U.S' surgery.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104059_TextContext: We're from the Bai... No. I mean Astral Sanctuary under Grove Enterprises!
AVGEvent_Season3.240104120_TextContext: We thought she'd come to HQ...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101021_TextContext: We would like to express our deepest sympathies.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104118_TextContext: We've reached out to Grove Enterprises, but...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108163_TextContext: I am nothing but a clown. No one would care if I were to just disappear...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108186_TextContext: I'm just an impostor. It's not my right to do that...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104149_TextContext: We were talking about the game...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104011_TextContext: I heard the energy price hike was his idea!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101109_TextContext: I heard you were someone who rarely takes action.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103082_TextContext: Neither I, Navigator, nor Astral Sanctuary is still associated with P.U.S.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104027_TextContext: I'm on a mission. I can't let people hear me.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102014_TextContext: I see in Astral Sanctuary something you don't.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108161_TextContext: I'm a thief who stole her life... In a dream that is not mine... Fantasizing about becoming the heroine in someone else's story...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101151_TextContext: I'll get straight to the point.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104113_TextContext: Do you take me for a fool? Are you really that clueless?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105072_TextContext: I look forward to seeing the real you beneath the mask...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104104_TextContext: What I believe doesn't matter. The important thing is that...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102054_TextContext: I'm sure this will be a valuable investment.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107186_TextContext: I swung at you. Yet you took a huge risk to...
AVGEvent_Season3.240103083_TextContext: I didn't say that's why I'm here, did I?
AVGEvent_Season3.240100018_TextContext: I'll put you six feet under!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106222_TextContext: I'll put you six feet under!
AVGEvent_Season3.240104138_TextContext: Get better at the game before running your mouth.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107145_TextContext: You'd have destroyed yourselves without New Bethlehem lifting a finger.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101096_TextContext: I didn't expect the person who invested in Astral Sanctuary... to be such a unique gentleman.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101064_TextContext: I'm slightly hesitant about whether I should treat you as an ordinary person.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108285_TextContext: New Bethlehem shall guide the world in the right direction.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108182_TextContext: I'm not giving up on any patient!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101053_TextContext: I have more interesting things in mind...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108188_TextContext: You're the only Audrey I have ever known!
AVGEvent_Season3.240107192_TextContext: I hate losing. Tell me how you did it.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105070_TextContext: I will remember you, Lady Butterfly of the Compound Eye.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101164_TextContext: Have you forgotten the rules of the alliance, Audrey? This matter is strictly between the Bai Group and Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103085_TextContext: I read the Bureau of Investigation's report on the Grove Bank incident...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106005_TextContext: I thought The Great Artist was messing with me again...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108157_TextContext: I've disappointed people again, haven't I...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104134_TextContext: I haven't provided feedback to you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107127_TextContext: I had no idea you were capable of this!
AVGEvent_Season3.240105049_TextContext: I'm asking you about Audrey Grove!
AVGEvent_Season3.240107083_TextContext: I have no intention to fight, but if you don't stand down...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102023_TextContext: I hope for your sake that you know what you're doing.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106076_TextContext: That's why I have to defeat him in the most legitimate way!
AVGEvent_Season3.240108184_TextContext: It's time for you to fulfill your part!
AVGEvent_Season3.240103040_TextContext: So, you don't have to give me an answer...
AVGEvent_Season3.240107205_TextContext: Does that mean you will go to war with New Bethlehem?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101159_TextContext: Sell the patent to us. This is the condition for the Bai Group to provide additional financing to Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108039_TextContext: I'm going to destroy all the covers... You won't be able to hide for long!
AVGEvent_Season3.240108010_TextContext: It's boring catching prey that doesn't move, that's all...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108263_TextContext: It's you again, Rafa! Have you missed the taste of my fists?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108040_TextContext: Rafa! You've destroyed my spider silk, too! I don't get a fix on her position now!
AVGEvent_Season3.240104094_TextContext: Thanks to that, PR and Security have decided to ground me.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109015_TextContext: Does this fulfill my promise to visit Astral Sanctuary?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106181_TextContext: Guarding the entrance as instructed by the boss...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101011_TextContext: Next on the agenda, the Grove Bank incident.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102070_TextContext: The Bureau of Investigation has not been able to identify the mysterious enemy, while The Scissors claim to have nothing to do with it...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106117_TextContext: Let me go! What was in that thing...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106065_TextContext: Relax. No explosions or bullets this time. No one will get hurt.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106086_TextContext: Are you not satisfied with New Bethlehem's plan?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105053_TextContext: Regardless of her past connections with New Bethlehem, the new Audrey is no longer associated with the organization.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104058_TextContext: Nonetheless, I have to record this. Which company do you work for?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102017_TextContext: In that case... Alright, I'll sell.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107144_TextContext: Had I known you people at Urbino were into infighting...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108006_TextContext: You mean you picked her up after the fight was over.
