AVGEvent_Season3.240103014_TextContext: She said she'd visit... I even made a new trial batch of Starlight Coffee for her.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106114_TextContext: Of all the choices, you just had to choose the one where you'd suffer the most.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102044_TextContext: I'll find a way to resolve your financial issues.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103007_TextContext: Celestia, if I get sick again, can I come back and play with you?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101068_TextContext: I can't help but feel envious of Celestia, who has such a reliable friend by her side...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106041_TextContext: Not yet... I believe I can make you an offer you can't refuse.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107151_TextContext: Oh, you... How are you still standing?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109023_TextContext: Is that so? I haven't noticed...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101166_TextContext: It's up to Miss Celestia whether to accept it or not.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103023_TextContext: Indeed... You have become an indispensable part of Astral Sanctuary before I could realize it.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109028_TextContext: Right... It was a miracle for you to recover from acute collapse syndrome.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103013_TextContext: Yes... But it's been a while since I last saw her.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108183_TextContext: Yes... You did promise me that...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106200_TextContext: Didn't you say she was no match for you?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106093_TextContext: Besides, isn't New Bethlehem the mastermind behind all of this?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105022_TextContext: Be honest. Take this as my advice.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102073_TextContext: Our former business partners are unanimously kicking us while we're down. Such synergy could only have resulted from the instigation of a board member.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103125_TextContext: There was a company... Under the leadership of the young heir, it was reborn from familial strife.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101112_TextContext: Very well. Show me what you've got!
AVGEvent_Season3.240109080_TextContext: Clear, concise, well-organized... Completely different from Kokona's report...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102069_TextContext: The impact of the Grove Bank Incident is far greater than she anticipated...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102011_TextContext: We will acquire all shares of Astral Sanctuary held by the Bai Group, thus avoiding any conflicts of interest. Surely, this doesn't violate any alliance rules, right?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106085_TextContext: And then, Grove Enterprises shall be free from all the negative publicity and reborn as the victim.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104073_TextContext: Grove Enterprises is suspected of being involved in a top-level leak. We're just following orders.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105044_TextContext: With the support of New Bethlehem, Grove Enterprises took down all its competitors and ascended to the position of permanent director.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103132_TextContext: New Bethlehem is behind the rise of Grove Enterprises.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102071_TextContext: Painting Utopia Security refuses to comment on the matter. Public opinion blames the riot on the refugees. Grove Enterprises is being held responsible for failing to respond to the disaster.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106036_TextContext: The Eye of P.U.S is watching you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103074_TextContext: Flavia, the Eye of P.U.S. A pleasure to meet you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104008_TextContext: Is P.U.S in cahoots with Urbino?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108259_TextContext: P.U.S sniper... This is getting out of hand.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101030_TextContext: That's unfair. I know Grove Enterprises to be a responsible company.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103103_TextContext: Cruel, cold-blooded, efficient. Stopping at nothing to achieve their goals.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103128_TextContext: Cruel, cold-blooded, efficient. Stopping at nothing to achieve their goals.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108027_TextContext: Rather than killing my prey, I prefer watching them struggle.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107189_TextContext: Tell me. How did you do it?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108160_TextContext: After all... I am not Audrey...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106019_TextContext: After all, you're no match for me.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106028_TextContext: You've shown no positive intention. We can't talk business like this.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103068_TextContext: Nothing. I just had a friendly chat with the lovely, recently discharged kid.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104057_TextContext: Haven't you heard? Due to special circumstances, HQ is closed for the day.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108118_TextContext: None shall escape from the hunt!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106052_TextContext: That's right. We planted the bombs that destroyed Komos Tower.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102009_TextContext: I am. An investment that does not generate profit is a bad debt.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109089_TextContext: This whole incident is quite similar to what your father, George Lee, experienced, don't you think?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105011_TextContext: Suspected of planning and executing multiple terrorist attacks.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102028_TextContext: Think about my proposal at the council.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105012_TextContext: Inciting the public, wreaking havoc, enjoying others' disgraces... What a bunch of childish interests.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105009_TextContext: Special observation subject. Danger level: S.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108026_TextContext: “Hunter”? That's a bit barbaric, don't you think?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107005_TextContext: Have you any idea what it feels like to have your prey in your sight all the time?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101143_TextContext: That's enough, Bai Mo. Our guests have been waiting for a while now.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106197_TextContext: What do we do now? We have to take her back to New Bethlehem, don't we?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104095_TextContext: Despite being the leader of the alliance, I can only hide out here. Boring.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104099_TextContext: Grove Enterprises is the biggest suspect in the alliance as of now.
AVGEvent_Season3.240100010_TextContext: Are you an enemy or an ally of Urbino?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106214_TextContext: Are you an enemy or an ally of Urbino?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109056_TextContext: The current Audrey Grove is not associated with New Bethlehem.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103142_TextContext: Perhaps she does have nothing to do with New Bethlehem now.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101009_TextContext: Hmpf! Now she's nothing but a young girl without a clue about anything.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108008_TextContext: Do it while she's passed out before she wakes up and causes all sorts of trouble.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107147_TextContext: It's time to say goodbye to your friend.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105096_TextContext: By the independent authority of the Compound Eye, I hereby conscript you two into the Spec Ops squad.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106083_TextContext: The Bai Group should be overwhelmed trying to deal with public opinion as we speak.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106077_TextContext: Victory through such an underhanded trick is not victory at all!
AVGEvent_Season3.240101144_TextContext: We're here about Astral Sanctuary, Mr. Bai.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104102_TextContext: Mr. Bai, do you also believe that it was Lady Audrey who leaked the information and spread your scandal?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101098_TextContext: Mr. Bai, we have come today because...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102008_TextContext: Are you giving up on Astral Sanctuary, Bai Mo?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101153_TextContext: You should know, Bai Mo, that Astral Sanctuary's treatment of collapse syndrome is the best in the industry.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101048_TextContext: Mr. Bai, what brings you to this boring meeting of ours?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104107_TextContext: Between Grove and Bai, whoever loses is going to be attacked by the vultures.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101152_TextContext: We didn't invest in Astral Sanctuary because we were philanthropic.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104122_TextContext: Could you please set aside your prejudice against Grove Enterprises for a moment, Mr. Bai, and help us find Lady Audrey...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104077_TextContext: Leader? What are you doing down here?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106025_TextContext: That's all I can tell you for now.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106195_TextContext: It would appear that... collapse syndrome unlocked the shackles of her rationality, granting her more powerful strength than usual.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104096_TextContext: I guess being the leader doesn't make you free.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109060_TextContext: Looks like their infiltration is deeper than I imagined...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101138_TextContext: Looks like the game's too difficult for you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107152_TextContext: Only you could have gone head-to-head with Audrey in that state.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108237_TextContext: That hurt... Aren't we best friends?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109043_TextContext: That's exactly something you would say...
AVGEvent_Season3.240103087_TextContext: Makes me want to teach the current investigators how to properly write documents...
AVGEvent_Season3.240108224_TextContext: What a great play... Up next, you're going to defeat the witch who cast the curse, right?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106196_TextContext: What a rare case. She's got a terrible monster locked inside of her all this time.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104035_TextContext: Thank you for your hard work.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105035_TextContext: How rude. You made me draw my weapon.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106179_TextContext: I have confirmed that Audrey has made contact with New Bethlehem...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101058_TextContext: It's just... company matters. Don't worry about me.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109072_TextContext: When the curtains rise, I'll still need someone like you...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104056_TextContext: Hold on! We're representatives of a company affiliated with Urbino!
AVGEvent_Season3.240106199_TextContext: Wait, Julian! You're leaving me alone with that monster?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108226_TextContext: The Neutroville explosions, Grove Bank... the letter you received, and the Bai Group scandal...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104125_TextContext: It seems that you have yet to learn the rules of Urbino from our previous negotiation.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107184_TextContext: The name's Fuchsia. I'm a mercenary.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107216_TextContext: My boss told me that there is no reason to reject a fair deal.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104031_TextContext: To make matters worse... the reports cite credible internal meeting records.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101173_TextContext: Moreover... Astral Sanctuary will not seek additional financing from the Bai Group. We will find a way to resolve our current situation!
AVGEvent_Season3.240103138_TextContext: Besides... Wasn't she the biggest victim of the Grove Bank Incident?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106070_TextContext: Besides... as much as I hate to admit it, Bai Mo is a business genius.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101149_TextContext: Moreover, Astral Sanctuary, in its current state, faces the same ending no matter how hard you try.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101148_TextContext: As for the climax... Forgive my bluntness, but your pitiful dance moves were no climax but a dull ending.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105045_TextContext: As for the Grove Bank Incident, it was merely a show, aimed at fooling all of you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102022_TextContext: Profit and value are the drive behind Urbino.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105052_TextContext: Ever since she suffered from amnesia as a result of collapse syndrome, her and Grove Enterprises' actions have drastically changed.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103140_TextContext: Since a certain point in time, Audrey's and Grove Enterprises' actions have changed.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103055_TextContext: You've kept it close ever since that day.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108264_TextContext: You insolent brat! You got lucky last time!
AVGEvent_Season3.240104098_TextContext: As for you two... Your timing is terrible. You've walked straight into the line of fire.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102077_TextContext: As for the Bai Group... it's hard to say.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103127_TextContext: Through slander and hostile takeovers... they defeated one competitor after another using the most efficient methods.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101147_TextContext: The variation in dance moves symbolizes Astral Sanctuary's helplessness in facing the unfortunate reality...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101125_TextContext: Dancing should be a free thing. Don't treat it as a burden.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101121_TextContext: Rhythmic, dynamic, confrontational. I like it... Are you sure you can handle it?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102025_TextContext: Although this is only a verbal agreement... Astral Sanctuary is now an ally of mine. It's not a chip for you to trade with.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106061_TextContext: Enough with your sour face. You'll stand to benefit from it.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108007_TextContext: Enough. Wrap her up with your web.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101007_TextContext: If she gets wind of this, it's going to be trouble for us, too...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102074_TextContext: Citaro Biotech, Cherrus Tactical, and Winkler Consortium... All of them have long coveted our share.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104100_TextContext: Had you not run into me, you'd be in serious trouble now.
AVGEvent_Season3.240100017_TextContext: You want to fight? In that case...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106221_TextContext: You want to fight? In that case...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106018_TextContext: Want to fight? I'm fine with that...
AVGEvent_Season3.240105078_TextContext: A pawn would be more than enough to capture her.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109019_TextContext: If you don't cure me, you're going to lose your big investor.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106062_TextContext: In order to make you the leader, we first have to take down that dancer.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105015_TextContext: If you consider this to be a “disgrace”, do you believe that all human emotions are innately disgraceful?
AVGEvent_Season3.240100011_TextContext: Your fate depends on your answer...
AVGEvent_Season3.240106215_TextContext: Your fate depends on your answer...
AVGEvent_Season3.240101026_TextContext: For allowing 20 billion in market value to evaporate in the span of a month?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106067_TextContext: It's time for the citizens of Neutroville to see the true face of that irresponsible leader. Wouldn't you like that?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108225_TextContext: Nice to meet you, I guess? I am The Great Artist playing the witch.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106047_TextContext: Easy for you to say... We are already stretched thin dealing with the current issues. What can a bunch of wannabe spies do for me?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108185_TextContext: You promised that you would visit Astral Sanctuary!
AVGEvent_Season3.240105088_TextContext: Eh? What are you reaching for? Stop, or I'll shoot!
AVGEvent_Season3.240103063_TextContext: Excuse me... may I help you?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101086_TextContext: Excuse me, where can we find Mr. Bai?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101091_TextContext: Excuse me, where can we find Mr. Bai?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107211_TextContext: Come with us. I know how to defeat them.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104043_TextContext: Follow me. I know a shortcut to avoid all the people at the main entrance.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101027_TextContext: As a permanent member of the board, Grove Enterprises is responsible for protecting all of Urbino's interests.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109018_TextContext: As your investor, I think this is the best way to inspect your facilities.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103016_TextContext: As a famous entrepreneur, she must be pretty busy.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108242_TextContext: Come over. Join me and reshape this world with your will. How's that sound?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108159_TextContext: It's only natural for me to end up this way.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104137_TextContext: I thought you were going to tell me something interesting... Make excuses much?
AVGEvent_Season3.240107217_TextContext: Or are you lying to me?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102079_TextContext: Perhaps it was part of his smokescreen... I can't figure it out.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102094_TextContext: How much more is there that I should know...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104013_TextContext: And turn off your stupid speaker!
AVGEvent_Season3.240107143_TextContext: Thanks for putting on a great show.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102038_TextContext: Remember when you came to me on behalf of Astral Sanctuary? I only did what you did back then.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108280_TextContext: Why have you done all this?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101168_TextContext: As its leader, you have my word.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103010_TextContext: Now, we can finally get back on track and focus on the prevention and treatment of collapse syndrome.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106058_TextContext: It should have been delivered by now.
AVGEvent_Season3.240104159_TextContext: Is this the answer you expected?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103149_TextContext: Could you answer the question, please?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108227_TextContext: I wrote the scripts for all those events. What's the matter? Aren't you going to attack?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101024_TextContext: This is the incident report that you filed, Lady Audrey.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102035_TextContext: That's the Unicorn Grove I know.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103110_TextContext: It's a dangerous organization. We don't know exactly how many of them there are or what they want. There is a scarce supply of reliable information about them.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107141_TextContext: At this rate, she'll be consumed by collapse syndrome...
AVGEvent_Season3.240104124_TextContext: This is not how you make a deal, Celestia.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103021_TextContext: A lot has been going on.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103144_TextContext: Is this really just a coincidence?
AVGEvent_Season3.240105037_TextContext: The beating should be left to Rafa.
AVGEvent_Season3.240105005_TextContext: Were you attracted by flowers, my lost butterfly?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103084_TextContext: Then... what are you doing here?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106205_TextContext: Did they just run away? Where is Audrey?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101060_TextContext: I wasn't going to let you face that unpredictable man all by yourself.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106194_TextContext: Wasn't she completely consumed by collapse syndrome? How did she go berserk all of a sudden?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101057_TextContext: You look troubled... Is everything okay?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106026_TextContext: Can we get to business now?
AVGEvent_Season3.240109059_TextContext: Someone else must have been the source of the leak.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102010_TextContext: In that case, Grove Enterprises will take over from you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101051_TextContext: Very well. Would you share your opinions on the topic of this session, Mr. Leader?
AVGEvent_Season3.240108015_TextContext: Then, why does my spider web sense prey...
AVGEvent_Season3.240105023_TextContext: Anyway, I have a date. So long.
AVGEvent_Season3.240103147_TextContext: Here comes the last question of today's interview:
AVGEvent_Season3.240107175_TextContext: By the way, I can walk...
AVGEvent_Season3.240102049_TextContext: Promise me that you will stick to what you started out to do, never giving up on any patient, no matter what happens.
AVGEvent_Season3.240102027_TextContext: Please consider this deal as my goodwill.
AVGEvent_Season3.240107220_TextContext: Let's get going, then, while I can still track them.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106198_TextContext: We're going to... leave it to you, Rafa! See you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101150_TextContext: You must know how to help us, right?
AVGEvent_Season3.240104128_TextContext: In that case, I'm putting Astral Sanctuary's patent as collateral...
AVGEvent_Season3.240109039_TextContext: The diary might have contained information related to New Bethlehem and the bracelet... You must be curious.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101102_TextContext: I've invested in that as well. Why don't you help me test it?
AVGEvent_Season3.240106017_TextContext: In that case, I should properly thank you.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106045_TextContext: I've explained everything in the email. That must be why you're here, no?
AVGEvent_Season3.240102101_TextContext: A new email? Another company report... What time is it?
AVGEvent_Season3.240103011_TextContext: The crisis has been averted thanks to Lady Audrey's timely investment.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101103_TextContext: Pick any song you like... We'll talk when you're done.
AVGEvent_Season3.240101127_TextContext: Dancing freely is good, but it requires talent and skills.
AVGEvent_Season3.240109027_TextContext: It's hard to believe you're the same girl who was ready to disappear.
AVGEvent_Season3.240106206_TextContext: This is unexpected... This isn't mentioned in the boss's contingency plan.
AVGEvent_Season3.240108254_TextContext: (Holding a rifle in one hand, The Great Artist fires an elegant yet unpredictable barrage of bullets as if she is dancing.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105062_TextContext: (The Great Artist, on the other hand, seizes the opportunity and breaks free from the fight.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105066_TextContext: (The Great Artist produces a deck of playing cards as if she is a magician.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103033_TextContext: (...What was I doing before coming to Astral Sanctuary?)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104055_TextContext: (A man who seems to be the captain of the guards approaches us.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107165_TextContext: (A pair of tiny yet strong arms picks up Celestia and me.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108233_TextContext: (In the devastated battlefield, Celestia and Fuchsia have been disarmed and taken as hostages by the New Bethlehem duo.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107103_TextContext: (A strange feeling whispers to Fuchsia's sensitive nerves.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102099_TextContext: (An absurd yet reasonable possibility sends chills down Audrey's spine.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109009_TextContext: (A ray of morning light shines through the curtain, gently covering the blonde girl on the bed.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107076_TextContext: (A dazzling flash cuts through the night.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105091_TextContext: (The unit number on the badge is unfamiliar to Michele.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108054_TextContext: (As expected, Fuchsia appears right in front of Julian's crosshair.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109005_TextContext: (The only difference is that a special guest is staying here.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108079_TextContext: (No! None of this is right. It's all wrong! Wrong!)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104045_TextContext: (As an experienced sniper, Kokona excels at using terrain to avoid being seen.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106127_TextContext: (Her visions intertwine, driving her to madness.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108169_TextContext: (Was not The Steel Unicorn, but you. The real you!)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103028_TextContext: (I blurt out the question without realizing it...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105002_TextContext: (In an inconspicuous alley, the sounds of the crowd gathered in the square nearby can be heard.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108099_TextContext: (Words are not necessary as Celestia and I lock eyes. We reach out at the same time to the crimson light.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104002_TextContext: (Unable to contact Audrey, we immediately reach out to Grove Enterprises.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108050_TextContext: (Unlike Rafa, Julian takes aim in a completely different direction...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108202_TextContext: (At the same time, I regain my senses.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108255_TextContext: (Shifting and dodging, they fight under the moonlight like a dance between a flower and a butterfly.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104004_TextContext: (Following the only clue we have, Celestia and I arrive at the most likely location for her meeting.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108153_TextContext: (For the alliance; for her family; she exhausts herself for responsibilities that were not hers.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108081_TextContext: (Why? Why do all branches lead to failure?!)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103123_TextContext: (Perhaps it is my imagination, but as Celestia asks the question, the atmosphere around Flavia suddenly changes.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109048_TextContext: (Perhaps I am seeing things, but I seem to have caught a glimpse of a crimson figure flickering across the window...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108152_TextContext: (An Audrey that has just awoken from collapse syndrome. An Audrey that is no Audrey at all. An Audrey who has just started reacquainting herself with the world.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101179_TextContext: (What is going to happen to Astral Sanctuary?)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107065_TextContext: (Fuchsia leaps from mid-air, appearing in a completely different direction from where she was before.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106105_TextContext: (The assassin, who has been hidden in a dark corner long before the conversation started, fires a syringe dart filled with a purple liquid from Audrey's blind spot.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108041_TextContext: (Judging by the situation, Fuchsia may stand a chance against the duo.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104003_TextContext: (The butler informs us that they have lost all contact with Audrey since she left for a business meeting this morning.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106165_TextContext: (Starting from her consciousness, delving into her subconsciousness and then unconsciousness...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108025_TextContext: (Emerging from the shadows, Fuchsia appears fine, having restored her mobility after a brief rest.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106110_TextContext: (The young man steps out of the shadows and restrains Audrey from behind.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107104_TextContext: (As if her opponent is not the girl in front of her, but a far more distant and immense existence...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108097_TextContext: (As if it is no longer the sky but the battlefield we are in.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101014_TextContext: (The door to the conference room opens, and countless eyes stare daggers into the figure who walks in.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101043_TextContext: (Accompanied by booming music, a figure in green bursts through the door and makes his way to the center of the room.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107031_TextContext: (As her heart beats, a powerful surge of current flows through her body.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108108_TextContext: (Amidst sparkling starlight, Celestia appears from a torn spatial rift.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101123_TextContext: (It seems that stepping on the corresponding pads at the right time scores points without any restrictions on what dance moves to use.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108093_TextContext: (Only this time, Celestia is next to me.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108279_TextContext: (Before they get away, there is one thing I must ask them.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106145_TextContext: (But the physical torment is not the hardest to bear.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105032_TextContext: (At the same time, The Great Artist takes out her weapon and parries Flavia's attacks equally fast.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107197_TextContext: (However, I ignored all those possibilities, firmly believing that Celestia would win. This must be how the miracle happened...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107210_TextContext: (But if I am being honest, even with Celestia's help, they do not stand a chance...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108043_TextContext: (But as the surrounding containers are corroded and destroyed by Rafa, Fuchsia has less and less space to maneuver. Eventually, she will have to face the pair head-on.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106095_TextContext: (How could you expect New Bethlehem to resort to legitimate means...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107058_TextContext: (Among the debris, there is half of Fuchsia's cloak...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109075_TextContext: (The proposal regarding the next alliance leader election.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104040_TextContext: (We should keep our suspicions about Audrey to ourselves for now.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106012_TextContext: (The implication is clear - it is a practice room used to rehearse the attack.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105057_TextContext: (Their weapons clash again, producing a grating screech.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107107_TextContext: (I need to run as fast as lightning again!)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107162_TextContext: (The flood extinguishes the flames, sweeping toward us with the debris of the battlefield.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103043_TextContext: (The thought that has been troubling me vanishes suddenly, never to come back.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105077_TextContext: (Realizing that it would be extremely difficult to pursue the real target, Flavia gives up to conserve energy.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105033_TextContext: (Her moves suggest that she has not been properly trained for combat.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107174_TextContext: (Having channeled power beyond her limit, the girl seems exhausted.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107105_TextContext: (Ten meters. Five meters... The girl is almost in range of Fuchsia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107195_TextContext: (In terms of one-on-one combat, she is probably the strongest fighter I have ever seen.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101135_TextContext: (Even though I have given up on the most difficult notes, it is still challenging trying to hit the remaining notes. The missed notes significantly reduce my total score.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108092_TextContext: (Once again, I see the familiar starry sky.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108049_TextContext: (As Fuchsia launches another surprise attack, Rafa immediately fires in the direction of the shot only to miss again.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108038_TextContext: (On the other side, although Rafa and Giuliano have the numerical advantage, their teamwork is practically nonexistent.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108232_TextContext: (I look toward the direction of Celestia's voice.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107054_TextContext: (Audrey fires at the next cover Fuchsia is about to hide behind.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108067_TextContext: (Having heard my shout, Fuchsia gives up on trying to dodge and keep charging at the bullet.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104069_TextContext: (Upon hearing their captain's order, two other guards immediately approach us, they are still unclear about the situation.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104047_TextContext: (After bidding farewell to Kokona, we successfully enter Urbino's headquarters.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103019_TextContext: (Standing with Celestia by the entrance of Astral Sanctuary, we both fall silent as time passes.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109079_TextContext: (After a formal exchange, Flavia hangs up.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101079_TextContext: (In the middle of the office, a young man in casual clothing is playing a dance arcade game.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108247_TextContext: (Lurking in the shadows behind Audrey, another Great Artist elegantly raises her rifle.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240100008_TextContext: (Across from her is a hunter, ready to bare its fangs.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106212_TextContext: (Across from her is a hunter, ready to bare its fangs.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101017_TextContext: (Directly opposite of her are the seats of Urbino's five permanent directors, but now, only three of them are occupied.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108037_TextContext: (Maneuvering between stacks of shipping containers, she constantly launches surprise attacks from unexpected angles.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104046_TextContext: (Following Kokona, we sneak into the building's fire escape unnoticed.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108096_TextContext: (As our thoughts become one, the starry sky gains great meaning.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109011_TextContext: (As Celestia and I enter the room, she turns her head away from the window, smiling at us.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108209_TextContext: (Before I have time to doubt myself, the diary has already been torn to pieces.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105075_TextContext: (After making their speeches, all of The Great Artist's clones begin to leave in different directions simultaneously.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108022_TextContext: (Standing next to Rafa, who is covering her ears, Julian has somehow produced a large sniper rifle of an unknown model.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107196_TextContext: (When Celestia impulsively intervened, I thought of countless possibilities of her failure in an instant...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108129_TextContext: (As Celestia and Fuchsia fight New Bethlehem, I seize the opportunity and run toward Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108121_TextContext: (At close range, with precise aim, she presses her gun to the prey's throat...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108203_TextContext: (While my consciousness is still blurry, I feel a sudden impulse...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108036_TextContext: (In the confined space, Fuchsia's strong sensory abilities give her the upper hand.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102059_TextContext: (Just as the car is about to leave her sight, I think I see...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107120_TextContext: (As Fuchsia falls, she catches a glimpse of a uniquely shaped bracelet faintly glowing.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108070_TextContext: (As Fuchsia launches her assault, Celestia forms a shield using her string ability to deflect the bullet, creating a window of opportunity for Fuchsia to get close to the enemy - our initial plan.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101072_TextContext: (Having arrived at the end of the corridor, Audrey knocks on the door.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101034_TextContext: (Is there any way out of this suffocating labyrinth?)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109074_TextContext: (On a desk in the meeting room, there lies a stack of paper...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240100006_TextContext: (Port Euler, the night sky comes alive with the sound of gunfire.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102056_TextContext: (Audrey stops walking and sees us off.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106144_TextContext: (Crawling on the ground, Audrey struggles against the pain piercing through her entire body.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101032_TextContext: (Audrey knows very well that she's in far more danger right now than she ever was the day of the incident.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106109_TextContext: (Audrey reflexively reaches for the dart, trying to remove it.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102058_TextContext: (I see Audrey smiling and slowly waving at us in the rearview mirror until she disappears into the crowd.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108198_TextContext: (Audrey's legs regain strength. Her eyes once again shine with light.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101016_TextContext: (Audrey's voice follows her footsteps, treading with conviction into a sea of thorns.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108130_TextContext: (Audrey's collapse syndrome symptoms are worsening. She needs immediate medical attention.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102068_TextContext: (Audrey looks troubled, an expression she would never show in front of others.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108135_TextContext: (Audrey's physical condition appears unharmed. The problem lies within her mind.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106010_TextContext: (Audrey carefully enters the room, glancing around while looking annoyed.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108167_TextContext: (She remains sitting desolately in her cage.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102088_TextContext: (She relies on the diary as much as she is afraid of it.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106033_TextContext: (She removes her hidden recording device and shows Rafa that there are no more hidden items on her.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107066_TextContext: (Everything she did has been preparing for this moment.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107011_TextContext: (Wielding a grenade launcher in her left hand and a machine gun in her right, she fires both weapons in combat.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102089_TextContext: (Piecing herself together using fragments from the diary, she fears being consumed by the very fragments.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108133_TextContext: (The blue cracks on her body indicate that her collapse syndrome has progressed to the mid-stage. She is steps away from an irreversible mental breakdown.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101019_TextContext: (Audrey now stands on the other side, accepting its judgment.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108147_TextContext: (I see a cage suspended above a spiral staircase.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104054_TextContext: (Not expecting us, the guards tensely raise their weapons.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104062_TextContext: (The security guard turns on his headset and reports in a low voice.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106032_TextContext: (Seeing as the other party has come prepared, Audrey gives up on pulling any tricks.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104074_TextContext: (The captain has given us an official explanation. I do not have a reason to argue with him.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102080_TextContext: (Setting aside this tangled issue of hers, Audrey tries to relax her body and mind.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109010_TextContext: (Her unhealed wounds serve as a reminder of the battle with New Bethlehem and herself.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103060_TextContext: (Like a butterfly making its gentle descent.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102003_TextContext: (Just as Celestia is about to step out of the door, Audrey stops her.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107051_TextContext: (I need to keep it up and deplete the prey's stamina.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108116_TextContext: (The battle takes a drastic turn. Wounded by Fuchsia's heavy firepower, the duo attempts to retreat.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108151_TextContext: (I see all around me memories belonging to Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106166_TextContext: The tentacles of collapse syndrome indiscriminately pull out everything that constitutes Audrey, laying them in front of her...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106189_TextContext: (A massive explosive blows the gate off the warehouse.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108168_TextContext: (The person who helped Astral Sanctuary and made a pact with us...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101132_TextContext: (Go all out, aiming for full combos)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108076_TextContext: (A vast stream of information instantly floods my mind. Just like back at Grove Bank, only clearer...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107111_TextContext: (A strong sensation of tearing causes Fuchsia's muscles to tense, leaving her immobilized.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108277_TextContext: (The intense ringing in my ears and dizziness give me a splitting headache.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103090_TextContext: (With Celestia's permission, Flavia produces the prepared materials and begins the inquiry.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108273_TextContext: (Having received an order, Julian produces a throwing object)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103009_TextContext: (Smiling as she bids farewell to the discharged patients, Celestia finally seems relaxed for the first time in a long time.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102086_TextContext: (After a moment of thought, Audrey turns off her computer, taking out a diary from a small safe under her desk.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108250_TextContext: (With a sudden gunshot, the clone of The Great Artist falls.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102100_TextContext: (The sudden email notification sound interrupts Audrey's thoughts.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103015_TextContext: (This is not the reason she has not visited, is it...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107138_TextContext: (The hooded girl appearing out of nowhere wraps the struggling Audrey in a flow of water.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102083_TextContext: (Thinking of this, Audrey feels an indescribable sense of contradiction.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106106_TextContext: (Caught off guard, Audrey fails to dodge in time as the dart hits her carotid artery.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108155_TextContext: (Quickening my pace, I arrive at the cage.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108128_TextContext: (Celestia and I have also arrived on the battlefield.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103095_TextContext: (Carefully observing Flavia's expression, I fail to find any flaw in her composed demeanor.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102057_TextContext: (We get in the limousine arranged by Audrey, heading toward Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108061_TextContext: (Can I do it? Like her... No way! I'll lose! I have to dodge it!)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107194_TextContext: (When Celestia and I arrived, Fuchsia was fighting Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108033_TextContext: (Hiding in the distance, Celestia and I observe the fight between Fuchsia and New Bethlehem.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109045_TextContext: (I need to try my best to explain what I understand to Celestia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108144_TextContext: (I feel a familiar sense of connection... just like the starry sky I was under with Celestia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103045_TextContext: (I am the Navigator of Astral Sanctuary, an undeniable fact.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108166_TextContext: (Audrey does not seem to hear my shout.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103092_TextContext: (If I recall correctly... Kokona was responsible for the report.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106191_TextContext: (A hooded girl and a young man tumble out of the burning warehouse.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108075_TextContext: (Responding to my thought, the bracelet glows with a blue light.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108111_TextContext: (The distorted force envelops Celestia and Fuchsia, deflecting all incoming attacks.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102007_TextContext: (Celestia looks at Audrey puzzledly as the latter walks straight to Bai Mo.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101039_TextContext: (Keep your head high and open your eyes. This battlefield is yours.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101037_TextContext: (Win allies, exchange favors, and use your cunning and intimidation when necessary...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107168_TextContext: (With it, Rafa and Audrey vanish from our sight.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107155_TextContext: (As Rafa raises her arm, the dark purple string energy gathers and shoots toward a toppled water tank nearby.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105030_TextContext: (She unsheathes her sword, takes a fighting stance, and strikes.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102105_TextContext: (Her heart racing, Audrey opens the email.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102064_TextContext: (As if she is the only one in the entire sleep unable to sleep.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103059_TextContext: (A long-haired elegant woman walks into Astral Sanctuary as if she owns the place.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108077_TextContext: (I see before my eyes countless scenarios; countless branches; countless choices...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101033_TextContext: (Providing an outlandish compensation or resigning as permanent director... neither of these are consequences that she can bear.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101080_TextContext: (Throughout the song, the man jumps, crosses his arms, and rubs his hands on both sides.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104050_TextContext: (Back at Urbino HQ after a while.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103030_TextContext: (Even though she is talking about my own background, it feels like I am hearing about it for the very first time...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102066_TextContext: (In the dim study, a string of red characters is glaringly bright.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103005_TextContext: (One by one, the patients are discharged after making full recoveries.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107102_TextContext: (Celestia advances relentlessly toward Fuchsia, dodging or slicing through all of the latter's shots.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101177_TextContext: (Once Celestia makes up her mind, no one may persuade her otherwise. She starts walking toward the exit without any hesitation.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104039_TextContext: (Seemingly hesitant, Celestia looks at me, seeking my opinion.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108080_TextContext: (Celestia has failed to stop the bullet, resulting in Fuchsia being defeated and New Bethlehem taking away Audrey...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105034_TextContext: (Was that purely based on instinct and reaction?)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102062_TextContext: (At night, light rain falls over Neutroville.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107163_TextContext: (We don't have time to get away!)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107012_TextContext: (Bullets, explosions, and flames form a tremendous onslaught against Fuchsia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108136_TextContext: (Based on my experience, in order to stabilize the mind of a collapse syndrome patient, their anchor point must be located.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102090_TextContext: (As a result, she has never finished reading it.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108217_TextContext: (As Audrey has said, the cracks all over her body begin to fade.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107010_TextContext: (Audrey is destroying everything before her in an unprecedented frenzy.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107033_TextContext: (Breathing as one with the battlefield, she perceives everything that is happening without having to look.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105080_TextContext: (Suddenly, new footsteps are heard in the alley.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108201_TextContext: (The heart's cage, which is stronger than anything else in the world, slowly cracks as the surroundings start to collapse.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101107_TextContext: (Offer to do it in her stead)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108059_TextContext: (With a muffled gunshot sound, Julian's bullet flies toward Fuchsia's head.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104052_TextContext: (Instead of the usual businessmen, there are armed security personnel.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107201_TextContext: (Unable to get the answer she wants, Fuchsia turns around and walks away.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108199_TextContext: (That's right. This is the Audrey I know.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107167_TextContext: (The roaring flood fades away, eventually merging with the sea.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108138_TextContext: (As I clear the spider web, an unusual item falls from Audrey's clothes.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108143_TextContext: (The gentle light envelops Audrey and me.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108018_TextContext: (Lurking in the shadows, Fuchsia realizes that she has stepped on a thin thread of spider silk...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106131_TextContext: (The burning scars burst open one by one as her memories and emotions are gradually stripped away.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106190_TextContext: (The raging flames ignite the surrounding goods, turning the building into an inferno.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106136_TextContext: (The scorching scars dig deep into her consciousness, piercing through her mind and reaching her soul.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102067_TextContext: (She clicks the inopportunely arrived email. Unsurprisingly, it is another report from Public Relations.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240100007_TextContext: (A noble unicorn gracefully steps out of a sea of fire.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106211_TextContext: (A noble unicorn gracefully steps out of a sea of fire.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107057_TextContext: (The explosions and the flames kick up a cloud of dust several meters high.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108179_TextContext: (The cage stands strong, but Audrey has finally heard the noises.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107067_TextContext: (There are no more barriers between the hunter and the prey. All that remains are the hunt and the hunted.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108218_TextContext: (Collapse syndrome is theoretically incurable... This is beyond consciousness restoration therapy.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108208_TextContext: (The diary is supposed to be the anchor point for treating Audrey's collapse syndrome. What consequences will there be if it is destroyed?
AVGEvent_Season3.240101124_TextContext: (Use small dance steps to conserve stamina)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102016_TextContext: (Bai Mo ponders briefly before making a decision.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106171_TextContext: (Until... the last one hangs by a thread...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101082_TextContext: (Captivated by the amazing performance, the three of us stand in silence until the arcade machine plays the congratulatory sound effect for setting a new record as the song comes to an end.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101077_TextContext: (It appears that this unassuming room is fully soundproofed.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101178_TextContext: (It seems that our negotiation with Bai Mo has failed.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103044_TextContext: (I see in front of me the familiar face of the girl who has stood by me all this time, exactly where I belong.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108154_TextContext: (The caged girl has jailed herself trying to become Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106123_TextContext: (Everything before Audrey begins to become blurry.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106134_TextContext: (The figure before Audrey becomes distorted, their words tearing apart.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101073_TextContext: (The ordinary door in front of us seems no different from the others.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103099_TextContext: (The hostility as a result of her identity is gradually eased.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101018_TextContext: (One of those vacant chairs was originally hers.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102107_TextContext: (A clap of thunder suddenly echoes outside.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102060_TextContext: (...The carefully maintained smile fading from her face.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103062_TextContext: (The woman who has suddenly appeared puts Celestia on high alert.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105068_TextContext: (The cards transform into several clones of The Great Artist.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108207_TextContext: (After a prolonged moment, I feel puzzled by this sudden thought.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109004_TextContext: (After the battle with New Bethlehem, Astral Sanctuary has resumed usual operations.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107046_TextContext: (The crimson lightning circles Audrey, swiftly maneuvering between covers, leaving the trail of bullets shot by Audrey far behind.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107177_TextContext: (Fuchsia puts Celestia and me down as if carrying us all this way has been a piece of cake.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107180_TextContext: (Seemingly displeased with my remark, Fuchsia throws me off. Luckily, I manage to land on my feet.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107026_TextContext: (Fuchsia takes out a tactical mask and puts it on without any hesitation.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108060_TextContext: (With her sharp senses, Fuchsia almost catches the trajectory of the bullet...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108055_TextContext: (Fuchsia sprints toward Julian as she has no time to dodge...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108120_TextContext: (Fuchsia once again bursts with power, dashing toward the two like a fleeting arrow.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108124_TextContext: (Someone firmly grasps the muzzle of Fuchsia's gun, causing her to miss.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107032_TextContext: (Every vein, nerve, and pore in her body expands, enhancing her sensory perception and reaction speed to the limit.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107038_TextContext: (Her muscles tense, she stomps the ground with full force and shoots out like a bolt of lightning.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103061_TextContext: (Beautiful, elegant... and a barely perceptible hint of danger.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101078_TextContext: (The reason for which lies in the center of the room.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108210_TextContext: (Audrey slowly opens her eyes, within which lies a clear will.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109046_TextContext: (Audrey smiles as she watches Celestia and me before turning her gaze back at the window.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108148_TextContext: (Audrey is sitting in the cage alone.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106013_TextContext: (The person who has invited her here is none other than the mastermind behind the attack.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107166_TextContext: (As a sudden gust of wind blows right next to me, the scene in front of me rapidly retracts.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103042_TextContext: (The illusion in my mind dissipates as if it never existed to begin with.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108278_TextContext: (The footsteps are receding. New Bethlehem must have seized the opportunity to retreat.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108266_TextContext: (The arrival of Flavia and the Sentinel Bureau squad tips the balance.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108252_TextContext: (Descending from the roof, Flavia gracefully lands atop a stacked shipping container along with the moonlight shining through the skylight.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105061_TextContext: (For an instant, Flavia hesitates as she ponders what The Great Artist has said.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104066_TextContext: (Although the content of the conversation remains unclear to me, I notice that the captain seems to become more and more nervous.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108115_TextContext: (Although it is not as exactly as the intel suggested, Fuchsia has anticipated Celestia's help. She seizes the opportunity and fires everything she has at the enemy.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109033_TextContext: (While memories of the event still linger in my mind... there are too many questions that cannot be explained by logic. The experience cannot serve as a reference for her treatment...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240109031_TextContext: (While memories of the event still linger in my mind... I did say a lot of embarrassing things. I should keep it a secret for now.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101137_TextContext: (Although it is just a game, it was much more tiring than I expected. Afterward, I feel like my body is falling apart.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108012_TextContext: (The spiders land around Audrey and work under Giuliano's command, weaving a web that binds Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108150_TextContext: (The stairs creak as I walk on them as if they might break at any moment.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105031_TextContext: (Her smooth moves are completed in an instant at a speed almost imperceptible to the naked eye.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107019_TextContext: (Unable to resist Audrey's fierce attacks, Fuchsia takes refuge in the shadows of shipping containers.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108127_TextContext: (The Astral Gate teleported more than just Celestia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107131_TextContext: (The girl Celestia defeated - Have I met her before?)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107053_TextContext: (Enraged by Fuchsia's actions, Audrey stops firing her machine gun and raises the grenade launcher in her left hand.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108132_TextContext: (Bound by the spider web, Audrey lies right in front of me.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107173_TextContext: (The mysterious girl has run for who knows how long while carrying us, finally stopping at a location far from the port.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106020_TextContext: (Otherwise, I wouldn't have accepted this job...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103098_TextContext: (The interview goes a lot more smoothly than expected. Flavia is easier to get along with than she appears to be.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101133_TextContext: (As much as I am trying my best, my body cannot keep up with the notes falling like a waterfall.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108175_TextContext: (My feeble body hits the steel cage, producing a dull thud.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107222_TextContext: (Now is the time to come up with a plan...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107110_TextContext: (The side effect of overloaded combat hits Fuchsia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101003_TextContext: (The grand conference room fills with chattering.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101114_TextContext: (The screen displays a long list of tracks.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101081_TextContext: (Astonishing combo numbers keep popping up on the scoreboard of the arcade machine.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108258_TextContext: (Out of his instinct as a sniper, Julian pushes Rafa aside as the bullet misses her head by inches.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108057_TextContext: (Almost there! Not close enough! Not accurate enough!)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108234_TextContext: (Did she single-handedly turn the tide of the battle?)
AVGEvent_Season3.240105076_TextContext: (The clones are intricately designed, indistinguishable even to someone as keen as Flavia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108083_TextContext: (In the corner of an image, I notice that Fuchsia's clothes are stained with the corrosive liquid shot by Rafa.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240102087_TextContext: (This is the only connection Audrey has with her past self.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108219_TextContext: (Such a phenomenon has never been observed on any of Astral Sanctuary's patients.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106011_TextContext: (The structure and the arrangement of items are almost identical to Grove Bank's vault.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240104075_TextContext: (It is better to cooperate for now...)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101134_TextContext: (Give up on the most difficult notes and try to hit the rest)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107159_TextContext: (Through the gaps in the water, I notice that Audrey's clouded gaze regains clarity in an instant.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108084_TextContext: (The liquid neutralizes Celestia's ability, rendering it useless.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108139_TextContext: (A paperback diary, a rarity in the modern world.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108267_TextContext: (Having recovered their strength, Celestia and Fuchsia move closer to Audrey and me amidst the gunfire.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103047_TextContext: (As I snap back to reality, I feel an unfamiliar weight on my wrist.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107077_TextContext: (A sharp blade lies between Fuchsia's gun and Audrey's heart, splitting the bullet in two.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107161_TextContext: (The water curtain comes pouring down, turning into a flood of destruction.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240106146_TextContext: (With the onset of collapse syndrome, the string sequences that record the very existence of Audrey rapidly disintegrate like a dying star collapsing on itself.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101076_TextContext: (As the door is opened, a blast of loud music pierces my eardrums.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107158_TextContext: (As Rafa speaks, the massive tank explodes thunderously. The unknown liquid within gushes out, forming a huge water curtain under Rafa's control.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240103004_TextContext: (As the aftermath of the Neutroville explosions settles, there are no more new patients for Astral Sanctuary to admit.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101130_TextContext: (As the track song hits its climax, the difficulty of the game significantly increases.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107027_TextContext: (The atomizer sprays crystalline powder that enters Fuchsia's nostrils as she breathes, entering her bloodstream.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101122_TextContext: (As the music starts, notes begin to drop from the top of the screen.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240101136_TextContext: (As the song comes to an end, a terrible score pops up on the screen - probably less than one-tenth of Bai Mo's.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108011_TextContext: (The dark-haired young man approaches Audrey, who is passed out on the floor, and flicks his wrist, releasing multiple spider droids.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240107050_TextContext: (In her hand, the Sawtooth is like an accurate and agile hunting knife, continuously firing bullets through gaps in covers toward Audrey's blind spots.)
AVGEvent_Season3.240108056_TextContext: (Wielding the flame-spitting Sawtooth, Fuchsia attempts to take down Julian before he can pull the trigger.)

AVGEvent_XingHui.146204005_TextContext: “People of different races and faiths live together in peace, building a brave new world.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204004_TextContext: “As the devastating war comes to an end, peace returns to this world.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204006_TextContext: “A world where people respect one another's dignity and right to live; where any barbaric acts of violence and terror are prohibited. War and aggression are a thing of the past.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204007_TextContext: “A world where all citizens of Earth are friends with one another.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204035_TextContext: “We must take the One Ring to the Land of Bliss!”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204039_TextContext: “She has undergone a mask transformation. She is no longer human!”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201034_TextContext: You'll be fine. Aren't you talking to me? There's still time. You must trust me...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203057_TextContext: Oh, Mr. Luna! You're looking much better today. Please tell Sunny I said hi.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201033_TextContext: Mm-hmm, I can help you... Yes, I'm a healer...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101003_TextContext: The astronomical observation event is tonight. I've got everything prepared. You just have to show up.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203058_TextContext: Mrs. Anna Pavlovna, how are you feeling today? Regarding you and your children...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203056_TextContext: Hello, Mrs. Gima and Mrs. Estina. You two are really inseparable.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202089_TextContext: From the Moon to the stars and the Sun, all celestial bodies are part of the vast universe.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101029_TextContext: A fireworks display will take place tomorrow. We're expecting a lot of tourists. Don't occupy this spot for too long.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201032_TextContext: Please don't be afraid. My name is Celestia. I work at Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202073_TextContext: The Moon isn't visible at this time. But we should still be able to see the stars...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202008_TextContext: “Hi, Celestia! The contract for the storage locker you rented in P.U.S is about to expire. I'm sending some of your old stuff to Astral Sanctuary. I hope they can help you decompress! Although I have no idea how to use any of them...”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202009_TextContext: “No matter how busy work gets, you must take care of your physical and mental health lest you get me worried about you!”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202010_TextContext: “I'll visit when I'm free! See you then!”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202058_TextContext: “Sorry! I got the boxes mixed up and accidentally opened yours. I promise that I didn't take anything...”
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201070_TextContext: ...If your singing is this bad, why did you volunteer to sing?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204094_TextContext: Do you really think so, Navigator?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204063_TextContext: ...The final wish hasn't been fulfilled, Navigator...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101026_TextContext: ...Navigator? A-Are you okay? Why do you stare at the map?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203033_TextContext: ...But now, I no longer blindly follow her orders as I did.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204091_TextContext: ...That it may only emit such a faint glow?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101035_TextContext: ...But I've only got electric sparklers. They are far from everyone's expectations...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201056_TextContext: ...In any case, we can't leave him. We need to get him back to Astral Sanctuary...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201054_TextContext: ...What happened to the left side of the screen?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202082_TextContext: ...I do not have the talent or ability to become a shining star. I knew that, even back then.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101017_TextContext: ...I wish we had a device to control the weather.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204079_TextContext: ...By the way, what's this thing poking me all this time?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203088_TextContext: You must have left quite the impression for being competent.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203085_TextContext: You must have left quite the lasting impression.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202095_TextContext: The thought that someone like you - someone who understands me - is sitting right next to me...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203076_TextContext: As different celestial bodies are born, they influence one another, forming the cosmos as we know it...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204021_TextContext: What movies do you like? I'm interested to know.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201003_TextContext: It's gone. I can't find it anywhere...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203013_TextContext: What should the theme of the event be?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203041_TextContext: By putting on this item from my childhood, I might feel something different?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204089_TextContext: Perhaps Astral Sanctuary is just like the sparkler.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203015_TextContext: Building a close-knit community centered around Astral Sanctuary? You always have such mature ideas, Navigator.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204074_TextContext: But if we fail to effect changes, future generations are destined to repeat the suffering of the past.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201095_TextContext: You've done very well. I can't praise you enough.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204092_TextContext: A faint glow that illuminates the path of life for many a person.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203006_TextContext: But emotional manifestations are, in fact, the external expressions of internal changes...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202083_TextContext: But mother didn't care about any of this. All she hoped was for me to take over her position and status at P.U.S.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201076_TextContext: You're the first person to be so kind to me...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203037_TextContext: I'm trying to solve the problem with magic items, just like Robot Cat.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201092_TextContext: It's going to cost a fortune to repair the screen alone; it's just not worth it.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204046_TextContext: Actually, we still have a couple of movies left. We have to return the projectors after the event ends, so...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202038_TextContext: I suddenly felt dizzy when I turned around just now...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201044_TextContext: Do you also like listening to music, Navigator? That's another thing you and I have in common.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201093_TextContext: If you don't mind, Navigator, use my Star Pad instead, although it's also quite old...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204083_TextContext: Would you like to light it up? Just flip the switch at the bottom.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201081_TextContext: His consciousness has finally stabilized, Navigator.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202030_TextContext: Navigator, are you... Are you receiving patients on my behalf?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203061_TextContext: I think we've got enough people here, Navigator. Shall we?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204073_TextContext: Even if my efforts prove to be futile; even if my hope fails to be fulfilled, just like those of the people of the past, Navigator, I shan't be discouraged.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204043_TextContext: The audience seems to be satisfied, Navigator. Movies truly are a captivating thing.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204028_TextContext: Excuse me, Navigator, I need to guide visitors to their seats.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101045_TextContext: There are a lot of people here, Navigator...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201038_TextContext: I know this is a bit out of the blue, Navigator... but are you familiar with a lot of songs?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201009_TextContext: Please calm the patient down. Make sure he stays where he is. Please!
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202047_TextContext: I'll leave it to you then, Navigator. I need a moment to clear my head.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202054_TextContext: What's wrong, Navigator? You look worried.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203036_TextContext: I see... Your intuition is usually right, far better than mine.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101051_TextContext: As I fell into a spiral of despair, Navigator, you found me even brighter stars.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201082_TextContext: He used to live with a loved one. But that person contracted collapse syndrome before he did and eventually went missing...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203021_TextContext: But I have no idea what to give out...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203009_TextContext: Only with timely intervention can our treatment offer the greatest benefits to the patients.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201084_TextContext: Only by humming this song could he remember that person...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202097_TextContext: The more I think about it, the more motivated I am.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201049_TextContext: Play the song on the Star Pad.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203073_TextContext: But without everyone, the city, the world - none of it could have been built.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201062_TextContext: But, Navigator, I never did well in music class back in school...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204068_TextContext: But the dream was never realized. Not even in this new world...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201048_TextContext: But I'm unfamiliar with current pop music. I'm not sure what to do... Have you any ideas, Navigator?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101032_TextContext: But Grand Beach is not far from here. The weather over there must be the same as here...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201085_TextContext: But now, he's forgotten the melody, remembering only the name...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201083_TextContext: Later, collapse syndrome began to affect his consciousness, and he started to forget everything about his loved one.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202029_TextContext: Phew... Eh? What time is it...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201096_TextContext: Surely, I'll learn a lot from you as we work together. I'm looking forward to that, Navigator!
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201059_TextContext: There is? What do you have in mind?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203067_TextContext: Really? Let's see... There they are! Are other bracelets engraved with names as well?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202056_TextContext: Uh. I don't remember ordering anything recently... Hmm?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201042_TextContext: You know the song, Navigator? That's great! I don't understand pop music nowadays...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204081_TextContext: Oh? Are you talking about the electric sparkler I put there to reserve the seat for you?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202086_TextContext: Mm-hmm. When I asked to forge my own path, she acquiesced to it.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203042_TextContext: Very well. I guess it doesn't hurt to try...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203060_TextContext: Yep. I have always insisted on remembering everyone by their name.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203008_TextContext: Mm-hmm. Consciousness restoration therapy cannot eradicate collapse syndrome; it only delays the progression.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204020_TextContext: Nice. I told everyone that they could bring their favorite movies to be played here.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201030_TextContext: I see. The patient's condition seems quite serious. I need to perform an emergency psychological intervention.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204045_TextContext: It's no big deal. Although it was quite busy during the day, I got some rest by watching movies.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204070_TextContext: I know. It's not because of the movie, but...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202088_TextContext: Mm-hmm. In fact, I've already found my answer.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201091_TextContext: There's no need to repair. It's an ancient item from my time at P.U.S, anyway.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204065_TextContext: Mm-hmm, the wish of the survivors.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201068_TextContext: I'm counting on you, then, Navigator!
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201088_TextContext: Heh... Please don't be nervous. I wasn't blaming you.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203039_TextContext: ...Got it. You're full of surprises... Ha-ha...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202079_TextContext: She had hoped that I would become a star more dazzling than anyone else.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203069_TextContext: We want everyone to understand that they are not alone. At Astral Sanctuary, we are all connected just like the crystals...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204088_TextContext: Since it's a toy that simulates fireworks, its brightness is low and its duration short...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201023_TextContext: 'Tis but a setback on the journey of life.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203018_TextContext: Before you started working at Astral Sanctuary, Navigator, this aspect of the work was always challenging for me.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202090_TextContext: In the endless darkness, each one of them emits their unique light.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203072_TextContext: We may not know one another in this city. We may feel like an atom; a speck of stardust...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101031_TextContext: The sea? Are you saying we should move the event to the beach?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204047_TextContext: I think we still have a few movies left.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202071_TextContext: Speaking of which, I haven't told you about my past.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201052_TextContext: Luckily, I've brought mine with me.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202031_TextContext: Well, I work here, don't I?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201077_TextContext: Had you not been here, Navigator, the situation could have been a lot worse.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203007_TextContext: Without active intervention, the patients will fall into a vicious cycle.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204075_TextContext: If that's the case, what good is a new body in a new world?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202094_TextContext: Had I not come to this realization, I would not be sitting here next to you...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203020_TextContext: If we prepare a meaningful item that emphasizes the theme of the event, the token itself will become a memory anchor, helping stabilize everyone's consciousness.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202068_TextContext: The sender is an old friend of mine from my days in P.U.S.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101024_TextContext: Right! I'd told everyone about the observation event. I need to notify them lest they make the trip for nothing...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203080_TextContext: By the way, it is my honor to introduce the navigator, who has also joined Astral Sanctuary and will be assisting everyone in the future.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204014_TextContext: By the way, how long is the festival going to last? Don't occupy the spot for too long. That's where the audience will be seated for the fireworks display in a week.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201051_TextContext: That's a great idea, Navigator! The Star Pad is a tablet computer, after all.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203075_TextContext: Just like the order of celestial bodies - it wasn't always there.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202096_TextContext: Illuminates my path like the Moon quietly accompanying me through the dark night.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202287_TextContext: Even though she never approved of my ideas.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201046_TextContext: As symptoms of collapse syndrome worsen, patients gradually lose stability of consciousness, unconsciously uttering certain words or phrases.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201086_TextContext: Fortunately, you were able to intervene in time. Now, we just need to take him back to Astral Sanctuary to further alleviate his condition.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203014_TextContext: How about emphasizing the connection between Astral Sanctuary and the citizens?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202093_TextContext: If she doesn't grant it, should I keep second-guessing myself, hoping to make sense of it all?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201072_TextContext: Anyway, I'll take responsibility for the potential consequences. Please start!
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201019_TextContext: Why are you and this gentleman... lying on the ground, stacked on top of each other...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203066_TextContext: Your and Sunny's names are each engraved on one of the crystals. I hope she'll like it.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202027_TextContext: Hello, is anyone here? Are you open...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202057_TextContext: Look, there's a holographic message next to the package.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203028_TextContext: Look, engraved on the back of the crystal with my name... And her name.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202055_TextContext: You received a package for me and were too busy to keep an eye on it, and someone had opened it?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202064_TextContext: You took it out while inspecting the package and have been holding on to it since?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203038_TextContext: Are you talking about the sci-fi cartoon where the protagonist's robot cat uses magical items to solve problems?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203005_TextContext: You're right. At its early stage, collapse syndrome does not yet affect deep consciousness, and its impact on behavior is limited.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203022_TextContext: Something I've been interested in? Actually, there is something... Starlight Coffee version 31.6.21.6. What do you think, Navigator?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201055_TextContext: Could it be possible that it was damaged when the patient knocked you over?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202040_TextContext: Are you saying it's a temporary dysfunction caused by lack of sleep?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203050_TextContext: What am I thinking of? Hmm... Are you good at handcraft, Navigator?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201014_TextContext: I-I can't stay here! I must find it!
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201020_TextContext: I'm as clueless as you are...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202004_TextContext: I can receive it on her behalf.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203078_TextContext: This is why the navigator and I crafted these souvenirs. We hope they could serve as an anchor point in your sea of consciousness...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101040_TextContext: I'll forward the contact details of all the participants. Let's notify them of the change of venue.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202102_TextContext: Would you like me to teach you how to observe celestial bodies?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202032_TextContext: I know, but you're still getting your bearings. You're busy enough already...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202078_TextContext: After I independently mapped the Southern Cross the first time I observed celestial bodies, she had this cross pendant made for me.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204019_TextContext: I've also brought some of my favorite movies.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203012_TextContext: Therefore, I would like to organize a free, public consultation session, endorsed by Astral Sanctuary, and focus on promoting consciousness restoration therapy.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204093_TextContext: There must be changes that you can effect.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202098_TextContext: If you don't mind, Navigator... I hope you'll stay by my side and keep guiding me.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203065_TextContext: A bracelet? That's an elegant gift. I can give it to my sister.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101023_TextContext: I'm sorry. I shouldn't be like this. I still have important work to do tomorrow...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202101_TextContext: Shall we put aside our work for now and take a proper break?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202033_TextContext: Leave it to me. Please write down the names of all the outpatients...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203019_TextContext: Then, the only remaining issue of importance is the selection of a token.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201090_TextContext: Please deduct the repair cost of the Star Pad from my salary...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204044_TextContext: Thank you for your hard work, Celestia.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203063_TextContext: What's the bracelet for, Miss Celestia?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201060_TextContext: You sing, Celestia. I'll tell you the lyrics.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203059_TextContext: Do you know everyone by name, Celestia?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202092_TextContext: Indeed. Why must I insist on seeking her understanding?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204023_TextContext: Indeed. This place is usually fully booked. But I told them this was an Astral Sanctuary event. They made an exception and rented it to us at a discounted price for the day.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203017_TextContext: Good idea. As a navigator, your very existence guarantees a relationship of trust.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204072_TextContext: Yes, it's just a movie. It's not because of it...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204048_TextContext: Yea. We've gone through all this trouble to borrow the equipment. It would be a shame if we don't finish all the movies, don't you think?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201079_TextContext: Yes... T-Thank you... Thanks... for helping me find... my stars...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201022_TextContext: Yea, I was a bit startled as well...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202041_TextContext: Now that I think about it, my sleep has been rather unstable over the past few days.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203004_TextContext: It's an early sign of collapse syndrome.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203064_TextContext: It's a token for attending today's event.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204029_TextContext: Look for two chairs with electric sparklers. I reserved them for us. Be right back!
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204067_TextContext: For future generations to strive to do better.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204082_TextContext: I wanted to use it to enhance the viewing atmosphere, but I was too focused on the movies that I forgot to use it...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101036_TextContext: There's no time to explain. Notify everyone to head to the beach!
