AVGEvent_XingHui.146203003_TextContext: Based on the recent visitor accounts, a common feeling of loneliness is the main drive for them to seek treatment at Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202077_TextContext: Mother would purchase all sorts of items unobtainable to others and reward me publicly.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203068_TextContext: They are. And all your names have already been engraved on my and the navigator's bracelet.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202076_TextContext: Every time I learned something new or did something other kids couldn't do...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101015_TextContext: You've been preparing for a long time...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101034_TextContext: Fireworks? Do you want to change the event to a fireworks shop?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202046_TextContext: If I force myself to work now, I'll only be a burden.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204024_TextContext: Movies are great for healing. Had you not mentioned them to me previously, I'd not have thought of this.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204013_TextContext: The film festival? Are you talking about the stalls the girl from Astral Sanctuary set up? That way.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203011_TextContext: With the number of patients coming here for consultations continuously on the rise, I feel like you and I are both overwhelmed.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101053_TextContext: I wish I could freeze time at this exact moment... Would you like that as well, Navigator?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203048_TextContext: Order is not something that comes falling from the sky.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201063_TextContext: N-Never mind. This is an emergency. A man's life is at stake.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201071_TextContext: N-Never mind. This is an emergency. A man's life is at stake.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201010_TextContext: Use your Star Pad to record his condition.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202044_TextContext: Pour a warm cup of water for Celestia
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101052_TextContext: I'm fortunate to have met you...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204025_TextContext: I've always liked movies, but I usually watch them by myself.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203032_TextContext: Planets orbit stars, never losing their way. This is the order of the celestial bodies.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201064_TextContext: Please don't make fun of me if I do a bad job, Navigator...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201094_TextContext: Anyway, it's your first day at work, Navigator, and you've already encountered such an unexpected situation.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203034_TextContext: What were you hoping to achieve with the bracelet, Navigator...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201087_TextContext: By the way, can the Star Pad be repaired?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202063_TextContext: By the way, what's with the telescope you're holding...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201045_TextContext: Wait. Now is not the time for chit-chat. I asked you this question because...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201069_TextContext: Eh? You want me to cover my ears? To avoid collateral damage?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201024_TextContext: Eh? Your ability to come up with something so cool in such a situation is amazing, Navigator...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201061_TextContext: Eh? You want me to sing? Are you saying it would be more effective if I were to sing?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203040_TextContext: Eh? You want me to put it on?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204098_TextContext: Thank you for staying by my side.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203031_TextContext: Mom once told me that all order of this mortal world is but an imitation of the cosmos above.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202075_TextContext: This telescope was a gift from my mother.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202065_TextContext: It sounds like you know about the package? Could you tell me what's going on?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201047_TextContext: These words or phrases are of significant importance to them, as they are the key to slowing the progression of collapse syndrome.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201089_TextContext: I got this Star Pad back at P.U.S. It's quite old; even if it weren't damaged today, it wouldn't have lasted much longer.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203027_TextContext: I made it with my mom when I was a child.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202069_TextContext: The telescope, along with the other items in the box, is part of my old stuff from back then...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203087_TextContext: Composed as ever. Well done, Navigator.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204050_TextContext: Um... I was wondering if you'd be free to watch the remaining movies with me...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201039_TextContext: The patient has calmed down, but he keeps murmuring the name of a song...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204066_TextContext: Back then, people hoped for a brand-new world.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201041_TextContext: It's a song about reminiscing about a loved one.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201006_TextContext: The song... Who was it... stars...
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202006_TextContext: The mail comes attached with a voice message. Please check it as well. Beep beep.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202011_TextContext: If you're done inspecting the content, I'll be on my way. Beep beep.
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204056_TextContext: (It is a movie about the Great War. Intently staring at the screen, Celestia watches as the fates of the characters unfold...)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204057_TextContext: (...We have almost lost track of time until the movie concludes with the narrator making a speech wishing for peace.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204076_TextContext: (...I am unable to answer such a complex question.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204010_TextContext: (...To this day, these wishes have never been fulfilled.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203023_TextContext: (...If I let her imagination run wild, we would end up giving away strange items. I need to divert her attention to something else.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202028_TextContext: (Not wanting to wake up Celestia, I place the package on the cabinet before standing in for her.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201037_TextContext: (However, the man still seems lost, and Celestia appears to be pondering.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203070_TextContext: (Unlike her usual quiet self, Celestia does not seem shy in front of all the visitors, trying hard to convey her thoughts.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203090_TextContext: (The event has been a success. Celestia and I promise the visitors that we will hold more similar events in the future.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204017_TextContext: (I had previously called in some favors and managed to get three projectors for Celestia. They have been set up in three small outdoor screening areas.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203024_TextContext: (Perhaps something from the package could help?)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204078_TextContext: (I have to break the silence... Is there anything I can do to divert her attention?)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202066_TextContext: (I recount the event of receiving the package on Celestia's behalf during the day.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203054_TextContext: (Celestia and I host the public consultation session, endorsed by Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204077_TextContext: (Seemingly having realized that, Celestia appears depressed.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203049_TextContext: (Seemingly having thought of something, Celestia brightens up a bit.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204038_TextContext: (The story seems to be about a military Humvee stalling in a war-torn city, resulting in a firefight in the streets. Celestia watches nervously.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204036_TextContext: (The story seems to be about a party of nine transporting a magic ring to the west. Celestia watches with great interest.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204040_TextContext: (It seems to be a horror superhero movie. Frightened, Celestia almost jumps out of her chair.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203030_TextContext: (Every time Celestia talks about her childhood, she seems shy for a moment before returning to her usual calmness.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204100_TextContext: (But the Moon and stars illuminate the quiet screening area and the last two members of the audience.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201097_TextContext: (I keep the partially damaged Star Pad as a memento of my first co-treatment with Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204015_TextContext: (Walking toward the direction indicated by the officer, I soon find Celestia and other volunteers busy at work.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101007_TextContext: (I meet Celestia in the lounge to find her looking rather gloomy.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202007_TextContext: (I accept the voice message from the delivery robot.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204053_TextContext: (I return with the joyful Celestia to our seats in the outdoor venue just for the two of us.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201080_TextContext: (The man expresses his gratitude to Celestia and me.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203062_TextContext: (Celestia and I take out the bracelets we have made in the past few days and hand them out to the patients.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203001_TextContext: (Celestia and I are organizing the medical records of the latest collapse syndrome patients.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204026_TextContext: (Celestia and I have a conversation about the event and movies.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204034_TextContext: (Snapping back to reality, I notice that Celestia has quietly greeted me and taken a seat. Sitting next to one another, we continue watching the movies.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204027_TextContext: (As I turn around, I realize that a lot of people have gathered at the venue.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204012_TextContext: (Unfamiliar with the area, I ask a nearby beach patrol officer for directions.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203025_TextContext: (Not knowing what could be useful, I pick a random item.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201031_TextContext: (Unfamiliar with the treatment procedure, I stand aside, carefully observing Celestia's every move.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101049_TextContext: (Amidst joyful cheers, the girl who has always put others before herself finally smiles heartily.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202104_TextContext: (Before the tiny Astral Sanctuary gets busy again, we quietly enjoy a moment of peace.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204009_TextContext: (After the war, people pray for everlasting peace, hoping that future generations could do a better job at maintaining it than their forefathers.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201007_TextContext: The distraught man is showing symptoms of collapse syndrome. I contact Celestia right away.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203045_TextContext: (Gently putting the bracelet on Celestia, I adjust the size to make sure it is comfortable.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203082_TextContext: (Whispering) Navigator, would you like to say hi to everyone?
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101019_TextContext: (Is there something I can do to mend the situation?)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204002_TextContext: (The old projector makes squeaking and creaking noises.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101005_TextContext: (With eager anticipation, I enter Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202036_TextContext: (Fortunately, standing right in front of her, I grab her hand.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204011_TextContext: (Celestia has invited me to attend Astral Sanctuary's open-air film festival taking place at Grand Beach.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101048_TextContext: (The brilliant colors of the fireworks light up her face... No further explanation is required.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204054_TextContext: (It is near midnight, and we have only one movie left.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202052_TextContext: (Suddenly, I notice that the package addressed to Celestia has been opened.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201018_TextContext: (In a daze, I hear Celestia's surprised voice.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204042_TextContext: (As the screenings come to an end, the audience slowly leaves the venue, reminiscing about the stories.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201029_TextContext: (I help the man up before explaining the situation to Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201011_TextContext: (Following Celestia's instructions, I take out the Star Pad she gave me.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201016_TextContext: (Trying to stop the collapse syndrome patient from leaving, I accidently get knocked down by him.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204031_TextContext: (The screenings are mostly composed of Old Earth movies: mystery, sci-fi, spaghetti Western... I quickly become engrossed.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201012_TextContext: (The Star Pad is a tablet computer we use to store the electronic medical record of collapse syndrome patients. But since today is my first day on the job, I have no idea how to use the patient management application.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204060_TextContext: (Still affected by the nostalgic atmosphere of the movie, Celestia sits there, blinking blankly.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203079_TextContext: (Celestia's heartfelt speech, although quiet, reaches the heart of everyone present.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202034_TextContext: (Holding her forehead, Celestia suddenly sways, her body tilted, nearly falling down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204030_TextContext: (Celestia rushes off before she can finish her sentence. I find our reserved seats and sit down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201028_TextContext: (Celestia's palms are sweaty, probably as a result of running.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201036_TextContext: (Celestia's psychological intervention seems to have taken effect as the patient gradually calms down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101047_TextContext: (Before Celestia finishes her sentence, a loud explosion startles her.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203029_TextContext: (Celestia shows me one of the bracelet's crystals, its backside engraved with her name in a child's handwriting.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201040_TextContext: (As Celestia tells me the name of the song, the patient lifts up his head, his eyes filled with longing.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202072_TextContext: (I hand the telescope to Celestia, and she begins to skillfully calibrate it.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101044_TextContext: (Arriving at the beach, we find a large crowd.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146203055_TextContext: (Patients of different identities, ages, and social statuses arrive. Celestia greets each of them proficiently.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202002_TextContext: (Arriving at Astral Sanctuary for work, I hear someone calling for Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204085_TextContext: (As instructed by Celestia, I “light” the sparkler.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204003_TextContext: (Cheering, shouting, and uproar, along with the roaring of war machines, echo around Celestia and me for a long time.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201074_TextContext: (The singing is neither moving nor unpleasant. Average at best.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201066_TextContext: (Her singing is neither moving nor unpleasant. Average at best.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202026_TextContext: (Taking a nap, Celestia seems more tired than usual.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201153_TextContext: (As I tap on the Star Pad, only the right side of the screen lights up.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201065_TextContext: (Looking up the lyrics using the partially damaged Star Pad, I teach the song to Celestia, who sings it for the patient.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204086_TextContext: (The sparkler's white light illuminates our faces as our eyes lock.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204055_TextContext: (The first shot of the movie shows columns of tanks advancing under the purple sunset, the sound of gunfire tearing through the quiet night.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101028_TextContext: (Looking over Celestia, I see the map of the area surrounding Astral Sanctuary on the monitor.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202012_TextContext: (After seeing the bot off, I walk into Astral Sanctuary, carrying the package.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202050_TextContext: (Seeing Celestia recover her strength, I start my own work, feeling relieved.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202103_TextContext: (Seeing Celestia gradually becomes happier, I finally feel at ease.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202005_TextContext: (After confirming that the packaging is intact, I accept the package from the delivery robot.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201002_TextContext: (On my first day heading to work at Astral Sanctuary, I am approached by a despondent man sitting by the plaza fountain.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101018_TextContext: (Seeing Celestia this defeated for the first time, I have no clue how to comfort her.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101004_TextContext: (The brief message conveys Celestia's excitement and a harmless joke.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101041_TextContext: (We urgently contact the participants and leave a notice of the change of venue on the electronic noticeboard by Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204018_TextContext: (Even though the projectors are quite old, they are technologically capable of displaying clear images under direct sunlight.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146202048_TextContext: (After calming Celestia down, I continue to receive visitors.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101002_TextContext: (A week after the movie night, I receive a text message from Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146204008_TextContext: (Facing the setting sun, soldiers lay down their arms, and children return to their homes.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146201073_TextContext: (In the end, I sing the song for the patient.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.146101042_TextContext: (Holding hands, Celestia and I rush to Grand Beach.)

BattlePassClue.11_NewsContent: In 1954, Italian mathematician Eugenio Calabi proposed the Calabi conjecture at the International Congress of Mathematicians - In a completely enclosed space, is it possible to have a gravitational field without matter? The conjecture was proved by Chinese-American scientist Shing-Tung Yau in 1976.

BattlePassClue.12_Content:
Nobunaga:
I don't have that many reasons for joining P.U.S.
I don't hold any hatred when it comes to The Scissors, only confusion. If I had to choose a reason... I just don't want to lose anything else. I once watched helplessly as everything I held dear was taken from me, little by little.
So, the day he left, I made a vow to protect everything around me.
I will achieve this goal. It is the only thing that gives my life value.

BattlePassClue.14_Content:
Lawine:
Most people are fooled by what they see in front of them. I was once the same. The meaning of my life? To uncover the hypocritical mask that Strinova wears.
In the final analysis, The Scissors are merely moths flying into the flames. We know that this world will burn us to ash, and yet we continue without hesitation, because what we see ahead is the only light.
What is that light, you ask?
Truth.
Everyone has the right to see the truth.

BattlePassClue.13_Content:
Celestia:
I... I just want to help people. Even in Strinova, there are still so many who suffer in poverty. If even I'm not willing to stand up and protect them, then who else do they have to turn to?
I know that poverty and suffering can never truly be eradicated, but even so, I will do my best to achieve this goal.
As for why... one shouldn't need a reason to help those around them, right?
Isn't this the freedom that Urbino promises?

BattlePassClue.10_NewsContent: The latest P.U.S financial report shows that in addition to the expansion and maintenance costs of key urban areas, Humanity's Corridor, and other facilities, they are investing more funds and resources into the True Wilderness. At the same time, greater emphasis has been placed on the R&D of weapons for two-dimensional combat. Even without official acknowledgment, can we surmise that new dangers have emerged in Strinova's True Wilderness?

BattlePassClue.10_Content:
Meredith:
There are laws to life that must be revered. Even after a hundred years, Strinova still hasn't learned this principle...
We are The Scissors. We are those who cut through falsehood. This is our original vision and our most sincerely held belief. Strinova will one day perish. Our only hope for survival is to return to where we came from.
Countless will perish for this goal. I will also fall, but even those who will not live to see the future must ensure The Scissors' mission succeeds to the very end.
When the time is right, we will return the truth to all humankind.
It's time they woke up from this dream of utopia.

BattlePassClue.11_Content:
Michele:
Eh? Why I want to join the battle? We're P.U.S investigators. Isn't it natural for an investigator to protect the safety of the public?
At the end of the day, it's all The Scissors' fault. This world has enough troubles, yet they still go out and cause so much chaos. If you ask me, we should lock them all up!
Hmpf! Rotten to the core!

CinematicCloister.6_Describe: The Navigator and Celestia arrive at the Urbino Business Alliance headquarters, seeking an audience with the mysterious Mr. Bai. An unexpected encounter and an unforeseen covenant await them.
CinematicCloister.17_Describe: In an inconspicuous alley of the Urbino Business Alliance, a song of butterflies and flowers is played.
CinematicCloister.18_Describe:
Stepping away from the stage, follow the shadows to the destination.
Tonight, the grandest flame shall be lit.
CinematicCloister.3_Describe: The Scissors split up in an attempt to seize the crystals amidst the chaos, leading to a confrontation between the two sides.
CinematicCloister.1_Describe: The Scissors team infiltrates Komos Tower to steal the high-purity crystals being refined by P.U.S in order to open a spatial rift.
CinematicCloister.4_Describe: The Scissors successfully obtain the crystals. Having realized The Scissors' plan, P.U.S forces arrive at the location to provide support...
CinematicCloister.16_Describe:
Searching for the shattered truth amidst a fragile situation.
Know this: words are mightier than swords.
CinematicCloister.13_Describe:
The business world is no different from a battlefield. For Audrey in her current situation, this is especially true.
In the aftermath, another war is about to begin.
CinematicCloister.5_Describe: As a result of The Scissors' Operation Crimson Blade, Komos Tower of Area 88, Neutroville, is all but destroyed. Amidst the ensuing chaos, multiple explosions have taken place across the realm. Astral Sanctuary is fully committed to treating the wounded. However, an unexpected change serves as an omen for a more devastating incident.
CinematicCloister.8_Describe: Back at the Sentinel Bureau headquarters, Kokona informs the others of unsettling news. The Navigator works with the Sentinel Bureau to counter the threat to Neutroville and uncover the enemy's hidden identity...
CinematicCloister.21_Describe:
As the dust settles, Audrey honors her promise at Astral Sanctuary.
However... where there is light, there are shadows.
CinematicCloister.9_Describe: While the Navigator is at the Sentinel Bureau, Grove Bank is violently attacked, revealing the identity of the mastermind behind everything. All by herself, Audrey forges a path to victory with blazing flames.
CinematicCloister.7_Describe: As security consultants of the Grove Corporation, the Navigator and Celestia prepare to collaborate with the local Sentinel Bureau of P.U.S. At the designated meeting place, the duo meets a vibrant new investigator. Unbeknownst to them, the newly formed squad is about to face a severe situation...
CinematicCloister.20_Describe:
We promised her that we'd save every patient.
The dawn only comes when we have endured the deepest darkness.
CinematicCloister.2_Describe: Lawine infiltrates the defense system of Komos Tower alone with the support of The Scissors team. Unexpectedly, the defense system is suddenly being updated...
CinematicCloister.14_Describe:
The heavy rain covers the windows of the Grove mansion as if it were liquid curtains.
A diary and a mail... unveil past hurt.
CinematicCloister.12_Describe:
In an unknown place at an unknown time.
The hunter and the prey face off against each other.
CinematicCloister.10_Describe: In the vault of Grove Bank, the Navigator's team faces a mysterious enemy, setting the stage for the final showdown. On the other side, the surrounded Audrey receives the most unexpected assistance...
CinematicCloister.15_Describe:
Hiding beneath the water, the malice begins to show its face.
Can you distinguish black from white on the chessboard?
CinematicCloister.19_Describe:
A crimson hunter and a flaming unicorn.
As two formidable opponents fight for their lives, who shall emerge victorious...

EventTalk.14609005_EventContent: “May the souls lost at sea find peace. May the lotus lanterns guide your way home.”
EventTalk.10104001_EventContent: “A good investigator never forgets discipline and the idea their badge represents.”
EventTalk.10103001_EventContent: “Once the seeds of hatred are sown, it will not be long before they start to sprout.”
EventTalk.14610004_EventContent: “As long as you gaze at the starry sky, one day, it will respond to you.”
EventTalk.10509003_EventContent: “Where are the rest of my kind?” The unicorn ponders in sadness.
EventTalk.10107010_EventContent: “Bablo Crystals are the essence of matter of Strinova and a crucial energy source for the Strinovians.”
EventTalk.10104009_EventContent: “Justice, Bravery, Perseverance.” Remembering these three words is a piece of cake.
EventTalk.10107011_EventContent: “From the defense mechanism of Komos Tower to the drawing of Superstrings and all aspects of their daily lives, Bablo Crystals are the essential element for everything.”
EventTalk.10503010_EventContent: “The tangled lines evoke a sense of suffocating despair. The dark paint outlines a bottomless abyss as if gazing at the viewer.”
EventTalk.10508006_EventContent: ...Actually, I've tried multiple methods to rationalize my daily schedule and consulted several advisors.
EventTalk.10509110_EventContent: ...I'll never do something as childish as that!
EventTalk.10109015_EventContent: ...No, I don't. Otherwise, I wouldn't be stuck.
EventTalk.10107106_EventContent: ...That's alright. I'm not the only one who didn't know.
EventTalk.10101011_EventContent: An investigator's daily routine involves completing field missions and writing reports, including both intense battles and bureaucratic work.
EventTalk.10109004_EventContent: Could you help me out, my good partner?
EventTalk.10505015_EventContent: After we visited Café Reminiscence, I thought it'd be nice to have coffee every now and then.
EventTalk.10502008_EventContent: Last time, we talked about our hobbies. Let's get to know each other's strengths and qualities this time.
EventTalk.10103020_EventContent: Let's watch that show together when you're free!
EventTalk.14604005_EventContent: We are free from illness, but we are susceptible to wounds. For ordinary Strinovians who do not suffer the misfortune of going to war, it makes no difference.
EventTalk.14604008_EventContent: What makes us different is that what comes pouring out of our wounds is not blood but a part of consciousness and string sequences.
EventTalk.14606006_EventContent: Keep thinking of the desserts you like and imagining their shapes until you dream about them...
EventTalk.14610017_EventContent: Nope. Let's keep it a secret for now. I must maintain a sense of mystery.
EventTalk.10502015_EventContent: You don't have to be this precise!
EventTalk.14608001_EventContent: Time flies; you've been working at Astral Sanctuary for a while now.
EventTalk.10105003_EventContent: I wonder if Mighty Meow could be a maneki-neko...
EventTalk.14610007_EventContent: By not giving up, even on starless nights.
EventTalk.10506018_EventContent: Without actually seeing a person, you'd never understand their feelings.
EventTalk.10101003_EventContent: Whether you counter public safety issues or face everyday challenges, feel free to contact your nearest security bureau.
EventTalk.10108014_EventContent: However, back then, it was because of my duty and responsibility as an investigator...
EventTalk.10502020_EventContent: How should we continue the conversation?
EventTalk.14601013_EventContent: But in the end, you were able to fully preserve and record the precious memories.
EventTalk.10109206_EventContent: But learning from others' experiences is part of the process.
EventTalk.10104014_EventContent: Trust me. I will not give up, for diligence and perseverance are part of what it takes to achieve justice.
EventTalk.14609014_EventContent: However, these are all local customs of Strian, much different from what we do at Astral Sanctuary.
EventTalk.10106016_EventContent: Just you wait, partner. One day, I'll be able to stand on my own feet as well!
EventTalk.10101012_EventContent: However, overcoming the monotony of work helps keep every day a fresh one. I find it quite interesting.
EventTalk.14608008_EventContent: However, Strian welcomes only artists who paint realism. I heard abstract and expressionist artists have complained to the mayor, accusing the latter of not respecting artistic freedom.
EventTalk.10109105_EventContent: Good idea! A fellow gamer friend once told me that making a game is all about learning as you play!
EventTalk.10509001_EventContent: The last unicorn in the world lives in a beautiful forest.
EventTalk.14609013_EventContent: People who have been apart from their loved ones go to the beach and release lotus lanterns, conveying their thoughts and wishes despite being in different parts of the world.
EventTalk.10108011_EventContent: Then, they contacted me, and I rushed to the scene to arrest the criminals. No one must harm you, Navigator!
EventTalk.14607003_EventContent: Urbino's Corridor issued us the latest firearm - the Dream Sea.
EventTalk.10110011_EventContent: Yes and no. I'm giving up on writing scripts for video games, but I have set a new goal...
EventTalk.10101013_EventContent: Should you run into any problems in the future, please feel free to come to me!
EventTalk.10108002_EventContent: I was in a hurry today and forgot to charge Mighty Meow... Pawtector's still got 20% charge left. I'll take it with me on the mission.
EventTalk.10105001_EventContent: While in Elitron on official duty earlier today, I saw that some antique shops were selling maneki-neko!
EventTalk.10105009_EventContent: I discussed this with Yvette, our researcher, and she insists that it's impossible for robo battlecats to be conscious...
EventTalk.10107001_EventContent: I was having lunch with Yvette today, and she shared with me her latest experimental method.
EventTalk.10504002_EventContent: After I finished with the client this evening, I passed by a tavern where this piece was being played.
EventTalk.10109005_EventContent: Why don't you seek inspiration from other games?
EventTalk.10506013_EventContent: My purpose hasn't changed since we first met...
EventTalk.14601014_EventContent: Judging from the results of our cooperation, the frequency of your string sequence is similar to that of mine. I believe that you'll make a fine navigator for me.
EventTalk.10509014_EventContent: One day, the unicorn disappears from the forest, leading to discussions by the other animals.
EventTalk.10107012_EventContent: From this perspective, protecting Bablo Crystals is the act of promoting the justice of PUS!
EventTalk.10106002_EventContent: He keeps asking others where his uniform and metal are. He keeps demanding to see his colleagues from the Sentinel Bureau!
EventTalk.10106007_EventContent: But he just won't listen... It's so frustrating!
EventTalk.10106010_EventContent: He was always like this, guarding the frontline day and night, never leaving his post without progressing the case.
EventTalk.10503117_EventContent: Off days are a luxury to me.
EventTalk.10110013_EventContent: Have you ever been to a cat café called Paw Pledge, partner?
EventTalk.10106011_EventContent: Partner, have you ever heard of The Burglar in Disguise, The Chainsaw Murderer, and The Mechanical Monster?
EventTalk.10109008_EventContent: You must be curious, partner, about why I'm writing a story for a game all of a sudden.
EventTalk.10110001_EventContent: There has been a major development regarding my game script, partner!
EventTalk.10104006_EventContent: The captain gave me a talking-to today, partner, because I didn't memorize the Investigator's Code of Conduct...
EventTalk.10103002_EventContent: Partner, I've just finished the latest episode of Paper Detective! What a twist...
EventTalk.10109002_EventContent: I'm writing my own video game script, partner.
EventTalk.10107008_EventContent: I wanted to share this article with you, partner.
EventTalk.14602009_EventContent: Coffee has accompanied me since the day Astral Sanctuary was founded.
EventTalk.10509021_EventContent: But I believe that beyond the forest, other than the desert, there lies a larger world.
EventTalk.10508007_EventContent: But when I close my eyes, no matter how hard I try, I just can't fall asleep... This has been going on for a long time now.
EventTalk.10502002_EventContent: But I feel that just reading the books doesn't quite cut it.
EventTalk.10510005_EventContent: But while organizing my violin scores today, I found a piece about this very story!
EventTalk.14603009_EventContent: After stringification, we're still the same, drawn to dreams with goals we wish to achieve.
EventTalk.14610010_EventContent: But I know that I must not give up, nor do I wish to. I must hold on until the day my star shines for me.
EventTalk.10104011_EventContent: However, the twenty-four articles of the Investigator's Code of Conduct... contain hundreds of words. I don't see how I can ever memorize all of them.
EventTalk.14609007_EventContent: I wonder if the ones lost at sea could feel the care and kindness in the lanterns.
EventTalk.10503019_EventContent: However, I'll still make time to contact my ally every now and then.

EventTalk.14602007_EventContent: Even after we made improvements to it, the guests still gave the feedback that it was too bitter and strong, making it hard for them to fall asleep at night.
EventTalk.10109014_EventContent: Do you not know the answer to that, either?
EventTalk.10106001_EventContent: My dad is such a workaholic... He hasn't even been discharged from the hospital, and he's been nagging at me, “Let me get back to work! I have to return to the frontline!”
EventTalk.10106109_EventContent: Dad would be very glad to hear that.
EventTalk.10104015_EventContent: Plus, I told you I'd protect you, didn't I? I won't be beaten by such a trivial matter.
EventTalk.14607008_EventContent: In the event of a complete collapse of consciousness, the souls of those Strinovians are forever trapped at sea, wandering in eternity.
EventTalk.10107107_EventContent: My specialty is arresting bad guys and upholding justice!
EventTalk.14604011_EventContent: Could you please explain it like I'm five?
EventTalk.10110012_EventContent: As for what it is exactly... Let's talk in person at a special location.
EventTalk.10504010_EventContent: Such things are unavoidable for an artist... Even the greatest of souls must experience hardship and mire.
EventTalk.10504016_EventContent: While I'm usually quite busy, I could make time for you if you're interested...
EventTalk.10101008_EventContent: Although the work can be repetitive and boring, I must fulfill my responsibilities as an investigator.
EventTalk.14610006_EventContent: How do I find my star?
EventTalk.10104113_EventContent: If only Captain and former captain could be as understanding as you.
EventTalk.10502215_EventContent: Let me see if I missed anything...
EventTalk.10110018_EventContent: Let me see... I have finished three pages in three days. I need twelve more pages. That means I've finished... 20%.
EventTalk.14602016_EventContent: Take care of your body and mind.
EventTalk.10107004_EventContent: Between you and me, all this specialized knowledge is a bit out of my area of expertise... Are you familiar with this field, Navigator?
EventTalk.14608002_EventContent: Speaking of which, Navigator, have you had the chance to take a walk around Strian?
EventTalk.10510009_EventContent: Speaking of which, it's been a while since I attended a tea party!
EventTalk.10108008_EventContent: Speaking of which, they already see you as their partner in justice, Navigator!
EventTalk.14607014_EventContent: Do not leave me alone at sea, Navigator.
EventTalk.14605016_EventContent: Please don't take my joke seriously. Artists paint with Bablo Crystals, a highly regulated scarce mineral, not obtainable without prior permission.
EventTalk.10508010_EventContent: Stress only motivates me to work harder! I won't let it beat me!
EventTalk.14609010_EventContent: As a healer, I've witnessed countless instances of broken Superstrings and string sequence deterioration. All the strings end up flowing to the sea of illusions outside Strinova.
EventTalk.14609004_EventContent: Artists would paint all kinds of lotus lanterns by the beach and gather for a moment of praying and reflection, silently reciting the following...
EventTalk.14604003_EventContent: As the number of wounded continues to rise, we at Astral Sanctuary have been trying to recruit more personnel.
EventTalk.10507024_EventContent: Are you... looking out for me?
EventTalk.10104104_EventContent: That's not a line from the new show; it's Captain's catchphrase!
EventTalk.10103023_EventContent: Hold your horses... You can spoil the show from the very beginning.
EventTalk.10105010_EventContent: That would make them quite lonely.
EventTalk.10106012_EventContent: My dad personally dealt with their cases and arrested every single one of them!
EventTalk.10107006_EventContent: It's outside my area of expertise as well.
EventTalk.10102009_EventContent: This is a rare opportunity for gamers to challenge one another!
EventTalk.10506009_EventContent: This method is widely used in business meetings. It helps both parties quickly understand one another and deduce ways for improvement and optimization.
EventTalk.14606011_EventContent: That's a bit hard for me... I actually woke up from hunger while dreaming last night...
EventTalk.14607012_EventContent: This is why I fight; this is what Urbino believes in.
EventTalk.14606013_EventContent: This is what separates ordinary folks from artists.
EventTalk.10503008_EventContent: This painting fetched an unbelievable price at the auction.
EventTalk.10509005_EventContent: This is a bedtime story about the last unicorn.
EventTalk.10504003_EventContent: What kind of piece is it?
EventTalk.10502115_EventContent: So the other party can get to know you better!
EventTalk.14603002_EventContent: It's the new song by Dream Chasers, a band from Arton City, and it's achieved the number one spot on the Strinova Singles Chart.
EventTalk.10505104_EventContent: I see. It's got a unique name.
EventTalk.14606015_EventContent: That being said, traditional cooking techniques might suit me better...
EventTalk.14605011_EventContent: Does that mean we won't have to research recipes when we make improvements to our Starlight Coffee at Astral Sanctuary? We can simply paint the kind of coffee we want.
EventTalk.14607007_EventContent: The sea gathers the consciousness and string sequences of Strinovian. If there are wounds on their paper bodies, the lost string sequences and consciousness flow to the sea like a river of hurt.
EventTalk.10505006_EventContent: The taste of the coffee is rather “special”... It's almost the raw flavor of coffee beans tasting of unprocessed sourness and bitterness!
EventTalk.10506008_EventContent: You may not be used to my briefing method.
EventTalk.10507110_EventContent: Stop bluffing! What evidence have you got?
EventTalk.10505002_EventContent: Did you send me this box of ver.23.8.19.62 Starlight Coffee?
EventTalk.14607005_EventContent: Through it, I feel the surging of the deep sea.
EventTalk.14604006_EventContent: Normally, wounds are only caused by dimensional oscillation bullets on the battlefield.
EventTalk.10110019_EventContent: You're the only person I want to take to that place... We'll see each other soon; I promise.
EventTalk.10506021_EventContent: In that case... I'll check my schedule later.
EventTalk.10110007_EventContent: I'm sure one of them will tell the story I've always wanted.
EventTalk.10506014_EventContent: Then let's find the time to meet in person!
EventTalk.10101015_EventContent: I'll leave it to you then.
EventTalk.10502007_EventContent: Allow me to provide a topic for discussion!
EventTalk.14602013_EventContent: From administration to treatment and logistics, I managed everything as if I were a one-man army. It was both exhausting and fulfilling.
EventTalk.10103008_EventContent: It's a locked-room mystery taking place at a factory in Preton.
EventTalk.10504006_EventContent: It's a piece filled with tenderness and sorrow yet not lacking in firmness and passion. I heard a great composer of the Old Earth dedicated it to the person he loved.
EventTalk.10110016_EventContent: That place is my secret base!
EventTalk.14610005_EventContent: Will my star keep waiting for me?
EventTalk.10502016_EventContent: The most important thing is asking about the other party!
EventTalk.10101007_EventContent: My superiors are concerned about whether we have fulfilled our civilian-related duties.
EventTalk.14609006_EventContent: Then, they'd write the names of the deceased on the lotus lanterns before releasing them into the sky.
EventTalk.14605009_EventContent: They paint the taste they expect.
EventTalk.10107003_EventContent: Firstly, they have to make a breakthrough on the purification limit of Bablo Crystals. Then, they have to solve the issue of transforming Bablo Crystals from a superposition to an eigenstate...
EventTalk.10103012_EventContent: (You patiently listen to Michele's analysis of the plot for an hour...)

FxFlying.40000001_Desc: As subtle as a gentle breeze.

Goods.10101002_Desc: From the Jungle series. Painted in green with orange streaks. Not the prettiest tool in the shed, but it gets the job done.
Goods.31001034_Desc: “Why do I always wear red? Because red brings good luck! The closer you are to me, the luckier you will be!”
Goods.10202002_Desc: From the Bushwhack series. Its classic camo is adaptable to many combat scenarios.

Goods.60000056_Desc: “Do you know what the world inside a donut is like?”
Goods.60000082_Desc: “Can you blow bubbles better than I can?”

Goods.10106111_Desc:
A Spring Blessing special version of the Polaris. Designed with the concept of the growing loong, it symbolizes Celestia's courage and determination she accumulated little by little through past challenges.

【“For the patients, I will retreat no more. He taught me that.】
Goods.10106108_Desc:
A special customized version of the Polaris featuring a smoothed barrel that provides better grip. The embellished azure crystals also serve as an energy source for the firearm, enabling its bullets to race toward the targets like shooting stars.

【“This is no ordinary wishing star. It always flies toward my desired target.”】
Goods.10106107_Desc:
A special customized version of the Polaris. The biggest difference between this version and the original is the removal of the weapon's coldness, making it more suitable for going out on dates. The scope also serves as a makeup mirror, enabling users to check their makeup anytime, anywhere.

【“That was fun! I need to touch up my makeup... Heh.”】
Goods.10106106_Desc:
Specialized Polaris model. This firearm was a gift obtained from the Space Expericenter in Polaris. Designed in the shape of a space station, it tells the tale of mankind's longing for the endless expanse. It's not exaggeration to say this firearm is industrial art made manifest.

【“For an endless sky, I offer my endless yearning.”】
Goods.10106201_Desc: The Polaris custom job's red rose across the barrel is meant to symbolize the fearsome sword of a knight in some kind of lost ballad of ancient heroism.

【As people are like roses, so are swords.
With fire as their soul and steel as their bones.
Amidst the intensifying gunfire, roses blossom.
The scarlet girl stepping onto the battlefield has long accepted the inevitability of withering.
As she takes a moment's respite, gently caressing the flowers,
to whom will she leave the garden of roses in her heart?】

A customized version of the Polaris cleverly incorporating the concept of healthcare, seemingly implying anti-war ideals...

【They save lives not in the hope of praise, nor do they raise their guns to fight.
In front of them lies war, and behind them, peace.】
Goods.10106104_Desc:
Artistic Polaris model. References to fairy tales from old Earth reveal a surprising innocence in this weapon's designer.

【Wrapped in fragile dreams, a child's innocence beams. Kindness and purity, in our essence, gleams.】
Goods.10403108_Desc:
A customized version of the Defending champion featuring enhanced sensitivity to light. Whether for photography or firing bullets, it performs in perfection.

【“This moment is worth capturing, don't you think?”】
Goods.10403201_Desc:
A customized version of the Defending champion. Its immaculate barrel bathes in the glory and victories of the Grove family. Fervent flames flow through it, symbolizing the indomitability of Lord Grove.

【To protect her family, the young girl picks up this gun and walks onto the battlefield.
As she picks up this newly upgraded firearm once again, there is now more composure and determination in her sorrowful expression.
The answers to those questions? Just like before, find them using bullets.】
Goods.10403106_Desc:
A customized artistic version of the Defending champion, adorned with strings of the guqin, concealing the pinnacle of technology under the classic design.

【In drifting clouds, her garments I find; in blossoms, her visage so fair. She shines by the balustrade, caressed by the dew-laden air.
Should Jade Mountain's peak hold her not in view, then beneath the moon, on gemstone terrace, she'll appear anew.】
Goods.10403104_Desc:
A customized artistic version of the Defending champion with its blueprint designed by Audrey. It incorporates four different musical elements, each string of notes producing a unique timbre while playing the same melody.

【It's a piano, a saxophone, an old vinyl record spinning in solitude, recording the dim days of the past.
I know not the rise and fall this gun has witnessed, but the moment it fires, everything from the past becomes clear.】
Goods.10403105_Desc:
A customized artistic version of the Defending champion. Its design is centered around the folk cultures of the ancient Earth, vividly depicting a deeply evocative cultural atmosphere.

【In ignorance of bountiful years true, chasing the fox god, a myth in view, finding none but illusions and emptiness.】

【The time for thinking is over - now we join the fight.
I've still got a long way to go to reach my goal.】

A customized version of the Judge. Under the setting sun, two cranes fly away, bidding farewell to the departed.

【The wings of the crane shall guide you home.】
Goods.10304102_Desc:
Conceptual Judge model. This firearm's cyberpunk theme and use of trendy colors makes it as thought-provoking as it is gorgeous.

【The neon has yet to lose its luster, as dawn remains steadfast in the face of night.
Though the glory of the past remains, under the clashing of steel, the light of civilization no longer shines.】
Goods.10304108_Desc:
A modified version of the Judge that incorporates chess pieces into the design, exclusively customized for chess show matches. Its sleek black and gold design makes it one of Nobunaga's favorites.

【“I will also think one move ahead of you.”】
Goods.10403107_Desc:
Customized Manor's Grace appearance. This firearm's intricate design and elegant drum prove that high art can be just as deadly.

【“Today's menu includes refreshing tea, delicious snacks, and a pile of bullets.”】

Goods.10501103_Desc:
Customized Beareas model. The luxurious purple paint, cute panda head, and violent bursts of fire all symbolize that underneath the cold exterior of this firearm's owner beats a passionate heart.

【The taciturn girl pursed her lips tightly, but didn't let out a sound. The sound of music dancing with gunfire would speak for her.】
Goods.10501104_Desc:
A customized version of the Beareas. Yvette drew this design in a daze while suffering Beareasm a ten-hour sugar deficiency.

【My hands... drew this without my permission, not because I wanted to try this new product.】
Goods.10501102_Desc:
Specialized Beareas model. The firearm's cold look has been completely transformed into a shape that represents life and the harvest... It's hard not to want to bite into this thing.

【Uhm... I know that you're hungry, but you're not supposed to use this for popcorn...】
Goods.10501109_Desc:
Specialized Beareas model. This firearm takes a bold approach, incorporating elements Beareasm tales of old. Inlaid with luminous pearls, it stands out with a luxurious sheen.

【“The pearl in your hand sparkles, dazzling ever more gloriously in the dark.”】
Goods.10101003_Desc: From the Paintbrush series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10202003_Desc: From the Paintbrush series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10304003_Desc: From the Paintbrush series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.

Goods.10301105_Desc:
Customized Chroma model. Perfect for outdoor combat scenarios. The firearm's camo is based on an animal that Maddelena encountered while painting in the wilds. Their cute expressions are enough to make even grizzled veterans let out a laugh.

【“This is my lil' companion, why don't you say hello?”】
Goods.10301104_Desc:
A customized creative version of the Chroma with a cute water gun design. When it fires, the bullets attack the target like raging waves.

【The sea is calm at times, but it can also swallow everything.
Freedom is different. Pursuing it may bring happiness or destruction.】
Goods.10301106_Desc:
A customized version of the Chroma featuring a streamlined space-aesthetic design with pink-purple energy clusters symbolizing cosmic nebulae. The energy clusters serve as a fluorescent agent as well as provide considerable power, enabling her work to shine brightly in the dark universe.

【“I will make you shine brightly. How's that?”】
Goods.10301108_Desc:
Specialized Chroma model. Adorned in bright green and decorated with cartoonish characters, this firearm is the perfect embodiment of Maddelena - romantic whimsy and childlike innocence.

【“It's funny, isn't it? When you're young, I couldn't wait to grow up. But now, I just want to be a kid again.”】
Goods.10301110_Desc:
Specialized Chroma model. Adorned in bright green and decorated with cartoonish characters, this firearm is the perfect embodiment of Maddelena - romantic whimsy and childlike innocence.

【“It's funny, isn't it? When we're young, we couldn't wait to grow up, and now that we're grown, we wish we could be children again.'"】
Goods.10301102_Desc:
A customized concept version of the Chroma. Inspired by Maddelena's esthetics, the design features her favorite bunny-themed elements.

【The last bunny rides a rocket into the depths of the universe.
Thus, we see vaguely the vast expanse of stars ahead as a spark rises into the unknown, marking the end of the glorious bunny civilization.】
Goods.10301107_Desc:
A lightweight modification of the Chroma featuring a design that incorporates an impressionistic approach to the concept of melody. When you fire it, the sound of gunfire becomes lively musical notes.

【“It's time to dance, my friends!”】
Goods.10104110_Desc:
A customized model of the Shadow. The sapphire is perfectly set in the hollowed-out barrel, symbolizing The Scissors' perfect plan.

[”It's time!”]
Goods.10104107_Desc:
A customized version of the Shadow featuring clever camouflage suitable for convert operations, embodying the concept of patience.

【“Hey, are the leaves talking?”】
Goods.10104101_Desc:
A customized version of the Shadow with gilded trims glowing like the setting sun and its crimson barrel resembling the red clouds of dusk, a splendid future people once hoped to see.

【“Beautiful as the evening glow may be, it cannot escape the storm that cleanses the sky.”】
Goods.10104106_Desc:
Customized Shadow model. Though the signature P.U.S blue and white color scheme may imply otherwise, this weapon was created by Quadrant Foundries.

【Ridding myself of falsehoods has allowed me to become who I am now.
No more needs to be said. One just needs to seek.】
Goods.10104201_Desc:
Personalized Shadow model. Adorned with plum blossoms and classical engravings, this weapon carries on the heroism of an old legend and the pride of the past. It will brave heaven and hell with its master, no matter the odds.

【As snow falls in the dark, the battlefield feels a frigid embrace.
As her comrades fell one after another, a lone general stood tall against gale and snow. The sudden snowstorm had buried everything underfoot - perhaps even the plum tree had found no reprieve.
As a leader of men, the general refused to submit. She would keep her promised meeting under that plum tree.
Even the cold winter could have a silver lining. Spring was not far away, surely...】
Goods.10501106_Desc:
A customized version of the Crystal Lock. An innocent and fragile ice core is sealed within the intricate metal barrel. The bullets it fires are no longer scorching but bone-chilling.

【“Don't worry. The bullet won't cause you pain, but it may hurt you in another way.”】
Goods.60000081_Desc: “May the world be full of colors.”
Goods.60000078_Desc: “The way I fell was pretty cool, right?”
Goods.60000077_Desc: “I'm the most handsome guy out here.”
Goods.60000087_Desc: “I've been looking forward to this day.”
Goods.60001016_Desc: “My mood is as sweet as a refreshing glass of juice.”
Goods.60000071_Desc: “If I get serious, Mighty Meow won't be the only thing I throw!”
Goods.20107206_Desc:
“The most important ability of a detective is...”
“What is it?”
“Uh... The ability to observe, summarize, analyze, and practice!”
“That's it? I thought you were going to tell me some secrets. Don't forget that you promised that you'd catch the thief first.”
“When did the thief say they'd make a move?”
“...Now.”
“Oh! Then I shouldn't waste my time here! I'm going to look for clues. See you!”

A girl with a cup of coffee in her hand goes from looking at a steam engine to touching the fossil of an ancient whale, wandering around mischievously. In the retro museum, a showdown between a detective and a thief is about to take place.
“I shouldn't have accepted this task. I have no experience dealing with thieves whatsoever...” The detective nervously sips her coffee.
The girl stands in front of the exhibit that has been troubling her - the Icarus Device. Crafted with retro steam technology, the legendary item can magically make the user fly with its delicate and complex mechanism. Although it is unsuitable for Maddelena in her Superstring Being form, it is the perfect collectible for Maddelena the collector.
A well-known thief has issued a warning letter, claiming that they will steal the Icarus Device under everyone's watch. Due to the busy shopping festival, the warning letter is not delivered to the museum until one day before the stated date. The worried curator then immediately requests Urbino's assistance.
To earn her coffee expenses for the following month and the maintenance fee for the Fully Automatic Creative Retro Victorian Steampunk Gothic Hand-Operated Mechanical Latte Mocha Espresso Flat White Compression Modulating Machine in her backpack, Maddelena chooses to join the battle.
However...

A modified lightweight version of the Solo Dance, serving not only as a weapon but also as lady's essential accessory that holds the secrets of beauty.

【“Be there in a second. I must touch up my makeup and take care of the nearby enemies. It won't take long.”】
Goods.60000012_Desc: “I'm going to bed... We'll talk tomorrow.”
Goods.10303103_Desc:
A customized version of the Dawn, suitable for use near water. The barrel features a trident, exuding a menacing aura.

【A hunter could be eyeing us right as we speak...
Just kidding. Don't be startled. Right now, we're the hunter.】
Goods.10303104_Desc:
A customized version of the Dawn featuring an enhanced streamlined design and decorative metal that Reiichi finds befitting for the theme of space fantasy. There also appear to be fragments of a solar panel, but what are they used for? Only Reiichi, the inventor, knows the answer.

【“What is the solar panel used for? I figured it would provide extra functions to the gun. Unfortunately, that's a failed experiment.”】

Modded Dawn model. With chess pieces incorporated into its design, this firearm was specially made for a chess exhibition match. Reiichi's made some personal modifications to the prototype, recreating the distinctive pegasus chassis and its distinctive pattern.

【“How many of my traps can you see through? How many can you escape? Moments of advantage are fleeting. Did you hear that? Tick. Tock.”】

A personalized version of the Quasar. Inspired by classic fighter jets, it utilizes aerodynamics to reduce air resistance when the firearm takes flight.
- The only problem remaining: How do we make the gun fly?

【If you strngify the gun, you could probably make it into a paper airplane!】
Goods.10202108_Desc:
A customized version of the Quasar created to commemorate Kokona's victory in a cycling competition. Light and stylish, the barrel is designed with inspiration from bicycle dynamics.

【“I'll tell you a secret: I am as fast as a bullet when I cycle.”】
Goods.10202102_Desc:
A tactical customized version of the Quasar featuring an atomic punk design. With a more comfortable grip and precise sight, it is better suited for long-range combat than the original.

【That is the atomic punk world.
An unrealistic future. A cold utopia. An eternal kingdom with hidden crises.
It is a world of hope, fantasy, hidden cruelness... one that is destined to fail.】
Goods.10202107_Desc:
A modified version of the Quasar featuring a new spray-painting process. Its precise sight can also be used to observe scanner malfunctions. Although it is only a minor improvement, Kokona has taken a liking to this modification.

【“Please don't point your gun at Mighty Meow, Kokona!】
Goods.10202104_Desc:
A customized version of the Quasar featuring many duck-themed elements, symbolizing the courage to ride waves.

【“Mission accomplished! Well done, Kokona!”

Goods.31002002_Desc:
【\“Have you ever truly gazed at the starry sky?”
“I heard there is a unique star for everyone, waiting alone in the universe, hoping someone would gaze at it.”
“If one day you discover a different kind of light while gazing at the sky, that's probably your star blinking at you.”
“Where is my star? Well... that's a secret.”

The girl never stops her pursuit of the night sky.
On countless nights of gazing at the starlight, the girl patiently waits for the one star in the vast galaxy that captures her light.
One, the star blinks at her.
And the entire night colors its colors.】
Goods.31002005_Desc:
【“Whether it's going on an adventure or simply sleeping in, one must do what they love the most on a rare off day!”
Having finished a day's work, Kokona changes into comfortable clothes and lays down.

Next to her are stacks of boxes and all kinds of items.
Among them are memorabilia she has not had time to organize and essential tools for her future explorations.
“Come on. Don't just stand there. Help me out.”】
Goods.31002006_Desc:
【“Today, I have to design a children's book for Astral Sanctuary. As for tomorrow, I promised my neighbor I'd help her design her living room...”
It is another incredibly fulfilling day for the girl who finds joy in helping others. But this time, you notice a hint of weariness in her expression.

“Hold on, Advisor. Don't move!
“That's it! That's the look!”
The girl exclaims as if she has found the world's rarest treasure.
“Since it's your day off... Advisor, would you model for me?”
The girl approaches the person she trusts the most, sharing her unique warmth, her eyes filled with you and only you.】
Goods.31002004_Desc:
【“What flower is this? It's an orchid.”
The floral fragrance of the tea wafts from the cups in front of Lawine and you.
The pale petals unfold in your cup of tea.
You notice that a similar flower is embroidered on her clothes.

“Orchids only bloom in spring, a season far too short in this world.”
As she sips some tea, the girl in front of you smiles, barely perceptible.
For her, this brief respite from all her responsibilities and duties is her spring.】
Goods.31002003_Desc:
【After playing a violin piece, Audrey sits next to you.
“Why do you still look so gloomy when I'm with you?”
“What are you worried about? The test we have to face? Or the inevitable collapse?”

She pours two cups of black tea and places one in front of you.
“Let go of all the troubles. Let us toast to hardship and... this world.”
As the cups touch, producing a crisp sound, the girl smiles confidently.】
Goods.31002001_Desc:
【As a super gamer, Michele owns many stylish and casual outfits. However, as she is also a cat lady, she prefers this cute cat-themed outfit, whether for its comfort or adorable cat-like colors.

“A cat showing its belly is a sign of being friendly and feeling safe.” The girl says, smiling.

Michele has changed her flashy gamer gear into a cute girl's outfit. Is the cat-like girl trying to tell you something?】
Goods.31001002_Desc:
【Having become a frontline investigator, Michele carries with her the will of all her predecessors. When a badge number is reactivated, the pitiful criminals better tremble in fear, for the successor of the White Tiger will defeat every single one of them.
“Listen up! I have surrounded you! Surrender now!” Michele once intimidated suspects like this during operations.
And then, she kept her word, single-handedly arresting dozens of suspects.
“I thought I was going to meet my demise right there and then. Was she going to devour us like a wild tiger?” - The criminal recalls, shivering in horror.】
Goods.31001001_Desc:
【The rose royal swordswoman gazes into the distance.
She sees nothing but carnage and rivers of blood.
The rose-decorated sword pierces an enemy's heart.
The rose is dyed in blood's hue; shadows cast wide their pall.
My mind, like the breeze, wanders far, unconfined by any wall.
“For you alone, the flowers unveil their bloom; should they fade, what sorrow calls?”】

Goods.10101106_Desc:
A customized winter version of the Inspector, balancing camouflage and cuteness. Its barrel has been specially treated and will not malfunction even in low temperatures. This is Michele's favorite paint job during challenges.

【“Approach them silently, as if you were a snow leopard!”】
Goods.31001014_Desc: Every moment in your company makes my heart race.
Goods.31001017_Desc: Please like something to drink? No, the bear just looks like that. It's not upset. Hold on. Don't go!
Goods.31000100_Desc: I decide who gets to pass.
Goods.10104104_Desc:
A biochemistry-themed version of the Shadow manufactured by Quadrant Foundries. Although the concept of “biochemistry” no longer exists in Strinova, its influence over the ancient Earth and its underlying warning persist.

【Biochemical weapons are but one of the countless bottom lines, but war knows no boundaries.
Cruel times will inevitably come to an end. The unrestrained power shall serve as humanity's despair.】
Goods.31000060_Desc: The accumulation of wealth begins with blueprints.
Goods.31000114_Desc: A proof of potential awarded to outstanding players of the 2023 Community Competition.
Goods.31000113_Desc: A proof of strength awarded to the strongest player of the 2023 Community Competition.
Goods.31000126_Desc: The starting point is also the endpoint.
Goods.30001004_Desc: A super popular anchor just announced...
Goods.22115070_Desc: Follow the butterfly, then step into its trap.
Goods.20109055_Desc: As a sniper, Reiichi has also participated in frontal assaults. Dressed in jungle-style attire, he is brave and ruthless, always managing to remain patient until the mission starts.
Goods.20132051_Desc: A combat uniform in white, red, and gold, making Ming look like a messenger calling for the holy fire to punish the sinners. Shoot and burn, until the true dawn arrives.
Goods.30000109_Desc: Repost this crab and riches are sure to fall into your lap.
Goods.30003005_Desc: A basic particle that has transitioned to a free neutron. Season 1 rank reward.
Goods.30003013_Desc: A basic particle that has transitioned to a free neutron. Season 2 rank reward.
Goods.31000043_Desc: Does Project Reincarnation bring tears of hope or despair?
Goods.31000065_Desc: Reincarnate and start a new life in the name of the past.
Goods.22115113_Desc: Blindly trusting the beauty will cost you life.
Goods.30001007_Desc: Bask in the joy of music.
Goods.30003003_Desc: Matter that has achieved atomic level. Season 1 rank reward.
Goods.30003011_Desc: Matter that has achieved atomic level. Season 2 rank reward.
Goods.31000087_Desc: I will reclaim the glories of the past.
Goods.31000047_Desc: As he stepped into the passage, he understood that he had put on another pair of shackles.
Goods.31000141_Desc: Only a few can take this punch!
Goods.22101073_Desc: It's my turn to protect everyone!
Goods.30000091_Desc: This formula transformed the old world.
Goods.22137110_Desc: This counts as a performance, too!
Goods.30002007_Desc: The person on this bounty seems familiar... Wait a moment, isn't this me?
Goods.20109056_Desc: Featuring crossed swords and mysterious tentacles, the outfit resembles the attire of an ancient pirate captain. Reiichi does not fear the curse of the sea, for he has already cursed himself.
Goods.20137052_Desc: A performance costume featuring patterns of stars. The fluttering starlight resembles Kanami's gorgeous dance moves.
Goods.30003017_Desc: Is this... the ultimate? Season 2 rank reward.
Goods.22137078_Desc: This performance is prepared for you!
Goods.30000049_Desc: This abstract work reflects humanity's first impression of Bablo Crystals.
Goods.30000111_Desc: This heartbroken bird needs your care.
Goods.30000088_Desc: This is how I interpret freedom.
Goods.30000107_Desc: These kinds of pranks don't faze me at all.
Goods.31000038_Desc: Does the blue represent calmness or cruelty?
Goods.30003004_Desc: A basic particle that has evolved into a proton. Season 1 rank reward.
Goods.30003012_Desc: A basic particle that has evolved into a proton. Season 2 rank reward.
Goods.31000004_Desc: We seek the future, truth, and resistance.
Goods.20132101_Desc:
A black outfit suitable for nighttime operations. It was originally intended to blend perfectly into the night, but at Ming's request, a touch of dark red was added, like a flame burning quietly - not dazzling, but never yielding. She will chase the night and drive it away.

【“Go home, kids. The night is my battlefield.”】
Goods.31001020_Desc: Voyaging across the cosmos, wandering through the celestial expanse.
Goods.31000046_Desc: On that day, she realized that it had always been absurd.
Goods.30002012_Desc: This tower will stand for eternity. Some call it a beacon. Others, a shackle.
Goods.31000021_Desc: The memories still linger in my mind.
Goods.30002009_Desc: What time is it? Are you still looking for a safe exit?
Goods.31000118_Desc: Restarting will only take five minutes.
Goods.31000131_Desc: The wildfire burns in eternity, and the roses never wither.
Goods.10201106_Desc:
A souvenir from the Golden Tree Symphony, this firearm is inspired by the flute. Will she recall memories when she picks it up?

[“H-Has the surprise been conveyed?”]
Goods.10202103_Desc:
A souvenir from the Metal Symphony Concert and one of Kokona's most cherished possessions. Holding it on the battlefield, Kokona attracts as much attention as a bard before elegantly eliminating her enemies.

【“It may be fun to keep making music with you.”】
Goods.10602107_Desc:
A weapon midfield from the musical instrument Bai Mo used during the Golden Tree Symphony. The horn of the tuba has been attached to the muzzle. Although it is unclear whether it increases firepower, it certainly feels more “free.”

【“Nice one, my friend! Let's play another song!”】
Goods.10104109_Desc:
A prize from Lux Concerta, transformed by Lawine into a commemorative firearm. Every now and then, she can be found brandishing the firearm and muttering something to herself.

【“The setting sun... It's glorious.”】
Goods.31001037_Desc: The chime of gold heralds spring's embrace, joy dancing with the breeze.
Goods.20107056_Desc: Trying to figure out how to express feelings through creation, Maddelena takes a part-time job as a courier. She believes that letters are an important medium to convey one's intentions. She has designed her backpack in the shape of a mailbox, inviting the delivery of any precious sentiments.
Goods.31000103_Desc: A fragmented world is not unlike pieces that have come apart.
Goods.20101054_Desc: Michele occasionally puts on this casual outfit and goes hiking in her free time. Be careful not to mistake her for a wildcat in the bamboo forest.
Goods.31000058_Desc: A Shangri-La one cannot easily return to.
Goods.31000128_Desc: Rainwater flows to the sky from the ground, and we walk above the clouds.
Goods.20109053_Desc: The white shirt makes Reiichi look like a physician. In fact, he is skilled only in emergency battlefield treatment. Everything he does is for victory.
Goods.30000101_Desc: The notes have gone mad. They're running away!
Goods.30000099_Desc: Paint and ice create an immersive picture.
Goods.20110051_Desc: A chef's outfit featuring patterns of fish and bamboo leaves, reminiscent of the aroma of sushi. To Bai Mo, freedom and delicacies are the two most significant things in life.
Goods.20137104_Desc:
The outfit Kanami wears as an idol for a rural show. The mud on her light dungarees skirt does not ruin her cute style. Kanami chooses to keep this outfit after the show has ended.

【“Watching the crops grow day by day makes me feel content.”】
Goods.20137055_Desc: Kanami's performance costume for a coffee brand promotion event, specially designed with latte art in mind, conveying the warmth of coffee to the fans.
Goods.20137105_Desc:
The outfit Kanami wears when invited to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. The outfit showcases her charm and coordination with the conductor. Intentional, perhaps?

【“I would like to dream the most beautiful dream with you.”】
Goods.20137103_Desc:
Kanami's choice of loungewear while on vacation. Few realize that under the spotlight, the invincible idol is just an ordinary girl offstage, entitled to enjoy her youthful moments.
However, as an idol, she is always keenly aware of others' gazes, making her feel a tad nervous and excited, holding onto the person standing next to her.

【Lup-dup... Do you hear Kanami's heartbeat?】
Goods.31001007_Desc: Kanami is everyone's idol, but... for now, let me be your maid.
Goods.20137051_Desc: Kanami's special performance costume, exuding a charming yet slightly dangerous aura. Perhaps she will appear in your dreams tonight.
Goods.20137006_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume. The banana and bamboo resemble a phoenix and a dragon.
Goods.20137005_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume. The nightingale's song lingers in the endless night.
Goods.20137004_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume in brilliant violet, blooming to its fullest.
Goods.20137003_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume in dazzling ochre, symbolizing the passionate flame in her heart.
Goods.20137007_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume. The gilded color reflects the idol's radiance.
Goods.20137002_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume in cyan, resembling delicate petals.
Goods.20137008_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume in green, symbolizing growth.
Goods.20108052_Desc: The elegant outfit embroidered with thorns and a sword symbolizes Nobunaga's uneasy fate and his determination to face hardships without fear.
Goods.31001012_Desc: The crane formation stands ready, but where lingers the friend once known?
Goods.31000082_Desc: There are shadows beneath the dawn.
Goods.20133052_Desc: A bold mix of black and white. Which side truly represents her? Meredith is as enigmatic as this outfit.
Goods.20128053_Desc: The black and red hues symbolize the calamity that befell her hometown. Lawine is determined to give it her all to prevent history from repeating itself.
Goods.20110054_Desc: A racing driver-style combat uniform in black and green, making Bai Mo appear dashing and distinctive. Speed and passion perfectly describe Bai Mo.
Goods.20132053_Desc: A combat uniform in black and blue, decorated with lightning and eagle emblems. Ming's eyes are as sharp as a hawk's. The outfit highlights a dangerously intimidating aura on her.

IdCard.31000001_Desc: “Making contact and observing are only the first steps. It's up to you to make the next move, Navigator.”

MapLoadingTips.16_Tips: Do not attempt to breach Audrey's barrage of fire unless absolutely necessary.
MapLoadingTips.8_Tips: You can always trust Celestia. She'll do the same for you.
MapLoadingTips.1_Tips: Sidestep to effectively dodge bullets coming from the front.
MapLoadingTips.2_Tips: Home to many humans, Strinova World is powered largely by string energy.
MapLoadingTips.7_Tips: There are many miracles in Strinova World. You just need to believe in yourself.
MapLoadingTips.13_Tips: If you're far away from a sniper, it's best to get behind cover. Try getting as close as possible before engaging to maximize your chance of success.
MapLoadingTips.18_Tips: Try not to attract fire to areas where your teammates are trying to flank.
MapLoadingTips.5_Tips: Symptoms of collapse disorder include loss of mental faculties and mania. Many institutions are putting forward their own theories on how to treat this disease.
MapLoadingTips.4_Tips: Bablo Crystals are the source of Superstrings. Scattered across the True Wilderness, they are the strongest energy source known to mankind.
MapLoadingTips.19_Tips: Stringification greatly increases your mobility. Master this power to outplay the opposition!
MapLoadingTips.20_Tips: If you can't break an enemy position, you might want to try communicating with your teammates to switch tactics.
MapLoadingTips.12_Tips: Remember to keep your temporary armor on so that Ming's ultimate remains active.
MapLoadingTips.3_Tips: When a teammate is knocked down, back them up as soon as possible.
MapLoadingTips.9_Tips: Kokona's masterpiece is her healing drone, a work of love she crafted with her friends in college.
MapLoadingTips.11_Tips: Figured it out yet? Reiichi and Nobunaga's passive is triggered when scoped.
MapLoadingTips.14_Tips: Bombs take time to detonate, so make sure you protect them from enemy defusal attempts while they're ticking down.
MapLoadingTips.15_Tips: Watch your back. Enemies can try to flank you.
MapLoadingTips.10_Tips: Bai Mo's active skill allows him to shift via stringification. As such, any skills that prevent stringification will render his active skill temporarily unavailable.
MapLoadingTips.17_Tips: When aiming at an enemy, make sure you're not standing directly behind a teammate. You wouldn't want to hurt them!
MapLoadingTips.6_Tips: Audrey holds the firm belief that heading into battle is its own form of honest work.

PlayModeControl.3_ModeInfo:
10-Player Rumble

Victory Conditions:
Comosstrings: During the Final Showdown, knock down all enemies or prevent the enemy from collecting 3,000 cores.
Core Catchers: During the Final Showdown, collect 3,000 cores.
PlayModeControl.10_ModeInfo:
15-Player Snowball Fight

Victory Condition:

1. Earn points by surviving or landing hits from within the battlefield
PlayModeControl.8_ModeInfo:
15-Player Hide-and-Seek

Victory Conditions:
1. Seekers: Find and defeat all Runners.
2. Runners: Evade the Seekers and stay alive until the end of the match.
PlayModeControl.4_ModeInfo:
5-Team 3v3 Brawl

Victory Conditions:

1. Defeat the specified number of enemies within the time limit

2. Rank in the top three teams at the end of the match
PlayModeControl.5_ModeInfo:
3v3v3 Team Arena

Victory Conditions:

1. Defeat the specified number of enemies within the time limit

2. Rank in the top two teams at the end of the match
PlayModeControl.1_ModeInfo:
5v5 Team Battle

Victory Conditions:：

1. First team to reach the designated number of defeats wins

2. At the end of the match, the team with the most enemy defeats wins
PlayModeControl.6_ModeInfo:
5v5 Escort Battle

Victory Conditions:
1. Attackers: Escort the payload to the destination within the specified time.
2. Defenders: Prevent the payload from reaching the destination within the specified time.
Special Mechanics:
1. Approach or stick on the payload to advance it forward.
2. You can adjust the String Energy Network while in a Safe Zone or waiting to respawn.
3. You can resupply your tactical items multiple times.
4. Team members will respawn together periodically.
PlayModeControl.2_ModeInfo:
5v5 Attack & Defend

Victory Conditions:

Attackers: Destroy the objective or defeat all Defenders

Defenders: Defend the objective
PlayModeControl.9_ModeInfo:
7V7 Objective Defense

Victory Conditions:
1. The first side to reach the required number of ore wins.
2. If the match ends, the side with the most ore wins.
