Weapon.10101002_Tips: From the Jungle series. Painted in green with orange streaks. Not the prettiest tool in the shed, but it gets the job done.
Weapon.10106111_Tips:
A Spring Blessing special version of the Polaris. Designed with the concept of the growing loong, it symbolizes Celestia's courage and determination she accumulated little by little through past challenges.

【"For the patients, I will retreat no more. He taught me that.】
Weapon.10106201_Tips: The Polaris custom job's red rose across the barrel is meant to symbolize the fearsome sword of a knight in some kind of lost ballad of ancient heroism.
Weapon.10106202_Tips: The Polaris custom job's red rose across the barrel is meant to symbolize the fearsome sword of a knight in some kind of lost ballad of ancient heroism.
Weapon.10106203_Tips: The Polaris custom job's red rose across the barrel is meant to symbolize the fearsome sword of a knight in some kind of lost ballad of ancient heroism.
Weapon.10106204_Tips: The Polaris custom job's red rose across the barrel is meant to symbolize the fearsome sword of a knight in some kind of lost ballad of ancient heroism.
Weapon.10106102_Tips:
A customized version of the Polaris. The red rose across the barrel is meant to symbolize the fearsome sword of a knight in some kind of lost ballad of ancient heroism.

【As people are like roses, so are swords.
With fire as their soul and steel as their bones.
Amidst the intensifying gunfire, roses blossom.
The scarlet girl stepping onto the battlefield has long accepted the inevitability of withering.
As she takes a moment's respite, gently caressing the flowers,
to whom will she leave the garden of roses in her heart?】
Weapon.10403106_Tips:
A customized artistic version of the Champion, adorned with strings of the guqin, concealing the pinnacle of technology under the classic design.

【In drifting clouds, her garments I find; in blossoms, her visage so fair. She shines by the balustrade, caressed by the dew-laden air.
Should Jade Mountain's peak hold her not in view, then beneath the moon, on gemstone terrace, she'll appear anew.】
Weapon.10403003_Tips: From the Multiverse series. Featuring a prominent Strinova pattern, this firearm's simple yet complex design exudes a novel charm.
Weapon.10106006_Tips: The Chimera series offers an elegant orange-themed mosaic with rather artistic results.
Weapon.10501103_Tips:
Customized Beareas model. The luxurious purple paint, cute panda head, and violent bursts of fire all symbolize that underneath the cold exterior of this firearm's owner beats a passionate heart.

【The taciturn girl pursed her lips tightly, but didn't let out a sound. The sound of music dancing with gunfire would speak for her.】
Weapon.10304003_Tips: From the Paintbrush series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Weapon.10301106_Tips:
A customized version of the Chroma featuring a streamlined space-aesthetic design with pink-purple energy clusters symbolizing cosmic nebulae. The energy clusters serve as a fluorescent agent as well as provide considerable power, enabling her work to shine brightly in the dark universe.

【“I will make you shine brightly. How's that?”】
Weapon.10104101_Tips:
A customized version of the Shadow with gilded trims glowing like the setting sun and its crimson barrel resembling the red clouds of dusk, a splendid future people once hoped to see.

【“Beautiful as the evening glow may be, it cannot escape the storm that cleanses the sky.”】
Weapon.10108007_Tips: The Prisma series was designed with the idea of refractive fragmentation in mind as its artistic purple shades evoke a kaleidoscopic feeling.
Weapon.10301007_Tips: The Prisma series was designed with the idea of refractive fragmentation in mind as its artistic purple shades evoke a kaleidoscopic feeling.
Weapon.10303002_Tips: The Tidal Wave series is composed of a series of blue modules meant to imitate the shape of a wave. The comparison may end here, but it is still a delightful model.
Weapon.10502101_Tips:
A modified lightweight version of the Solo Dance, serving not only as a weapon but also as lady's essential accessory that holds the secrets of beauty.

【Be there in a second. I must touch up my makeup and take care of the nearby enemies. It won't take long."】
Weapon.10502002_Tips: The Dreambreaker series combines patchy blues with the occasional mellow yellow in a shattering statement.
Weapon.10202102_Tips:
A tactical customized version of the Quasar featuring an atomic punk design. With a more comfortable grip and precise sight, it is better suited for long-range combat than the original.

【That is the atomic punk world.
An unrealistic future. A cold utopia. An eternal kingdom with hidden crises.
It is a world of hope, fantasy, hidden cruelness... one that is destined to fail.】
Weapon.10108053_Tips: A model in the House of Cards series that is coveted by the lively Urbino fighters, who favor bringing this artistic weapon into battle.
Weapon.10403053_Tips: A model in the House of Cards series that is coveted by the lively Urbino fighters, who favor bringing this artistic weapon into battle.
Weapon.10602104_Tips:
The Freedom Reigns custom job heavily leans into its metallic base reminiscent of freight machinery, which often leads others to fatally underestimate its strength in battle. After all, it's not called a “power brake” for nothing.

【You can't dash without mastering how to brake. Absolute control: that's the Urbino way.】
Weapon.10501006_Tips: The Sunset series blends a tastefully faded orange-white palette to symbolize the coming of twilight.
Weapon.10101104_Tips:
A customized concept version of the Inspector that boldly incorporates lave effects into the barrel, with flowing patterns that resemble the flames of purgatory.

【In the blue lava, justice prevails.】
Weapon.10102108_Tips:
A customized version of the Rebelflame featuring a radical design and passionate colors, vowing to light up the night.

【Burn! Flame is the romance of the night!】
Weapon.10602005_Tips: From the Bedazzle series. This firearm's blue highlights twist and turn, as if melting into the design.
Weapon.10202005_Tips: The Thunderfire series seamlessly blends contemporary sleekness with retro orange-gray criss-crossing elements.
Weapon.10104004_Tips: The Neon Rainbow SCIS-08 limited edition conveys its bold rebelliousness with an unruly color scheme. Perhaps this is why it has received so much favor with The Scissors.
Weapon.10202055_Tips: The Flying Bird series features a design that depicts a lively avian ecosystem, as well as a less conspicuous personal symbol of its user.
Weapon.10602054_Tips: The Flying Bird series features a design that depicts a lively avian ecosystem, as well as a less conspicuous personal symbol of its user.
Weapon.10102008_Tips: From the Arcane Purple series. Adorned in bright purple, this firearm exudes a sense of mystery.
Weapon.10105002_Tips: From the Arcane Purple series. Adorned in bright purple, this firearm exudes a sense of mystery.
Weapon.10201004_Tips: From the Arcane Purple series. Adorned in bright purple, this firearm exudes a sense of mystery.
Weapon.10108104_Tips:
Conceptual Sawtooth model. Its design is inspired by the hunters of old. Many eons ago, humanity lived in fear of hunters who roamed the night, for no one could be sure that they were not a target.

【In complete silence, she delivers an unknowable fate.】
Weapon.10102055_Tips: The Dragon Tiger series comes in a festive yellow and white combination. The lion dancer imagery remains particularly appealing to the defiant Scissors faction, with whom this particular design is popular.
Weapon.10105058_Tips: The Dragon Tiger series comes in a festive yellow and white combination. The lion dancer imagery remains particularly appealing to the defiant Scissors faction, with whom this particular design is popular.
Weapon.10201055_Tips: The Dragon Tiger series comes in a festive yellow and white combination. The lion dancer imagery remains particularly appealing to the defiant Scissors faction, with whom this particular design is popular.
Weapon.15201001_Tips: A super-stylish sword forged by an unknown master.
Weapon.10303106_Tips:
One of Reiichi's transformation attempts. The firearm's design has been modified to make it look like it's come from the black market. An excellent work of art — the camo might be a fake, but its lethality is unquestionable.

【"When true is false, false is true; when false is true, true is false."】
Weapon.10304104_Tips:
New model based on the Judge. The Bablo Crystal hidden inside has vastly improved the performance of this firearm.

【Why think about the past?
Reject the old. Eliminate the stragglers. Destroy those who can't see progress.
And then... Accept the next step of evolution.】
Weapon.10102104_Tips:
Based on the Rebelflame. This cutting-edge weapon has been redesigned by Quadrant Foundries, improving a variety of aspects while retaining the same basic shape.

【Just what catalyst is required to drive science forward?
——It's simple, war is what drives progress.】
Weapon.10603001_Tips: Full-auto combat shotgun. There's nothing quite like it.
Weapon.10501001_Tips: A light-weight submachine gun with an unusually high rate of fire and precision compared to most other weapons in its class. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.10502001_Tips: A light-weight submachine gun with an unusually high rate of fire and precision compared to most other weapons in its class. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.10105104_Tips:
Meredith's weapon during The Scissors' charity performance in Preton. Decorated with playing cards that not only disrupt the enemy's judgment but can also be used to perform magic tricks.

【“Surprised... or perhaps shocked?”】
Weapon.10602001_Tips: Highly reliable and durable, this semi-automatic combat shotgun features ghost ring sights for improved accuracy. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.12303001_Tips: Semi-automatic pistol with a reputation for its lethality. Comparable to any pistol you would find in Strinova World.
Weapon.10201001_Tips: Utilizing a short-recoil barrel system and semi-automatic firing, the anti-materiel sniper rifle delivers astounding power. Comes equipped with a 2.5x scope.
Weapon.15101001_Tips: The shotgun of choice for sentinels.
Weapon.18101001_Tips: Detonates shortly after impact, causing significant area damage.
Weapon.18201001_Tips: Emits a bright flash shortly after impact, temporarily blinding and deafening anyone within a large radius.
Weapon.18601001_Tips: Releases a healing mist on impact, temporarily restoring health to allies in its area.
Weapon.18401001_Tips: Generates a powerful gust on impact, floating all units within the wind field for its duration.
Weapon.18501001_Tips: Upon impact, explodes into a large paint pool, slowing and string-blocking enemies within its range.
Weapon.18301001_Tips: Releases a smoke screen on impact, obstructing vision.
Weapon.12101001_Tips: Micro SMG renowned for its ultra-high rate of fire and ease of concealment. Favored by many special force operatives.
Weapon.10108001_Tips: Balancing power and stability, this battle rifle is a fine example of Earth's industrial craftsmanship. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.12307001_Tips: Special pistol-like weapon that spits columns of flames at close range, instantly engulfing enemies in burning particle waves.
Weapon.18701001_Tips: Attaches to a surface and senses its surroundings, emitting an alarm when enemies pass by.
Weapon.18801001_Tips: Deploys a transparent shield on impact that intercepts enemy tactical items. The shield becomes visible to enemies only when intercepting.
Weapon.12501001_Tips: Boasts strong range and firepower, with a high rate of fire.
Weapon.10303001_Tips: This stable and durable marksman rifle offers excellent control. Its specially weighted rounds enhance long-range accuracy. Comes equipped with a 2.5x scope.
Weapon.10203001_Tips: Modified tactical sniper rifle. Featuring the perfect union of precision, power, and stealth, it was once the longest-range sniper rifle of old Earth. Comes equipped with a 2.5x scope.
Weapon.10202001_Tips: This tactical intervention sniper rifle perfectly combines precision, power, and stealth. Once the longest-range model among Earth's sniper rifles. Comes equipped with a 2.5x scope.
Weapon.10501051_Tips: Protagonist Astra series produced by Polaris Labs, a classic example of stylistic design incorporating the client's very specific demands.
Weapon.10304052_Tips: Part of the Summer Party series designed by Polaris Labs. This firearm's relaxed and lively design helps boost morale in the heat of battle.
Weapon.10101054_Tips: The Lucky Feline series produced by Polaris Labs draws inspiration from the lucky cat associated with good fortune, and perhaps also the designer's hopes of a satisfied client.
Weapon.10502054_Tips: The Lucky Feline series produced by Polaris Labs draws inspiration from the lucky cat associated with good fortune, and perhaps also the designer's hopes of a satisfied client.
Weapon.10201051_Tips: The Ronin series made by Quadrant Foundries. Waves dance on a mysterious and psychedelic purple, soothing the hearts of many a wandering warrior.
Weapon.10303051_Tips: The Ronin series made by Quadrant Foundries. Waves dance on a mysterious and psychedelic purple, soothing the hearts of many a wandering warrior.
Weapon.10106051_Tips: The Astrologist series developed by the Corridor is a cautious blend of enigma and popular trends, rumored to be the tortured work of the best in-house artist.
Weapon.10301051_Tips: The Astrologist series developed by the Corridor is a cautious blend of enigma and popular trends, rumored to be the tortured work of the best in-house artist.
Weapon.10104054_Tips: The House of Cards series from the Corridor earned its intriguing reputation partly from the client's meticulous requirements around an artistic avatar encircled by decorative card elements.
Weapon.10104001_Tips: This carbine assault rifle offers impressive stability and exceptional accuracy. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.12201001_Tips: Short-barreled shotgun with a relatively small frame. Its three-shot bursts make it the ideal CQC weapon.
Weapon.10202105_Tips:
Modded Quasar model. A piece of the outdoors that Kokona's modified into a firearm. She's carved some simple yet beautiful patterns to make the whole design pop. It's less of a weapon and more of a wild work of art.

【"Hmm... Isn't it a bit too pretty? Hehe, I guess it does fit the day!"】
Weapon.10102001_Tips: This high-performance, weather-resistant assault rifle delivers powerful firepower and unbeatable value. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.10106001_Tips: Excellent heat dissipation and durability. Top accuracy for close-range shots. Ergonomic design for smooth, ambidextrous use. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.10105001_Tips: The standout bullpup rifle, known for its exceptional all-around performance. A classic from old Earth firearms. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.10101001_Tips: Relentless firepower to dominate the battlefield, with an excellent balance of accuracy and firing rate. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.10402001_Tips: Superior accuracy to ordinary rifles and strong adaptability to tracer rounds of various calibers and types. Outputs a stable and sustained rate of fire, providing reliable support on the field.
Weapon.10301001_Tips: Balancing power and range perfectly, the marksman rifle excels at suppressing mid-to-long-distance targets. Comes equipped with a 1.5x scope.
Weapon.10304001_Tips: This automatic rifle uses high-powered rounds for superior combat effectiveness, making it suitable for all-weather operations. It comes with a 1.5x scope for enhanced accuracy.
Weapon.10403001_Tips: Known for its remarkable power and performance, this general-purpose machine gun was a classic harvesting weapon from old Earth's large-scale wars. Comes equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Weapon.10201106_Tips:
A souvenir from the Golden Tree Symphony, this firearm is inspired by the flute. Will she recall memories when she picks it up?
